NK101(de)004:1: // rat+nam ni d+hi nyapra&a&a&a t+ta s+ya ka t+ai ko dz+aa
NK101(de)004:2: li ka s+y+aa da r+sham b+he swa ri shu b+hed
NK101(de)004:3: s+yo lka y+aa sku ny+ts+ai kam na ma bi ha
NK101(de)004:4: ra ti sma //// rin po che gter gtad pa'i
NK101(de)004:5: 'grel chung 'phrul gyi me long gsal bar 'byed pa'i
NK101(de)004:6: 'od kyi lde'u mig ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK101(de)004:7: na mo gu ru b+h+yah ye grol gdod ma'i mgon po chos kyi sku //
NK101(de)004:8: gangs chen mtsho lnga'i bkod pa longs spyod rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:9: ston pa bcu gnyis mngon rdzogs sprul pa'i sku //
NK101(de)004:10: lhun mnyam sku gsum rgyal ba thog mar mchod //
NK101(de)004:11: skyes bu'i thugs las sems dpa' rdo rjer sprul //
NK101(de)004:12: sems lhag mchog sprul dus mthar sa la bkod //
NK101(de)004:13: dga' rab rdo rje 'dzam gling sgron mar shar //
NK101(de)004:14: dgongs brgyud ston pa rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:15: snying po'i mdzod 'dzin 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang //
NK101(de)004:16: dpal gyi seng ge mtsho skyes pad+ma'i zhal //
NK101(de)004:17: dz+ny+aa na s+au tra pan chen bi ma la //
NK101(de)004:18: brda brgyud rig 'dzin rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:19: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bee ro tsa na dang //
NK101(de)004:20: g.yu sgra snying po nyang ban ska cog zhang //
NK101(de)004:21: dam pa yab sras kun mkhyen snga phyi sogs //
NK101(de)004:22: snyan brgyud gang zag rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:23: khyad par gsang mdzod gter gyi sgo phye nas //
NK101(de)004:24: smin grol gdams pas skal ldan rjes bzung ste //
NK101(de)004:25: skyong mdzad mkhas grub yongs kyi rgyal po che //
NK101(de)004:26: kun mkhyen d+har+m+aa s+aa rar gus phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:27: sprul pa'i skyes bu thabs mkhas thugs rje'i bdag /
NK101(de)004:28: shes bya kun mkhyen zab mo'i chos tshul gyis //
NK101(de)004:29: bdag rgyud smin mdzad bka' drin mtshungs med rje //
NK101(de)004:30: 'khor ba'i mgon po mchog la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:31: theg rim kun gyi bka' dang dgongs 'grel sogs //
NK101(de)004:32: 'jug thabs yongs dang smin lam dbang gi sgo //
NK101(de)004:33: grol byed khrid sogs gdams pa'i bcud stsol ba'i //
NK101(de)004:34: 'dren mchog bla ma rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:35: de ltar brgyud gsum nor bu'i phreng ba la //
NK101(de)004:36: gus pas btud de sde gsum klong dgu'i bcud //
NK101(de)004:37: bka' yi yang snying byang chub sems kyi gter //
NK101(de)004:38: mngon gsum gtad pa'i man ngag 'dir gsal bya //
NK101(de)004:39: de la rgyud kyi don bkrol nas lung gi mdo bzung /
NK101(de)004:40: man ngag gi snying phyung nas dgongs pa'i la bzla /
NK101(de)004:41: gnas lugs kyi don bstan nas rig pa gnad la dbab /
NK101(de)004:42: lung rigs kyi brda grol nas byang chub sems mngon
NK101(de)004:43: sum du ston pa rin po che gter gtad pa
NK101(de)004:45: rig 'dzin chen po sh+r+ai sed+hasa mdzad pa'i rin po che rgyan las /
NK101(de)004:46: man ngag 'byung khungs lo rgyus don //
NK101(de)004:47: 'jug sgo theg pa yo ga'i don //
NK101(de)004:48: rten gyi gang zag dgos pa'i don //
NK101(de)004:49: dril nas mtshan gsol rtsa ba'i don //
NK101(de)004:50: dbu zhabs dkyus bshad tshig gi don //
NK101(de)004:51: spyi don lnga yi bshad pa yin //
NK101(de)004:53: spyi don chen po lnga yi sgo nas bshad pa las /
NK101(de)004:54: dang po lo rgyus kyi don la'ang /
NK101(de)004:55: sku gsum gyi bshad lugs spyir bshad pa /
NK101(de)004:56: brgyud pa'i bab tshul bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:58: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las /
NK101(de)004:59: dang por yid ches pa yi khungs bstan phyir /
NK101(de)004:60: lo rgyus don gyi bshad lugs bstan par bya //
NK101(de)004:63: bshad rgyud nges don mdo bcu las /
NK101(de)004:64: lo rgyus don la rnam gsum ste //
NK101(de)004:65: byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad pa dang //
NK101(de)004:66: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa dang //
NK101(de)004:67: tshig sdeb legs pas bshad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:69: ston pa kun tu bzang pos dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la bshad pa ste /
NK101(de)004:71: byin gyis rlabs kyi bshad pa ni //
NK101(de)004:72: rang bzhin chos kyi gzhal yas nas //
NK101(de)004:73: ston pa kun tu bzang po yang //
NK101(de)004:74: mtshan ma'i sku gsung mi mnga' bar //
NK101(de)004:75: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK101(de)004:76: bzang ngan blang dor med pa ru //
NK101(de)004:77: kun bzang nyid du byin rlabs nas //
NK101(de)004:78: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs la brgyud //
NK101(de)004:79: byin gyis rlabs kyis bshad ces bya //
NK101(de)004:82: byin rlabs chos skus don gyi gsung //
NK101(de)004:83: brjod med don gyis byin gyis brlabs //
NK101(de)004:84: don gyi mi gnyis brgyud pa can //
NK101(de)004:85: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon pa //
NK101(de)004:86: man ngag tshad mas rang mtshan ston //
NK101(de)004:87: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag tu'o //
NK101(de)004:89: brgyud pa gsum la sbyar ba na /
NK101(de)004:90: man ngag tshad ma mtshan nyid drug dang ldan pa la brten nas byin chos nyid rang chas la /
NK101(de)004:91: rlabs rtog pa chig chad du shar ba la byin gyis rlabs kyi bshad ces bya'o //
NK101(de)004:93: ston pa rdo rje sems dpas yang sprul dga' rab rdo rje la gsungs pa ste /
NK101(de)004:95: rang gi ngo bos bshad pa ni //
NK101(de)004:96: skye med dbyings kyi pho brang na //
NK101(de)004:97: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' yang //
NK101(de)004:98: mtshan ma'i sku gsung mi mnga' bar //
NK101(de)004:99: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK101(de)004:100: skye 'jig med pa'i ngo bo dang //
NK101(de)004:101: rdo rje nga yi ngo bo ru //
NK101(de)004:102: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan la //
NK101(de)004:103: rig pa'i 'og min gnas su bshad //
NK101(de)004:104: rang gi ngo bos bshad ces bya //
NK101(de)004:107: longs skus dgongs pa brda sgo nas //
NK101(de)004:108: rang gi ngo bos rang shar mtshon //
NK101(de)004:109: ngo bos mi gnyis ma nor nges //
NK101(de)004:110: brda bral rang grol rang rig nyams //
NK101(de)004:111: rang mtshan yul med rang shar ba'o //
NK101(de)004:113: rig pa'i 'og min gnas su bshad //
NK101(de)004:116: rig pa phyi nang med pa spros mtshan gang gis
NK101(de)004:117: kyang 'og tu ma gyur par rnam par dag pa'i
NK101(de)004:118: thugs la brgyud pa'i bshad lugs yin te /
NK101(de)004:120: rnam rtog mtshan ma ji snyed pa //
NK101(de)004:121: ji bzhin mi 'gyur de nyid gsal //
NK101(de)004:122: gnas 'gyur rgyal ba'i lung chen yin //
NK101(de)004:124: de'ang ma nor nges pa'i slob dpon gyis man ngag gis /
NK101(de)004:127: go ba bzhin rtogs pas rang rig pa'i tshad ma yul med du shar ba'o //
NK101(de)004:129: ston pa dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK101(de)004:130: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs pa la tshig nyung ngus don kun rdzogs par bshad pa ste /
NK101(de)004:132: tshig sdeb legs pa'i bshad pa ni //
NK101(de)004:134: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan des //
NK101(de)004:135: chos nyid skye ba med pa de //
NK101(de)004:136: skye ba med pa'i tshig brjod pas //
NK101(de)004:137: skye ba med pa'i don rtags su //
NK101(de)004:138: rin chen gser gyi glegs bam la //
NK101(de)004:139: bee d+aur zhun ma'i rang nan gyis //
NK101(de)004:140: tshig dang yi ger bris bsdebs nas //
NK101(de)004:141: phyi rabs rnams kyi btsas su bzhag /
NK101(de)004:142: tshig sdeb legs pas bshad ces bya //
NK101(de)004:145: sprul pa'i dbang pos tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK101(de)004:146: tshig tu bsdeb legs don kun mtshon //
NK101(de)004:147: brgyud pas brda sprod yi ger bkod //
NK101(de)004:148: spyi tsam yid ches rdzogs lung yin //
NK101(de)004:150: de gnyis kyi don la yid ches kyi nges pa
NK101(de)004:151: rdzogs pa'i ched du brjod bya rang mtshan dang mthun
NK101(de)004:152: par rgyal ba sku bzhi'i bka' dri ma med pa'i
NK101(de)004:153: snying po tshig sdeb legs shing tshad ma gsum dang
NK101(de)004:154: ldan par bshad pas nges don lung gi tshad ma'o
NK101(de)004:155: // de'ang sprul pa'i bka' lha mi dang nyan thos
NK101(de)004:156: nas a nu'i bar gyi theg pa kun kyang ma
NK101(de)004:157: 'dres par rim gyis mtshon pa'i cha nas rdzogs pa
NK101(de)004:158: chen po'i 'jug sgo dang lam stegs yin pas kun
NK101(de)004:161: yongs rdzogs kyi gnas lugs ston pa bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung a ti yo ga kho na'o //
NK101(de)004:162: gnyis pa brgyud pa'i bab tshul bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK101(de)004:164: byung tshul nyi ma'i snying po las //
NK101(de)004:166: ngo bo nyid shar chos sku yis //
NK101(de)004:167: bdag po'i rkyen byas longs skur snang //
NK101(de)004:168: de las sems dpa' rdo rje 'chang //
NK101(de)004:169: yon tan ma 'gags yul la shar //
NK101(de)004:170: rang gi ngo bo'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK101(de)004:171: shar ba yang sprul thugs sras kyis //
NK101(de)004:172: tshig tu bsdeb pa sbyar legs mdzad //
NK101(de)004:173: de las rig pa 'dzin pa bzhi //
NK101(de)004:174: smin nas dam par dge slong che'i //
NK101(de)004:175: thugs kyi 'od zer bdag mun bsal //
NK101(de)004:176: rnam snang byin brlabs mtha' yi mi //
NK101(de)004:177: gsal mdzes rim gtad nan tan chongs //
NK101(de)004:178: dgongs pa rig pa snyan du'o //
NK101(de)004:179: zhes gsung pas man ngag 'di yi bka' srol la grags pa ltar 'chad de /
NK101(de)004:180: slob dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:181: sna tshogs theg pas don mdzad pa //
NK101(de)004:182: thun mong tshar gcod spyod sgyur sdud //
NK101(de)004:183: rdzogs nas snying po rnal ma nyid //
NK101(de)004:184: shes gnas ma brtsal rang grol ba'i //
NK101(de)004:185: bstan pa 'byung dus gsum gnyis tshe //
NK101(de)004:186: dam pa yang sprul yul dang phrad //
NK101(de)004:187: ces gsungs pas tshul de nyid bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:190: gang zag snyan brgyud dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:192: dgongs pas brgyud de bstan pa rin po che lha gnas su byung ba dang /
NK101(de)004:193: de nas mi yul du ji ltar byung tshul bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:195: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi gnas su /
NK101(de)004:196: rang byung gi ston pa dpal kun tu bzang pos /
NK101(de)004:197: rigs kyi sangs rgyas lnga la snying po rnal ma
NK101(de)004:198: don gyi rgyud sgrib med zang thal du bstan pas
NK101(de)004:199: 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i skur 'od du 'bar
NK101(de)004:202: sems kyi sangs rgyas kun bzang gis //
NK101(de)004:203: yang dag gdon gyi 'og min du //
NK101(de)004:204: kun rig rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK101(de)004:205: rang gsal nyag gcig byin rlabs snang //
NK101(de)004:206: mi bskyod rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK101(de)004:207: ma nor rang snang yul med shar //
NK101(de)004:208: bshad pas ma rtogs bzhag pas rig /
NK101(de)004:209: rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud de bzhugs //
NK101(de)004:210: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar te /
NK101(de)004:211: de'ang rtsol ba'i theg pa mthar phyin te snying po rnal ma 'byung ba'i dus la bab pa na /
NK101(de)004:212: thugs rjes bzung bar bya ba don las shar ba'i
NK101(de)004:213: rgyal po dam pa yang sprul gyi yul dang phrad
NK101(de)004:214: de / man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las gong gi 'phror /
NK101(de)004:215: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas chen du //
NK101(de)004:216: bzang skyong lha yi sras thu bor //
NK101(de)004:217: bzhes pa'i sems lhag rtags can la //
NK101(de)004:218: mthangs su yang sprul rang grol nas //
NK101(de)004:219: dus mthar sar gshegs sgron ma mdzad //
NK101(de)004:220: snang ste rang rigs ston pa la //
NK101(de)004:221: bsnyad pas brgya byin bka' drin gyis //
NK101(de)004:222: ye shes can la gnad nas bskul //
NK101(de)004:223: dgongs pa chos nyid nam mkha' la //
NK101(de)004:224: thugs rje ye shes nyi shar bgros //
NK101(de)004:225: rgyab tshab mi bskyod rdo rje la //
NK101(de)004:226: bka' yi bgro ba bskul sbyar bas //
NK101(de)004:227: rang bzhin mngon mdzad ye shes las //
NK101(de)004:228: thugs rje sprul pa'i rdo rje 'chang //
NK101(de)004:229: sprul pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK101(de)004:230: rtse lnga rdo rje 'khor lo bcas //
NK101(de)004:231: mkhyen pas bdud 'joms rgyud du gcod //
NK101(de)004:232: rang 'bar rtsal gyis bstan pa sgrogs //
NK101(de)004:234: lha gnas chen po sum cu rtsa gsum du /
NK101(de)004:235: phyag na rdo rje'i sprul pa lha de wa bzang
NK101(de)004:236: skyong zhes bya ba la sras lnga brgya dang rtsa
NK101(de)004:237: gcig mnga' ba'i thu bor sku'i skye ba bzhes pa'i
NK101(de)004:238: kun dga' snying po bya ba lus rdo rje'i skyil
NK101(de)004:239: krung dang ngag rdo rje'i bzlas pa la dga' ba'i
NK101(de)004:241: lha'i dbang po sprul pa'i brgya byin gyis sems lhag can du mtshan btags te /
NK101(de)004:243: lha bu gzhan rnams dga' ba'i tshal na rol mo
NK101(de)004:244: dang rtsed 'jo dang glu dbyangs dang tshigs bcad la
NK101(de)004:245: dga' zhing sems lhag can ni bsam gtan gyi khang
NK101(de)004:246: bur gcig pur sdod pa la dga' bas so //
NK101(de)004:247: lha'i bu dam pa de la /
NK101(de)004:248: nyams kyi rmi lam bzhi byung ste /
NK101(de)004:250: yang sprul mthangs su thub drug thim //
NK101(de)004:251: tshangs dang khyab 'jug gu lang zos //
NK101(de)004:252: nyi zla lag thogs 'jig rten snang //
NK101(de)004:253: mkha' sprin rin chen mdog lnga las //
NK101(de)004:254: bdud rtsi'i char bab chag btab steng //
NK101(de)004:255: mchod rten bang rim bum pa 'khyil //
NK101(de)004:256: srog shing rdo rje rtse dgu par //
NK101(de)004:257: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'i //
NK101(de)004:258: kha la bzhugs pa rnam bzhi snang //
NK101(de)004:260: thub drug thim pa ni yang sprul snang nus pa dang /
NK101(de)004:261: lha gsum zos pa ni dug gsum rang grol nas byang chub tu rdzogs pa dang /
NK101(de)004:262: nyi zla thogs pa ni 'jig rten gyi sgron ma mdzad pa dang /
NK101(de)004:263: bum pa 'khyil ba'i steng du bzhugs pa ni dus
NK101(de)004:264: matha'i skad cig mar mthar thug gi sar gshegs pa'i
NK101(de)004:265: rtags te / rang dang rigs mthun pa'i ston pa lha'i dbang po la bsnyad pas /
NK101(de)004:268: snying po rnal ma 'byung ba'i dus //
NK101(de)004:269: yang sprul snang nus dus gsum byang chub rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:270: 'jig rten mun sel dus matha'i sa non pa'i //
NK101(de)004:271: thugs sras 'dzam gling dpal gyur mtshar bgrang am //
NK101(de)004:273: gling bzhi tshogs par shes nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas ye shes kyi sku can thams cad la /
NK101(de)004:274: sems lhag can gyi don du /
NK101(de)004:275: gsung gi mnga' bdag thams cad kyis //
NK101(de)004:276: rtsol ba'i theg pa mthar bton nas //
NK101(de)004:277: rtsol med theg pa mi gsung pa //
NK101(de)004:278: thugs rje chen po yas lam ci //
NK101(de)004:279: lkal ldan gdul bya mchis pas na //
NK101(de)004:280: lhun grub theg pa gsung du gsol //
NK101(de)004:281: zhes gnad nas bskul ba dang /
NK101(de)004:282: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs pa chos nyid
NK101(de)004:283: kyi nam mkha' la thugs rje ye shes kyi nyi
NK101(de)004:284: ma shar nas bka' bgros te /
NK101(de)004:285: rgyal tshab longs sku rdo rje sems dpa' la bka' bgros pa'i gsung mthun par mgrin gcig tu /
NK101(de)004:286: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK101(de)004:287: thugs rje'i rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK101(de)004:288: sangs rgyas kun gyi mdzad par bshad //
NK101(de)004:289: gsung gi mnga' bdag thams cad kyi //
NK101(de)004:290: ye shes rang bzhin khyod yin pas //
NK101(de)004:291: thams cad byang chub sems su gsal //
NK101(de)004:292: ma lus bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
NK101(de)004:293: sku yi ngo bo de ldan pas //
NK101(de)004:294: rmad byung rol pa'i sku ru shar //
NK101(de)004:295: gsung gi mnga' bdag thams cad kyi //
NK101(de)004:296: gsung gi bdag nyid rig pa'i gsung //
NK101(de)004:297: rmad byung rol pa'i gsung du shar //
NK101(de)004:298: tshig gcig don kun rdzogs pa'i bdag /
NK101(de)004:299: rin chen 'phrul gyi snying po'i sgo //
NK101(de)004:300: skal ldan rnams la bstan du gsol //
NK101(de)004:301: rin chen 'phrul gyi thabs ldan pas //
NK101(de)004:302: gang 'dod mthun pa'i sgo de nas //
NK101(de)004:303: rtsol med dbyig dang phrad par gyis //
NK101(de)004:304: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo la //
NK101(de)004:305: brjod pa'i tha snyad kun bral yang //
NK101(de)004:306: ma rtogs blo la tshig sgo nas //
NK101(de)004:307: gsung gi sgron mas gsal bar gyis //
NK101(de)004:309: de nas dpal rdo rje sems dpas phyag na rdo
NK101(de)004:310: rje'am sems dpa' rdo rje rang bzhin ye nas gnas
NK101(de)004:311: pa'i don mngon du mdzad pa'i ye shes kyi thugs
NK101(de)004:312: la sprul te / rin po che rang 'bar gyi 'khor lo lag tu gtad de /
NK101(de)004:313: sprul sku dang longs sku gnyis kyi ye shes kyi
NK101(de)004:314: mkhyen pas bar du gcod pa'i bdud 'joms shing rgyun
NK101(de)004:315: du gcod pa'i rtags su phyag g.yas na rdo rje
NK101(de)004:316: rtse lnga dang / nyon mongs pa rang ye shes
NK101(de)004:317: su 'bar ba'i rtsal gyis bstan pa zab mo sgrogs
NK101(de)004:318: pa'i rtags su g.yon na 'khor lo bsnams pa'o //
NK101(de)004:319: de'ang man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:321: gzi byin las grub gnod sbyin 'dul //
NK101(de)004:322: skabs kyis gsang bdag bskul ba las //
NK101(de)004:323: gnod 'dul gsang ba'i mnga' bdag pos //
NK101(de)004:324: zhal bzhes phyogs bzhir rgyal ba la //
NK101(de)004:325: rwa chod bsal phyir shes sgrub don //
NK101(de)004:326: the tshom bzhi bcod pha ga la //
NK101(de)004:327: kun rig chos sku longs spyod rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:328: rig bdag rje btsan dam pa des //
NK101(de)004:329: rtsol bral sa la bskul bas bslang //
NK101(de)004:330: sems dpa' gus pas zhu bar 'dun //
NK101(de)004:331: brjod par bya ba'i don klong dgu //
NK101(de)004:332: don las 'khrul pa rtogs gnas grol //
NK101(de)004:333: rtsa ba lnga dril ma 'dres rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:334: gnod 'dul gsang sngags mnga' bdag des //
NK101(de)004:335: mthar thug sems dpa'i mtshams sbyar nas //
NK101(de)004:336: dam pa yang sprul dpa' bo brlabs //
NK101(de)004:337: sum cu rtsa gsum bum thog steng //
NK101(de)004:338: rgyal thabs rdzogs par dbang rdzogs mdzad //
NK101(de)004:339: bstan pa lha gnas gsum du rgyas //
NK101(de)004:341: de nas spyir sku'i gzi byin las grub pa'i gsang
NK101(de)004:342: ba'i bdag po gnod sbyin gos sngon can rnams 'dul
NK101(de)004:343: ba dang gnyis su med kyang bye brag tu rang
NK101(de)004:344: bzhin ma bcos pa'i byin rlabs las rang shar ba
NK101(de)004:346: gnyis med ye shes gsang ba'i don //
NK101(de)004:347: bya med mi rtsol ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:348: dbu ma ched po drang po'i lam //
NK101(de)004:349: 'dus pa'i tshogs la bstan par gyis //
NK101(de)004:350: zhes snying po rnal ma ston pa'i gnas skabs kyis bskul ba las /
NK101(de)004:351: gsang ba'i mnga' bdag sems dpa' rdo rjes //
NK101(de)004:352: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK101(de)004:353: tshig gi spyod yul ma yin pas //
NK101(de)004:354: bdag gi 'grol bar shin tu dka' //
NK101(de)004:355: ma rtogs pa la tshig sgo nas //
NK101(de)004:356: mtshon nas rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:357: ci rigs par ni rnam par 'grol //
NK101(de)004:360: shar phyogs rdo rje rnam par gnod pa'i zhing khams na /
NK101(de)004:361: de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje gsang ba zhes bya
NK101(de)004:362: ba mi phyed pa'i 'khor dang bcas te bzhugs pa
NK101(de)004:363: la / sems nyid rdo rje lta bu la //
NK101(de)004:366: sems nyid mi 'gyur rdo rje la //
NK101(de)004:367: skye dang 'gag pa yod ma yin //
NK101(de)004:368: rnam rtog blo la skye 'gag byung //
NK101(de)004:370: de bzhin du lho phyogs rin po che snang ba na /
NK101(de)004:371: de bzhin gshegs pa rin po che'i zhabs zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)004:372: rang 'bar snang ba'i khri la bzhugs te /
NK101(de)004:373: nyid kyi 'khor la gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid ston zhing bzhugs pa la /
NK101(de)004:374: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK101(de)004:375: rgyu rkyen rtsol bas ma bsgrubs par //
NK101(de)004:378: ka sha ka yi rgyan bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:379: rgyu 'bras mthar phyin gzhi nas rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:380: thams cad rang byung snying po'i mchog /
NK101(de)004:381: gsang ba'i thabs kyis rtogs gyur na //
NK101(de)004:384: yang nub phyogs pad+ma brtsegs pa na /
NK101(de)004:385: bcom ldan 'das pad+ma'i 'od ces bya ba /
NK101(de)004:386: dri ma med pa pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs te nyid
NK101(de)004:387: kyi 'khor la gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid
NK101(de)004:389: sems gnyis pad+ma ltar dag la //
NK101(de)004:390: gzung 'dzin dri ma ji ltar byung //
NK101(de)004:393: 'dam gyi skyon gyis gos pa med //
NK101(de)004:394: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni //
NK101(de)004:396: rnam rtog blo la 'khor ba byung //
NK101(de)004:398: de nas byang phyogs rnam dag grub pa na /
NK101(de)004:399: de bzhin gsheg pa grub par snang ba zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)004:400: rang bzhin snang ba'i gdan la bzhugs te nyid kyi
NK101(de)004:401: 'khor la gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid ston
NK101(de)004:403: btsal med sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK101(de)004:406: rang byung ye shes rtog gyur na //
NK101(de)004:407: mdzad pa byin gyis rlabs las 'char //
NK101(de)004:409: de ltar shes bya gzhi dang bsgrub bya 'bras bu'i don la /
NK101(de)004:412: 'gro don 'grub tshul gyis the tshom bzhi bcad de /
NK101(de)004:413: dbyings lhun mnyam yangs pa'i bdag la dgongs pa chos
NK101(de)004:414: sku las mdzad pa longs sku'i rnam par snang ba
NK101(de)004:415: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK101(de)004:416: rje btsan gdod ma'i spyi dpal dam pa des /
NK101(de)004:418: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs kyi bcud //
NK101(de)004:419: ye shes gsang ba rtogs par gyis //
NK101(de)004:420: zhes rtsol bral gyi sa la bskul bas gleng bslang ba na /
NK101(de)004:421: gdul bya'i snang ngor sems dpa' rdo rje stan las langs te gus pas zhus pa /
NK101(de)004:422: khyod ni gsung gi seng ge ste //
NK101(de)004:423: ye shes gsang ba ma rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:424: bim pa ra yi 'bru bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:426: ye shes gsang ba rtogs par gyis //
NK101(de)004:427: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag khyod kyi bstan //
NK101(de)004:428: de dag nged kyis ma rig pas //
NK101(de)004:429: ye shes gsang ba bstan du gsol //
NK101(de)004:432: sems dpa' rdo rje da nyon cig /
NK101(de)004:433: ye shes gsang ba'i rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:434: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med //
NK101(de)004:435: nam mkha' bzhin du kun la khyab //
NK101(de)004:436: ma rig ye shes tha dad med //
NK101(de)004:437: ma rtogs rtogs pa lam du gcig /
NK101(de)004:438: ye shes gsang ba'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK101(de)004:439: rang rig 'od gsal rnam par dag /
NK101(de)004:440: rnam rtog ye shes nyid du gnas //
NK101(de)004:441: gzhir zhag rang lugs rin chen mdzod //
NK101(de)004:442: rang byung ma btsal gdod nas dag /
NK101(de)004:443: ye shes gsang ba'i rnam pa ni //
NK101(de)004:444: sna tshogs snang la ngos gzung med //
NK101(de)004:445: mi dmigs sgyu ma lhun grub ni //
NK101(de)004:446: rtag par gsal na lta ba yin //
NK101(de)004:447: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs te zhus lan 'dres ma'i rjod byed kyis /
NK101(de)004:448: bstan pa rin po che klong chen po dgu la sogs pa don gyi gnas lugs dang /
NK101(de)004:449: de las ma rtogs par 'khrul ba dang /
NK101(de)004:450: yang dag par rtogs pa dang /
NK101(de)004:451: de la gnas pa'i thabs dang /
NK101(de)004:452: mthar grol ba 'bras bu dang lngar rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK101(de)004:453: du dril nas bstan pa sogs gcig dang du ma
NK101(de)004:454: las 'das pa'i tshul gyis ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs
NK101(de)004:455: par gsungs so // des na bshad par bya ba
NK101(de)004:456: rin po che gter gtad pa nyid kyang man ngag
NK101(de)004:458: de nas gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i gsang sngags kyi mnga' bdag des /
NK101(de)004:459: mthar thug ston pa'i rgyud rnams sems dpa' rdo rje'i
NK101(de)004:460: tshig gi mtshams sbyar gyis bsdus nas gdul bya dam
NK101(de)004:461: pa yang sprul dpa' bo byin gyis brlabs pa ni
NK101(de)004:462: / lha'i gnas sum cu rtsa gsum du mchod rten
NK101(de)004:463: bum pa 'khyil ba'i thog 'khor lo 'bar ba'i lte
NK101(de)004:464: ba'i steng du 'od zer gyi zhags pas drangs te
NK101(de)004:465: / bzhag pa la / rgyal thabs spyi blugs yongs
NK101(de)004:466: su rdzogs par dbang bskur nas rtsol bcas dang rtsol
NK101(de)004:467: med kyi dbang kun rdzogs par mdzad de /
NK101(de)004:468: rtogs grol chig chod du mthar thug gi sa la
NK101(de)004:469: skad cig gis bkod nas bstan pa rin po che
NK101(de)004:470: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' bdag tu gyur te rtsol
NK101(de)004:471: med kyi bstan pa lha gnas 'og min dang /
NK101(de)004:473: sum cu rtsa gsum rnams su dar zhing rgyas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:474: gnyis pa bstan pa rin po che mi yul du ji ltar byung ba ni /
NK101(de)004:475: man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:477: 'dzam gling snod ldan bcud bral bar //
NK101(de)004:478: gzigs nas gsang bdag rdo rje 'chang //
NK101(de)004:479: sa pa sprul pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK101(de)004:480: lha las grol ba de bsdus btsud //
NK101(de)004:481: 'dzam gling mtshan can g+ho ma la'i //
NK101(de)004:482: thugs las bshos nas sku la bzhag /
NK101(de)004:483: dpa' bo bzhad mdzad rdo rje bltams //
NK101(de)004:484: dam shod gling gi dur khrod du //
NK101(de)004:485: dbang bskur bstan pa bshad tshul mdzad //
NK101(de)004:486: dur khrod ma mo gshin rje la //
NK101(de)004:487: dam brtsal las la bsgo bar mdzad //
NK101(de)004:488: u rgyan rdo rje can gnas su //
NK101(de)004:489: klong dgu bam po nyi khri bsdus //
NK101(de)004:491: mi'i yul shing 'dzam bu brgyan pa'i gling na rnal
NK101(de)004:492: ma'i snod khyad par can yod kyang bcud kyi stongs
NK101(de)004:493: par gzigs nas gsang bdag chen po rdo rje 'chang
NK101(de)004:494: gis mthar thug gi sa pa sprul pa'i rang bzhin
NK101(de)004:495: lha sems lhag can las grol bas snying po'i ston
NK101(de)004:496: pa de nyid yi ge h'u du bsdus nas thugs
NK101(de)004:497: kar btsud de / 'dzam bu'i gling na o rgyan yul //
NK101(de)004:498: yon tan lag nas 'char ba'i rigs //
NK101(de)004:499: skyon bral sgyu spangs pa ra ni //
NK101(de)004:500: gter chen bdud rtsis nad sbyangs shing //
NK101(de)004:502: bya'i rgyal po ngang par sprul nas babs te shing
NK101(de)004:503: mo glang gi lor dbyar zla ra ba'i tshes brgyad
NK101(de)004:504: la rdo rje'i gling phug na lcam mtshan dang ldan
NK101(de)004:505: pa la g+ho ma la gnas pa yi thugs kar
NK101(de)004:506: mchu lan gsum gtugs te thugs las mchu yis bshos
NK101(de)004:507: nas thugs sras sku'i lhums su bzhugs pas bde ba
NK101(de)004:508: cher skyes so // de nas zla dgu ngo bcu
NK101(de)004:509: na thugs ka nas rtsol med kyi theg pa ston
NK101(de)004:510: pa'i rtags rdo rje rtse mo dgu pa zhig byung
NK101(de)004:511: cher skyes so // ste / 'od du zhu ba las /
NK101(de)004:512: khye'u mtshan dpe dang ldan pa skye lugs gsum po
NK101(de)004:513: rang lhun grub gsum du bsgral nas 'khor ba'i g.yul
NK101(de)004:514: las rgyal ba'i dpa' bo chen po /
NK101(de)004:515: phyag g.yas na rdo rje dang g.yon na dril bu
NK101(de)004:516: bsnams shing rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhal
NK101(de)004:517: 'don mdzad pa zhig byung ba na /
NK101(de)004:518: sngon ston mchog sh+aakya thub pa bltams pa'i dus kyi ltas ltar byung nas /
NK101(de)004:519: sh+aakya'i rigs thams cad bzhad par mdzad cing dgyes pa'i
NK101(de)004:520: rab tu gyur pas dga' rab rdo rje zhes bya
NK101(de)004:522: de nas lho nub ngam shod gling gi dur khrod
NK101(de)004:523: du gsang ba'i bdag po dngos su byon nas dbang
NK101(de)004:524: bskur zhing bstan pa bshad tshul tsam mdzad de dngos
NK101(de)004:525: su lha yul du gsungs pa yin /
NK101(de)004:526: dur khrod kyi ma mo dang las kyi gshin rje
NK101(de)004:527: rnams la dam tshig rtsal nas bka' dang bstan pa
NK101(de)004:528: srung ba'i las la bsgo bar mdzad cing gsang ba'i
NK101(de)004:529: gnyen gtad de / gsang ba'i bdag pos bskul ba /
NK101(de)004:530: rgyal thabs spyi blugs rdzogs dbang zung //
NK101(de)004:531: spros pa'i sems ldan don la sbyor //
NK101(de)004:532: rang bzhag rig pa ma yin par //
NK101(de)004:533: brda sgo rtog pa'i rjes ma 'brang //
NK101(de)004:535: de nas dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK101(de)004:536: dga' rab rdo rje bdag nyid kyang //
NK101(de)004:537: de wa bzang skyong bu thu bo //
NK101(de)004:538: kun dga' snying po bya ba yin //
NK101(de)004:539: lag na rdo rje dbang bskur te //
NK101(de)004:540: 'dzam gling nyid du rgyal tshab bya'o //
NK101(de)004:541: zhes nyams tshangs pa'i mgur bzhengs te //
NK101(de)004:542: o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i yul rdo rje gling phug gi gnas su /
NK101(de)004:543: brjod bya klong chen po dgu rjod byed don sde
NK101(de)004:544: tshan dang tshig shwa lo ka sum brgyar bam po
NK101(de)004:545: byas te bam po nyi khrir bsdus pa la sogs
NK101(de)004:546: rdzogs pa chen po'i bka' thams cad bsdu bar mdzad
NK101(de)004:547: de bzhugs so // de las spyi blugs sras gcig la brgyud pa dang /
NK101(de)004:550: nyi shu rtsa gcig la brgyud pa rnams su grags pa las /
NK101(de)004:552: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen kho na la bshad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:554: bram ze bde mchog snying po /
NK101(de)004:555: rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo /
NK101(de)004:556: blon po gang ba bzang po'i bu a tsar+ya a lo ke dang gsum la bshad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:559: rgyal po d+ha hen ta lo /
NK101(de)004:561: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza /
NK101(de)004:562: lha'i rgyal po ma h+aa r+aa dza /
NK101(de)004:564: sh+r+ai sing+ha dang bdun la bshad pa ste gzhan drug
NK101(de)004:565: ni sgom chen du dbang bskur la sh+r+ai sing+ha ni
NK101(de)004:566: rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ro //
NK101(de)004:570: dge slong ma kun dga' ma'am /
NK101(de)004:571: bi ma la yan chad la bshad pa ste /
NK101(de)004:572: mkhas pa gnyer gcig po kun gyis dga' rab rdo
NK101(de)004:573: rje'i zhal mthong yang bzhes tshul mi 'dra ba snang
NK101(de)004:574: ngo // de bzhi las lugs 'di ni dang po ltar te /
NK101(de)004:575: gnyis pa rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud pa ni /
NK101(de)004:576: man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:578: kho bo rje btsun 'jam dbyangs kyis //
NK101(de)004:579: byin brlabs dbang bskur lung bstan nas //
NK101(de)004:580: dam pa de la 'dun pa las //
NK101(de)004:581: ye shes rigs can mkha' 'gro mas //
NK101(de)004:582: brdas bskul byin rlabs ldan byas nas //
NK101(de)004:583: dam pa ga la ba der phyin //
NK101(de)004:584: 'dun pas brtags spyos brda bkrol te //
NK101(de)004:585: rgyal ba 'gro ba zam chad pa //
NK101(de)004:586: rna brgyud rdo rje'i zam btsugs nas //
NK101(de)004:587: bo zos na yang lan grangs 'gas //
NK101(de)004:588: rang grol bde chen rang gtad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:590: rgya gar shar phyogs na bram ze dpal ldan bde
NK101(de)004:591: skyong gi bu snying po grub pa zhes bya ba
NK101(de)004:592: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyis byin gyis brlabs shing dbang
NK101(de)004:593: bskur ba zhig 'phrul gyi man ngag snying po rnal
NK101(de)004:594: ma'i don la mos pa la /
NK101(de)004:595: lhag pa'i lhas lung bstan pa /
NK101(de)004:596: dbul po rang gter rnyed 'dod na //
NK101(de)004:597: rdo rje gling phug gnas ri la //
NK101(de)004:598: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras las //
NK101(de)004:599: lde'u mig long la rang gter thon //
NK101(de)004:601: der dga' rab rdo rje yang sprul dam pa de la 'dun pas tshol du phyin pa na /
NK101(de)004:602: lho nub ngam shod gling du /
NK101(de)004:603: ye shes kyi rigs can sh+r+ai tsa mun+d+ri sogs mkha' 'gro ma gsum gyis /
NK101(de)004:604: chu bo'i gzhung la zhon nus sam //
NK101(de)004:606: 'phrul gyi me long lta byed dam //
NK101(de)004:607: nor bu rin chen lon nges sam //
NK101(de)004:610: sgom pa rgyun chad med par chu bo'i gzhung la
NK101(de)004:611: lung rigs kyis yid ches par byas nas zhon par
NK101(de)004:612: nus sam / rtog pa don gyi gshis lugs gtan
NK101(de)004:613: tshigs kyis gzhigs te mthar phyin par 'bigs pas mtshon
NK101(de)004:615: lta ba 'phrul gyi me long dpe yis mtshon nas lta bar byed dam /
NK101(de)004:616: man ngag nor bu rin chen 'bras bur rang gsal gyi dgos 'dod 'byung bar len nges sam /
NK101(de)004:617: zhes pa'i brdas bskul ba na /
NK101(de)004:619: yid ches bar gyis la sgro 'dogs chod dang /
NK101(de)004:620: dpe las cung zhig snang nas dgos pa'i don 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)004:621: zhes brjod de byin gyis brlabs nas lung bstan pas myur du phyin no //
NK101(de)004:622: de ka na shin tu bsgres pa'i skyes bu gcig gzims nas bzhugs pa la /
NK101(de)004:623: dang ba'i mthu skyed de 'dod yon mang po phul nas mchod pas /
NK101(de)004:625: 'dod ldan ma yin gzungs mdzes la //
NK101(de)004:626: brten pas tshim pa cang yod dam //
NK101(de)004:627: sol ba'i ljon shing bye ma'i gser //
NK101(de)004:628: brgya la srid kyang cang shes sam //
NK101(de)004:631: sngags don ni ngan pa yin na khyod ci byed /
NK101(de)004:633: de nas lung bstan bsnyad pas /
NK101(de)004:634: snod brtags pa'i phyir dpe la brten pa'i brda yis spyo ba gsum mdzad de /
NK101(de)004:635: dang po gdams tshul la spyo ba /
NK101(de)004:636: 'o na brag 'di'i rtsa ba na phug gsum yod pas der song la gdams par rigs su gsungs /
NK101(de)004:638: gcig na bram ze gtsang ma bcud g.yo zhing za ba la stobs zhan par mthong /
NK101(de)004:639: gcig na rma bya dug gis mdzes par mthong /
NK101(de)004:640: steng ngos kyi bar na drang srong bcud len mkhan
NK101(de)004:641: thams cad bcud du len pa zhig mthong nas slar
NK101(de)004:642: phyin pas / de la cang go'am gsungs /
NK101(de)004:646: blang dor byas pas su zhig grol //
NK101(de)004:647: brtul zhugs can la mdog sdug tsam //
NK101(de)004:648: mkhas par blang dor ci byar yod //
NK101(de)004:651: rang gnas ma shes pa la mtshal bas dbu drangs nas /
NK101(de)004:652: rgyu mtshan nyid pa ltar don ma mthong bas zhe 'dod can /
NK101(de)004:653: sngags phyi pa ltar mnyam pa nyid la blang dor gyi ji ltar grol /
NK101(de)004:654: sngags nang pas brtul zhugs la gnas kyang mdog sdug
NK101(de)004:655: pa tsam yin na don phyogs med la mkhas par
NK101(de)004:656: blang dor gyi rtsol ba yod dam /
NK101(de)004:658: de nas bar pa snod bcud la sbyor ba /
NK101(de)004:660: 'o na brag 'di'i rked pa na chu shing gi
NK101(de)004:661: sdong po'i rtsa na ma he mo zhig zho skyel
NK101(de)004:662: du 'ong gis de la zho zhos la bum par
NK101(de)004:664: brag 'di'i rtse mo tsa na ka'i shing bu'i rtsa ba na /
NK101(de)004:665: sa la gnas pa la dbang che ba seng ge dkar mo zhig /
NK101(de)004:668: rang skad 'don zhing 'ong gis ma 'jig par rtsar chor la /
NK101(de)004:669: gser gyi za ba 'dir zho zhos la bcud long zhig /
NK101(de)004:672: de ka tshugs 'dug nas 'o ma tshan gnyis snod
NK101(de)004:673: gnyis su blugs nas bla ma'i spyan sngar mchis pa
NK101(de)004:674: na / ma he'i zho seng ge'i zho'i zla la blugs pas bcud du gyur /
NK101(de)004:675: de ni gol sa mi spong bar la zla ba'i dape'o //
NK101(de)004:676: gser skyogs kyi nang du seng ge'i zho gcig ma
NK101(de)004:677: he'i zho'i steng du blugs pas zho ngan dor te
NK101(de)004:679: de ni shan 'byed de rang sar gtan la 'bebs pa'i dape'o //
NK101(de)004:680: rdza'i bum par ma he'i zho'i steng du seng ge'i zho blugs pas rdza chag zho bo'o //
NK101(de)004:681: de ni snod ngan la chud za ba'i dape'o //
NK101(de)004:683: cang ma go lags zhus pas /
NK101(de)004:686: bcud la khyad par de yod pas //
NK101(de)004:687: snod la khyad par de tsam gnas //
NK101(de)004:688: rig pa'i mig can don la rton //
NK101(de)004:690: de nas tha ma rtogs thabs la spyo ba /
NK101(de)004:692: 'o na 'di nas shar phyogs b+ha g+ha la na mkhar chen po gcig la /
NK101(de)004:696: gnas sgo gcig ste sgo brgyad yod /
NK101(de)004:697: de'i nang na phyi ru lta zhing nang na gnas pa'i rgyal po gcig la /
NK101(de)004:701: rgyal po de la 'khor grangs med pa yod pas shin tu dbang che /
NK101(de)004:702: des nor bu rin po che ma bral bzhin du brkyang /
NK101(de)004:703: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan chen po ni ma bskyel
NK101(de)004:704: bzhin gcig nas 'gro ba thams cad dbul phongs par
NK101(de)004:705: byed do // da nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul 'di na /
NK101(de)004:706: gdeng chen po dang ldan pa'i skyes bu gsum gyis
NK101(de)004:707: dmag dpon byas te sgo brgyad dang ldan pa'i khri
NK101(de)004:709: rtse gsum mtshon cha rang 'od 'bar ba ni thogs /
NK101(de)004:710: gzhan gyi mtshon gyis mi phigs pa'i go cha sra ba ni gyon nas /
NK101(de)004:711: 'khor brgyad khri bzhi stong dang bcas te dmag 'dren gyis /
NK101(de)004:712: der song la phyi sgo lnga la drangs tsa na /
NK101(de)004:713: dbang po yul ston gyi bu mo lnga yod /
NK101(de)004:715: shin tu mdzes pa'i cha lugs dang ldan pas /
NK101(de)004:716: de la stobs su yod kyis re dogs ma byed par song zhig /
NK101(de)004:717: phyi sgo lnga na sgo srung lnga la bu bzhi
NK101(de)004:718: bzhi yod pa la bu thu bo ni o rgyan
NK101(de)004:719: sgyu ma las grub pa'i yul na /
NK101(de)004:720: gdengs chen po mnga' ba'i skyes bu rgyal po tshugs na gnas pa bya ba gcig yod /
NK101(de)004:721: bu gnyis pa ni b+ha g+ha la'i gtsang sme re dogs can gyi yul na /
NK101(de)004:722: bram ze drag pa can bya ba gcig yod /
NK101(de)004:724: nyes legs mdzes sdug gi yul sh+r+ai lan+d+ra na /
NK101(de)004:725: rig byed bzo mkhan dpyad pa bya ba gcig yod /
NK101(de)004:726: tha chung ni gcod pa tshogs 'dus kyi yul w+aa ra na s+ai na /
NK101(de)004:727: gcod mkhan tha snyad 'dogs pa'i zhal che ba bya ba gcig yod /
NK101(de)004:728: de la thabs shes na bu thu bos nu bo
NK101(de)004:729: gsum zil gyis mnan te bsgral tu btub pa 'di
NK101(de)004:730: lta ste / 'u cag pha gcig gi bu la
NK101(de)004:731: nga rgyal po tshugs na gnas pa ltar khyed kyang
NK101(de)004:732: de bzhin du gnas par gyis shig /
NK101(de)004:735: gtsang smer spyod pa dang bzo dang tshong gi bar zhog la de la ma gnas shig /
NK101(de)004:741: de na nor bu rin po che chu dwangs yod pas des dbul ba'i dri ma sel nus te /
NK101(de)004:742: dbugs de tsam phyin nas bzo las byas pa'i rgyal mtshan btsugs par gyur te /
NK101(de)004:743: de yis yul khams de rgyal po'i rigs rgyud du bsgyur bas 'bangs kyi ming yang med de /
NK101(de)004:744: rgyal po'i tha snyad kyang rang grol lo //
NK101(de)004:746: gnas thabs sprul pa bsam yas las //
NK101(de)004:747: mtshan ma bzhi ldan dang pos bsgral //
NK101(de)004:748: snang ba mi dgag zhan mi bya //
NK101(de)004:749: ngal gso lags tsam dmar thag yod //
NK101(de)004:751: de nas yar phyin nas phyi nang gi bar sgo na /
NK101(de)004:752: ma 'ongs lung ston gyi bu mo dang /
NK101(de)004:753: 'das pa gleng slong gi bu mo skad tshangs pa'i dbyangs ltar snyan la /
NK101(de)004:754: gtam rgyud tshangs pa chen po ltar mkhas pa gnyis
NK101(de)004:755: kyi yid phrogs bya ba shor bar byed pa yod
NK101(de)004:756: kyi / der zhor la she bcad /
NK101(de)004:757: sgo'i nang na sgo srung bya ba mang po bya ba yod /
NK101(de)004:758: de la bu gsum yod pas /
NK101(de)004:759: bu thu bo ni don med thang chad bya ba'i yul na byas pa don med bya ba yod /
NK101(de)004:760: tha chung ni zin med sgyid lug bya ba'i yul na byed pa zin med bya ba yod /
NK101(de)004:761: bar pa ni 'od ma'i tshal gyi dgon pa na
NK101(de)004:762: gdengs chen po ldan pa'i skyes bu 'dzangs po gzu
NK101(de)004:763: bor gnas pa bya ba zhig yod pas /
NK101(de)004:764: bu che chung bu mo gnyis kyi gtam rgyud la ma mthun te rtsod pa byung bas /
NK101(de)004:765: bu bar ba des che chung thabs kyis dbang du byas te bsgral du btub pa ni /
NK101(de)004:766: lar gtam rgyud la dgos pa ci yod /
NK101(de)004:767: bya ba mang la zin pa nyung /
NK101(de)004:768: don chung la nyes pa mang /
NK101(de)004:769: des na 'u bu gsum bde ba 'dod pa la gcig pas /
NK101(de)004:770: sdug bsngal gyi rgyu bya ba zhog la dgon par bde ba la 'dong ngo //
NK101(de)004:771: zhes 'dod pa gcig par drangs te 'dzangs pas zhi dal gyis ri rgod klungs su phab nas /
NK101(de)004:772: rtsod pa med pas gzu bo'i tha snyad kyang rang grol lo //
NK101(de)004:776: de na nor bu rin po che bkra shis yod
NK101(de)004:777: pas des bkres pa'i dbul ba sel te 'byung chen
NK101(de)004:778: gtos kyi rgyal mtshan gtsugs par gyur to //
NK101(de)004:780: smra mkhan bu mo thabs kyis sbyar //
NK101(de)004:781: bya mang zin nyung zhor she bcad //
NK101(de)004:782: 'dzangs pas gcad pa'i ngag don mnyen //
NK101(de)004:783: rtog pa gras thag der chad la //
NK101(de)004:784: snang ba rang sar des grol 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:786: de nas yar phyin pas nang du bstan pa'i sgo 'gram na /
NK101(de)004:787: rak+sha stobs po che'i bu lnga rno 'jug gi mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs nas /
NK101(de)004:788: deng rang la shed skyed cing nus pa'i stobs skyed par byed pa yod kyi /
NK101(de)004:789: sgo'i nang na sgo srung sdig can spyi la rang du dmigs ba bya ba yod /
NK101(de)004:790: de la bu stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi yod /
NK101(de)004:791: tha chung o rgyan thor cog can 'di na gdengs
NK101(de)004:792: chen po mnga' ba'i skyes bu dpa' bo g.yul 'joms
NK101(de)004:794: phu bo rnams kyi yul ni na rag gdong chen na yod pa la /
NK101(de)004:795: thabs shes na tha chung des phu bo rnams zil
NK101(de)004:796: gyis mnan te bsgral btub pa yin 'di ltar te
NK101(de)004:797: / 'u cag thams cad dpa' bo mthar thug na kun gyi stobs nga nyid la rdzogs pa la /
NK101(de)004:798: srin pos shed skyed du ci yod /
NK101(de)004:799: rno 'jug gsod pa'i mtshon cha kun //
NK101(de)004:800: rang la rang 'joms ma brlag gam //
NK101(de)004:801: yul ngan pa de zhog la /
NK101(de)004:802: rin po che'i gling bde ba can du 'dong ngo //
NK101(de)004:803: zhes byas te thams cad dpa' bor gyur pa la /
NK101(de)004:804: mi mthun pa'i dgra med pas dpa' bo'i tha snyad kyang rang grol lo //
NK101(de)004:806: sgo gtan bcag /'khor sa phyags mas btab ste /
NK101(de)004:807: de na nor bu rin po che dbang gi rgyal po yod pas /
NK101(de)004:808: de las bdud rtsi'i char phab ste dbul ba dang /
NK101(de)004:810: bkra mi shis pa thams cad bsal te /
NK101(de)004:811: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan btsugs par gyur to //
NK101(de)004:813: dpa' bo mtshon cha lcags kyu lnga //
NK101(de)004:814: bdag gi longs spyod rang la bzlog /
NK101(de)004:815: gzung 'dzin mi spang rang la bzla //
NK101(de)004:818: de nas ya bgrod pa med pa'i tshul du phyin pas /
NK101(de)004:820: lta ba phyi ru lta la /
NK101(de)004:821: gnas pa nang na gnas pa'i rgyal po bya ba bzhugs pas /
NK101(de)004:822: de'i spyi bo'i gtsug na yid bzhin gyi nor bu
NK101(de)004:823: rin po che bsam 'phel bya ba yod kyis de
NK101(de)004:825: der phyin nas btsal bas ci yang ma rnyed pa la /
NK101(de)004:826: da yar rnyed par mi 'dug pas slar ldog gam bsam pa las /
NK101(de)004:827: nam mkha' nas sh+r+ai tsa mu n+d+ris /
NK101(de)004:830: rang la yod nas gzhan du tshol //
NK101(de)004:831: btsal bas skyes bu su yis rnyed //
NK101(de)004:832: brda la don tshol de ya mtshan //
NK101(de)004:833: zhes brjod de ga zha chen po btab pas /
NK101(de)004:838: dpe la brten nas don cung zad tsam du snang ba las /
NK101(de)004:839: brda ji bzhin du ma 'phrod nas /
NK101(de)004:843: rgyal sar gton nas rang dbang bskur //
NK101(de)004:844: dbul bor rang gter lag tu gtad //
NK101(de)004:845: nges par bstan gyi gus par longs //
NK101(de)004:846: zhes gsungs nas rgyal thabs spyi blugs tshangs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:848: rin po che'i gter gtad de //
NK101(de)004:849: sku gsum dgongs pa thugs kyi bcud //
NK101(de)004:851: de nas snying po grub pas /
NK101(de)004:852: bdag ni bskal pa thog med nas //
NK101(de)004:853: rang gter yid bzhin rin chen bral //
NK101(de)004:854: dam pa mchog gis rang gter stsal //
NK101(de)004:855: dbul sel bde ldan sku drin che //
NK101(de)004:857: gser gyi brag phug yu ba can du mkha' 'gro
NK101(de)004:858: ma'i lo lnga brgya rtsa bcur dgongs pa la bzhugs
NK101(de)004:859: te / yi dam gyi lhas lung bstan pa'i mtshan 'jam dpal bshes gnyen no //
NK101(de)004:860: de la lha yul sum cu rtsa gsum du de
NK101(de)004:861: wa r+aa dza zhes bya ba sar chud pa'i rig
NK101(de)004:862: 'dzin gyi go 'phang la gnas pa zhig yod pa
NK101(de)004:863: la / bsod nams kyi g.yengs pas yid dbyung nas
NK101(de)004:864: mi yul gyi snying po rnal ma a ti yo
NK101(de)004:866: sh+aakya'i rigs d+harma sh+ri'i sras su skye ba bzhes te /
NK101(de)004:867: o rgyan yul du 'jam dpal bshes gnyen che ba
NK101(de)004:868: 'dzin cing spyod pas 'dul phyir khye'u chung zur phud
NK101(de)004:869: can du bzhugs pa dang 'phrad pas lha mig gis
NK101(de)004:870: mkhyen te / 'dun zhing dang bas 'dod yon du mas mchod de /
NK101(de)004:871: lha gnas sum cu rtsa gsum du //
NK101(de)004:872: bdud rtsi sman las sar chud pas //
NK101(de)004:873: snying po'i don la rtsal ma 'byongs //
NK101(de)004:874: byams pa'i nyi shar zhags pas zungs //
NK101(de)004:876: bskal par spyod daka'i dri ma can //
NK101(de)004:877: rnal ma ma bcos dag pa'i chus //
NK101(de)004:878: rtsol nad mig nas dag par bkru //
NK101(de)004:879: gdod sems rang so'i gnyug mar zhog /
NK101(de)004:881: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:883: rin po che'i gter gtad de /
NK101(de)004:884: bskul ba rkyen gyi man ngag /
NK101(de)004:885: sgom pa'i sa mi rnyed phyir sgom pas rnyed par mi 'gyur te /
NK101(de)004:886: sems kyi spyod yul shes pa de dag chos rnams kyi ni chos nyid yin /
NK101(de)004:887: rnam bral gang la'ang mchog dang tha ma med pa'i lam mchog 'di sgom mo //
NK101(de)004:888: 'du byed ma skyes chos kun 'byung med shin tu chos rnams mya ngan 'das //
NK101(de)004:890: de nas d+he wa r+aa dzas /
NK101(de)004:891: rtsol bas yid 'byung rtsol med btsal //
NK101(de)004:892: gzhan nas rtsol med ma rnyed de //
NK101(de)004:893: rtsol bcas sems nyid rtsol bral bde //
NK101(de)004:894: e ma ho rang grol sku drin che /
NK101(de)004:896: za ma tog gi bsil khang du lo brgya rtsa bdun du ngang las ma g.yos par gnas te /
NK101(de)004:897: lhas a mri ta d+harma r+aa dza zhes btags so //
NK101(de)004:898: de la 'og min rgya mtsho'i gling khams nas yang
NK101(de)004:899: dag tshe dbang thob pa klu'i rgyal po dga' bo
NK101(de)004:900: de / rang gi las las grub pa'i gdug pa'i nus mthu la yid dbyung nas /
NK101(de)004:901: mi yul na snying po rnal ma gnas pa la thugs dgyes nas /
NK101(de)004:902: gdol ba'i rigs a ba d+ha murnya bya ba'i sras
NK101(de)004:903: su lus blangs pas snga ma'i las kyis sbrul mgo
NK101(de)004:905: pha ma skrag nas dur khrod du bskyal ba la /
NK101(de)004:906: su tras skad cher phung ste /
NK101(de)004:907: byol song gdug pa klu las ni //
NK101(de)004:908: snying po'i rten du lus 'phangs na //
NK101(de)004:909: las kyi 'brel bas pha dang ma //
NK101(de)004:910: skal ba ma gcad phung po skyed //
NK101(de)004:912: bden no snyam nas blangs te gsos pas mdze shu sos pa sogs legs pa cher byung bas /
NK101(de)004:913: ming n+aa ga sam kri ta btags so //
NK101(de)004:914: de nas za ma tog gi bsil khang gi rtsa
NK101(de)004:915: bar r+aa dza ha sti la smin pa'i lam zhi
NK101(de)004:916: khro phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang thob nas snod du
NK101(de)004:917: rung ba las bdud rtsi chos rgyal dang mjal bas
NK101(de)004:918: yid bzhin nor bu zhig phul te /
NK101(de)004:919: gdug pa'i sems kyis byol song lus sems smin //
NK101(de)004:920: bsod nams las kyi yon tan dpag med kyang //
NK101(de)004:921: snying po'i don med snying po'i rten la 'phangs //
NK101(de)004:922: snying po'i don rtsol thugs rje'i zhags pas zungs //
NK101(de)004:924: gser zor seng ge'i 'o ma ltar //
NK101(de)004:925: rigs la rgyud gtad snying por smin //
NK101(de)004:926: gdug sems spangs pa'i snying po'i don //
NK101(de)004:927: spyan lngas ma gzigs de nyid rtogs //
NK101(de)004:929: bsil khang du rgyal thabs kyi dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:931: rin po che'i gter gtad de /
NK101(de)004:933: rang grol brda sprod skabs phye la //
NK101(de)004:934: phyogs bral rgyas gdab brda don bral //
NK101(de)004:935: spros bcad khyad par 'phags pa ni //
NK101(de)004:936: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK101(de)004:938: de nas n+aa ga sang skri tas //
NK101(de)004:939: che mchog rang sems rin po che //
NK101(de)004:941: gdod nas ma bral shugs kyi spangs //
NK101(de)004:942: gter chen rang gtad sku drin che //
NK101(de)004:943: zhes rtogs pa phul te gang+ga rgya mtsho'i gling du
NK101(de)004:944: 'khar sa ba ne'i lo stong du bcud la gnas
NK101(de)004:945: pas / lhas n+aa ga r+aa dza g+hu na garba
NK101(de)004:946: zhes lung bstan cing dbang bskur ba'i ya mtshan no
NK101(de)004:947: pas / // de la ri rab kyi byang phyogs
NK101(de)004:948: na gnod sbyin gyi bu mo de ma zhes bya
NK101(de)004:949: pas / // ba / ri rab kyi lcog bzhi
NK101(de)004:950: la gnas pa'i lag na rdo rje bzhi'i sring mor
NK101(de)004:951: pas / // ba / gyur pa / kri ya'i
NK101(de)004:952: sgo nas tshe dbang rig 'dzin thob pa zhig yod
NK101(de)004:953: pas / // ba / gyur pa / pa las
NK101(de)004:954: / rang gi las kyis grub pa'i nus pa dang
NK101(de)004:955: pas / // ba / gyur pa / pa las
NK101(de)004:956: / / rdzas kyi gnyer la g.yengs pas yid dbyung
NK101(de)004:957: nas mi yul na snying po rnal ma gnas pa
NK101(de)004:959: rgya gar shar phyogs rgyal po srid srungs kyi sras mor lus blangs pas /
NK101(de)004:960: de la sras mi mnga' bas rdzun byas te sras gzigs so //
NK101(de)004:961: 'di shin tu dkon pa las mthong bas ma'i rtsar
NK101(de)004:962: yang mi gnang gsungs te sbas nas gsol ba las
NK101(de)004:963: / b+ha g+ha la'i lo nyer bzhi bod lo bcu gnyis lon nas rgyal sar 'don pa la /
NK101(de)004:965: snying po'i don la gnas smin nas //
NK101(de)004:966: bcu gnyis lo ru srid tsam bzung //
NK101(de)004:967: gnod sbyin grags ldan bu zhog la //
NK101(de)004:968: rang gi smon pa da mthar dbyung //
NK101(de)004:969: zhes grags pas sngon gyi smon pa dran nas ming
NK101(de)004:970: po bzhi la nus pa bskul bas grags ldan gyi
NK101(de)004:971: bu gnod sbyin mo byang chub ji 'dra ba zhig
NK101(de)004:972: bskyal bas / de rgyal po la gtad de srid
NK101(de)004:973: bzung bas mi'i cha byad mi 'dra nas spyugs pa
NK101(de)004:974: las bod kyi mi mang po 'phel bar yang grags
NK101(de)004:975: bskyal bas / la / de nas byang chub kyis /
NK101(de)004:976: bsam gtan gyi gling orgyana thor cog can du snying po'i don brtsal bas /
NK101(de)004:977: ri ma la ya'i rtsar smad 'tshong ma sangs rgyas ma la smin pa'i lam blangs /
NK101(de)004:978: b+ha g+ha la'i gling nas gter long zhes phyag na rdo rjes lung bstan pas /
NK101(de)004:979: der phyin nas klu'i rgyal po dang mjal /
NK101(de)004:980: seng ge'i lta stangs kyis zhal du bltas te /
NK101(de)004:981: nyon mongs dbang chen gnod sbyin mo lus thob /
NK101(de)004:982: mos pa'i rtsol ba drag pas lha zhal 'khums /
NK101(de)004:983: smon pa'i mthun 'phangs bla ma'i spyan sngar mchis /
NK101(de)004:984: snying po'i don stsol thugs rje'i lcags kyus zung /
NK101(de)004:985: zhes zhus te lus mdzes pa rat+na'i rgyan gyis spras pa yon du phul bas /
NK101(de)004:986: dad pas 'phangs pa'i lus sems can //
NK101(de)004:987: 'dod pa'i gter dang dregs sems btang //
NK101(de)004:989: gter nor dregs sems de ltos dang //
NK101(de)004:992: rgyal po mngon grub kyi dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:993: bsgyur ba gsum gyi man ngag gis bde ba thig le'i klong brdol /
NK101(de)004:994: rin po che'i gter gtad de /
NK101(de)004:996: lung bcud rdzogs pa'i thig le can //
NK101(de)004:997: rang lus rtogs pa'i ye shes te //
NK101(de)004:998: de bzhin ye shes gdags gzhi can //
NK101(de)004:999: rgyu rkyen bral bas dngos grub med //
NK101(de)004:1004: rgyu dang rtsol bas bcos thang chad //
NK101(de)004:1005: 'dod gter dregs sems nyid ma nor //
NK101(de)004:1006: brda brten rgyu grol sku drin che //
NK101(de)004:1007: zhes gtang rag phul te don grub rat+na'i khang bur o rgyan gyi lo lngas bcud rdzogs so //
NK101(de)004:1008: de dag ni 'chad pa pos tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis gsungs te /
NK101(de)004:1009: nyan pa po'i shes rab kyi dbang po brgyud pa sprul pa'i rig 'dzin sha stag go //
NK101(de)004:1010: de la dge slong ku ku r+aa dza zhes bya
NK101(de)004:1011: ba rgyal po in+d+ra b+ho d+hi'i mchod gnas ma h+aa
NK101(de)004:1012: yo ga'i tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad la mnga' brnyes pa
NK101(de)004:1014: lhag pa'i lhas lung bstan pa /
NK101(de)004:1015: gnod sbyin phyug po rdzas la srid //
NK101(de)004:1016: sgeg mo 'dod pas ngoms pa nyung //
NK101(de)004:1017: sa gsum sems dpa' sred pa'i chos //
NK101(de)004:1018: phyogs 'dzin thongs la snying po longs //
NK101(de)004:1019: zhes thos nas rang gi shes rab kyi bsam pas bltas te /
NK101(de)004:1020: rdo rje'i phug tu ru dga' rab rdo rje la snying po'i don bzhugs par rig gnas /
NK101(de)004:1022: phug sgor 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang 'jal ba na /
NK101(de)004:1024: gzhu bkang ba yi mda' rtse ni //
NK101(de)004:1025: don grub rin chen khang bu na //
NK101(de)004:1026: gnod sbyin rigs can byang chub mo //
NK101(de)004:1027: 'bigs pa mthar phyin der longs shig /
NK101(de)004:1030: kye ho rig pa grub pa mo //
NK101(de)004:1031: gnyis med ye shes las grol ba'i //
NK101(de)004:1032: khyad 'phags don de grub srid dam //
NK101(de)004:1033: mos pas 'dun gyis thugs rjes zungs //
NK101(de)004:1035: kun mkhyen phyogs ris kun grol la //
NK101(de)004:1036: dngos po stong pa gnyis med gnyis //
NK101(de)004:1037: rtogs thabs yin kyang rgya chad min //
NK101(de)004:1038: gnyis med 'dzin pa'i rig pas ltos //
NK101(de)004:1040: rgyal po mngon grub kyi dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:1041: bde chen rig pa'i thig le'i klong brdol /
NK101(de)004:1042: rin po che'i gter gtad de /
NK101(de)004:1044: gnyis med gnyis su med min zhing //
NK101(de)004:1045: dgongs pa mang btags phyogs ma zhan //
NK101(de)004:1046: rig don so las ma 'das na //
NK101(de)004:1047: gnyis med gnyis bcas rang btang zhog /
NK101(de)004:1049: de nas ku ku r+aa dzas /
NK101(de)004:1052: dpal ldan bcos ldan mas bdag brlabs //
NK101(de)004:1053: rigs dang mthun pa'i las spyad pas //
NK101(de)004:1054: chen po las 'phags don grol drin //
NK101(de)004:1056: don grub rin chen khang bur b+ha g+ha la'i lo
NK101(de)004:1057: brgya rtsa lngas bcud la dbang thob par gyur to
NK101(de)004:1058: // de la yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang bar
NK101(de)004:1059: bar dge slong sh+r+ai sing+ha pra b+h+au ta zhes bya
NK101(de)004:1060: ba rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal gzigs shing pan+di ta
NK101(de)004:1061: lnga brgya la rig pa'i gnas sbyor ba /
NK101(de)004:1062: dge slong ma kun dga' ma las rdzogs pa chen
NK101(de)004:1063: po'i brda shas thob pa zhig bzhugs pa la ku
NK101(de)004:1064: ku r+aa dzas snying po bzhag pa'i rten brtsal bas
NK101(de)004:1065: / tshe stod la o rgyan gyi rgyal po de
NK101(de)004:1066: wa r+aa dza dang mjam dpal nas bzhag par 'dod
NK101(de)004:1067: kyang rgyal rigs kyis dregs nas gtad rgya ma rdzogs
NK101(de)004:1068: / / tshe smad la sh+r+ai sing+ha dang 'phrad pas snod ldan du rig nas /
NK101(de)004:1071: rang bzhag don la gnas 'dod na //
NK101(de)004:1072: rin chen gling nas nor bu longs //
NK101(de)004:1073: dbul ba sel nus 'ga' yod dam //
NK101(de)004:1075: de la spro ba cher skyes te sgo gsum 'dud pa dang bcas pas /
NK101(de)004:1076: ma bskul don la rab brtson pa'i //
NK101(de)004:1077: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag dge slong che //
NK101(de)004:1079: thugs rjes bde chen spro bar mdzad //
NK101(de)004:1081: 'du khang bar ma ru sgo brgyad dang ldan pa'i gsal byed kyi dal la brten nas /
NK101(de)004:1082: rgyal po tshangs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:1083: bstan pa'i klong brdol rin po che'i gter gtad de /
NK101(de)004:1085: rang gsal ngang la phyogs med ltos //
NK101(de)004:1086: ma nor bcos med rang sor zhog /
NK101(de)004:1087: sgo gsum ma bcing bag yangs spyod //
NK101(de)004:1088: rgyan dang bcas pa'i lus la rton //
NK101(de)004:1089: zhes gsungs te gtad rgya mdzad do //
NK101(de)004:1091: 'dod bcas lta ba nyid phyogs bral //
NK101(de)004:1092: gtad 'dzin sgom pa ma gtad gsal //
NK101(de)004:1093: blang dor spyod pa bag yangs bkrol //
NK101(de)004:1094: bdag nyid rgyan bcas sku drin che //
NK101(de)004:1096: de nyid yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang du chos
NK101(de)004:1097: grwa'i mkhan po dang man ngag gi bdag po mdzad
NK101(de)004:1098: cing dgongs pa'i don bskyangs so //
NK101(de)004:1099: de dag ni rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud pa ste /
NK101(de)004:1100: phyag mtshan 'ga' zhig na rgyan gyi rig 'dzin bzhi
NK101(de)004:1101: zhes pa'i tshig la brten nas ku ku r+aa dza
NK101(de)004:1102: nas snyan brgyud du bzhag kyang 'dir brgyud srol thams
NK101(de)004:1103: cad la sgrags pa ltar ro //
NK101(de)004:1104: gsum pa gang zag snyan du brgyud pa'i tshul ni /
NK101(de)004:1105: de la bod kyi dge slong gan jag thang ta
NK101(de)004:1106: zhes bya ba rus pa gor dpal rnam par snang
NK101(de)004:1107: mdzad kyi zhal mthong ba des /
NK101(de)004:1108: dka' slas chen pos rgya gar du phyin te /
NK101(de)004:1109: rig 'dzin chen po sh+r+ai sing+ha sogs mkhas pa nyer gcig gam nyer gsum gyi zhal mjal /
NK101(de)004:1110: thun mong gi rig pa nas sngags phyi nang gsang ba mtha' dag rdzogs pa na /
NK101(de)004:1112: ma skyes rnam dag rdzogs pa che //
NK101(de)004:1113: spros bral thig le nyag gcig la //
NK101(de)004:1114: bzang ngan mtho dman mi bdog kyang //
NK101(de)004:1115: la zlo'i chos gcig bskur te zhu //
NK101(de)004:1117: chos rnams zad par skyel ba yi //
NK101(de)004:1118: rdzogs chen theg pa'i yang rtse 'di //
NK101(de)004:1119: kun dang kun gyi thun mong min //
NK101(de)004:1120: blo rab 'ga' la bstan par bya //
NK101(de)004:1122: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos kyi gsang mdzod sgo phyes /
NK101(de)004:1123: spyi blugs tshangs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:1124: srung bral rig pa'i dam tshig phog /
NK101(de)004:1127: man ngag gi gnad bsdebs nas gnang ste /
NK101(de)004:1128: chos kyi dbyings la zad med kyang //
NK101(de)004:1129: de bzhin nyid ni gcig shes na //
NK101(de)004:1130: ma lus de la yongs su rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:1131: de las yod na si ti kan //
NK101(de)004:1134: shan dbye la bzlas rgyu khrol la //
NK101(de)004:1135: brgyud pa'i gdams pas mngon sum ston //
NK101(de)004:1136: dben par rang sems goms par gyis //
NK101(de)004:1137: smin par gyis shig kye thugs sras //
NK101(de)004:1139: de nas bee ro tsa na nas /
NK101(de)004:1140: sprul pa gshegs shul rdo rje gdan //
NK101(de)004:1141: snying po'i don rdzogs skal bzang rje //
NK101(de)004:1142: nges pa yin pas des mngon bstan //
NK101(de)004:1143: bdag rgyud rang grol sku drin che /
NK101(de)004:1145: ma skyes rdo rje bde ba'i sku //
NK101(de)004:1146: bzhi bcu rtsa bdun zab mo'i gsung //
NK101(de)004:1147: gnyis med ye shes nam mkha'i thugs //
NK101(de)004:1148: sh+r+ai sing+ha'i sku gsung thugs la bstod //
NK101(de)004:1149: ces gtang rag gi bstod pa mdzad do //
NK101(de)004:1150: de nas bod yul du byon nas /
NK101(de)004:1151: mdo sngags kyi chos mang po bsgyur /
NK101(de)004:1152: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan la rdzogs pa chen
NK101(de)004:1153: po'i gdams ngag zab mo phog nas bod kyi rgyal
NK101(de)004:1157: gdams ngag mthar ma phyin par sku tshe'i smad la rgyal mo tsha ba rong du byon no //
NK101(de)004:1158: rong nag po'i yul du slob ma'i mchog gsum la rim pa gsum du brgyud pa las /
NK101(de)004:1159: rgyal rong brag lha mgon po'i dgon par g.yu sgra
NK101(de)004:1160: snying po zhes bya ba lo bcu gsum pa la
NK101(de)004:1161: sgra bsgyur rdzogs par bslab pa nas /
NK101(de)004:1162: theg pa'i ru shan phyed pa na /
NK101(de)004:1164: snying po rnal ma don gyi rgyud /
NK101(de)004:1165: rang la shar bas rtsol ba spangs //
NK101(de)004:1166: nges par rtogs na nyag gcig ste //
NK101(de)004:1167: shes pa thag chod lung bzhin gnyer //
NK101(de)004:1168: zhes gsungs pas g.yu sgra mkhas pas cung zad rtogs te /
NK101(de)004:1169: sang skri ta yi sgra goms te //
NK101(de)004:1170: rig pa'i steng du yid ma ches //
NK101(de)004:1171: tha snyad tshig la ma brten pa'i //
NK101(de)004:1174: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po drug la sogs pa
NK101(de)004:1175: rdzogs pa chen po snying po rnal ma'i mdzod kyi
NK101(de)004:1176: sgo phyes / spyi blugs tshangs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK101(de)004:1179: don thugs la dril nas brdar bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1180: rtogs tshad mthar phyin pa na bskur ba /
NK101(de)004:1181: byang sems rang byung kun dngos can //
NK101(de)004:1182: rgyal po mngon sum grub pa yi //
NK101(de)004:1184: shugs la skal ldan smin par gyis //
NK101(de)004:1185: zhes gsungs te gtad rgya mdzad do //
NK101(de)004:1186: de nas g.yu sgra snying pos /
NK101(de)004:1187: sgra bshad don mtshon de dpyad kyis //
NK101(de)004:1188: brda bral rang grol yongs ma dpyad //
NK101(de)004:1189: bskal bar 'thims pa'i mun nag tshogs //
NK101(de)004:1190: yud la gsal mdzad sku drin che //
NK101(de)004:1192: rgyal mo tsha ba rtag rong gi dben par lo lnga yis phur pa thebs pas /
NK101(de)004:1193: rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur nas bee ro'i bka' bzhin
NK101(de)004:1194: bod yul dbus su yar gshegs pas pan chen bi
NK101(de)004:1196: zhal mjal te rdzu 'phrul 'gran pa dang man ngag
NK101(de)004:1197: gi bka' bsdur bas 'dab chags ma bu bsdebs pa
NK101(de)004:1198: bzhin byung nas bod rnams yid ches te bee ro
NK101(de)004:1199: tsa na la yang dag bcu gcig gis bstod do
NK101(de)004:1200: // de nas g.yu sgras gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la snga 'gyur lnga la sogs pa gsungs /
NK101(de)004:1201: bla ma gsal rab chen po la sems phyogs khams lugs su grags pa'i brgyud srol thams cad gnang /
NK101(de)004:1202: bee ro'i zhal slob semamsa phyogs kyi brgyud pa tha
NK101(de)004:1203: ma'i bdag po lho brag pa sangs rgyas mgon po
NK101(de)004:1204: la gdams ngag gi 'phros gtad rgya gsum pa'i lugs
NK101(de)004:1205: tshangs par bstan / dbus pa rgya blo gros gzhon
NK101(de)004:1206: nu la rgyud sde nyer lnga phra mo dang bcas
NK101(de)004:1207: tshangs par bstan / pa gtad de / de gnyis bee ros lung bstan pa'ang yin te /
NK101(de)004:1208: las can pam dang rgya gnyis byung //
NK101(de)004:1209: bka' bzhin legs par smin par byas //
NK101(de)004:1211: rong du gshegs khar dbas sgom rdo rje rgyal mtshan
NK101(de)004:1212: la rgyal thabs kyi dbang dang man ngag gi gzer
NK101(de)004:1213: bu thams cad rdzogs par gnang ngo //
NK101(de)004:1214: de ltar sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen po nas brgyud pa'i bka' srol thams cad /
NK101(de)004:1215: spyir mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi bstan pa dang po gnyags la bab /
NK101(de)004:1217: tha ma zur la bab pa dang /
NK101(de)004:1218: khyad par khams lugs ni byang ston rnam dag nas brgyud cing /
NK101(de)004:1219: sems phyogs brgyud pa tha ma ni pam sangs rgyas
NK101(de)004:1220: mgon po nas gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pa
NK101(de)004:1222: gzhan yang spam mi pham mgon po la gtad pa'i
NK101(de)004:1223: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa sogs kun 'dus yongs
NK101(de)004:1224: rdzogs kyi tshul du kun mkhyen bla ma kahthoga pa
NK101(de)004:1225: chen po shar pa shes rab seng ge zhes bya
NK101(de)004:1226: ba rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs mi gzugs su shar
NK101(de)004:1227: ba de la bka' babs par gyur to //
NK101(de)004:1228: yang skor thung shes rab ye shes kyis su legs pa'i sgron ma'i sras gzhon nu snying po dang /
NK101(de)004:1229: so ye shes dbang phyug gi sras gsum dang khyad
NK101(de)004:1230: par du sras che ba skal po la zhus pa
NK101(de)004:1231: las skor lugs pa zhes su gyes kyang tshig gi
NK101(de)004:1232: brgyud pa las sgom pa'i don rgyud med par yang
NK101(de)004:1233: grags mod / don du snga 'gyur lnga la shin tu mkhas pa zhig byon pas /
NK101(de)004:1234: brgyud tshul de'ang zur gyi brgyud pa 'di la 'dus par mngon no //
NK101(de)004:1235: de dag las man ngag gi rgyal po gter pa
NK101(de)004:1236: gtad 'dir 'adi'ang gdan la sa chen po'i mkhas grub
NK101(de)004:1237: 'od gsal gyi sku can gong ma rnams nas dpal
NK101(de)004:1238: yul rig 'dzin chen po'i bar dam pa rnams kyi
NK101(de)004:1239: spyod yul du bzhugs pa kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron
NK101(de)004:1240: me dang sangs rgyas lag 'chang gi zab khrid sogs
NK101(de)004:1241: kyis gsal yang / da lta'i phyag dpe 'di ni
NK101(de)004:1242: bdag cag gi bla ma dam pa bka' drin mtshungs
NK101(de)004:1243: med skyabs rje thams cad mkhyen pa mtshan brjod par
NK101(de)004:1244: dka' yang don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te
NK101(de)004:1245: kyis gsal yang / / thub bstan chos kyi rgya
NK101(de)004:1246: mtsho o rgyan bstan 'dzin rgyal mtshan byams pa 'od
NK101(de)004:1247: zer dpal bzang po gang gis lho brag nyi lde'i
NK101(de)004:1248: dge 'phel gyi gtsug lag khang nas dpe gter gyi
NK101(de)004:1249: tshul du spyan drangs pa ste /
NK101(de)004:1250: rig 'dzin bdud 'dul rdo rje'i gter lung las /
NK101(de)004:1251: shar kah thog gi bstan pa bag la zha /
NK101(de)004:1252: de gsal byed d+h+aarma'i ming can 'byung /
NK101(de)004:1254: rdo grub 'jigs med phrin las 'od zer gyi gsang ba'i lung bstan las /
NK101(de)004:1255: kahthoga pa yi bstan pa la spyan ras gzigs kyi
NK101(de)004:1256: sprul pa ni chos kyi rgya mtsho zhes bya 'byung
NK101(de)004:1257: de dus sh+aa kya'i bstan pa ni phyogs rnams kun
NK101(de)004:1258: tu snang bar byed ces dang pad+ma 'od gsal mdo
NK101(de)004:1259: sngags gling pa'i thugs sgrub yid bzhin nor bu'i lung
NK101(de)004:1260: byang snying gi me long las /
NK101(de)004:1261: gnyags lo'i skye ba'i sgyu 'phrul gyis zab mo bstan pa'i rgyud rnams bshad ces dang /
NK101(de)004:1262: de nyid kyi lo rgyus shel gyi phreng ba las /
NK101(de)004:1263: gnyags chen dz+ny+aa na rtogs pa rang rgyud grol mdo
NK101(de)004:1264: sngags zung 'brel 'chad rtsom sgron me sbar zhes dang
NK101(de)004:1265: / gsang sngags gling pa'i gter lung las //
NK101(de)004:1266: skal ldan bzhi pa kahthoga byang shar mtshams rgyal mtshan
NK101(de)004:1267: ming can dbang gi rtags 'char ba ma bslabs chos
NK101(de)004:1268: rnams khong nas rdol ba 'byung zhes dang /
NK101(de)004:1269: khrag 'thung bdud 'joms rdo rje'i gter lung las /
NK101(de)004:1270: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la bstan pa'i snying
NK101(de)004:1271: po dam pa ni gsal byed d+harma'i ming can zhig
NK101(de)004:1272: the tshom med par snang bar 'gyur zhes dang /
NK101(de)004:1273: grwa mda' karma'i lung bstan las /
NK101(de)004:1274: kahzhesa bya ba'i dgon par ru d+harma'i ming can skyes
NK101(de)004:1275: bu 'byung bshad sgrub bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan sgreng sngon
NK101(de)004:1276: med dpal ri'i blos bslangs byed 'brel tshad rnga yab
NK101(de)004:1277: gling du 'dren zhes pa la sogs rdo rje'i lung
NK101(de)004:1278: gis basngagasa pa'i tshad ma'i grub don gyi 'bras bu
NK101(de)004:1279: mngon par snang ba'i bdud rtsi'i cha shas so //
NK101(de)004:1280: de ltar bshad pa 'di ni ji skad du /
NK101(de)004:1281: bee ro tsa na 'dra ba'i lo ts+aa ba //
NK101(de)004:1282: sngar yang ma byon phyis kyang 'byor re skan //
NK101(de)004:1283: lo ts+aar btags kyang don la pan+di ta //
NK101(de)004:1284: 'di yis chos drin yod do phyi rabs rnams //
NK101(de)004:1286: brgyud tshul 'di'i man ngag gi rgyal po'i bka' babs
NK101(de)004:1287: tshul gangs ri'i ljongs 'dir ji ltar byung ba'i lo
NK101(de)004:1288: rgyus bye brag tu smos pa ste /
NK101(de)004:1290: rdzogs pa chen po'i zab rgyud /
NK101(de)004:1298: yang ti sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor rnams las dngos su
NK101(de)004:1299: bstan pa la sogs pa sde gsum klong dgu kun
NK101(de)004:1300: gyi don 'grel bcud kyi yang snying ni bka' dri
NK101(de)004:1301: ma med pa man ngag gi rgyal po gsang ba
NK101(de)004:1302: zab mo 'di nyid yin pas de dag kun gyi
NK101(de)004:1303: brgyud tshul rnams shes par bya zhing kun gyi dgongs
NK101(de)004:1304: pa'i zab gnad dril ba la mkhas pa gal che
NK101(de)004:1305: ba dang / khyad par du sgra thal 'gyur chen po las /
NK101(de)004:1306: bka' gsang nges pa bcu bdun dang //
NK101(de)004:1307: bstan pa'i gzer dang 'phrul yig bcas //
NK101(de)004:1308: sprul sku'i zhing khams thog ma la //
NK101(de)004:1309: ston pa kun tu bzang po yis //
NK101(de)004:1310: stug po bkod pa'i gnas su gsung //
NK101(de)004:1311: de nas lcang lo can gyi gnas //
NK101(de)004:1312: kun gzigs rnam par snang mdzad kyis //
NK101(de)004:1313: 'di nyid bzung bas rigs lngar smin //
NK101(de)004:1314: dee 'das nga yis bzung ba yis //
NK101(de)004:1315: bstan pa'i srog shing dam pa yi //
NK101(de)004:1316: sangs rgyas stong dang rtsa gnyis ni //
NK101(de)004:1318: bardzusa dang sgo nga las skyes dang //
NK101(de)004:1319: drod dang mngal nas skyes pa yi //
NK101(de)004:1320: sems can rnams ni smin par byed //
NK101(de)004:1321: gdul gzhi'i bstan pa 'di nyid las //
NK101(de)004:1323: 'di yi mdzad pa sum cu drug /
NK101(de)004:1324: sku gsung thugs la brten nas ni //
NK101(de)004:1325: gdul yul sems can rnams la snang //
NK101(de)004:1327: nub phyogs u rgyan dag gi yul //
NK101(de)004:1328: d+ha na ko sha'i lha lcam la //
NK101(de)004:1329: pha med bu ni badz+ra he //
NK101(de)004:1331: de yis rjes bzung nub kyi phyogs //
NK101(de)004:1332: bram ze'i phru gu ldan ldan pa //
NK101(de)004:1334: lo ni bdun cu rtsa lnga 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:1335: de yi rjes su skal ldan pa //
NK101(de)004:1336: so shi'i gling zhes bya ba yi //
NK101(de)004:1337: khyim bdag rigs la sh+r+ai sing+ha //
NK101(de)004:1339: de rjes 'dzin pa gdol pa'i rigs //
NK101(de)004:1341: de rjes 'dzin pa khyim bdag rigs //
NK101(de)004:1342: phyag rgya rgya chen dag gis 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:1343: de yi rjes la rgyal po'i rigs //
NK101(de)004:1344: sprul pa phyag brnyan bcas pas 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:1345: de yi rjes la dge sbyong gzugs //
NK101(de)004:1346: lhun gyis rgyal mtshan dag gis po //
NK101(de)004:1348: de rjes sa la gnas pa yi //
NK101(de)004:1349: byang chub sems dpa' dag gis 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:1350: de 'og lag na rdo rje yi //
NK101(de)004:1352: de 'og rgyal po seng ge ste //
NK101(de)004:1357: de 'og dge slong dpal dang ldan //
NK101(de)004:1358: de nas bloo gros mchog gis 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:1359: zhes rgyal ba sku gsum la dgongs pas brgyud de /
NK101(de)004:1360: rig 'dzin chen po bzhi la brda yis brgyud nas
NK101(de)004:1361: gang zag la snyan du brgyud pa bod yul nas
NK101(de)004:1362: chos rgyal chen po sogs su lung bstan pa ltar
NK101(de)004:1363: rang rang gi skabs kyi lo rgyus la mkhas shing
NK101(de)004:1364: rgyal ba'i bka'i khyad chos la nges pa rnyed na
NK101(de)004:1365: yi ge'i grangs sogs sgro 'dogs thams cad chod cing
NK101(de)004:1366: de dag gi zab gnad mtha' dag man ngag 'dir
NK101(de)004:1367: 'dus la / man ngag 'di'i dgongs pa'i don 'khrul
NK101(de)004:1368: med du nges na de dag gi zab cing rgya
NK101(de)004:1369: che ba'i don gnad kun gyi dgongs pa'i mthil du
NK101(de)004:1370: sleb pa ni tshad mas grub pa yin pas blo
NK101(de)004:1371: dang ldan pa rnams kyis spyi rgya gcod pa la'ang
NK101(de)004:1372: 'dus la / mkhas par bya'o // gnyis pa yo ga'i don ni /
NK101(de)004:1374: theg pa'i khyad par so sor dbye ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:1375: yo ga don gyi rtsa ba bstan par bya //
NK101(de)004:1377: ye shes gsang ba dang kun byed sogs las yo ga rnam pa bzhi bshad de /
NK101(de)004:1379: lha dang gtsang ba len zhing rtog pa dang sme
NK101(de)004:1380: ba dor ba'i spyod pa can te blang dor can
NK101(de)004:1382: ma h+aa yo ga ni bsnyen sgrub bzhis rtsol zhing sgrub pa dang /
NK101(de)004:1383: a nu yo ga ni rgyu snang ba dbyings dang 'bras bu dran rtog ye shes su 'dod cing /
NK101(de)004:1384: a ti yo ga ni de dag las grol ba'o //
NK101(de)004:1385: de ltar yo ga bzhi la sogs pa theg pa
NK101(de)004:1386: thams cad kyi khyad par a ti yo gas 'byed
NK101(de)004:1387: cing kun gyi dgongs pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK101(de)004:1390: yo ga rnam pa bzhi bshad pa //
NK101(de)004:1391: theg pa kun gyi bsdu sa yin //
NK101(de)004:1392: yo ga blang dor spyod pa can //
NK101(de)004:1393: ma h+aa yo ga rtsol zhing sgrub //
NK101(de)004:1395: a ti yo ga de las grol //
NK101(de)004:1398: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga'i don 'dis ni /
NK101(de)004:1399: theg pa'i shan 'byed rdzogs pa'i lung zhes bshad //
NK101(de)004:1401: des na a ti yo ga ni che ba lnga
NK101(de)004:1402: dang ldan pas theg pa'i rim pa kun las khyad
NK101(de)004:1405: mngon par sangs rgyas che bas ni //
NK101(de)004:1406: gsum grol rang gzhung a ti dngos //
NK101(de)004:1407: thams cad de yin blang dor bral //
NK101(de)004:1408: yo ga a tir la bzlas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:1409: rtsol sgrub mi gnas bdag nyid che //
NK101(de)004:1410: ma h+aa a tir la bzlas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:1412: a nu a tir la bzlas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:1413: thams cad bla dang rgyas btab pa //
NK101(de)004:1414: sangs rgyas med pa'i che ba ste //
NK101(de)004:1415: a ti yo ga'i a ti'o //
NK101(de)004:1417: gsum pa dgos ched kyi don ni /
NK101(de)004:1419: dgos ched dbang po yang rab ste //
NK101(de)004:1420: ri rab rdul du brtsi ba dang //
NK101(de)004:1421: bskal chen skad cig mar brtsi zhing //
NK101(de)004:1422: blo la shwa lo ka 'don zhing //
NK101(de)004:1423: tha snyad bye brag shes pa dag /
NK101(de)004:1424: yang rab ma yin don la rtsing //
NK101(de)004:1425: don gyi gnas lugs mthar phyin go //
NK101(de)004:1426: phyogs su blo gros ma lhungs par //
NK101(de)004:1427: spyi sar bzhag nas thun mong blos //
NK101(de)004:1428: shes bya gcod cing rtogs nus pa'i //
NK101(de)004:1429: don du dbang pos gsungs pa yin //
NK101(de)004:1431: gdul bya las 'phro dang skal bar ldan zhing blo
NK101(de)004:1432: gros phul du byung ba rnams la rdzogs pa chen
NK101(de)004:1433: po'i don bstan pas rtsol sgrub kyi bya ba mi
NK101(de)004:1434: dgos par sems kyi rang bzhin ji ltar ba bzhin
NK101(de)004:1435: du mthong zhing rtogs nas grol bar 'gyur ba'i ched
NK101(de)004:1438: rtsol sgrub bya mi dgos par bstan pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:1439: dgos ched don gyi dgos pa de ru bstan //
NK101(de)004:1441: byang chub sems rtogs chos nyid mngon 'tshang rgya //
NK101(de)004:1442: des na skal ldan dgos ched bstan pa yin //
NK101(de)004:1444: bzhi pa rtsa ba'i don ni /
NK101(de)004:1446: dril nas ming du gang btags pa //
NK101(de)004:1447: gcig rtogs pas ni kun rig pas //
NK101(de)004:1448: dgos pas cir btags der 'dus la //
NK101(de)004:1449: rtsa ba'i don ces gsungs pa yin //
NK101(de)004:1451: chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi rang snang du bstan pa'i phyir na /
NK101(de)004:1452: byang chub kyi sems ma gtogs chos bzhan med la /
NK101(de)004:1453: de nyid thig le nyag gcig rang rig sems kyi
NK101(de)004:1454: chos nyid du ye nas rin po che gser sa
NK101(de)004:1455: le sbram gyi gter ltar gnas pa nyid /
NK101(de)004:1456: tshad ma gsum gyis mngon sum du rang la gtad pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:1457: don thams cad kyi rtsa bar ston pa ste /
NK101(de)004:1459: byang chub sems ni chos kun rtsa ba ste //
NK101(de)004:1460: rtsa ba yin pas thams cad don yang 'dus //
NK101(de)004:1462: 'dis ni rtog ldan chos kyi rjes 'brangs dag 'jug pa'i phyir dgos sogs chos bzhi'ang bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1464: gnas lugs byang chub kyi sems lhun grub gsum mam
NK101(de)004:1465: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi bdag nyid
NK101(de)004:1466: ye na gnas kyang rtog pas bsgribs te mi gsal
NK101(de)004:1467: bar dper na phyi nang gi rgya mtsho chen po'i
NK101(de)004:1468: gser gyi 'og gzhi ltar rang bzhin gyi snang ba
NK101(de)004:1469: brjod pa'i yul dang bral ba de nyid yin te
NK101(de)004:1473: byang sems lhun grub gsum rang bzhin //
NK101(de)004:1474: gnas la mi gsal rtog pas bsgribs //
NK101(de)004:1475: mtsho chen gser gyi 'og gzhi ltar //
NK101(de)004:1476: rang snang yul bral de brjod yul //
NK101(de)004:1478: de nyid ji bzhin du ston pa'i rjod byed ni /
NK101(de)004:1479: thun mong gi ston pa rnam 'dren sh+aakya thub pas
NK101(de)004:1480: rtsol bcas kyi theg pa mthar phyin par gsungs te
NK101(de)004:1481: mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu byung tshul gyi
NK101(de)004:1482: lo rgyus ltar bstan pa rin po che rdzogs pa
NK101(de)004:1483: chen po 'phrul gyi me long gi bka' lung dang
NK101(de)004:1484: man ngag gi rim pa ma lus pa yang dag
NK101(de)004:1486: 'dir ni man ngag gi rgyal po rin po che gter gtad pa nyid do //
NK101(de)004:1487: des na nges par yid ches rnyed pa ma zad
NK101(de)004:1488: don du 'gyur ba'i the tshom gyis kyang 'jug par
NK101(de)004:1489: rigs te / theg pa kun kyang gzhung lugs dang
NK101(de)004:1490: tha dad pa min pas bslab byar ma gyur pa
NK101(de)004:1492: gdul bya'i blo rim gyi 'jug sgor drang nges gnyis
NK101(de)004:1493: su shar yang dngos don mtshon pa'i bka'i tshig la
NK101(de)004:1494: yangs dog med par gsungs pa dang sbyor bar bya
NK101(de)004:1496: thun mong ston pas rtsol ba'i chos //
NK101(de)004:1498: don du dbang pos gsol btab ste //
NK101(de)004:1499: ngang gsol rig pa'i skyes chen de //
NK101(de)004:1500: kun gyi ngo bor rang gnas pas //
NK101(de)004:1501: 'od ltar snang gnyis longs sku la //
NK101(de)004:1502: don gyi shugs kyis bskul grags snang //
NK101(de)004:1503: de las rang snang rdo rje 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:1504: dgos pas lnga la the tshom bcad //
NK101(de)004:1505: yang sprul thugs sras ngo bor mdzad //
NK101(de)004:1506: bka' lung man ngag rim snang mdzad //
NK101(de)004:1507: rtsol bral gnas phyir nges pa yin //
NK101(de)004:1508: de yang the tshom yul gyur na //
NK101(de)004:1510: don du 'gyur tsam re zhig rigs //
NK101(de)004:1511: kun kyang gzhung lugs tha dad min //
NK101(de)004:1512: bslab byar ma gyur med gsungs sbyor //
NK101(de)004:1515: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gnyis byang zhing bsod nams
NK101(de)004:1516: dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas thabs phun
NK101(de)004:1517: sum tshogs pas 'khor ba'i pha rol tu 'gro bar
NK101(de)004:1519: rjod byed tshig gi lam rkyen gyis brjod bya'i don
NK101(de)004:1520: mtshon pa la brten nas rtogs pa don gyi lam
NK101(de)004:1521: mchog rang rgyud la gsal bar shar ba na /
NK101(de)004:1522: lam des gdul bya gzhan 'dren pa nyid yin te /
NK101(de)004:1524: de la gnyis gnyis byang rdzogs nas //
NK101(de)004:1526: tshig lam rkyen gyis don mtshon nas //
NK101(de)004:1527: don lam rgyud la gsal shar bas //
NK101(de)004:1531: gzhi'i nyes pa ma rig pa dang brtags snang gi sdug bsngal /
NK101(de)004:1532: lam gyi nyes pa phyogs 'dzin dang gnyen pos rtsol
NK101(de)004:1533: ba'i nad las nges par grol nas mthar thug gi
NK101(de)004:1534: 'bras bu bde ba chen po rang las shar te
NK101(de)004:1535: gzugs sku gnyis kyis gdul bya kun sgrol ba'i mdzad
NK101(de)004:1536: pa byin gyis rlabs las snang ba ste /
NK101(de)004:1538: sdug bsngal rtsol ba'i nad la nas //
NK101(de)004:1539: bde chen rang shar kun sgrol ba //
NK101(de)004:1540: byin gyis brlabs snang yang dgos so //
NK101(de)004:1543: lhun gnas bde chen rtogs goms las //
NK101(de)004:1544: ma rig brtags pa rang grol nas //
NK101(de)004:1545: rtsol ba'i nad bral mthar son dang //
NK101(de)004:1546: rang rang 'dod gnas cher rgyas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:1549: chos nyid kyi gnas lugs dang rtogs goms byed pa lam pa dang thob bya 'bras bu dag ni /
NK101(de)004:1550: dper na gser gong las byas pa'i rdzas mi 'dra
NK101(de)004:1551: ba rnams ngo bo gser du gcig pa bzhin du
NK101(de)004:1552: ngo bos bdag nyid gcig pas 'brel la /
NK101(de)004:1553: gnas lugs dang de nyid ston par byed pa tshig gi lam dang don gyi lam ni /
NK101(de)004:1556: lam ni don dang tshig las te //
NK101(de)004:1557: don ni thug phrad gsum yin la //
NK101(de)004:1558: de yi brda sprod tshig gi lam //
NK101(de)004:1559: zhes pa ltar don gyi lam mtshon byed kyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK101(de)004:1560: tshig gi lam ni de nyid brda thabs kyis mtshon par 'brel la /
NK101(de)004:1561: 'bras bu dang don lam dang lam pa dag ni
NK101(de)004:1562: thob par bya ba dang 'thob par byed pa dang
NK101(de)004:1564: lam gyi ngo bo dang 'bras bu ni /
NK101(de)004:1565: 'bras bu thabs las byung ba dang lam ni de'i
NK101(de)004:1566: cha rkyen gyi thabs su 'brel te thabs dang thabs
NK101(de)004:1567: byung yin la / 'khrul pa'i snang ba ni de min pa la der 'dzin pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:1568: de nyid rang grol bar byed pa'i lam gyis grol
NK101(de)004:1569: te mthar phyin gyi 'bras bu byung bas na dang
NK101(de)004:1570: po dang gnas skabs kyi 'brel ba byas pa tsam
NK101(de)004:1571: las mthar thug bdag nyid gcig par ngo bos 'brel
NK101(de)004:1572: lo // de ltar bstan pa 'og ma dang mthun
NK101(de)004:1573: par bshad pas dbang rnon rtog pa dang ldan pa
NK101(de)004:1574: lam 'dir 'jug pa dag don la drang bar bya
NK101(de)004:1575: ba'i phyir brjod par zad de /
NK101(de)004:1577: gnas lugs lam pa 'bras bu dag /
NK101(de)004:1578: gser gong rdzas bzhin ngo bos 'brel //
NK101(de)004:1579: gnas lugs ston tshig don gyi lam //
NK101(de)004:1580: mtshan gzhi mtshan nyid mtshon par 'brel //
NK101(de)004:1581: 'bras bu don lam lam pa dag /
NK101(de)004:1583: lam gyi ngo bo 'bras bu ni //
NK101(de)004:1584: thabs las byung ba cha rkyen thabs //
NK101(de)004:1586: rang grol lam gyi grol mthar phyin //
NK101(de)004:1587: byung byas mthar thug ngo bos 'brel //
NK101(de)004:1588: mthun pas rtog 'jug drang bar zad //
NK101(de)004:1590: lnga pa tshig gi don la /
NK101(de)004:1591: tshig don gyi ngo bo ngos bzung zhing bshad thabs lnga'i skyon yon bcas te mdor bstan /
NK101(de)004:1592: man ngag rgyal po'i dbu zhabs dkyus bshad kyi tshig
NK101(de)004:1593: don gzhung gi gsang ba zab mo rgyas par bkrol
NK101(de)004:1594: ba gnyis las / dang po ni /
NK101(de)004:1595: kun byed rgyal po'i le'u nyer gcig pa las /
NK101(de)004:1596: sems kyi rang bzhin tshig tu brjod med de //
NK101(de)004:1597: ma brjod sems kyi rang bzhin mi snang bas //
NK101(de)004:1598: mi snang mtshon du med ces ma brjod na //
NK101(de)004:1599: kun kyang rang sems ma mthong rtsol sgrub byed //
NK101(de)004:1600: des na brjod med tshig gi don yang bshad //
NK101(de)004:1602: theg pa'i rim pa brgyad kyis tha snyad la brten
