NK101(de)004:1603: pa'i tshig gi rjod byed las khyad par du 'phags
NK101(de)004:1604: pa'i man ngag gi rgyal po'i thabs kyi gsang ba
NK101(de)004:1605: gnas lugs rjen par ston pa'i brda thabs zab mo
NK101(de)004:1606: rin chen 'phrul gyi me long mtshon byed tshig gi
NK101(de)004:1607: sgron ma la brten nas rang gnas kyi chos nyid
NK101(de)004:1608: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par rang grol rig pa'i
NK101(de)004:1609: mngon sum du gsal bar ston pa ste /
NK101(de)004:1610: rgya mtsho klong gsal gyi rgyud las /
NK101(de)004:1611: dper na mun nag rdzas stor la //
NK101(de)004:1612: lag nom btsal ba rnyed par dka' //
NK101(de)004:1613: snang gsal sgron me la brten nas //
NK101(de)004:1614: btsal bas rnyed pa the tshom med //
NK101(de)004:1615: de bzhin ma rig mun gnag tu //
NK101(de)004:1616: chos nyid nor bu stor ba de //
NK101(de)004:1617: tha snyad tshig gis rnyed par dka' //
NK101(de)004:1618: ma nor bla ma'i bka' drin gyis //
NK101(de)004:1619: rin chen brda yis rnyed par 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:1621: rim pa gsum bsdus pa'i man ngag las /
NK101(de)004:1622: dngos su brda yis don bstan pa //
NK101(de)004:1623: bsam yas brgyud pa brda drug rgya //
NK101(de)004:1624: rgyu 'bras mthar min rang byung ye shes brda //
NK101(de)004:1625: bcos bslad mthar min rdzogs pa chen po'i brda //
NK101(de)004:1626: ji bzhin nyid gnas byang chub sems kyi brda //
NK101(de)004:1627: gzhan nas mi tshol lhun gyis grub pa'i brda //
NK101(de)004:1628: sdug bsngal mthar min bde ba chen po'i brda //
NK101(de)004:1629: ldog pa mi gnas phyogs su ma lhungs par //
NK101(de)004:1630: ji bzhin ma yin brda yis don dang sprod //
NK101(de)004:1631: brda dag mnyes byas bla mas ston 'gyur gyis //
NK101(de)004:1632: brda bral gol sgrib rig pas nyams tshod zung //
NK101(de)004:1634: de yang bshad thabs lngas bshad pa'i skyon ni //
NK101(de)004:1635: bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde'i mig las //
NK101(de)004:1636: lo rgyus don gyis ma bshad na //
NK101(de)004:1637: yid ches byung khungs mi nges pas //
NK101(de)004:1638: yid mi ches pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:1639: rtsa ba'i don gyis ma bshad na //
NK101(de)004:1640: chos kun sems su mi 'dus pas //
NK101(de)004:1641: pra yas pa yi skyon du 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:1642: yo ga don gyis ma bshad na //
NK101(de)004:1643: theg pa'i shan thang mi phyed pas //
NK101(de)004:1644: ral mi phyed pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:1645: dgos ched don gyis ma bshad na //
NK101(de)004:1646: rtsol dang sgrub pa ma byas par //
NK101(de)004:1647: sangs rgyas sa la don med 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:1648: tshig gi don gyis ma bshad na //
NK101(de)004:1649: tshig dang don du mi ldeb pas //
NK101(de)004:1652: des na bshad thabs lnga yis legs par bshad pa'i yon tan ni /
NK101(de)004:1654: de bzlog bshad pa'i yon tan yin //
NK101(de)004:1656: man ngag zab mo ji ltar byung tshul lo rgyus
NK101(de)004:1657: kyi don gyis bshad pas bstan pa rin po che
NK101(de)004:1658: tshad mar brgyud de byung ba'i khungs la brten nas
NK101(de)004:1659: phyir rabs kyi skal ldan rnams yid ches skye ba'i
NK101(de)004:1661: rtsa ba don gyis bshad pas chos thams cad sems
NK101(de)004:1662: nyid du 'dus par nges nas don gyi bsdus shes
NK101(de)004:1663: pas / tshig gi bzhag sa rnyed pa'i yon tan yod la /
NK101(de)004:1664: yo ga don gyis bshad pas theg pa'i rim pa
NK101(de)004:1665: kun gyi shag ral phyed nas gong ma la ltos
NK101(de)004:1667: 'og ma la ltos te sgrib pa sel shes pa'i yon tan ldan zhing /
NK101(de)004:1668: dgos ched don gyi bshad pas /
NK101(de)004:1669: gshis kyi gnas lugs rtsol sgrub bya btsal las 'das
NK101(de)004:1670: par rtogs nas lam gyis rtsol ba'i zug rngu las
NK101(de)004:1671: grol ba'i yon tan yod do //
NK101(de)004:1672: tshig gi don gyis bshad pas tshig dang don du bsdebs te 'bru choms shing /
NK101(de)004:1673: de ltar choms pas don gyi bcud 'byin te tshig
NK101(de)004:1674: gi sgron ma la brten nas rang gnas don gyi
NK101(de)004:1675: gser mchog 'dzad med 'dod rgu'i gter chen rang las
NK101(de)004:1676: rnyed pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa nyid de /
NK101(de)004:1677: kun byed rgyal po las kyang /
NK101(de)004:1678: des na gtan tshigs don gyi bshad lugs lngas //
NK101(de)004:1679: kun byed rgyal po byang chub sems kyi don //
NK101(de)004:1680: ma nor nges par gtan la 'bebs par byed //
NK101(de)004:1682: nyi zla kha sbyor sogs las kyang 'byung ngo //
NK101(de)004:1683: gnyis pa man ngag gi rgyal po'i dbu zhabs dkyus
NK101(de)004:1684: bshad kyi tshig don gzhung gi gsang ba zab mo
NK101(de)004:1686: 'jug pa'i yan lag klad kyi don /
NK101(de)004:1687: 'jug yul bshad bya gzhung gi don /
NK101(de)004:1688: zhugs pa rdzogs pa mjug gi don dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:1689: dang po la man ngag gi rgyal po'i mtshan bstan pa /
NK101(de)004:1690: thun mong min pa'i ston pa la phyag 'tshal ba gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:1695: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1697: rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul gyi legs par sbyar ba'i skad du /
NK101(de)004:1700: de nyid boda yul gyi skad du chos dang mthun par bsgyur na /
NK101(de)004:1701: rin po che gter gtad pa mdor bsdus pa /
NK101(de)004:1703: de'ang mtshan gyi 'bru bod skad ltar bshad na /
NK101(de)004:1704: gnas lugs rtogs pa'i ngang la lhun rdzogs kyi yon
NK101(de)004:1705: tan rnams nor bu rin po che dbang gi rgyal
NK101(de)004:1706: po las dgos 'dod 'byung ba ltar rtsol sgrub mi
NK101(de)004:1707: dgos par 'char ba'i sems nyid kyi gter chen po
NK101(de)004:1708: mngon sum du gtad pa'i man ngag gi snying po
NK101(de)004:1709: dam pa mdor bsdus pa nyid nyung gsal du 'grel
NK101(de)004:1712: dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK101(de)004:1715: rang bzhin lhun grub gzhi yi klong //
NK101(de)004:1716: ngo bo rang byung ye shes klong //
NK101(de)004:1717: don la skye med gnyis med klong //
NK101(de)004:1718: thog mtha' med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK101(de)004:1719: bdag nyid 'bras bu ye grub klong //
NK101(de)004:1720: sna tshogs gcig 'dus gcig las shar //
NK101(de)004:1721: zhes pa'i dgongs pa ltar thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK101(de)004:1722: dpal gsum gyi gsang don bla na med pa'i theg
NK101(de)004:1723: pa'i khyad par dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK101(de)004:1724: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i phyogs med kyis phyogs 'dzin gyi mtshan ma bcom /
NK101(de)004:1725: ngo bo nges pa med par cir yang shar bas
NK101(de)004:1726: rig pa rang byung du gsal ba'i rgyan dang ldan
NK101(de)004:1727: / don skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin gyis gang
NK101(de)004:1728: la'ang gnyis su med pas gnyis 'dzin gyi mtha' las
NK101(de)004:1729: 'das te bdag nyid chen po thog mtha' med par
NK101(de)004:1730: rang grol bas rig pa rang snang snga phyi med
NK101(de)004:1731: pa'i rtogs pa don gyi dpal mngon du byas pas
NK101(de)004:1732: khyad chos drug dang ldan pa'i nang gsal gzhon nu
NK101(de)004:1733: bum skur mngon par byang chub ste rang gzhan gyi
NK101(de)004:1734: don kun rdzogs pas ston pa chos thams cad kyi
NK101(de)004:1735: gnas lugs bzang ngan blang dor med pa dang rnam
NK101(de)004:1736: dbye spros pa'i mtha' las 'das pa kun tu bzang
NK101(de)004:1738: gzugs su snang ba thams cad bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK101(de)004:1739: kun tu bzang po'i sku phyogs med rgyan gyi 'khor
NK101(de)004:1740: lo // sgra ru grag pa thams cad bcom ldan
NK101(de)004:1741: 'das dpal kun tu bzang po'i gsung phyogs med rgyan
NK101(de)004:1742: lo // gyi 'khor lo / dran dang rtog pa
NK101(de)004:1743: thams cad bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po'i thugs
NK101(de)004:1744: phyogs med rgyan gyi 'khor lor ye klong dbyer med
NK101(de)004:1745: chen po mnyam pa nyid du shar ba'i rtsol bral
NK101(de)004:1746: bde ba chen po la yon tan thams cad lhun
NK101(de)004:1747: gyis grub pa'i gdod ma'i mgon po de la dgongs
NK101(de)004:1748: pa mngon du gyur cing go ba klungs su gyur
NK101(de)004:1749: pas lta ba mjal ba'i tshul gyis phyag 'tshal lo
NK101(de)004:1750: lo // gyi 'khor lo / // zhes dbyer med du rtogs pas brda mjal /
NK101(de)004:1751: rig pa'i me tog dor ba ste /
NK101(de)004:1752: sngon byung du sprul pa'i sku mchog dga' rab rdo rjes 'tshal ba'o //
NK101(de)004:1753: der ma zad rjes 'jug tu 'di la 'chad nyan
NK101(de)004:1754: byed pa rnams kyis kyang lus ngag yid gsum gus
NK101(de)004:1755: pa'i tshul du 'tshal pa'ang yin no //
NK101(de)004:1756: gnyis pa 'jug yul bshad bya gzhung gi don dngos la /
NK101(de)004:1757: man ngag gi ngo bo mdor bstan pa /
NK101(de)004:1758: de yi rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK101(de)004:1759: 'byung ba'i dus bstan te gtad rgya mdzad pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:1761: rang snang mod kyang sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1762: kun tu bzang po klong drug pa las /
NK101(de)004:1763: 'jig rten kun gyi spyod yul ni //
NK101(de)004:1764: nga nyid snang ba'i rang bzhin la //
NK101(de)004:1765: sus kyang mthong ba med pa yi //
NK101(de)004:1766: snang ba rang rig pa'i zhing //
NK101(de)004:1769: thams cad rang snang nyid gnas la //
NK101(de)004:1770: sgrib pa med kyang snang rkyen bral //
NK101(de)004:1771: mi shes blo yis nan brtags pas //
NK101(de)004:1773: 'du byed rlung gis g.yos pas na /
NK101(de)004:1774: snod bcud sdug bsngal ngo bor grub //
NK101(de)004:1775: ces sogs gsungs pa ltar gnas lugs rang snang yul
NK101(de)004:1776: med du gnas pa yin mod kyang de nyid dang
NK101(de)004:1777: mi mthun pa mtshon par byed pa'i brda dang mtshon
NK101(de)004:1778: bya rtogs pa'i don dang bral te lhan cig skyes
NK101(de)004:1779: pa'i ma rig pas rang ngo ma shes shing /
NK101(de)004:1780: de la brten nas kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig
NK101(de)004:1781: pas bdag tu rtog pa'i mthu las gzhan du'ang snang
NK101(de)004:1782: ste rang gzhan gnyis su grub pa dang /
NK101(de)004:1783: de'i cha las zhen pa nyon mongs pa dug lnga byung zhing /
NK101(de)004:1784: de lngas kun slong byas pas 'adu byed sems pa'i
NK101(de)004:1785: ngo bo yang srid 'phen zhing g.yo bas rlung gi
NK101(de)004:1786: bdag nyid las gsum spyad pas des 'khor ba'i dngos
NK101(de)004:1787: po 'gro ba rigs drug tu smin pa'o //
NK101(de)004:1788: de las grol ba'i thabs mthar thug pa rtogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:1789: rgyu yi rkyen lhun gyis gnas pa'i bde ba chen
NK101(de)004:1790: po de nyid / spyir lung rigs man ngag gsum mam /
NK101(de)004:1791: khyad par thug phrad gsum gyis ngo shes nas /
NK101(de)004:1792: de'i don la 'dris shing goms nas ngan song dang
NK101(de)004:1793: theg dman du ldog pa med par sdug bsngal dang
NK101(de)004:1794: rtsol pa'i nad las grol zhing /
NK101(de)004:1795: sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan mngon shes dang
NK101(de)004:1796: 'bras chos lnga mtshan dpe ye shes 'gro don rnams
NK101(de)004:1797: shugs las ma btsal bar 'char ba des na rang
NK101(de)004:1798: gi semas nyid ni yon tan mi zad pa'i gter
NK101(de)004:1800: gang gtad na de lta bu'i gter de gang na
NK101(de)004:1801: gnas na rang nyid la gnas para gang ltar gtad
NK101(de)004:1802: na chos nyid rtogs pa la mi bslu bas tshad
NK101(de)004:1803: ma lung rigs man ngag gsum dang ldan par 'jam
NK101(de)004:1804: dpal bshes gnyen nyid la gtad kyis gus pas longas
NK101(de)004:1806: gnyis pa de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:1807: chos nyid gzhi'i gnas lugs gter dang 'dra bar rang la ye nas gnas tshul /
NK101(de)004:1808: de nyid ma rtogs pas 'khrul te sdug bsngal dang rtsol ba'i nad kyis 'khyams tshul /
NK101(de)004:1809: de ltar gnas pa'i don de nyid lta bas mngon
NK101(de)004:1810: sum du rtogs te gter chen rang la gtad tshul
NK101(de)004:1811: / de la 'dris goms byed pa'i thabs kyis rtogs don mthar dbyung ste grol ba thob tshul /
NK101(de)004:1812: de ltar mngon du gyur te 'bras bu lhun gyis grub nas ngang la rdzogs tshul dang lnga las /
NK101(de)004:1814: mthun dpes mtshon te ston pa yang sprul nyid kyi don mchog mngon du byas tshul /
NK101(de)004:1815: rtogs don de'i rang bzhin dang mtshan nyid dngos bzung ba /
NK101(de)004:1816: de nyid brda thabs kyis mtshon te legs par ngo sprod pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:1818: gtsug gi rgyan la sogs rkang pa bcus bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1819: dper na klu yi rgyal po'i spyi gtsug gi rgyan
NK101(de)004:1820: gyi nor bu rin po che la dgos pa thams
NK101(de)004:1821: cad tshangas yang klu gdugs pa'i dbang du byas pas
NK101(de)004:1822: 'gro ba'i dbul ba ma sel ba de nyid skyes
NK101(de)004:1823: pa rabs kyi sde las dge don du grag pa'i
NK101(de)004:1824: rgyal bus sngon gyi bsod namsa bsags pa'i dbang gis
NK101(de)004:1825: thoba pa na / nor bu rin po che de
NK101(de)004:1826: rgyal matshana gyi rtse mo la btagsa nas mchod pas
NK101(de)004:1827: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi char bzang po phab ste
NK101(de)004:1828: des 'gro ba'i dbul ba bsal te 'dod pa'i bde
NK101(de)004:1829: ba la longs spyad pa lo rgyus gtam rgyu las
NK101(de)004:1831: ye nas rang nyid la lhun gyis grub par gnas
NK101(de)004:1832: pas rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal med pa'i gnas lugs bde
NK101(de)004:1833: ba chen po de nyid ma rtogs shing phyin ci
NK101(de)004:1834: log tu brtags pas bag chags kyi rnyoga pas lhun
NK101(de)004:1836: lha'i dbang po'i dus la bab par mkhyen nas phyogs
NK101(de)004:1837: bcu'i sangs rgyas la bskul ba'i bka' drin gyis gsang
NK101(de)004:1838: bdag phyag na rdo rjes lhun gnas mngon sum du
NK101(de)004:1839: bstan nas / de la goms shing 'dris par byas
NK101(de)004:1840: pas bag chags kyi rnyog gzhi sangas te rnam byang
NK101(de)004:1841: gi rgya mtsho dwangs pa la sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK101(de)004:1842: che ba'i yon tan gyi gzugs brnyan rang shar ba
NK101(de)004:1843: ni rtsol bas bsgrubs pa'i theg pa gzhan dang mtshungs
NK101(de)004:1844: pa med par rtsol med bde ba chen po rang
NK101(de)004:1845: la shar bas grol ba mthar thug tu gyur to
NK101(de)004:1846: bstan nas / // 'di ni sngon byon dam pa'i
NK101(de)004:1847: rnam thar gsungs pa yin pas de la brten nas
NK101(de)004:1848: rjes 'jug mkhas pa'i nyams len kyang shes par bya'o
NK101(de)004:1850: dus gsum bde gshegs sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1851: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pas rtogs pa'i ye
NK101(de)004:1852: shes dang 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems nyid ma
NK101(de)004:1853: nor bar yul med du rang snang ba dang /
NK101(de)004:1854: bla ma'i drin gyis thob pa'i gnas lugs rang ngo
NK101(de)004:1855: shes pa'i rig pa yul med du rang shar ba
NK101(de)004:1856: dang gsum po de dag rang bzhin ye nas dbyer
NK101(de)004:1857: med du gnas pa ni dper na gser gyi gong
NK101(de)004:1858: bu sa le sbram las byas pa'i rdzas rnams ming
NK101(de)004:1859: dang dbyibs dang byed las dang dngos po bzhi'i sgo
NK101(de)004:1860: nas tha dad yin kyang ngo bo gser du gcig
NK101(de)004:1861: pa la rnam dbye med pa bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:1862: de ltar yang klong rab 'byams rgyal po las /
NK101(de)004:1863: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid la //
NK101(de)004:1864: 'bras bu mi zad gter dang ldan //
NK101(de)004:1866: snang grags thams cad de la spyod //
NK101(de)004:1867: btsal ba med pa'i bya bral dang //
NK101(de)004:1868: nam mkha'i klong ltar yongs la khyab //
NK101(de)004:1869: gser gyi rdzas ltar gcig las snang //
NK101(de)004:1870: tha dad shar yang gcig tu rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:1872: man ngag gser gyi sbubs mchu klong gsal ye shes kyi mar me las /
NK101(de)004:1873: lhun gyis grub pa 'bras bu mi zad gter //
NK101(de)004:1874: 'khor 'das thams cad de las 'byung bas gzhi //
NK101(de)004:1875: rtsol ba med pa'i bya bral nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)004:1876: gser gyi rdzas ltar gcig las tha dad shar //
NK101(de)004:1877: rtsa ba mi 'gyur 'bras bu gcig tu snang //
NK101(de)004:1878: de las byung ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK101(de)004:1879: nyid kyi ngo bor ma gyur gzhan med pas //
NK101(de)004:1880: ma spros kun la khyab par gdal pa'i klong //
NK101(de)004:1882: de lta bu'i gdod ma'i chos nyid kyi don de
NK101(de)004:1883: nyid ji ltar gnas pa'i mtshan nyid kyang lhun grub
NK101(de)004:1884: gsum mam ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi
NK101(de)004:1886: 'khrul pas brtags zhen gyi snang ba las ye nas
NK101(de)004:1887: dben pa ni sems kyi rang bzhin spros bral lhun
NK101(de)004:1888: grub kyis smag gi mun rub ltar du brtags zhen
NK101(de)004:1889: cir yang ma dmigs pas ther zug rtag pa las
NK101(de)004:1890: grol te ngo bo ka dag tu bzhugs shing /
NK101(de)004:1891: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i dus nyid na yang
NK101(de)004:1892: sems kyi mtshan nyid rang rig lhun grub kyis ye
NK101(de)004:1893: nas gnyis snang mi gnas par rang gsal ba ni
NK101(de)004:1894: nyi ma'i snying po la rang chas kyi 'od zer
NK101(de)004:1895: sgrib pa med pa dang 'dra bas rang bzhin 'od
NK101(de)004:1896: gsal gyi ye shes su lhun gyis grub par gnas
NK101(de)004:1897: la / ye shes rig pa'i rang snang gi rol
NK101(de)004:1898: pa cir yang 'phrul pa ni rnam pa sgyu ma
NK101(de)004:1899: lhun grub kyis ma 'gags par 'char ta stong pa
NK101(de)004:1900: phyang chad ma yin pas chu nyid rlabs su shar
NK101(de)004:1901: ba dang 'dra bar rang byung gi thugs rjes kun
NK101(de)004:1904: gzhi mtshon dpe yi rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:1905: mun pa chu dang nyi mas bstan //
NK101(de)004:1906: sems nyid rig pa ka dag la //
NK101(de)004:1907: zhen pas brtags pa'i snang med pas //
NK101(de)004:1908: smag gi mun rub lta bur bshad //
NK101(de)004:1909: dngos med rig pa rang snang la //
NK101(de)004:1910: ye shes rol pa mi 'gag pas //
NK101(de)004:1911: chu yi gnyer ma lta bur bshad //
NK101(de)004:1912: ma bcos sems kyi mtshan nyid la //
NK101(de)004:1913: rtsol bas bkag pa ma yin yang //
NK101(de)004:1914: gdod nas dag pa'i dri med pas //
NK101(de)004:1915: nyi ma shar ba lta bur bshad //
NK101(de)004:1916: tha dad rtag par 'dzin pa dang //
NK101(de)004:1917: rol pa'i snang ba bkag pas chad //
NK101(de)004:1918: mtha' bral dbu ma'i don 'dzin pa'i //
NK101(de)004:1919: mtha' gsum gsal ba'i dgos pa'o //
NK101(de)004:1921: de ltar grol gzhi don gyi gnas lugs 'di ni dbyings chen ngo bo ka dag /
NK101(de)004:1922: lhun grub rang gsal ye shes /
NK101(de)004:1923: dbyer med thugs rje'i rnam pa gsum ye nas ma
NK101(de)004:1924: 'dres la mtha' bral chen por yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:1925: rig pa 'dus ma byas pa yin pas rtag chad
NK101(de)004:1926: dang de gnyis bral nas dbus su 'dzin pa'i mtha'
NK101(de)004:1927: gsum las grol ba'i dgos pa yod pas na mtshan
NK101(de)004:1928: nyid dbyer med chen por bstan pa yin te /
NK101(de)004:1929: rin po che 'byung bar byed pa sgra thal 'gyur rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK101(de)004:1930: ka nas dag pas dri ma zad //
NK101(de)004:1931: ngo bo ye nas 'khrul ba med //
NK101(de)004:1934: kun la khyab pas thugs rje ste //
NK101(de)004:1938: chos nyid stong pa kun khyab phyir //
NK101(de)004:1939: ye shes rang ngor gnas pa la //
NK101(de)004:1940: gsum gyi tshul du dbyer med do //
NK101(de)004:1942: kun tu bzang po klong drug pa las /
NK101(de)004:1943: gdos bcas mtshan ma rang dag phyir //
NK101(de)004:1944: gting gsal chen po'i gzhi mar gnas //
NK101(de)004:1945: khyab dang khyab pa nyid kyis stong //
NK101(de)004:1946: phyang nas chad pa med par snang //
NK101(de)004:1947: gsal byed snang ba'i cha ma 'gags //
NK101(de)004:1948: snying po thams cad bcud 'dus pas //
NK101(de)004:1949: dri ma med cing rang sar dag /
NK101(de)004:1950: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsang chen du //
NK101(de)004:1951: rang bzhin gyi ni cha la bzhugs //
NK101(de)004:1952: thugs rje'i snang cha sna tshogs 'char //
NK101(de)004:1954: de nyid rdo rje'i lus la ji ltar gnas pa'ang /
NK101(de)004:1955: gzugs kyi phung po skye mched tshul las bskyed nas /
NK101(de)004:1956: gnas thams cad 'dus pa'i lus kyi dkyil tsit+ta rin
NK101(de)004:1957: po che ye shes kyi gnad dang yon tan 'byung
NK101(de)004:1958: bas gzhal yas khang dam pa sku gsum gyi gnas
NK101(de)004:1959: na / ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i ye shes kyi cha stong pa chen po dang /
NK101(de)004:1960: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi cha gsal ba 'gag med dang /
NK101(de)004:1961: thugs rje kun khyab kyi cha dbyer med du 'dus pa'i rig par gnas la /
NK101(de)004:1962: de yang ngo bo sku yi rang gdangs zhal phyag
NK101(de)004:1963: rang sa na rdzogs la 'od kyi gting mdangs ston
NK101(de)004:1964: te shes bya la kha phyir ma bltas pa dper
NK101(de)004:1965: bum nang sku'i tshul du nang gsal du bzhugs la
NK101(de)004:1966: / rang bzhin lhun grub kyi rang gdangs sku de dag kyang 'od kyi gong bur gnas shing /
NK101(de)004:1967: thugs rje kun khyab kyi gdangs las 'od de dag
NK101(de)004:1968: kyang kha dog gi rigs rnams so sor ma 'dres
NK101(de)004:1971: lus kyi dus na 'di lta ste //
NK101(de)004:1973: tsit+ta rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK101(de)004:1974: ngo bo ka nas dag pa'i cha //
NK101(de)004:1975: stong gsal 'dus pa sku yi gdangs //
NK101(de)004:1976: zhal phyag rdzogs pa bum sku'i tshul //
NK101(de)004:1977: lhun grub 'od kyi gong bur gnas //
NK101(de)004:1978: thugs rje kha dog so sor gsal //
NK101(de)004:1980: rang rig ye shes lus la gnas //
NK101(de)004:1981: til 'bru las ni mar bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:1982: lus kyi bkrag dang gzi mdangs ni //
NK101(de)004:1983: ye shes rlan gyis khyab par byed //
NK101(de)004:1985: de lta bu'i chos nyid de yi bzhugs tshul ji
NK101(de)004:1986: lta ba bzhin du skal ldan rnams kyis rtogs par
NK101(de)004:1987: bya ba'i phyir sgra yis mtshon pa'i brdar btags shing
NK101(de)004:1988: tshig sdebs legs pas bstan te bka' stsal pa yin
NK101(de)004:1989: no // des na shing zhes pa na mtshams sbyor gyi sgra lta bur 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)004:1991: ji ltar 'khrul tshul gyi brda dang /
NK101(de)004:1992: de las grol tshul gyi brda bstan pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:1994: shes bya re zhig sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:1995: de yang shes nas grol bar bya ba ni /
NK101(de)004:1996: skabs 'dir re zhig rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad yod pa las ni /
NK101(de)004:1997: kun gzhi gcig la gzhi sbyor gnyis su shes par
NK101(de)004:1998: byas te tshogs bdun la skye lugs gsum du bstan
NK101(de)004:2000: de nyid rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir na gzhi don gyi
NK101(de)004:2001: kun gzhi rnam byang dwangs par gnas pa de nyid
NK101(de)004:2002: tshogs bdun bag chags kyi rnyog pas bslad pa'i sbyor
NK101(de)004:2003: don dang gnyis su bstan pas so //
NK101(de)004:2004: de la tshogs bdun gyis gzhi don ma spangs kyang
NK101(de)004:2005: ngo ma shes nas bral bar snang bas skye lugs
NK101(de)004:2006: gsum du shar ba yin te /
NK101(de)004:2007: sgo lnga mtshan ma'i yul gyi rnam par skye ba dang /
NK101(de)004:2008: yid shes spros pa sna tshogs kyi rnam par skye ba dang /
NK101(de)004:2009: nyon yid nga bdag gi rnam par skye bas so //
NK101(de)004:2010: des na rnam shes tshogs bdun la gsal bar myong ba skye lugs gsum gyis bstan par mdzad do //
NK101(de)004:2011: de yi brda yanga rgya gar shar phyogs yul gyi
NK101(de)004:2012: bkod pa rgya che bas sam yang na 'khrul pa
NK101(de)004:2013: shar ba'i phyogs byings che zhing mang bas b+ha g+ha
NK101(de)004:2014: lar te la zhes bya ba na /
NK101(de)004:2015: mkhar chen pa ni zag bcas kyi phung po'am lus
NK101(de)004:2016: yin la de la sgo brgyad ni don dbang po
NK101(de)004:2017: drug sogs lhan cig 'byung ba'i gnas brgyad du go
NK101(de)004:2018: ste nyer spyod skye ba'i sgo yin pas so //
NK101(de)004:2022: gnam sgo gcig dang ldan pa yi nang na /
NK101(de)004:2023: lta ba phyir yul la phyogs te don dang sems
NK101(de)004:2024: can la lta zhing gnas pa nang na mi 'gyur
NK101(de)004:2025: bar gnas pa'i rgyal po chen po gcig ni kun
NK101(de)004:2026: gzhi ste gzhi sbyor ma phye ba'o //
NK101(de)004:2027: de la 'khor sems byung ni nyon mongs dang rnam
NK101(de)004:2028: rtog gi rnam pa grangs med pa yod cing nang
NK101(de)004:2029: na sgo srung ni rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad
NK101(de)004:2030: dang / sgo gtan ni mtshan mar 'dzin pa /
NK101(de)004:2031: spros pa sna tshogs su 'dzin pa /
NK101(de)004:2032: nga bdag tu 'dzin pa gsum dang /
NK101(de)004:2033: spyod yul gyi gnas 'khor ba'i sa ni rigs drug
NK101(de)004:2034: gi snang ba yod pas rgyal po ni shin tu
NK101(de)004:2035: dbang chen po yin zhing nor bu rin po che
NK101(de)004:2036: ma bral bzhin du mi mngon par byed pas rkun
NK101(de)004:2037: po dang mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan ma bskyel bzhin
NK101(de)004:2038: du gcig par snang bas 'gro ba dbul bar byed
NK101(de)004:2040: gdengs chen ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2041: gzhi nyid 'bras bur nges pa'i tshad ma rtogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:2042: gdengs chen po dang ldan pa'i sgo nas de dag
NK101(de)004:2043: gi g.yul ngo 'joms pa'i dpa' bo lhun grub gsum
NK101(de)004:2044: gyi rang 'od 'bar ba'i thugs phrad gsum ni /
NK101(de)004:2045: gdams ngag gi 'byung gnas rgya gar nub phyogs me tog rigs lngas dbu rgyan byed pa'i yul lam /
NK101(de)004:2046: yang na rnam rtog nub pa'i phyogsa gong na med
NK101(de)004:2047: cing mdzes pas u rgyan thor cog cana gyi gnas
NK101(de)004:2048: na / 'jug sgo theg pa brgyad lam stegs su
NK101(de)004:2049: ldan pa'i khri rkang mdzod mig brgyad ldan sngon du
NK101(de)004:2051: rtsa ba rig par gcig pas gang gis kyang gong mchod pas rtsa mo /
NK101(de)004:2052: thug phrad gsum na shes pa gsum sgrol bas mtshon cha /
NK101(de)004:2053: skye lugs gsum po rang lhun grub gsum du 'bar
NK101(de)004:2054: bar byed pas 'od de des sgo srung dang sgo
NK101(de)004:2055: gtan dang 'akhara sa dag rim pa bzhin du rang
NK101(de)004:2056: bsgral rang bcag phyags mas btab pa rnams byas nasa
NK101(de)004:2057: 'khor sems dang sems byung rnams rgyal po kun gzhi
NK101(de)004:2058: dag pa'i ngang nyid la bsdus pasa sbyor don rang
NK101(de)004:2059: grol te phyi ru don dang sems can la bltar
NK101(de)004:2060: zhes lta ba med par nang gzhi don dus gsum
NK101(de)004:2061: du mi 'gyur bar gnas pa nyid ni nor bu
NK101(de)004:2062: la longs spyod cing mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan gzugs
NK101(de)004:2063: pa'i dgos pa yang yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)004:2064: de ltar brda thabs zab mos ji bzhin du mtshon
NK101(de)004:2065: pa'i 'phrul snang sna tshogs pa'i khams can gyi rang
NK101(de)004:2066: bzhin dang gnyis su med pa'i shes bya don gyi
NK101(de)004:2067: gnas lugs sems nyid rang 'od gsal ba gsang sngags
NK101(de)004:2068: kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK101(de)004:2070: 'khor ba'i shes pa glo bur ba //
NK101(de)004:2071: rang bzhin ma yin rkyen gyis snang //
NK101(de)004:2072: brjod pa'i brnyan ma nyid dang mtshungs //
NK101(de)004:2073: rnam par rtog pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK101(de)004:2074: gong ltar brtags pa gzhan du mthong //
NK101(de)004:2075: du ma rim gyis rtog pa dag /
NK101(de)004:2076: sgo rnams kun tu rgyu ba ste //
NK101(de)004:2077: mi gcig skar khung du ma bzhin //
NK101(de)004:2078: don gyi rnam byang du ma min //
NK101(de)004:2080: mtha' bral lta ba'i don ldan gyis //
NK101(de)004:2081: rang bzhin dgongs pas gnas par bya //
NK101(de)004:2084: rnam shes brgyad las kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:2085: ma rtogs rnyog pas spags pas tshogs bdun gyis //
NK101(de)004:2086: bag chags gzhi ru smin pa sbyor ba don //
NK101(de)004:2087: bdun po grol na bag chags rnyogs pa dwangs //
NK101(de)004:2088: byang sems gzhi don yon tan gzugs brnyan shar //
NK101(de)004:2089: bdun la sgo lnga yul lngar gsal mi rtog /
NK101(de)004:2090: yid kyis rjes 'brangs yul la mtshan mar gzung //
NK101(de)004:2091: nyon mongs can yid kun gzhi kha nang bltas //
NK101(de)004:2092: nga bdag phrar 'dzin yid kyi rjes 'brangs nas //
NK101(de)004:2093: bdag dang bdag gir gzung 'dzin lnga sogs 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:2094: yid kyi rnam shes de gnyis rjes su'ang 'brang //
NK101(de)004:2095: rang rgyud snga ma tsam gyi rjes su 'brang //
NK101(de)004:2096: de gsum lhun grub gsum las ma 'das la //
NK101(de)004:2097: thug phrad gsum gyis de ltar ngo sprod nas //
NK101(de)004:2098: de yi so la brtag dpyad med par bzhag /
NK101(de)004:2101: rang bzhin spros bral lhun grub /
NK101(de)004:2102: rnam pa sgyu ma lhun grub /
NK101(de)004:2103: mtshan nyid rang rig lhun grub gsum ste /
NK101(de)004:2105: gzhi don lhun grub rnam gsum la //
NK101(de)004:2106: rnam pa rang bzhin mtshan nyid rnams //
NK101(de)004:2107: bde ba chen por lhun grub pa //
NK101(de)004:2108: dus gsum bde gshegs ye shes dang //
NK101(de)004:2109: 'gro drug sems kyi ma bcos pa //
NK101(de)004:2110: tha dad ma yin rang bzhin gcig /
NK101(de)004:2113: gnas lugs rang byung ye shes te //
NK101(de)004:2114: rnam pas don rdzogs rol pa'i rgyan //
NK101(de)004:2115: stong nyid dngos bral rang grol rgyan //
NK101(de)004:2116: de mkhyen rang gsal skyon las grol //
NK101(de)004:2117: ye rdzogs gzhi yi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK101(de)004:2120: cis kyang mtshon 'das dbyer med grol //
NK101(de)004:2121: cir yang ma 'gags lhun grub rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:2122: de mkhyen rang gsal ma gos dag /
NK101(de)004:2123: gdod nas ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:2126: sgo lnga sprul sku thug phrad dang //
NK101(de)004:2127: nyon yid longs sku thug phrad dang //
NK101(de)004:2128: yid shes chos sku thug phrad du shar bas sbyor
NK101(de)004:2129: don rang grol nas kun gzhi ma bcos par rang
NK101(de)004:2130: rig byang chub kyi sems su dbyer med yongs rdzogs
NK101(de)004:2131: kyi ngo bor rnam par dag pas thig le nyag
NK101(de)004:2132: gcig gi dgongs don ji bzhin du rtogs par byed
NK101(de)004:2134: byang chub kyi sems nyi ma'i 'od zer las /
NK101(de)004:2135: gcod byed yul gnyis gsum 'brangs rnams //
NK101(de)004:2136: ngang gis mi gnas spros bral byang //
NK101(de)004:2137: rten lnga rang bzhin mi 'gag shar //
NK101(de)004:2138: sgyu ma'i rnam par khyab pas chub //
NK101(de)004:2139: nang bltas ngar 'dzin de mtshan nyid //
NK101(de)004:2140: rtogs na rang rig gnyug ma'i sems //
NK101(de)004:2141: mi gnas mi 'gag dbyer med gsum //
NK101(de)004:2142: phyogs su ma lhungs ro gcig pa //
NK101(de)004:2143: kun gzhi ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:2146: ngos bzung 'das pa'i ye shes su //
NK101(de)004:2148: de ltar mkhyen pa'i rang rig pa //
NK101(de)004:2149: khyab la ma 'dres rang gsal lo //
NK101(de)004:2150: de yi rnam 'phrul rol pa'i chos //
NK101(de)004:2151: sprul pas don rnams grub ste rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:2152: de dag dbyer med 'dres pa'ang min //
NK101(de)004:2153: mtshan nyid las grol mtshan nyid do //
NK101(de)004:2157: rin chen gsung gi brtag pas shes //
NK101(de)004:2158: 'gro drug sems can thams cad la //
NK101(de)004:2159: rang gnas ye shes nyid ldan pa //
NK101(de)004:2160: brtag pa gsum gyis shes par 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:2161: ming dang sems kyis ye shes tshol //
NK101(de)004:2162: dngos po gang yang rung ba las //
NK101(de)004:2163: brtags pas rang log shes pa 'byung //
NK101(de)004:2164: rin chen bzhin du 'gyur ba med //
NK101(de)004:2166: man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:2167: rtogs pa'i thabs su cir mtshon mod //
NK101(de)004:2168: don du ye shes 'od gsal nyid //
NK101(de)004:2169: snying po kun bral ma 'dres rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:2170: brjod bya nyag gcig nyid mthun pa //
NK101(de)004:2171: nges don snying po nyag gcig mod //
NK101(de)004:2174: skye lugs gsum gyi rnam rtog thams cad nges don
NK101(de)004:2175: bdud rtsi'i man ngag spu gri lta bu'i brda thabs
NK101(de)004:2176: kyis gcig chod du bcad nas rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed
NK101(de)004:2177: pa la ma ltos par rang gnas sku gsum rang
NK101(de)004:2178: chas la ma bcos rang lugs su 'jug pas bar
NK101(de)004:2179: gzhan med par rtogs pa cig char du 'char ba
NK101(de)004:2180: la gsungs te / ye shes gsang sgron las /
NK101(de)004:2181: yang dag gdams ngag rgyal po 'di //
NK101(de)004:2182: bka' rgyud spu gri lta bu ste //
NK101(de)004:2184: 'byung ba sems la gnas par bya //
NK101(de)004:2185: gang la mi ltos man ngag rgyud //
NK101(de)004:2186: zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes ni //
NK101(de)004:2187: rang lugs bzhin du shes par bya //
NK101(de)004:2188: rgyu dang rkyen la rag ma las //
NK101(de)004:2189: thug phrad shugs kyi lhug pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2190: sku gsum 'bras bu rang chas la //
NK101(de)004:2191: ye shes rang chas zang ka ma //
NK101(de)004:2192: 'di ni rang la byin gyis brlabs //
NK101(de)004:2194: man ngag nges par lung bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:2195: de las mi 'da' ngang bsdam pa //
NK101(de)004:2196: mtshan ma lnga dang de rjes ming //
NK101(de)004:2197: ngar 'dzin gzhan rtog rgyun lang can //
NK101(de)004:2198: kha 'byams spyi bltas tsam min par //
NK101(de)004:2199: sgyu ma spros bral rang rig par //
NK101(de)004:2200: thug phrad nyid du thal byung bas //
NK101(de)004:2201: gsum la btud cing gras thag bcad //
NK101(de)004:2202: rang log thug phrad rang sor bzhag /
NK101(de)004:2205: rin po che gter gtad pa las /
NK101(de)004:2206: gnas lugs bde chen gyi rang bzhin bstan pa'i le'u sta skabs dang po rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2208: spros bral don gsal chen po'i rgyud las /
NK101(de)004:2209: rigs kyi le'i zhes pa ni /
NK101(de)004:2210: so so'i sa mtshams dang chos gzhan ma 'dres te gang mtshon pa'i don gtso bor bshad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2211: skabs zhes pa thams cad le'i don dang don 'byung ba'i gzhi ma 'gags par shes pa la bya'o //
NK101(de)004:2213: gnyis pa de nyid ma rtogs pas 'khrul te sdug bsngal dang rtsol ba'i nad kyis 'khyams tshul la /
NK101(de)004:2214: don gyi ngang las 'khrul pa 'byung tshul gyi ngo bo ngos bzung /
NK101(de)004:2215: rang bzhin gyi snang ba la 'khrul pa'i bag chags kyi rnyog tshul dpes bstan /
NK101(de)004:2216: de ltar 'khrul pa'i rnam grangs kyi mtshan nyid dbye ste bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:2218: rang byung lnga ru sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2219: bde chen klong 'byams kyi bsam gtan las /
NK101(de)004:2220: ma bcos sems kyi klong dkyil nas //
NK101(de)004:2221: rang byung ye shes don shar bas //
NK101(de)004:2222: steng 'og phyogs mtshams yongs la brdal //
NK101(de)004:2223: nyag gcig dbyings la kun gsal bas //
NK101(de)004:2224: mthong dang thos dang dran pa dang //
NK101(de)004:2225: rig pa'i ngo la gang snang ba //
NK101(de)004:2226: yul med gcig las shar bas na //
NK101(de)004:2227: snang ba med cing 'grib pa med //
NK101(de)004:2230: ma bcos rang byung ye shes ni //
NK101(de)004:2231: rang byung ye shes lnga snang la //
NK101(de)004:2232: phyin ci log gi bsam pa yis //
NK101(de)004:2233: ye shes nyid du ma rtogs te //
NK101(de)004:2234: yang dag zhen pa lnga ru mthong //
NK101(de)004:2235: zhen pa lnga yi 'bras bu ni //
NK101(de)004:2236: khams gsum sems can nyid du shar //
NK101(de)004:2237: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyu rkyen byed pa med par
NK101(de)004:2238: rang byung gi ye shes lnga ru rtag tu rang
NK101(de)004:2240: rang ngo rang gis ma rig pa nyid de /
NK101(de)004:2241: rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir na mtshon byed nor bu rin
NK101(de)004:2242: chen lta bu gdams ngag gi rkyen meda pas na
NK101(de)004:2243: ma rig la / gang du na rang byung ye
NK101(de)004:2244: shes nyid du ma rig pa ste lhan cig skyes
NK101(de)004:2245: ma rig la / pa zhes bya / de yi
NK101(de)004:2246: nga bdag tu 'dzin par byas nas kun brtags kyi
NK101(de)004:2247: ma rig pa'i mdud pa dgrol dka' bas shin tu
NK101(de)004:2249: de'i mthu lasa gzhan du'ang snang ste /
NK101(de)004:2250: de gnyis kyi cha las 'dzin pa'i kun rtog nyon mongs pa dug lngara smin te /
NK101(de)004:2251: nang na sa bon gyi bdag nyid dug lnga yi
NK101(de)004:2252: cha can rtsa ba dang nye ba'i nyon mongs pa
NK101(de)004:2253: du ma gnas pas de dag gis kun nas bslang
NK101(de)004:2254: ba'i 'du byed kyi las dge ba dang mi dge
NK101(de)004:2255: ba dang mi g.yo ba dang gsum mam yang na
NK101(de)004:2256: lus ngag yid kyi las gsum gyi ma tog phyi
NK101(de)004:2257: ru rgyas pas re zhig gi 'bras bu 'gro ba
NK101(de)004:2258: rigs drug po las gsum las grub pas bdud bzhi
NK101(de)004:2259: la sogs pa zhor snang gi duhkhasa rtag tu nyen
NK101(de)004:2260: pa yin te / slob dpon lha'i rgyal pos /
NK101(de)004:2261: yul na mi gnas nges rkyen bral //
NK101(de)004:2262: rang gis rang ngo ma shes pas //
NK101(de)004:2263: don du gnas kyang ngo bos bskal //
NK101(de)004:2264: ngang 'dzin gzhan snang tha dad brtags //
NK101(de)004:2265: cha las nyon mongs lnga yi bdud //
NK101(de)004:2266: chos nyid spros bral bcad ltar 'phros //
NK101(de)004:2267: 'du byed mthu yis phung po blangs //
NK101(de)004:2268: sgyu ma'i rnam pa mtshan mar bcas //
NK101(de)004:2269: srog rgyun brten pas nus zad 'pho //
NK101(de)004:2270: 'gyur med bcad ltar chu bzhi srid //
NK101(de)004:2271: rtog pas gzhan du bzung ba yis //
NK101(de)004:2272: slu ba'i bri tas dngos grub bcad //
NK101(de)004:2273: bzhi yis byang chub sems bslad de //
NK101(de)004:2274: sdug bsngal rtsol ba'i nad kyi mnar //
NK101(de)004:2277: rang snang mod kyang sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te //
NK101(de)004:2278: yin lugs chos nyid rang bzhin gyi snang ba yin
NK101(de)004:2279: mod kyang rang gis rang ngo ma rig ste bdag
NK101(de)004:2280: tu 'dzin pa'i mthu can gyi bgo gzhi de la
NK101(de)004:2281: bgo byed kyis bzhag pa'i las dang nyon mongs rnams
NK101(de)004:2282: kyi sa bon la sogs pa bgas kyis chagas pa
NK101(de)004:2283: ni dper na ras dkar po gur du phub pa
NK101(de)004:2284: la dri ma bgas kyis chags pa ji lta ba
NK101(de)004:2285: bzhin no // de ltar yang thal 'gyur las /
NK101(de)004:2286: chos nyid rang gdangs snang ba las //
NK101(de)004:2287: rtog 'dzin snang bas yid phrogs te //
NK101(de)004:2288: 'khrul cha'i yul ni phra mo'i las //
NK101(de)004:2289: bsgribs shing rang snang ma dag gyur //
NK101(de)004:2290: de yis bag la nyal ba nyid //
NK101(de)004:2291: phra zhing rdul gyi cha dag ni //
NK101(de)004:2293: phra bas phra 'gyur shes pa las //
NK101(de)004:2294: rtog dpyod gzung cha gnyis su song //
NK101(de)004:2295: phra rdul ye shes snang ba 'gags //
NK101(de)004:2296: yul shes thad ka tsam du shar //
NK101(de)004:2298: gsum pa de ltar 'khrul pa'i rnam grangs kyi mtshan nyid dbye ste nges par bstan pa la /
NK101(de)004:2299: zhen pas 'khrul pa 'gro ba rigs drug dang /
NK101(de)004:2300: rkyen gyis 'khrul pa phyi nang gi grub mtha' bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2302: las rlung drag po sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2303: zhen rtog la brten nas zag pa dang bcas pa'i
NK101(de)004:2304: las gsum gyi g.yo bas 'du byed sems pa'i rlung
NK101(de)004:2305: ni shugs drag po can du gyur te de nyid
NK101(de)004:2306: kyi nus pa'i mthu mche bas zhen pa 'gro ba
NK101(de)004:2307: rigs drug gi 'khor lo ni las kyi shugs kyis
NK101(de)004:2308: yang nas yang du bskyal bas 'khor ba zhes su
NK101(de)004:2310: sred srid ma rig dbang gis skye bo rnams //
NK101(de)004:2311: mi dang lha dang ngan song rnam gsum po //
NK101(de)004:2312: 'gro ba lnga po dag tu mi mkhas 'khor //
NK101(de)004:2313: dper na rdza mkhan 'khor lo bskor ba bzhin //
NK101(de)004:2316: ma rig la sogs bcu gnyis chas //
NK101(de)004:2318: de yi nang shas 'byung ba'i lus //
NK101(de)004:2319: phung po rnams dang khams dang yang //
NK101(de)004:2320: skye mched las kyi tshogs la 'dus //
NK101(de)004:2321: nyon mongs 'dus pa dpag med las //
NK101(de)004:2322: 'gro ba'i lus kyi rtog tshogs sdud //
NK101(de)004:2323: rten 'brel tshogs pa du ma las //
NK101(de)004:2324: mi mthun gzugs sogs bye brag go //
NK101(de)004:2325: zhes gsungs pa ltar phyi dang nang gi rten 'brel
NK101(de)004:2326: bcu gnyis snod bcud la cha phra rags dang grangs
NK101(de)004:2327: mang nyung du 'khor ba'i tshul ni //
NK101(de)004:2328: dper na zo chu'i brgyud pa'i 'khor lo dang 'dra
NK101(de)004:2329: bar rgyun mi 'chad cing de dag la dbral dka'
NK101(de)004:2330: bar zhen nas a 'thas su gyur pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2331: de bas na rin po che rgyan las kyang //
NK101(de)004:2332: yin par gnas dang ma shes pa //
NK101(de)004:2333: snga phyi mi gnas thog ma med //
NK101(de)004:2334: tshad las 'das pas tha ma'ang bral //
NK101(de)004:2335: rgyun du mi stongs 'khor lo bskor //
NK101(de)004:2336: zo chu brgyud pa'i 'khor lo ltar //
NK101(de)004:2337: phyi nang bcu gnyis shugs kyis bskyar //
NK101(de)004:2338: yod pa min kyang don ltar snang //
NK101(de)004:2339: rkyen gyis dkrugs pa'i dbang po bzhin //
NK101(de)004:2340: ma rig 'dam gyi phung po la //
NK101(de)004:2341: nyon mongs dug lnga gzhi btab pas //
NK101(de)004:2342: sdug bsngal sna tshogs nyes pas nyen //
NK101(de)004:2343: thar pa bde chen srog bral ba'o //
NK101(de)004:2346: de ltar dngos med ma shes na /
NK101(de)004:2347: phung po khams dang skye mched la //
NK101(de)004:2348: gzung 'dzin dag gis gzung nas ni //
NK101(de)004:2349: 'khor ba nyid la yun ring gnas //
NK101(de)004:2350: khams gsum pa yi khang pa ru //
NK101(de)004:2351: mi dang gzugs kyi brtson rar tshud //
NK101(de)004:2352: ma rig las kyi lcags kyis bsdoms //
NK101(de)004:2353: rang byung sgron ma nyid dang bral //
NK101(de)004:2354: 'khor ba'i mun nag stug pos g.yogs //
NK101(de)004:2355: 'dod chags lan tsh+wa'i ro la chags //
NK101(de)004:2356: gti mug zhags pas dam du bcings //
NK101(de)004:2357: zhe sdang me yi tshad pas gdungs //
NK101(de)004:2358: nga rgyal dag gis mgo gtums te //
NK101(de)004:2359: phrag dog nyid kyi sgo mos dkrigs //
NK101(de)004:2360: khong khro la sogs dmag gis bskor //
NK101(de)004:2361: dran bsam nyid kyi g.yas g.yon brten //
NK101(de)004:2362: gzung 'dzin zhags pas skye nas btags //
NK101(de)004:2363: snga phyi bag chags 'dam du bying //
NK101(de)004:2364: rnam smin nyid dang lag sprel te //
NK101(de)004:2365: las kyis ma bu mtshams sbyar nas //
NK101(de)004:2366: gcig nas gcig tu zo chu bzhin //
NK101(de)004:2367: bzang ngan rim pa'i lus blangs te //
NK101(de)004:2368: so so'i rigs su skye bar 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:2370: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho'i gting du bying //
NK101(de)004:2371: ngan song lcags kyus snying nas bzung //
NK101(de)004:2372: rang gis rang bcing nyon mongs dgra /
NK101(de)004:2373: dmyal ba par ni mi chur snang //
NK101(de)004:2374: yi dwags rnams la bkres dang skom //
NK101(de)004:2375: byol song rnams la na bun ltar //
NK101(de)004:2376: mi rnams phung po khams dang ni //
NK101(de)004:2377: skye mched 'byung ba lnga ru snang //
NK101(de)004:2378: de yang bde sdug btang snyoms so //
NK101(de)004:2379: lha min rnams la go mtshon te //
NK101(de)004:2380: lha rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan no //
NK101(de)004:2382: gnyis pa rkyen gyis 'khrul pa phyi nang gi grub mtha' bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:2384: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2386: rkyen gyis 'khor lo gsum dang brgyad //
NK101(de)004:2387: ces rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2388: ston pa dang bstan pa'i rkyen gyis 'khor ba'i 'khor
NK101(de)004:2389: lo ma go la gol ba ni phyin ci log
NK101(de)004:2390: tu 'phyan pa mu stegs sde gsum dang /
NK101(de)004:2391: bka' la phyogs char bzung brtsol ba'i theg pa brgyad
NK101(de)004:2392: de 'di ni phyogs tsam rtogs kyang rnal ma yang
NK101(de)004:2393: dag par ma rtogs pas bzhag pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2394: gnyis pa la sogs pas 'khrul pa phyi rol ba sde gsum dang /
NK101(de)004:2395: rtsol bas 'khrul pa theg rim rnam brgyad bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2396: dang po la mdor bstan dang /
NK101(de)004:2399: gsum gyi 'khor lo sogs rkang pa gnyis kyi bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2400: de rnams las log pa gsum gyis rkyen la brten
NK101(de)004:2401: pa'i 'khor lo ni yin lugs las phyir la phyogs
NK101(de)004:2402: te phyin ci log tu bskor pas 'khor ba las
NK101(de)004:2403: ma 'das pa'o // de'i dbang gis gnas lugs kyi
NK101(de)004:2404: don lhun grub gsum la rgyab kyis phyogs par gyur
NK101(de)004:2405: te lam gol ba la zhugs pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2407: las 'bras la rmongs pas log pa gsang tshig pa phyi ma rgyang du 'phen pa'i sde /
NK101(de)004:2408: skur 'debs kyi lta bas log pa chad lta ba mur thug tu 'dzin pa'i sde /
NK101(de)004:2409: sgro 'dogs kyi lta bas log pa rtag smra ba ther zug tu 'dod pa'i sde dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:2411: las las gyur pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2412: tshe 'di'i bde sdug gi khyad par sngar gyi dge
NK101(de)004:2413: sdig gi las kyi mthu las gyur pa la blos
NK101(de)004:2414: ma dpyad de las rgyu 'bras la rmongs pa'i dbang
NK101(de)004:2415: gis tshe 'di yi ched du mthu dang stobs dang
NK101(de)004:2416: btsan pa phyug por sgrub pa la brtson par byed
NK101(de)004:2417: de 'jig rten pa'i gsang tshigs la brten pa'i brtul
NK101(de)004:2418: zhugs kyi spyod pa drag po la spyod pas na
NK101(de)004:2419: 'adi'ang log par rtog pa'i grangs su bsgrangsa pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2420: gal te 'di nyid yang dag pa'i gnas la mos
NK101(de)004:2421: pa can yin na thabs 'dzud bsre ba'i lung gis
NK101(de)004:2422: don dang mthun par mtshams phyogs su drang la /
NK101(de)004:2423: ma mos na btang snyoms su bzhag go //
NK101(de)004:2425: tshe snga phyi la skur pa 'debs pa thar pa nges legs la skur pa 'debs pa /
NK101(de)004:2426: snang chos thams cad la skur pa 'debs pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:2428: phyang chad la las sogs rkang pa bco lngas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2429: snga phyi 'brel ba'i mu med pas phyang chad du
NK101(de)004:2430: smra ba la las 'dod pa ni tshe snga phyi
NK101(de)004:2431: med par tshe 'di gang tsam zhig tu 'dod la
NK101(de)004:2432: / de nyid kyang khu khrag dang sa chu me
NK101(de)004:2433: rlung 'byung ba bzhi po 'dus pa yi nus mthu
NK101(de)004:2434: las mngon par gsal ba'i sems can dang mi gsal
NK101(de)004:2435: ba'i snod kyi sems pa can glo bur du byung
NK101(de)004:2436: ba yin gyis las kyi 'bras bur mi 'dod la
NK101(de)004:2437: / / yang na gang gi de nyid bzhi zhes
NK101(de)004:2438: pa 'di yis 'byung bzhi don dam du 'dod pa
NK101(de)004:2440: slar yang 'byung ba'i nus pa zad nas der thim
NK101(de)004:2441: ste lus sems rgyun chad pa na srid par nying
NK101(de)004:2442: mtshams sbyor ba med pa ni dper na me shi
NK101(de)004:2443: nas thal ba rlung gis khyer te me'i rgyun 'brel
NK101(de)004:2444: ba gzhan skye ba med pa dang 'dra bar 'dod
NK101(de)004:2445: pa'o // 'di dag gi sngon kyang rgyal ba'i bka'
NK101(de)004:2446: zhes bka' yis dngos lan mdzad nas ma bzlog pas
NK101(de)004:2447: na gting nas byang chub kyi sa bon tshig pa
NK101(de)004:2448: can gyi phyogs lhung gi gang zag la log par
NK101(de)004:2449: lta ba'i nyen chen po dag yod pas sdig tu
NK101(de)004:2450: skur ba'i rigs la btang snyoms su bzhag go //
NK101(de)004:2451: 'on kyang mos pa can la nye du kha lan
NK101(de)004:2452: byed pa dang 'dra bar thabs 'dzud bsre ba'i lung
NK101(de)004:2453: ni de dang mthun par 'dren mar spyad nas mthar
NK101(de)004:2455: gal te blo 'am rigs pa spyi sar 'jog pa
NK101(de)004:2456: yi gang zag tshad mar mthong na khas len pa
NK101(de)004:2457: de la dang po lung lasa tshe snga phyi dang
NK101(de)004:2458: las 'bras rnams bshad pas na yod par dpag par
NK101(de)004:2459: bya ste mdo sde las brgya pa dang skyes rabs
NK101(de)004:2461: de yang rmi lam nyams pa sems med pa'i gnyid
NK101(de)004:2462: 'thung dang brgyal ba'i tshe shes pa rgyun chad kyang
NK101(de)004:2463: phyis su sngar gyi rgyun las 'byung bas tshe phyi
NK101(de)004:2464: ma'ang de bzhin du 'byung bar grub bo //
NK101(de)004:2465: de nyid gtan tshigs su 'god tshul /
NK101(de)004:2467: rang gi rigs 'dra snga ma'i rgyu las 'byung ba yi shes pa yin te /
NK101(de)004:2469: ci'i phyir na res 'ga' ba rnams su dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:2471: zhes 'bras bu'i rtags la sbyar bas rigs pa de yis rgyu snga ma yod par sgrub bo //
NK101(de)004:2472: gal te snga ma'i rgyu la ma brten par glo
NK101(de)004:2473: bur du 'byung ba'ang res 'ga' bar ma grub ste
NK101(de)004:2474: / re zhig rtag dngos su 'dod pa rnams la
NK101(de)004:2475: ldog pa mi 'dra ba'i khyad par gcod pa'i thal
NK101(de)004:2476: 'gyur gyi gtan tshigs rtag tu yod pa'am med pa
NK101(de)004:2478: rgyu med gzhan la mi ltos pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:2479: zhes pa'i rtags su khas blangs sbyar la /
NK101(de)004:2480: rtag tu yod na rgyun chad pa nyams la /
NK101(de)004:2484: la las snga phyi sogs tshigs bcad bzhis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2485: yang la las 'dod pa ni tshe snga phyi tsam ni yod par 'dod la /
NK101(de)004:2486: 'on kyang nges par legs pa'i 'bras bu thams cad mkhyen pa la med ces skur pa 'debs te /
NK101(de)004:2487: ji ltar na nges par legs pa de ni nyon
NK101(de)004:2488: mongs pa dug gsum las grol ba la 'dod par
NK101(de)004:2489: 'dug kyang de ni mi 'thad pas te /
NK101(de)004:2490: nged kyi 'dod pa ni dug gsum sems kyi rang
NK101(de)004:2491: bzhin yin pas de gsum spangs na sems de yang
NK101(de)004:2493: sems med pas dug gsum las grol ba po ni
NK101(de)004:2494: gang su zhig yin te grol rgyu med pa'i phyir
NK101(de)004:2495: / dper na nag po spangs na sol ba med par 'gyur bas dkar po gang zhig gtong /
NK101(de)004:2497: der ma zad dug gsum ni spong bas mi 'gyur bar rtag pa yin la /
NK101(de)004:2498: spang ba'i thabs kyang med cing spang thabs shes pa'ang med la spang du btub pa'ang min te /
NK101(de)004:2499: dug gsum de ni ngo bo nyid kyis mi 'gyur bar gansa pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:2501: de yang rigs chad btang snyoms su bzhag pa la
NK101(de)004:2502: sogs pa gsum ni sngar bshad pa bzhin du mthun
NK101(de)004:2503: par sgrub ste / khyad par gyi rigs pa yang
NK101(de)004:2504: dag pas sun dbyung ba yang dang po ma nges
NK101(de)004:2505: te rnyog chu dang 'dra bas dwangs su btub la
NK101(de)004:2506: par sgrub ste / / gnyis pa ma grub ste
NK101(de)004:2507: dug gsum gyi rgyu bdag 'dzin dang rkyen gzhan snang
NK101(de)004:2508: ba dang ldan pas mi rtag pa yin cing /
NK101(de)004:2509: gsum pa gnyen po'i ye shes kyis spong bar byed pas thabs yod la /
NK101(de)004:2510: bzhi pa bla ma brgyud pa dang ldan pa'i man ngag yod pas spong yang shes shing /
NK101(de)004:2511: lnga pa ye shes de nyid dug gsum de yi rang bzhin yin pas spang du btub la /
NK101(de)004:2512: tha ma dug gsum spangs te gnas 'gyur ba ni
NK101(de)004:2513: rang rig pa'i mngon sum mo zhes rang rig mngon
NK101(de)004:2514: sum gyis grub pas ngo bo nyid kyis mi gnas
NK101(de)004:2515: so // des na bka' yi brgyud pa rnams ni
NK101(de)004:2516: 'das pa byung zin par bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu yi
NK101(de)004:2517: rtags la brten nas rgyud snga ma sngon du song
NK101(de)004:2518: ba dang rgyu rkyen dang ldan pa mi rtag par
NK101(de)004:2519: so // sgrub cing / de yi rang bzhin rtogs
NK101(de)004:2520: nas gnas tshul gyi don du byas pa la brten
NK101(de)004:2521: te nges par legs pa nyid du rang grub par
NK101(de)004:2522: so // sgrub cing / sgrub bo // de bas na slob dpon shes rab 'byung gnas kyis /
NK101(de)004:2523: gang gzhan la 'chad pa la don dang mthun zhing
NK101(de)004:2524: 'gal ba med pa des gzhal bya de mngon sum
NK101(de)004:2526: rang rang gis yul dpyod pa bzhin /
NK101(de)004:2527: gzhung 'bum pa la sogs pa 'chad pa po des kyang don dang mthun zhing 'gal ba med do //
NK101(de)004:2528: zhes bya bas bsgrubs par nus so //
NK101(de)004:2530: ngag gi spu ris zin na 'gal ba med pas 'dir yang de ltar sbyar ro //
NK101(de)004:2531: yang na rkang pa 'di'i don bka' brgyud 'dir ni
NK101(de)004:2532: 'bras bu rang snang nyid du lhun gyis grub par
NK101(de)004:2533: bzhed pas chad pa'i mtha' las grol ba'o //
NK101(de)004:2534: zhes su 'grel kyang rung bar mngon no //
NK101(de)004:2536: la las lung tsam sogs tshigs bcad gcig tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyi bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2537: yang la las 'dod pa ni rgyal ba'i lung gi
NK101(de)004:2538: bral phyogs tsam la brten nas chos thams cad ci
NK101(de)004:2540: ci yang ma yin pa rang yanga ma yin par 'doda de khas len spangs pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2541: grub mtha' 'di ltar 'dzin pa ni bsgyur bar dka' zhing rang la'ang 'byung nyen che la /
NK101(de)004:2542: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa la slu bar byed
NK101(de)004:2543: pas lam gyi gzugs brnyan tsam yina zhing yang dag
NK101(de)004:2544: pa'i lam min pas dang po kho'i 'dod pa de
NK101(de)004:2545: las bzlog pa tsam du chos thams cad ci yang
NK101(de)004:2546: yin par khas len te bsgrub par bya'o //
NK101(de)004:2547: gsum pa sgro 'dogs kyi lta bas log pa rtag smra ba ther zug tu 'dod pa'i sde la /
NK101(de)004:2549: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2551: ther zug pa dag rig bzhir gnas /
NK101(de)004:2552: zhes rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2553: mu stegs pa'i grub mtha' rtag pa ther zug tu
NK101(de)004:2554: 'dod pa dag ni rigs mi 'dra ba bzhir gnas
NK101(de)004:2555: pa'o // de dag kyang gang zhe na /
NK101(de)004:2557: rig byed pa rig pa la sgro 'dogs pa /
NK101(de)004:2558: bye brag pa shes bya la sgro 'dogs pa /
NK101(de)004:2559: grangs can pa rang bzhin dang shes rig la sgro 'dogs pa /
NK101(de)004:2560: gcer bu pa du ma ro gcig la sgro 'dogs pa dang zhi las /
NK101(de)004:2562: rig pa gzung 'dzin sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2563: rang gi rig pa gzung 'dzin gnyis las grol ba
NK101(de)004:2564: yi rtag gcig bde ba rang dbang can gyi bdag
NK101(de)004:2565: ste / bdag de la gzugs med pas dngos po yod pa las grol zhing /
NK101(de)004:2566: bdag ni yod pas dngos po med pa las kyang
NK101(de)004:2567: grol ba tsam du gnas pas blang ba dang dora
NK101(de)004:2568: ba gnyis dang bral bar 'dod do //
NK101(de)004:2569: de yang ldog pa bems po las log pa dang
NK101(de)004:2570: bcas par shes pa'i rgyud du rang blo la snang
NK101(de)004:2571: ba'i rig pa de la nga bdag tu 'dzin pa
NK101(de)004:2572: dang bcas par 'dod pa de las blang dor gnyis
NK101(de)004:2573: dang brala nas dngos por gyur pa dang dngos po
NK101(de)004:2574: med pa las grol te gnyis ka min par smra
NK101(de)004:2575: na / so so'i skye ba'ang byang chub de nyid yin par shin tu 'thad par 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)004:2577: las las thams cad sogs rkang pa lngas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2578: yang ther zug pa la lasa 'dod pa ni /
NK101(de)004:2579: snod bcud thams cad rdul phra rab 'dus 'dus pa las grub par 'dod do //
NK101(de)004:2580: de yang rdul gnyis bar med par 'byar ba la yan lag can gyi rdzas dang /
NK101(de)004:2581: de gnyis 'byar ba la rdzas gzhan zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)004:2582: de yi rdul phran ni rtag la rags pa yan
NK101(de)004:2583: lag can ni rtag pa min te mi rtag par
NK101(de)004:2584: 'dod cing / snying gi dkyil na sems can thams
NK101(de)004:2585: cad la bdag ces bya ba byed pa po rang
NK101(de)004:2586: dbang thob pa de dag kyang rdul las grub pa
NK101(de)004:2587: shes sbyangs pa dang 'dra ba la sogs par 'dod
NK101(de)004:2588: de gzhan yang tshig drug gi 'dod pa sbyar ro
NK101(de)004:2589: 'dod cing / // 'dir rdul las grub pa'i bdag
NK101(de)004:2590: ni shes pa med pa'i bems po la yon tan
NK101(de)004:2591: gyi chas rdul du 'dod pa yin gyi /
NK101(de)004:2592: thogs pa dang bcas pa'i rdul la go bar mi bya'o //
NK101(de)004:2593: de yang rdul phra mo nyid phrad ma phrad dang
NK101(de)004:2594: bltas ma bltas dang ring thung gi phyogs chas gzhigs
NK101(de)004:2595: na cha med kyi rdzas su ma grub pas yon
NK101(de)004:2596: tan dang la sogas zhes las dang spyi bye brag
NK101(de)004:2597: 'du ba rnams kyi tha snyad spangs te don la'ang
NK101(de)004:2600: la las yon tan sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2602: rdul mun snying stobs kyi yon tan gsum gyi rang
NK101(de)004:2603: bzhin cha mnyam pa ni gtso bo ste de nyid
NK101(de)004:2604: rtag par 'dod la rgyu yi dus na'ang 'bras bu
NK101(de)004:2605: gnas te rdzogs par 'dod pa yin no //
NK101(de)004:2606: grub mtha' de la yang sgrub byed kyi tshad ma yod pa ma yin la /
NK101(de)004:2607: dug gsum gyi rang bzhin ni mi rtag pa yin
NK101(de)004:2608: zhing rgyu rkyen dang bcas par ni sngar chad lta'i
NK101(de)004:2609: skabs su bshad pa nyid do //
NK101(de)004:2610: der ma zad rgyu yin pa ru khas blangs nas
NK101(de)004:2611: 'bras bu rdzogs par brjod pa ni rang tshiga gis
NK101(de)004:2612: rang gi 'dod pa bsal ba yina pas na blun
NK101(de)004:2613: ba'i ngaga tu rig par bya'o //
NK101(de)004:2615: kha cig rdzas gcig sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2616: yang kha cig gi 'dod pa ni /
NK101(de)004:2617: nor bu gzi'i bdag nyid ltar rdzas gcig nyid kyang kun gyi dngosa gzhi can yin la /
NK101(de)004:2618: 'dod pas bcings te nges par smra ba mu stegs
NK101(de)004:2619: kyi lta ba sum bargya drug cu rtsa gsum lasa
NK101(de)004:2620: grol te khyu machaga gi mdoga risa ltas gyur pa
NK101(de)004:2621: 'di nyid rtogs nas loga pa'i spyod pa me lnga
NK101(de)004:2622: brten pa la sogs pa la spyad pas sngar byas
NK101(de)004:2623: kyi sdig sgrib rnams dag par 'dod do //
NK101(de)004:2624: de yang las dang rtog mthun gyi snang ba'i rdzas
NK101(de)004:2625: gcig nyid rdzas kun gyi dngos gzhi min te dbang
NK101(de)004:2626: po'i mngona sum dang 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:2627: zhes pa'i tshad mas kho'i 'dod pa bsal ba dang /
NK101(de)004:2628: gzhan yang sgrub byed kyi tshad ma gang yang ma grub pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2629: rtag pa rang byung gi thams cad mkhyen pa dbang
NK101(de)004:2630: phyug nyid kyis thams cad kyi rang rgyu sngon song
NK101(de)004:2631: med par 'dod pa'i tha snyad spangsa te don yang
NK101(de)004:2633: des na rang bzhin spros bral mnyam pa nyid kyi nyams ni 'thad bar nges te /
NK101(de)004:2635: yang na rkang pa'i 'di nyid bka' rgyud 'di yi
NK101(de)004:2636: ring lugs ltar rang bzhin spros bral mnyam pa nyid
NK101(de)004:2637: kyi nyams pa'i 'thad par nges te /
NK101(de)004:2638: rtag mtha' la mi gnas pas so //
NK101(de)004:2639: zhes su 'grel kyang rung bar mngon no //
NK101(de)004:2640: gnyis pa rtsol bas 'khrul ba theg rim rnam brgyad bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:2643: don bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:2645: 'jug pa'i sgo brgyad sogs rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2646: de la blo dang mos pa'i rim pa ltar so
NK101(de)004:2647: sor 'jug pa'i sgo yi theg pa brgyad kyi 'khor
NK101(de)004:2648: lo de la / spang bya dang gnyen po lhan
NK101(de)004:2649: cig tu mi gnas pas 'gal bar bltas te spong
NK101(de)004:2650: bar 'dod pa nyan rang byang sems gsum dang /
NK101(de)004:2651: bdag gcig par 'brel ba'i stobs kyis sgrub par 'dod
NK101(de)004:2652: pa sngags phyi nang gi sde lnga dang brgyad do
NK101(de)004:2654: 'gal bar bltas te spang ba mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum dang /
NK101(de)004:2655: 'brel bar bltas te sgrub pa gsang sngags kyi theg pa sde lnga bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2659: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa gsum las /
NK101(de)004:2661: dang po bka' yi sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2662: de yang 'gal spong gsum gyi dang po ston pa
NK101(de)004:2663: sangs rgyas kyi bka' yi gzhi 'dzin pa nyan thos
NK101(de)004:2665: 'gro ba rigs drug dang log pa gsum gyi zhen
NK101(de)004:2666: pa rtags kyi snang ba ni phyin ci log pa
NK101(de)004:2667: yin te / so so'i skye bo dang mu stegs kyi gang zag gi bdag mi gnas pas so //
NK101(de)004:2668: zhes 'gogs shing chos kyi bdag tsam ma khegs pas lhag ste yod par lta ba ni /
NK101(de)004:2669: phyi gzung bar bya ba'i yul rdul phra rab don dam pa rdul du grub la /
NK101(de)004:2670: nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cig ma yang de ltar don dam du yod de /
NK101(de)004:2671: de dag bcom gzhigs kyis mi gnod pas so //
NK101(de)004:2672: lam sdug kun 'gog lam gyi 'phags pa'i bden pa
NK101(de)004:2673: bzhi la nges par brten nas 'bras bu sgrub pa'i
NK101(de)004:2675: de yang rdul phra mo phyogs chas gzhigs nas bzung ba ma grub cing /
NK101(de)004:2676: de 'dzin pa'i yan lag sems dang sems byung skad
NK101(de)004:2677: cig ma'ang dus kyi chas spangs pa yin pas mi
NK101(de)004:2679: de las byung ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2680: spyir nyan thos de la brten pa las bye brag
NK101(de)004:2681: gi khyad par du byung ba srid pa tha ma'i
NK101(de)004:2682: dus su dge bshes la mi ltos par rang gi
NK101(de)004:2683: ye shes kyis rtogs pa cana te /
NK101(de)004:2684: des phyi nang gi rten 'brel gyi 'byung ldog sgyu
NK101(de)004:2685: ma dang mig yor ltar rtogs pa la brten pasa
NK101(de)004:2686: na gzung yul gzugs chos bco lnga las gcig rnam
NK101(de)004:2687: par rig byed min gzugs ma gtogs par gzhan bcu
NK101(de)004:2688: bzhi po rten 'brel tu rtogs te rdul phran nyid
NK101(de)004:2689: ma grub par lta ba can la /
NK101(de)004:2690: nang 'dzin pa'i yan lag sems dang sems byung rnams
NK101(de)004:2691: skad cig mar nges par grub pas bden par lta
NK101(de)004:2692: ba'o // de yang gzung ba'i yul bden par yod
NK101(de)004:2693: pa min kyang de la 'dzin pa'i yan lag ni
NK101(de)004:2694: nges par yod par lta na /
NK101(de)004:2695: yul med pa'i shes pa nges gang la nges par
NK101(de)004:2696: 'dzin te dper na gdung rgyud chad pa'i sras bzhin
NK101(de)004:2697: du rigs pas 'thad pa'i 'dzin pa ni yod pa
NK101(de)004:2698: ma yin no // gsum pa ni /
NK101(de)004:2699: nar son pa yis sogs tshigs bcad gsum dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2700: lta ba bdag med gnyis ka rtogs shing spyod pa
NK101(de)004:2701: gzhan don la zhugs pas lta spyod nar son pa'i
NK101(de)004:2702: theg pa chen po yis ni /
NK101(de)004:2703: gzung ba rdul dang 'dzin pa skad cig ma'i chos kyis bdag kyang spangsa la /
NK101(de)004:2704: dngos por snang ba'i rnam pa la rtag pa dang
NK101(de)004:2705: bden pas stong pa ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK101(de)004:2706: yin la / don dam par spros pa thams cad
NK101(de)004:2707: yongs su zhi ba yin pas dngos po rnams kyi
NK101(de)004:2708: rang bzhin gang du'ang ma grub par 'dod cing /
NK101(de)004:2709: de ltar gang gis phye na yul can blo 'khrul
NK101(de)004:2710: ma 'khrul dang yul dngos po dang des stong pas
NK101(de)004:2711: rnam pa gnyis su phye ba'o //
NK101(de)004:2712: de yang dngos po rnams don dam par ranga bzhin med par bden na /
NK101(de)004:2713: blos brtags pa 'khrul pa'i rnam pa yul kun rdzob
NK101(de)004:2714: la brten pa'i sa lam phar phyin rnams kyis ci
NK101(de)004:2715: zhig bya ste / 'khrul ba yin pas so //
NK101(de)004:2716: gal te 'khrul ba yin kyang yang dag pa'i kun
NK101(de)004:2717: rdzob kyis 'bras bu thob pa'i don byed nus pas
NK101(de)004:2718: dang du blang bya yin no zhe na /
NK101(de)004:2719: de ltar na smig rgyus kyang skom pa sel ba'i don byed nus par thal /
NK101(de)004:2720: don la 'khrul par mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:2723: khyod kyis don dam pa'i bden pa shes bya'i gshis
NK101(de)004:2724: rang bzhin med par 'dod pas na stong pa byang
NK101(de)004:2725: chub kyi lta bar song ba de kun rdzob 'khrul
NK101(de)004:2726: pa la brten pas chad lta de las bzlog tu
NK101(de)004:2727: btub bzhig gam ci zhig yin /
NK101(de)004:2728: dper na chu brgal ba'i mi gru la zhugs pa
NK101(de)004:2729: rnams kyis gru'i thag pa la lag pas zana pas
NK101(de)004:2730: na / gru zhig pas mi 'jigas so zhes zer
NK101(de)004:2731: ba ltar 'dir yang kun brtags 'khrul pa la brten
NK101(de)004:2732: pas chad ltas mi 'jigs par 'dod pa ni de
NK101(de)004:2734: gal te sngar yod phyis med chad lta yin la /
NK101(de)004:2735: ye nas stong pas chad pa mi 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK101(de)004:2736: gdod nas dngos po yod par ma grub pa de
NK101(de)004:2737: don du bden par 'dod pa nyid stong pa phyang
NK101(de)004:2738: chad min na gzhan gyi gtan tshigs cis zhes ci
NK101(de)004:2739: yis phyang chad pa yana te khyad par cung zad
NK101(de)004:2740: kyang med do // gnyis pa 'brel bas bltas te
NK101(de)004:2741: sgrub pa gsang sngags sde lnga'i theg pa bshad pa
NK101(de)004:2742: la dmigs pa'i khyad par gyis bsgyur te sgrub pa
NK101(de)004:2743: kyang med do // dang / thabs shes kyi khyad
NK101(de)004:2744: par gyis dbang du byas te sgrub pa gnyis las
NK101(de)004:2745: kyang med do // dang / / dang po la /
NK101(de)004:2750: 'brel sgrub phyi gsum zhes pas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2751: 'brel bas sgrub pa lnga la bsgyur te sgrub pa ni /
NK101(de)004:2752: gsang sngags phyi pa rnam pa gsum mo //
NK101(de)004:2759: kun rdzob sogs rkang pa phyed lngas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2760: de dag gi dang po kri ya pa'i 'dod pa la /
NK101(de)004:2761: kun rdzob tu mtho 'jam rtsub pa la sogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:2762: snang ba rnams de bzhin gshegs pa dang pad ma
NK101(de)004:2763: dang rdo rje'i rigs gsum gyi lha yi dal yin
NK101(de)004:2764: la ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa tha dad
NK101(de)004:2765: bzang ngan rje bo dang 'bangs kyi tshul 'dra zhing
NK101(de)004:2766: / spyod pa dang rdzas gtsang mas 'bras bu grub la /
NK101(de)004:2767: don dam du spros pa'i mtha' bzhi'i dri ma dag pa yi chos nyid du 'dod do //
NK101(de)004:2768: de yang don dam dag par bden pa la spyod
NK101(de)004:2769: pa khrus dang gtsang sbra bya dgos pas lta spyod
NK101(de)004:2770: ya cha ni 'khrul pa yin no //
NK101(de)004:2772: khye bel 'dod pas sogs tshigs bcad gcig gi bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2773: khye bel ltar lta spyod ma nges pa'i u pa
NK101(de)004:2774: ya'i 'dod pa ni gong 'og gnyis ka ltar bzhed
NK101(de)004:2775: pas don dam par stong pa nyid du lta la
NK101(de)004:2776: / kun rdzob tu snang ba rnams yul dang yul
NK101(de)004:2777: can nam bya byed gang rung bsdus pa'i rigs bzhi
NK101(de)004:2778: lha'i dal te ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa
NK101(de)004:2779: dpon g.yog gi tshul du tha dad bzang ngan du
NK101(de)004:2780: / lta zhing / kri ya pa ltar las dang bya ba spyod cing /
NK101(de)004:2781: yo ga pa ltar lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin te gnyis kyis mthu las 'bras bu sgrub pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2782: de yang snga ma kri ya pa dang phyi ma
NK101(de)004:2783: yo ga pa gnyis kyi lta spyod la skyon brjod
NK101(de)004:2784: pa'i rjes su 'di la'ang gnod do //
NK101(de)004:2786: rnal 'byor pa ni sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2787: rnal 'byor pa yi lta ba ni kun rdzob tu
NK101(de)004:2788: snang ba'i rnam pa 'di dag rigs lnga lha'i dal
NK101(de)004:2789: du gsal na ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa
NK101(de)004:2790: grogs po'i tshul du tha dad dang bzang ngan mnyam
NK101(de)004:2791: par lta la / don dam par rnam par snang
NK101(de)004:2792: mdzad chen por stong pa nyid phyogs ris bral bar
NK101(de)004:2793: rtogsa nas bsam gtan gyi yan lag gzhi stong pa
NK101(de)004:2794: par lta la / / gdan zla ba /
NK101(de)004:2797: sku yongs rdzogs kyi mngon par byang chub pa lnga dang /
NK101(de)004:2798: dbang byin rlabs ting nge 'dzin dang mtshad pa'i cho
NK101(de)004:2799: 'phrul bzhi ste dgu dang ldan pa'i sgo nas lha
NK101(de)004:2800: bsgoms pas 'bras bu stug po bkod pa'i sangs rgyas
NK101(de)004:2802: de yang don dam par rnam par snang mdzad chen
NK101(de)004:2803: po la phyogs ris med pa yin na yang kun
NK101(de)004:2804: rdzob tu dgongs rgyud tha dad gyur la rigs lnga
NK101(de)004:2805: phyogs ris dang bcas pa yin nam ci ltar 'dod
NK101(de)004:2806: / des na bden gnyis res 'jog gi bsam gtan
NK101(de)004:2807: gyis 'bras bu gcig tu sgrub par 'dod pa ni
NK101(de)004:2808: dper na tsha reg dang grang reg gi nus pa
NK101(de)004:2809: gcig tu bsdus nas gtso sreg phyogs gcig tu sgrub
NK101(de)004:2812: phyi nas don grub sogs rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2813: rang gi sems las phyi rol nas ye shes pa
NK101(de)004:2814: la bsgrub bya'i don gyi dngos grub len te nang
NK101(de)004:2815: gi chos nyid du 'dod pa min pas /
NK101(de)004:2816: spyod pa dam rdzas la mi spyod cing dam tshig
NK101(de)004:2817: mnyam par mi srung ba la sogs pas nang pa
NK101(de)004:2818: min pa de tsam la gsang sngags phyi par 'dod
NK101(de)004:2819: pa yin no // gnyis pa thabs shes kyi khyad par gyis dbang du byas te sgrub pa la /
NK101(de)004:2821: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2823: nang gnyis zhes pas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2824: nanga pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la rnam grangs gnyis kyis bstan pa las /
NK101(de)004:2827: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK101(de)004:2828: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2830: rnal 'byor chen po sogs rkang pa phyed dang bcas
NK101(de)004:2831: pa'i tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan
NK101(de)004:2832: te / de la gsang sngags nang gi rgyud rnal
NK101(de)004:2833: 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga pa dag gi
NK101(de)004:2834: te / bzhed pa ni / lta bas snang stong
NK101(de)004:2835: zung 'jug gi don de gsal bar rtogs na sgom
NK101(de)004:2836: pa cho ga lnga dang sngags kyi yan lag lngas
NK101(de)004:2837: lha bskyed pa'i thabs kyi rnal 'byor la rtsol ba
NK101(de)004:2838: gtsor zhes gtso bor byas te bsgoms pas brtan pa
NK101(de)004:2839: te / bzhed pa ni / na / shes rab
NK101(de)004:2840: rdzogs pa'i rim pa mi rtog pa'i don la ngang
NK101(de)004:2842: de yang lta ba dbyer med du 'adda pa dang bcas par gyur la /
NK101(de)004:2843: sgom pa bskyed rdzogs kyi rtsol ba can du gyur pa yin na /
NK101(de)004:2844: gnas lugs phyogs med kyi ngang du gnas par 'dod kyang de'i don dang 'gal ba kho na'o //
NK101(de)004:2846: rjes su rnal 'byor sogs tshig bcad gnyis rkang gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2847: de nas gsang chen rjes su rnal 'byor a nu yo ga pa rnams kyi 'dod ba ni /
NK101(de)004:2848: yul du snang ba thams cad kun tu bzang mo
NK101(de)004:2849: ye ji bzhin pa'i chos kyi dbyingsa su gnas la
NK101(de)004:2850: / yul can rig pa kun tu bzang po rang
NK101(de)004:2851: bzhin 'od gsal gyi ye shes su lhun gyis grub
NK101(de)004:2852: pas de gnyis gdod ma nas dbyer med chen por
NK101(de)004:2853: 'adu ba dang 'bral ba mada pa'i sras rtsa ba
NK101(de)004:2854: byang chub kyi dkyil 'khor du nges te /
NK101(de)004:2855: ma h+aa'i gnyis med du 'dzin pa las grol nas bad ba chen po'i sku ru 'dod la /
NK101(de)004:2856: de ltar rtogs nas rgyu ni snang ba rnams dbyings
NK101(de)004:2857: su bsgom pa las 'bras bu ni dran rtog thams
NK101(de)004:2858: cad ye shes nyid du 'char bar 'gyur zhing /
NK101(de)004:2859: spyod pa dang dam tshig la sogs pa'i rkyen la rag las par 'dod pa'o //
NK101(de)004:2860: de yang lta ba bde chen gyi phyogs ris dang
NK101(de)004:2861: bcus shing sgom pa rgyu dbyings dang 'bras bu ye
NK101(de)004:2862: shes cana te / des na bde chena kyang tshig
NK101(de)004:2863: brjod tsam las mtshan nyid pa dngos su rtogs pa
NK101(de)004:2864: dang bral bas shin tu mthar phyin te rtsol ba
NK101(de)004:2865: med par ma bcos pa'i don la rnal mar 'byor
NK101(de)004:2867: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK101(de)004:2868: rdo rje gling phug sogs rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2870: lhun grub phyogs med ma rtogs pas //
NK101(de)004:2871: lta ba'i 'dod gzhung du mar byung //
NK101(de)004:2872: blo dang chos su ma 'dres pas //
NK101(de)004:2873: mnyam nyid lta la phyogs su zhen //
NK101(de)004:2874: kun rig shes pa ma skyes pas //
NK101(de)004:2875: yul med gcig pa ris su gcod //
NK101(de)004:2876: rang byung phyogs med ma shar bas //
NK101(de)004:2877: mun pa'i klong na tshod kyis 'jal //
NK101(de)004:2878: zhes gsungs pa ltar theg pa'i rim pa brgyad po
NK101(de)004:2879: de dag kyang snying po rnal ma'i theg pa 'di
NK101(de)004:2880: la bsgrun na / dper na rda rja gling phug gi rked pa na /
NK101(de)004:2881: snying po med pas chu shing gi rtsa ba na
NK101(de)004:2882: gnas pa'i ma he mo de zho skyel du 'ong
NK101(de)004:2883: yang de'i mar bcud la snying po snum pa tsam
NK101(de)004:2884: las med pa ltar du rang sa thob kyang mthar
NK101(de)004:2885: phyin par nus pa ma yin te /
NK101(de)004:2887: ma bcos ci yang ma yin la //
NK101(de)004:2888: cir yang 'dzin pa'i sems kyis brtags //
NK101(de)004:2889: bgrod med 'bras bu lhun grub la //
NK101(de)004:2890: lam brgyad bgrod pas bgrod med bslad //
NK101(de)004:2892: de'i tshul ni lta ba'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:2893: chos kun phyogs grol kun gsal rang grol kyang //
NK101(de)004:2894: ma rtogs yul min rkyen bral rang bzung bas //
NK101(de)004:2895: tha dad snang zhing nyon mongs las kyis dkrugs //
NK101(de)004:2896: zhen drug 'khor lo sdug bsngal d+r+wa bar tshud //
NK101(de)004:2897: spang 'gegs spyod sgyur rtsol sgrub rgyu 'bras kyis //
NK101(de)004:2898: sdug bsngal rtsol ba'i nad kyis 'khor ba las //
NK101(de)004:2900: des na snying po rnal ma'i don de ji bzhin
NK101(de)004:2901: du ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis 'khrul pa'i phyogs su
NK101(de)004:2904: gsang sngags gcig la khyer so dgu //
NK101(de)004:2905: de yang rnam pa tsam du snang //
NK101(de)004:2906: rim pa dgu yi ngo bo yis //
NK101(de)004:2907: rang snang ye shes don ma rtogs //
NK101(de)004:2910: rang rig mngon sum mthong med pas //
NK101(de)004:2911: rim dgu'i 'dod pas grol ba min //
NK101(de)004:2912: chos nyid zad cing mthar phyin pas //
NK101(de)004:2913: sku gsum lam gyi snang ba'o //
NK101(de)004:2915: 'di'i rim pa dgu la 'jig rten pa'i theg pa'am
NK101(de)004:2916: yang na a ti yo ga thun mong gi skor
NK101(de)004:2917: la'ang gsungs so // 'on kyang nges don gyi mdo
NK101(de)004:2918: dang rgyud sde'i zab don dngos su rtogs na 'di'i
NK101(de)004:2919: don la shugs kyis 'jug pa yin pas mthar thug
NK101(de)004:2920: gi don la dgongs pa'i gnad gcig 'bab pa kho
NK101(de)004:2921: la'ang gsungs so // na'o // le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK101(de)004:2922: rin po che gter gtad pa las /
NK101(de)004:2923: gnas lugs ji bzhin du ma rtogs par de ma
NK101(de)004:2924: yin pa la der 'dzin pas 'khrul pa'i rnam grangs
NK101(de)004:2925: bstan pa'i le'u ste skabs gnyis pa legs par bshad
NK101(de)004:2926: pa'o // gsum pa de ltar gnas pa'i don nyid
NK101(de)004:2927: lta bas mngon sum du rtogs te gter chen rang
NK101(de)004:2929: dpe dang bcas te chos nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba rang ngo sprod tshul mdor bstan /
NK101(de)004:2930: de'i rang bzhin man ngag tshad ma'i brda thabs la brten nas rgyas par bshad /
NK101(de)004:2931: de ltar rang mtshan mthong bas lta ba'i gdengs tshad ngos bzung /
NK101(de)004:2932: rtogs pa de nyid gzhan las 'phags pa'i nges gsang gi khyad par bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)004:2934: rgyal po gsal rgyal sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2935: dper na yul ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal
NK101(de)004:2936: du grags pa'i ngang rgyud bzang zhing nges pa de
NK101(de)004:2937: la rang gi bsod nams kyi mthus pa yab rtsibs
NK101(de)004:2938: kyis 'phur tshangs byin zhes bya bas longs spyod mi
NK101(de)004:2939: zad pa'i gter chen po gtad pa ltar du /
NK101(de)004:2940: bka' drin can gyi bla ma dam pas sems kyi
NK101(de)004:2941: chos nyid la yon tan mi zad pa'i rang gi
NK101(de)004:2942: gter gnas pa de legs par rnyed nas skal ldan
NK101(de)004:2943: la gtad par mdzad pa ni gang zhe na /
NK101(de)004:2944: le'u dang por bshad pa'i shes bya re zhig brgyad la ni /
NK101(de)004:2945: zhes pas shes bya'i rnam grangs tshogs brgyad du snang ba de la /
NK101(de)004:2946: chos nyid rtogs pa'i don la mi slu bas tshad
NK101(de)004:2947: ma gsum gyi dang pos zhes bya bral rdzogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:2948: lung gis yid ches par byas nas /
NK101(de)004:2949: de ltar gtan tshigs gsum gyis gzhigs te dpes mtshon
NK101(de)004:2950: pa dang rnam grangs gsum gyis spyi'i rnam pa rtogs
NK101(de)004:2951: par byas nas drod dang ldan par gyur pa na
NK101(de)004:2952: / bla ma mchog gis gsal byed rina chen snang
NK101(de)004:2953: ba'i gdams ngag snyan khung brgyud pas chos nyid rang
NK101(de)004:2954: gi mtshan nyid mngon sum du bstan te brda don
NK101(de)004:2957: tshad ma gsum gyis mtshon tshul spyir bshad /
NK101(de)004:2958: rin chen brgyud pas mtshon tshul bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2963: de gsum gyis don rtogs tshul bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)004:2965: skal dman rnams thabs chen brgyud pa'i lung gis ji ltar mtshams par drang tshul /
NK101(de)004:2966: skal ldan la bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung gis rang mtshan nges par ston tshul gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:2968: skal zhan dad can sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2969: de yang gdul bya blo dang skal ba zhan cing
NK101(de)004:2970: dad pa can gyi slob bu de la thabs chen
NK101(de)004:2971: brgyud pa'i lung theg ba brgyad po blo dang gang
NK101(de)004:2972: 'tsham par bstan pas brgyud nas drang ba ni /
NK101(de)004:2973: rjod byed kyi tshig dang brjod bya'i don mi mthun
NK101(de)004:2974: par don gzhan la dgongs pas brgyud nas 'dren pa'i
NK101(de)004:2975: bka' lung gi tshig sna tshogs su ston pa ste
NK101(de)004:2976: / dper byis pa g.yang sa las 'dren pa'i phyir
NK101(de)004:2977: du stag 'ong nor bu sbyin zer ba dang 'dra
NK101(de)004:2978: / ba'o // 'dir drang nges kyi khyad par ni /
NK101(de)004:2979: brjod bya gnas lugs sems kyi de kho na nyid la brgyud nas 'jug pa drang don /
NK101(de)004:2980: dngos su 'jug pa nges don yin gsungs /
NK101(de)004:2982: skal ldan bya bral sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:2983: gdul bya a ti'i skal ba dang ldan pa'i blo
NK101(de)004:2984: mchog mnga' ba de la bya bral rdzogs par ston
NK101(de)004:2985: pa'i lung zab mos bden cing nges pa'i don mtshon
NK101(de)004:2986: nas dngos su drang bar byed pa'i lung ni rnam
NK101(de)004:2988: gol sa shan 'byed par byed pa bram ze'i gzhung dang /
NK101(de)004:2989: rang gzhung la zlo ba rgyal po'i rgyud dang /
NK101(de)004:2990: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa man ngag gi
NK101(de)004:2991: rgyud dang gsum gyi tshig gis yid ches par bya
NK101(de)004:2992: ba ste / rin po che rgyan las /
NK101(de)004:2993: bram ze rtsa ba'i rgyu drug la //
NK101(de)004:2994: gol ba'i gzhi dang gol ba dngos //
NK101(de)004:2995: dngos 'dzin sun dbyung rang gzhung dang //
NK101(de)004:2997: de yang bkru bya gdong pa la //
NK101(de)004:2998: bkru rgyu dri ma ngos 'dzin ni //
NK101(de)004:3000: rigs gtsang mdangs gsal byed pa yin //
NK101(de)004:3001: yan lag rgyud sde bcu gsum drug /
NK101(de)004:3002: shan gyi chos su 'byung ba yin //
NK101(de)004:3003: rgyal po rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga la //
NK101(de)004:3004: la zla'i sa dang bzla rgyu byed //
NK101(de)004:3005: bzla ba'i thabs dang yon tan ni //
NK101(de)004:3006: mnga' ru bsdu ma bsdu rgyu dang //
NK101(de)004:3007: bsdu byed bsdu thabs yon tan dag /
NK101(de)004:3008: mnga' ris mgo nag rgyal po nyid //
NK101(de)004:3009: zhi ba'am drag pos longs spyod pa'o //
NK101(de)004:3010: gzhi dang snang grags byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:3011: lung rigs man ngag rang grol bas //
NK101(de)004:3012: bde ba chen por gsal ba yin //
NK101(de)004:3013: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK101(de)004:3014: mnga' ba'i rtsal du byung ba yin //
NK101(de)004:3015: yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga la //
NK101(de)004:3016: zhing dang sku dang thugs gsum las //
NK101(de)004:3017: yul dang lus dang yid byung bas //
NK101(de)004:3018: ston byed ngag tu rgyud gsum byung //
NK101(de)004:3019: yon tan cha las bcu bdun lnga //
NK101(de)004:3020: brgya rtsa lnga ru shar ba yin //
NK101(de)004:3021: man ngag rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga la //
NK101(de)004:3022: gnas lugs 'khrul tshul bstan pa'i thabs //
NK101(de)004:3023: goms par bya thabs spyir 'bras bu //
NK101(de)004:3024: gtso ru gang snon rnams lngar phye //
NK101(de)004:3025: yan lag bcu gnyis lngar byung ba //
NK101(de)004:3026: lus dang yan lag tshul yin no //
NK101(de)004:3028: gnyis pa gtan tshigs tshad ma la //
NK101(de)004:3029: ris med mnyam pa chen po'i gtan tshigs gsum gyis thig le nyag gcig tu sgrub pa dang /
NK101(de)004:3030: dbyings ye zung du 'jug pa'i gtan tshigs mchog gis gzung 'dzin rang grol du sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:3035: ngang dang rang bzhin bdag nyid che //
NK101(de)004:3036: zhes rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3037: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems zang thal du dngos
NK101(de)004:3038: su ston pa'i tshad ma'i rigs pa mthar thug pa
NK101(de)004:3039: ni / rang rig pa ngang gis skye ba med par gsal ba dang /
NK101(de)004:3040: rang bzhin rig pa 'gag med du cir yang snang ba dang /
NK101(de)004:3041: bdag nyid che'am chen po snang stong tha dad med par gtan la 'bebs pa dang gsum ste /
NK101(de)004:3043: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni //
NK101(de)004:3044: dman pa'i sems kyis mi rtogs te //
NK101(de)004:3045: gtan tshigs gsum gyis shes par bya //
NK101(de)004:3046: ngang ni rig pa gsal ba ste //
NK101(de)004:3047: rang bzhin rig pa cir yang snang //
NK101(de)004:3048: bdag nyid snang stong tha dad med //
NK101(de)004:3049: bsgrub bya dag gi rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:3050: 'khrul ba byang chub sems su shes //
NK101(de)004:3053: rang gsal ngang gi gtan tshigs /
NK101(de)004:3054: kun snang rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs /
NK101(de)004:3055: gnyis med bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs gsum las /
NK101(de)004:3057: ma g.yos mtshon pa sogs rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3058: de yang sna tshogs su snang yang gnas lugs las
NK101(de)004:3059: ma g.yos par mtshon pa ni rang gi gtan tshigs
NK101(de)004:3060: nyid yin te / de la mu mtha' cir yang
NK101(de)004:3061: snang bas don chos nyid cara yang grub pa min
NK101(de)004:3062: nyid yin te / te / des na mu matha'i
NK101(de)004:3063: phyogs gcig tu grub pa min pas mu mtha' phyogs
NK101(de)004:3064: gcig tu snang ba yang ma nges pa'i phyir rig
NK101(de)004:3065: pa mthas ma bsgribs gsal ba'o //
NK101(de)004:3066: de nyid dbang gi klong las rgyud drug rtog pa thams cad dang /
NK101(de)004:3067: mya ngan 'das pa rgyal ba'i thugs //
NK101(de)004:3068: ma lus bde chen rig pa'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:3069: ji bzhin ma bcos ngang du gsal //
NK101(de)004:3070: kun rdzogs spros pa med pa'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:3071: gcig 'dus ma lus kun gyi bdag /
