NK101(de)004:3072: rnam par rtog pa'i rgyu ba bral //
NK101(de)004:3073: dus gsum bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK101(de)004:3074: rtsol dang bral bas rgyun mi 'chad //
NK101(de)004:3075: rnam rtog mtshan ma ji snyed pa //
NK101(de)004:3076: ji bzhin mi 'gyur de nyid gsal //
NK101(de)004:3077: gnas 'gyur rgyal ba'i lung chen yin //
NK101(de)004:3080: ma nor bcos med sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3081: chos nyid ma nor bar bcos su med pa rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK101(de)004:3082: phyi yul du grub pa min la nang rig par yang rgya ma chad de /
NK101(de)004:3083: des na yul shes gnyis nang nas sems las skye ba min te rang snang nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:3084: de la mthar snang gi gzung 'dzin mi dmigs par
NK101(de)004:3085: ngo bo ye shes nyid rgyu rkyen med par rang
NK101(de)004:3086: snang ba yin pas phyi gzung ba'i yul mi spong
NK101(de)004:3087: nang 'adzana pa'i sems mi 'gegs te rig pa'i ye
NK101(de)004:3088: shes nyid rgyu rkyen la rag ma lasa par cir
NK101(de)004:3089: yang snang zhing nges med du gsal ba'o //
NK101(de)004:3090: des na ye shes gsang ba las //
NK101(de)004:3091: snang ba brtags par zhen mod kyang //
NK101(de)004:3092: ma bcos snang ba brtags pa min //
NK101(de)004:3093: rol pa sgyu ma lhun grub ste //
NK101(de)004:3094: rtsol med sgyu ma bde mchog yin //
NK101(de)004:3095: mi 'gyur rdo rje btsan po yin //
NK101(de)004:3096: ma bcos lhun grub chen po la //
NK101(de)004:3097: nges pa med pas gsang bar bshad //
NK101(de)004:3100: bdag nyid chen po sogs tshigs bcad gcig rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3101: ye bab rang rdzogs kyi bdag nyid chen po snang stong dbyer med kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK101(de)004:3102: snang ba bde ba chen po rtsol ba med pa dang /
NK101(de)004:3103: yul meda cing rang riga pa ngos gzung las 'das
NK101(de)004:3104: pa'i stong nyid dam pa gnyis gdod nas tha dad
NK101(de)004:3105: med par rtogs te chos thams cad byang chub kyi
NK101(de)004:3106: sems thig le nyag gcig tu shes pa la de
NK101(de)004:3107: las gzhan du snang ba dang bzang ngan gyi rtog
NK101(de)004:3108: pa thams cad dang bral bas bdag nyid chana po
NK101(de)004:3109: thog mtha' med pa'i gting gsal bya ba dang bral
NK101(de)004:3110: ba'i zang thal gcig tu gnas pa nyid ces tha
NK101(de)004:3111: snyad tsam du btagsa shing mtshon par mdzad pa yin
NK101(de)004:3112: te / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK101(de)004:3113: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK101(de)004:3114: thams cad byang chub sems su shes //
NK101(de)004:3115: gang ltar gnas kyang chos nyid do //
NK101(de)004:3118: ngang bdag nyid chen por gsal ba'i phyir na /
NK101(de)004:3120: gzhan yang rab tu bshad bya ba //
NK101(de)004:3121: sku yi mtshan nyid rab shes pas //
NK101(de)004:3123: sku yi rang bzhin yongs shes pas //
NK101(de)004:3124: gsal dang stong pa'i so mtshams zin //
NK101(de)004:3125: ngo bo shes pas stong par dag /
NK101(de)004:3126: ngang shes pas ni mi rtog skye //
NK101(de)004:3127: bdag nyid chen po shes pa yis //
NK101(de)004:3128: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rtsa ba gcod //
NK101(de)004:3129: de dag gis ni rang grol gdengs //
NK101(de)004:3130: byas pa med par thob par nges //
NK101(de)004:3131: zhes rig pa'i ye shes sku ru shar ba'i mtshan
NK101(de)004:3132: nyid la rang bzhin skye med mtha' grol gyi ngo
NK101(de)004:3133: bo phyogs med rang grol nyid du rgyud rang brtan
NK101(de)004:3134: par gnas pas bdag nyid chen por gyur pa med
NK101(de)004:3135: pa'i don to // gnyis pa dbyings ye zung du
NK101(de)004:3136: 'jug pa'i gtan tshigs mchog gis gzung 'dzin rang grol
NK101(de)004:3138: yul snang rlabs ltar sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3139: dbyings dang ye shes kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK101(de)004:3140: yul du snang ba rnams ni chu nyid rlabs su
NK101(de)004:3141: snang ba ltar rang snang gi yul dbyingsa nyid rnam
NK101(de)004:3142: par dag pa ni rgyu yin te /
NK101(de)004:3143: de las yul can rig pa mi rtog pa'i ye shes nyid 'bras bur shar bas /
NK101(de)004:3144: dbyings zhes rgyu dang ye shes zhes 'bras bu gnyis
NK101(de)004:3145: mtshan nyid mi gnyis te gcig tu 'dus pas gzung
NK101(de)004:3146: 'dzin gyi mtha' las rang grol ba'i bde ba chen
NK101(de)004:3147: po la / gzung 'dzin ma spangs thig le nyag
NK101(de)004:3148: gcig ma bsgrubs par gtan tshigs brten te bltas pas
NK101(de)004:3149: don chos nyid mjal bar 'gyur te /
NK101(de)004:3151: dbyings dang ye shes gtan tshigs ni //
NK101(de)004:3152: dbyings ni dag pa'i rgyu yin te //
NK101(de)004:3153: ye shes 'bras bu nyid du gsal //
NK101(de)004:3156: gsum pa mthun dpe tshad ma la //
NK101(de)004:3157: chos nyid dang mi mthun par 'khrul pa snang tshul gyi dpe dang /
NK101(de)004:3158: chos nyid dang mthun par rang snang phyogs med kyi dpe bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:3160: dper na thag pa sogs rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3161: de yang don dang mi mthun pa'i dpe ni /
NK101(de)004:3162: dpera na chos can blo 'khrul ba la thag pa sbrul du snang ba yang /
NK101(de)004:3163: gtan tshigs thaga pa'i mtshan nyid sbrul mina pas /
NK101(de)004:3164: sbrul 'dzin du skyes pa'i shes pa bden pa min te /
NK101(de)004:3165: zhes dam bca' ba ltar 'dir kyang da bzhin du
NK101(de)004:3166: skye lugs gsum du snang yang bden pa min no
NK101(de)004:3168: blo 'khrul pa la skye lugs gsum du snang ba chos can /
NK101(de)004:3169: der 'dzin gyi shes pa bden pa min te /
NK101(de)004:3170: don chos nyid kyi mtshan nyid skye lugs gsum du mi gnas pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:3171: dper na thag pa sbrul du 'dzin pa bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3174: mthun pa nam mkha' sogs rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3175: yon tan gyi ldog cha re res gnas lugs dang mthun pa yi dpe ni /
NK101(de)004:3176: nam mkha' dang rgya mtsho dang nor bu rin chen dbang gi rgyal po la sogas pa rnams te /
NK101(de)004:3178: nam mkha' rgya mtsho rin po che //
NK101(de)004:3179: sman dug 'byung ba nyi ma dang //
NK101(de)004:3180: gser bzhin phyogs med rgya che zab //
NK101(de)004:3181: mi rtog re skong rkyen gyis snang //
NK101(de)004:3182: rtsal snang gsal rkyen ma rag brtan //
NK101(de)004:3183: yon tan cha res kun kyang mthun //
NK101(de)004:3185: dpe de dag kyang don chos nyid kun mnyam gdal
NK101(de)004:3186: khyab chen po'i spyi'i phyogs kyi ldog cha 'gas te
NK101(de)004:3187: cha 'ga' res kun kyang mthun pa yin la /
NK101(de)004:3188: 'di dag las gzhan yang mu tig phreng ba las /
NK101(de)004:3189: de lta bu yi sems nyid ni //
NK101(de)004:3191: dgos pa tshang bas bang mdzod bzhin //
NK101(de)004:3192: gang bstan snang bas me long 'dra //
NK101(de)004:3193: dri med gsal bas shes sgong 'dra //
NK101(de)004:3194: snang ba sna tshogs za 'og gur //
NK101(de)004:3195: spro bsdu med pas khyung chen 'dra //
NK101(de)004:3196: lta ba'i rtsal rdzogs seng ge bzhin //
NK101(de)004:3197: gting rdzogs khyab pas rgya mtsho 'dra //
NK101(de)004:3198: rang byung grol bas nam mkha' bzhin //
NK101(de)004:3199: thams cad brten pas sa gzhi ltar //
NK101(de)004:3200: yul rnam kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK101(de)004:3201: zhes gsungs pa sogs dpe mang du 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3202: bzhi pa de gsum gyis don rtogs tshul ni /
NK101(de)004:3203: kun kyang spyi la rtogs pas gnas //
NK101(de)004:3205: de ltar lung dang gtan tshigs dpe yi tshad ma
NK101(de)004:3206: gsum po kun kyang don chos nyid rang bzhin gyi
NK101(de)004:3207: snang ba'i spyi yi rnam pa tsam la rtogs par
NK101(de)004:3208: byed pas shes byed kyi thabs dam pa nyid du
NK101(de)004:3210: gnyis pa rin chen brgyud pas mtshon tshul bye brag tu bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:3211: chu bo bzhin rdzogs kyi bla mas skal ldan la
NK101(de)004:3212: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid dngos su ston tshul
NK101(de)004:3213: mdor bstan / de nyid mtshan thabs kyi brda don
NK101(de)004:3214: zab gsang ngo sprod kyi man ngag rgyas par bshad
NK101(de)004:3215: mdor bstan / pa gnyis las / dang po ni /
NK101(de)004:3216: rang gi mtshan nyid sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3217: de nas chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid rang rig
NK101(de)004:3218: par rtogs pas rina chen brgyud pa'i gsal byed kyi
NK101(de)004:3219: nges pas mngon sum par shes pa yi thabs mchog
NK101(de)004:3220: bla na med pa ni ji lta bu yin zhe
NK101(de)004:3222: lung dang bla ma'i man ngag rig pa'i nyams //
NK101(de)004:3223: blo dang 'tsham tshad rgyud drang thabs lung gis //
NK101(de)004:3224: des mtshon bya bral rdzogs lung nyi khri ba //
NK101(de)004:3225: des mtshon mkha' khyab byang chub sems lung gis //
NK101(de)004:3226: skal ldan snod skyon bral na gtan la phebs //
NK101(de)004:3227: ston pa'i rigs su nges na nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)004:3228: de la yid ches dmigs nas gdams pas dgrol //
NK101(de)004:3229: dbang thob lung mkhyen gdams pa'i rig pa shar //
NK101(de)004:3230: rang gshis sgro skur bral grub bla ma la //
NK101(de)004:3231: skal ldan skyon bral rgyal sras slob ma des //
NK101(de)004:3232: dad mos gus pas zhus te thugs rjes gnang //
NK101(de)004:3233: yi ge dkyus dang snyan rgyud rang grol bas //
NK101(de)004:3234: nges par yid ches gdeng du phebs par bya //
NK101(de)004:3235: rig nyams sgro skur bsal la nges don gnas //
NK101(de)004:3236: snang grags byang chub sems su lhun grub pa //
NK101(de)004:3237: rigs pa bzhi yis sgro skur the tshom bsal //
NK101(de)004:3238: bsregs bcad brdar bas sa gser nges brtags ltar //
NK101(de)004:3239: chos nyid bya byed ltor shar 'thad pas sgrubs //
NK101(de)004:3241: rin po che phreng ba las /
NK101(de)004:3242: thun mong khyad par dbang rdzogs shing //
NK101(de)004:3243: lung gsum tshig gi brgyud pa can //
NK101(de)004:3244: rang grol man ngag bar ma chad //
NK101(de)004:3245: mngon sum grub pas yid ches pa'i //
NK101(de)004:3246: bla ma rin chen srog gi gzungs //
NK101(de)004:3247: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar dbang rgyud man ngag grub
NK101(de)004:3248: pa'i chu bo bzhi'i rgyun ma chad pa'i bla ma
NK101(de)004:3249: dam pa des / rgyal ba'i gdung 'tsho ba ba'i
NK101(de)004:3250: thugs sras a ti'i skal ba dang ldan pa'i slob
NK101(de)004:3252: kun gzhi'i chos nyid bag chags rnam par byang bar
NK101(de)004:3253: gnas bya de nyid tshogs bdun dang lhan cig tu
NK101(de)004:3254: ldan pas bag chags dang gcig tu bsres pa yi
NK101(de)004:3255: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi la /
NK101(de)004:3256: rtogs pa'i gdengas chen po thug phrad gsum gyis thig
NK101(de)004:3257: le nyag gcig tu bstan te brda sprod pa yin
NK101(de)004:3259: lta ba'i klong gi sngar gnyis par drangs pa'i 'phro las /
NK101(de)004:3260: ma 'dres 'khor ba'i chos la rab grol zhing //
NK101(de)004:3261: rdzogs pas 'das mtha' mi gnas dgrol bya'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:3262: dad tsam gang zag rjes 'brang lung tsam min //
NK101(de)004:3263: chos kyi rjes su tshad ma rnam gsum gyis //
NK101(de)004:3264: ma bcos ye gnas yul med rang gsal du //
NK101(de)004:3265: rtogs thabs lta bar kun 'dus de bstan bya'o //
NK101(de)004:3267: mngon sum snga ma gsum gyis ma 'dres sku gsum rang snang gi dgongs par ston pa dang /
NK101(de)004:3268: rnal 'byor mngon sum gyis yongs rdzogs dbyer med mnyam grol gyi dgongs par ston pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:3271: rmad byung gzhal yas spros bral ni //
NK101(de)004:3272: 'bar ba'i ye shes bde gshegs gsum //
NK101(de)004:3273: thug phrad nyid du bzhag pa ste //
NK101(de)004:3274: bla ma'i zhal nas shes par bya //
NK101(de)004:3278: bde gshegs gsum gyi skur ldan pa //
NK101(de)004:3279: rnam grol 'bras bu rang bzhag yin //
NK101(de)004:3280: gzhi nas ma g.yos rang bzhin grub //
NK101(de)004:3281: ces sogs gsungs pa la brten nas bshad na /
NK101(de)004:3282: dbang po'i mngon sum du sprul sku thug phrad kyis
NK101(de)004:3283: rnam pa sgyu ma lhun grub tu ngo sprad pa
NK101(de)004:3284: / yid kyi mngon sum du chos sku thug phrad
NK101(de)004:3285: kyis rang bzhin spros bral lhun grub tu ngo sprad
NK101(de)004:3286: / pa / rang rig mngon sum du longs sku
NK101(de)004:3287: thug phrad kyis mtshan nyid rang rig lhun grub tu
NK101(de)004:3288: ngo sprad pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:3290: mkhar chen sgo brgyad sogs tshigs bcad lnga dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3291: sngar bshad pa ltar mkhar chen po gcig la sgo brgyad yod pa las /
NK101(de)004:3292: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po lnga yi sgo rnams
NK101(de)004:3293: kyi phyi nang dbang po yul ston gyi bu mo
NK101(de)004:3294: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga ni 'dod pa'i
NK101(de)004:3295: yon tan sdug snyan zhim bro 'jam pa lnga bsnams
NK101(de)004:3296: nas cha lugs mdzes mas de la stob par byed
NK101(de)004:3297: la / sgo de'i nang na sgo srung rnam shes lnga po la /
NK101(de)004:3298: re re la'ang bu sems las byung ba bzhi bzhi
NK101(de)004:3299: yod pa las bu phu bo ni rtogs pa'i gdengs
NK101(de)004:3300: chen po mnga' ba'i rgyal po ma 'khrul bar tshugs
NK101(de)004:3302: snang la 'dzin pa med pas sgyu ma ma btsal bas lhun grub kyi yul la rol ba'o //
NK101(de)004:3303: bu gnyis pa ni brama za ltar ltog pa rtsing
NK101(de)004:3304: ba can te gtsang sme dang re dogs kyi yul
NK101(de)004:3305: la rol lo // bu gsum pa ni rig byed
NK101(de)004:3306: bzo mkhan ltar dpyod pas shes pa zhib pa ste
NK101(de)004:3307: nyes legs dang mdzes sdug gi yul la rol lo
NK101(de)004:3308: la rol lo // // bu bzhi pa ni zhal che gcod mkhan ltar tha snyad 'dogs te /
NK101(de)004:3309: zhal che gcod pa tshong dus kyi yul la rol bar byed do //
NK101(de)004:3310: de la rtogs pa'i rang sa bzung ba'i man ngag gi thabs shes na /
NK101(de)004:3311: ma 'khrul bar gnas pa'i phu bos nu bo gsum
NK101(de)004:3312: po dabnga du byas nas bsgral du btub ste ji
NK101(de)004:3313: ltar btub na / nga ni tshugs na gnas pa'i rgyal po yin na /
NK101(de)004:3314: nu bo khyed gsum dag kyang ji ltar de bzhin
NK101(de)004:3315: du pha rnam pa sgyu mar gacaga pa yin pas
NK101(de)004:3316: / las thabs rtog dpyod tha snyad 'dogs pa gsum
NK101(de)004:3317: la ma gnas shig dang nga bzhin du 'gyur ro
NK101(de)004:3318: / // des sgo gtan mtshan mar 'dzin pa bcag
NK101(de)004:3319: ste 'khor sa rigs drug gi yul lnga'i snang ba
NK101(de)004:3320: mthar 'dzin dang bcas pa phyags nas rang snang ba
NK101(de)004:3321: bde bas dbul ba'i dri ma sel byed bzhi cha'i
NK101(de)004:3322: nor bu chu dwangs sprul sku mngon sum gyis blangs
NK101(de)004:3323: nas longs spyod de dkyil 'khor lnga ye shes bzo
NK101(de)004:3324: las byas pa stag gi rgyal mtshan nyid gsal bar
NK101(de)004:3325: / // btsugs so // de'i tshe sgo lnga'i yul
NK101(de)004:3326: lnga rnams rgyal po'i zhes rgyal po chen po snang
NK101(de)004:3327: la mi rtogs pa'i mnga' ru bzhes te /
NK101(de)004:3328: de las gzhan pa'i 'bangs med pas rgyal po'i tha
NK101(de)004:3329: snyad kyang rang sar grol nas yul lnga'i 'khrul snang
NK101(de)004:3330: log pas ye shes kyi rang 'od ngos bzung med
NK101(de)004:3331: par rol pa sgyu ma bde mchog tu gsal ba
NK101(de)004:3332: yin te / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK101(de)004:3333: bzhi cha'i rig pa rang gsal de /
NK101(de)004:3334: dus gsum bde gshegs snying po yin //
NK101(de)004:3335: gsum ldan 'khor ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3336: dus tshod bla ma'i zhal las shes //
NK101(de)004:3337: gzhan du'ang de bzhin kho na yin //
NK101(de)004:3340: snang la mi rtog don la ma 'khrul bar //
NK101(de)004:3341: sgo lngas yul lnga rnam pa sgyu mar bcad //
NK101(de)004:3342: sdug bsngal rtsol sgrub bcas tshe nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)004:3343: sprul sku ma btsal gnas par 'thad pas grub //
NK101(de)004:3346: dbang po pad+ma rgyal po'i thugs //
NK101(de)004:3347: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)004:3348: mthong ba log pa gzhan 'dod kyang //
NK101(de)004:3349: sprul sku dang po gzhan las min //
NK101(de)004:3350: kun bzang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa nyid //
NK101(de)004:3351: snang ba'i tshul gyis gzung byas la //
NK101(de)004:3352: dran pa'i tshul gyi nyams su blangs //
NK101(de)004:3354: rin chen gsum gyi brtag pa las //
NK101(de)004:3355: thabs kyi bye brag shes gyur na //
NK101(de)004:3356: thog ma'i pad+ma ji bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3358: de nas rgyal ba'i gral du gnas //
NK101(de)004:3359: thugs rje kun ldan rnyog pas bslad //
NK101(de)004:3360: dwangs ma dus gsum 'gyur ba med //
NK101(de)004:3364: dbang po yul la gang snang ba //
NK101(de)004:3365: ye shes 'od du kun la gnas //
NK101(de)004:3366: bkra gsal gzugs kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NK101(de)004:3367: 'od gsal rang byung ngo mtshar che //
NK101(de)004:3368: brjod bral sgra yi dkyil 'khor la //
NK101(de)004:3369: rna ba'i ye shes rang bzhin gsal //
NK101(de)004:3370: rang bzhin sna tshogs dri dag la //
NK101(de)004:3371: ye shes gsal ba rang byung sems //
NK101(de)004:3372: mu kha ro yi dkyil 'khor la //
NK101(de)004:3373: lce yi ye shes ngo mtshar che //
NK101(de)004:3374: gsal ba reg bya'i rang bzhin la //
NK101(de)004:3375: shes rab lus kyi rang byung gnas //
NK101(de)004:3377: de ltar rtogs pa'i don la sel med pa des
NK101(de)004:3378: na rang snang thig le nyag gcig tu grol bas
NK101(de)004:3379: rang gdangs sgyu ma lhun grub ris med mnyam pa
NK101(de)004:3381: de bas na thig le nyag gcig ces pa'i nges tshig kyang /
NK101(de)004:3382: ye shes gsang ba rin po che sgron ma'i rgyud las /
NK101(de)004:3383: thig le mi 'gyur rang sems skye med yin //
NK101(de)004:3384: le ni gang la khyab mnyam pa nyid du gsal //
NK101(de)004:3385: nyag ni phra bas skal med spyod yul min //
NK101(de)004:3386: cig ni rang byung ye shes rang snang ngo //
NK101(de)004:3387: zhes dang byang chub sems yid skyobs kyi dngos po gnas lugs kyi yi ge las /
NK101(de)004:3388: gsang sngags gnas lugs thig le nyag gcig ste //
NK101(de)004:3389: kun bral kun dngos ci spangs ci ma spangs //
NK101(de)004:3390: thig ni mi g.yo mi 'gyur ma nor drang por spros dang bral //
NK101(de)004:3391: le ni kun dngos khyab bdal cir yang shar //
NK101(de)004:3392: nyag ni zab cing phra ste brtags par dka' //
NK101(de)004:3393: gcig ni ci smras ci dran yul sems bdag gi dbyings //
NK101(de)004:3395: kun bral phyogs ris bdag gzhan rgyu 'bras spros pa bral //
NK101(de)004:3396: kun dngos rang nyid ma rig cir yang shar //
NK101(de)004:3397: ci spangs rang rig rang rtogs thams cad rang du brlag /
NK101(de)004:3398: ci ma spangs pa snang srid ma bcos rang sar grol //
NK101(de)004:3399: zhes gsungs pas chos nyid mnyam pa chen po rang
NK101(de)004:3400: snang ris med kyi klong du shes par bya yi
NK101(de)004:3401: mngon sum phyogs gcig par gzung bar mi bya'o //
NK101(de)004:3403: gcig ni phyi nang sogs tshigs bcad lngas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3404: spros pa sna tshogs su gcod par byed pa'i yid
NK101(de)004:3405: kyi rnam par shes pa gcig ni phyi sgo lnga
NK101(de)004:3406: dang nang nyon yid gnyis kyi bar sgo yid kyi
NK101(de)004:3408: ma 'ongs lung ston pa dang 'das pa gleng slong
NK101(de)004:3409: gi bu mo skad tshangs pa'i dbyangs ltar snyan la
NK101(de)004:3410: gtam rgyud tshangs pa chen po ltar mkhas pa gnyis
NK101(de)004:3411: kyis yid 'phrog nas bya ba mang pos don med
NK101(de)004:3413: sgo'i nang na sgo srung yid kyi rnam par shes
NK101(de)004:3414: pa bya ba manga po zhes bya ba yod de
NK101(de)004:3415: / de la bu gsum yod pa las bu chen
NK101(de)004:3416: po ni sngar byas pa thams cad don med du
NK101(de)004:3418: bu chung ba ni phyis byed pa thams cad zin pa med pa zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)004:3419: bu bar ba ni rtogs pa'i gdengs chen po dang
NK101(de)004:3420: ldan zhing rtsod pa mi byed pas 'dzangs pa bar
NK101(de)004:3421: na yod pas gzu bor gnas pa zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)004:3422: de la bu chen po ni don med thang chad kyi yul la rol lo //
NK101(de)004:3423: bu chung ba ni zin med sgyid lug gi yul la rol zhing /
NK101(de)004:3424: bu bar pa ni mtha' bral 'od gsal gyi dgon par rol ba las /
NK101(de)004:3425: bu che chung gnyis bu mo gnyis kyi gtam rgyud dag la ma mthun te rtsod pa byed do //
NK101(de)004:3426: de yang ma bcos rang grol du 'char ba'i man
NK101(de)004:3427: ngag gi thabs shes na bu bar pas gong 'og
NK101(de)004:3428: gnyis thabs kyis dbang du byas te bsgral du btub
NK101(de)004:3429: pa ni / ngas ni gtam rgyud la bsam pa mada de /
NK101(de)004:3430: bya ba mang la zin pa nyung /
NK101(de)004:3431: don chung la nyes pa mang bas so //
NK101(de)004:3432: des na sdug bsngal gyi rgyu bya ba sna tshogs zhog la 'od gsal gyi dgon para 'dod dang /
NK101(de)004:3433: bu khyed gnyis kyang bar pa nga bzhin du bde ba 'dod pa la gcig par 'dug pas so //
NK101(de)004:3434: zhes pas drangs te 'dzangs pas zhes 'dzangs pa zhi
NK101(de)004:3435: dal can gyis ri rgod klungsa su phaba par byas
NK101(de)004:3436: te nges sgo gtan spros pa sna tshogs su 'dzin
NK101(de)004:3437: pa bcag ste 'khor sa rigs drug gi spros pa'i
NK101(de)004:3438: yul snang phyogs 'dzin dang bcas pa phyag nas rang
NK101(de)004:3439: bzhin gnyug ma'i don gyis dbul ba'i dri ma sel
NK101(de)004:3440: byed rtsol bral gyi nor bu bkra shis chos sku
NK101(de)004:3441: thug phrad kyis blangs te longs spyad nas rang bzhin
NK101(de)004:3442: spros bral gyi ye shes ri rab lta bu'i 'byung
NK101(de)004:3443: chen gtos kyi rgyal mtshan btsugs so //
NK101(de)004:3444: de ltar che chung rtsod pa meda pas bar ba
NK101(de)004:3445: gzu bo'i tha snyad kyang rang sar grol te spros
NK101(de)004:3446: pa'i rtog 'dzin dang brda don du zhen pa'i blo
NK101(de)004:3447: dang bral bas gnyug ma'i rig pa rang so na
NK101(de)004:3450: rtsol bral zin dang ma bzung bar //
NK101(de)004:3451: gsang ba'i 'khor lo ye shes gter //
NK101(de)004:3452: gsang sngags gter gyi mdzod 'dzin cing //
NK101(de)004:3453: rig pa'i bstan pa sgrogs pa'i bdag /
NK101(de)004:3456: yid kyi ye shes zin dang ma bzung bar //
NK101(de)004:3457: spros pa'i rang bzhin spros bral nyid du zin //
NK101(de)004:3458: bsam gyis mi khyab dus su nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)004:3459: chos sku ma btsal gnas par 'thad pas grub //
NK101(de)004:3462: gsang ba'i pad+ma sngags kyi sems //
NK101(de)004:3463: dpyod pa bral ba'i dus na shes //
NK101(de)004:3464: btang bzhag rang bzhin bya ba bral //
NK101(de)004:3465: 'khor ba rnam par mi sems te //
NK101(de)004:3466: mya ngan 'das pa'i rgyu ba'ang bral //
NK101(de)004:3467: rdzogs pa'i dgongs pa bya med la //
NK101(de)004:3468: dus gsum ma yengs srog tu sems //
NK101(de)004:3469: blang dor mi mnga' lta ba med //
NK101(de)004:3470: rang bzhin rgyal ba'i lta ba yin //
NK101(de)004:3471: mi rtsol dbu ma drang po'i lam //
NK101(de)004:3472: gang gis ma bcos thugs kyi lam //
NK101(de)004:3475: gcig ni nang bstan sogs tshigs bcad bzhi dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3476: bag chags kyi shes pa'i rgyud la ngar 'dzin pa'i
NK101(de)004:3477: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid gcig ni kha nang
NK101(de)004:3478: du kun gzhi la bstan pa'i sgo dang mtshungs par
NK101(de)004:3480: srid po stobs chen nyon yid las byung ba'i bu
NK101(de)004:3481: spun dug lnga ni rno zhing 'dzugs pas rang la
NK101(de)004:3482: rang gsod pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs nas /
NK101(de)004:3483: rang nyid la shed cher skyed cing nus pa'i mthu stobs dang ldan par byed la /
NK101(de)004:3484: sgo de'i nang na sgo srung sdig can spyi la
NK101(de)004:3485: rang du dmigs pa bya ba de la bu nyon
NK101(de)004:3486: mongs pa lnga dang stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi
NK101(de)004:3487: yod do // de rnamas 'dus pa'i tha chung mthar
NK101(de)004:3488: thug tha ma ni rtogs pa'i gdengas chen po mnga'
NK101(de)004:3489: ba'i dpa' ba nyon mongs pa'i g.yul ngo 'joms par
NK101(de)004:3490: byed pa zhes bya ba gnas la /
NK101(de)004:3491: de dag gi yang phu bo rnams ni dngos dang
NK101(de)004:3492: brgyud pa'i tshul gyis na rag dmyal ba'i yul na
NK101(de)004:3493: yod cing / tha chung rang rig ni dgos pa
NK101(de)004:3494: 'dod rgur 'byung bas bde ba chen po rin chen
NK101(de)004:3495: gyi gling na yod pa la /
NK101(de)004:3496: yul med 'dzin bral du gsal ba'i man ngag gi
NK101(de)004:3497: thabs shes na bu chung bas gcen po rnams thabs
NK101(de)004:3498: kyis dbang du byas te bsgral du btub pa ni
NK101(de)004:3499: / 'u cag kun kyang dpa' bor mthar thug pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:3500: tha chung nga nyid la nyon mongs pa kun gyi stobsa thams cad rdzogs par gnas na /
NK101(de)004:3501: khyed cag gis shed cher skyed cing nus pa'i stobs
NK101(de)004:3502: shugs dang rno mtshon kun gyis rang la rang gis
NK101(de)004:3503: 'joms par byas nas ma brlag gam /
NK101(de)004:3504: de bas na yul ngan pa na rag gi rtena de bor la /
NK101(de)004:3505: bde chen rin chen gyi gling du 'dong ngo //
NK101(de)004:3507: des sgo gtan nga bdag tu 'dzin pa bcag ste
NK101(de)004:3508: 'khor sa rigs drug gi bdag gzhan du snang ba
NK101(de)004:3509: dmigs 'dzin dang bcas pa phyags nas rtsol bral gyi
NK101(de)004:3510: bde bas dbul ba dang rtsol ba'i nad dang phyogs
NK101(de)004:3511: lhung gi bkra mi shis pa thams cad sel byed
NK101(de)004:3512: rang rig pa'i nor bu rin chen dbang gi rgyal
NK101(de)004:3513: po longs sku thug phrad kyis blangs nas longs spyad
NK101(de)004:3514: de / rang byung rig pa'i ye shes rdo rje
NK101(de)004:3515: lta bur mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan legs par btsugs
NK101(de)004:3516: de / so // de'i tshe na thams cad dpa'
NK101(de)004:3517: bo chen por gyur te mi mthun pa med pas
NK101(de)004:3518: dpa' bo'i tha snyad kyang rang sar grol te brda
NK101(de)004:3519: grol rang byung rang shar du rtogs pas rang rig
NK101(de)004:3520: bde ba chen por ye gsal phyogs med kyi ngang
NK101(de)004:3521: du gdal khyab chen por gnas pa yin te /
NK101(de)004:3523: shes rab gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK101(de)004:3524: dgu rum sbas pa dag yin yang //
NK101(de)004:3525: gsal byed sgron ma de yis mthong //
NK101(de)004:3526: ye gsal chen po phyogs med gdal //
NK101(de)004:3527: phyi nang med par kun la gsal //
NK101(de)004:3530: rang rig mngon sum ngar 'dzin nyon mongs che //
NK101(de)004:3531: sings kyis rig la gang du'ang mi rtog par //
NK101(de)004:3532: rang rig bde chen shar dus nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)004:3533: longs sku lhun gyis gnas pa 'thad pas grub //
NK101(de)004:3536: snying gi pad+ma rin po che //
NK101(de)004:3538: chags pa la sogs nyon mongs lnga //
NK101(de)004:3539: mthar thug tha ma'i dus na mthong //
NK101(de)004:3540: gang skyes dus na yul mi dpyad //
NK101(de)004:3541: mi dgag ngo bo nyid la bzhag /
NK101(de)004:3543: gnyis pa rnal 'byor mngon sum gyis yongs rdzogs dbyer med mnyam grol gyi dgongs par ston pa ni /
NK101(de)004:3544: gcig la gsum byung sogs tshigs su bcad pa phyed dang gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3545: sgra thal 'gyur chen po rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK101(de)004:3546: 'khor ba rnams kyi thog ma ni //
NK101(de)004:3547: mi 'byed byas med rang bzhin las //
NK101(de)004:3548: dmigs par 'dzin pa'i yul shar te //
NK101(de)004:3549: rtog 'dzin las ni tha dad snang //
NK101(de)004:3551: 'khrul gzhi rang ngo ma shes pa'i thig le nyag
NK101(de)004:3552: gcig la skye lugs gsum du byung nas rnam par
NK101(de)004:3553: shes pa tshogs bdun gyis rgyud dkrugs pas gzhi don
NK101(de)004:3554: dwangs pa'i rgya mtsho lta bur gnas pa de nyid
NK101(de)004:3555: bag chags kyi rnyog pas bslad de sbyor ba don
NK101(de)004:3556: gyi kun gzhir smin pa'i dbang gis 'khrul ba'i 'khor
NK101(de)004:3559: bya ba med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK101(de)004:3560: gdod nas rtsol med lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:3561: ye shes nyi ma'i snying por shar //
NK101(de)004:3562: rang gsal mun pa ye nas dag /
NK101(de)004:3565: rang rig stong nyid sprul pa'i rnam pa can //
NK101(de)004:3566: ngang la gnas pas bag chags rnyog gzhi dwangs //
NK101(de)004:3567: rnal 'byor shin tu rdzogs gsal sku gsum dang //
NK101(de)004:3568: rtog pa rang grol ye shes ma 'khrul 'thad //
NK101(de)004:3571: gsang ba'i pad+ma chos kyi sku //
NK101(de)004:3572: ma bcos rang gsal gzung 'dzin bral //
NK101(de)004:3573: rdzogs pa'i longs spyod bde ba'i sku //
NK101(de)004:3574: sprul sku gang la'ang ngos gzung med //
NK101(de)004:3575: dbyer med rig pa gcig la gnas //
NK101(de)004:3577: rtogs pas gzhan nas ma 'ongs te //
NK101(de)004:3578: rang byung snying po thog ma med //
NK101(de)004:3579: spros bral nam mkha' lta bu nyid //
NK101(de)004:3580: rgyal ba'i sku dang rang bzhin ldan //
NK101(de)004:3582: sprul sku dbang po'i mngon sum nor bu chu dwangs lta bu dang /
NK101(de)004:3583: chos sku yid kyi mngon sum nor bu bkra shis lta bu dang /
NK101(de)004:3584: longs sku rang rig mngon sum nor bu rin chen
NK101(de)004:3585: dbang gi rgyal po lta bu dang gsum gyis rim
NK101(de)004:3586: pa bzhin du rgya mtsho chen po'i rnyogs pa sangs
NK101(de)004:3587: 'o ma'i ngo bor byas bdud rtsa dwangs gsal 'khyil
NK101(de)004:3588: ba'i klong du gyur pa ltar /
NK101(de)004:3589: rnam shes tshogs bdun la thug phrad gsum gyis rtogs
NK101(de)004:3590: pa'i ngo bo nyid de byang chub kyi sems thig
NK101(de)004:3591: le nyag gcig tu shin tu rdzogs par kun gsal
NK101(de)004:3592: rnal 'byor mngon sum gyis mtha' grol zang thal du
NK101(de)004:3593: mthong bas / bag chags kyi rten gzhi sbyor ba
NK101(de)004:3594: don gyi kun gzhi rang sar grol te sku gsum
NK101(de)004:3595: dbyer med yongs rdzogs ngo bo nyid kyi sku ru
NK101(de)004:3596: shar nas ye shes sgrib med du gsal ba la
NK101(de)004:3597: mthong bas / / tha snyad du ma bcos pa
NK101(de)004:3598: dang lhun gyis grub pa dang rig pa rang gsal
NK101(de)004:3599: pa zhes su btags pa'ang dgos pas zhes gnas lugs
NK101(de)004:3600: kyi ngo bo mtshon pa'i phyir dgos dbang gis btags
NK101(de)004:3601: pa yin gyi don thun mong min par gnas par
NK101(de)004:3602: yin pas sgra ji bzhin pa min te /
NK101(de)004:3604: gzung ba med pa'i snang ba la //
NK101(de)004:3605: 'dzin pa med pa'i sems shar ba //
NK101(de)004:3606: dpyod pa med pa'i mig gis mthong //
NK101(de)004:3607: chos nyid med pa'i lam nas drangs //
NK101(de)004:3608: lta sgom med pa'i gzhi la bskyal //
NK101(de)004:3609: byar med rtsol bral 'bras bur dril //
NK101(de)004:3610: 'di la snang mtha' mi gnas so //
NK101(de)004:3611: zhes gsungs pa sogs shin tu mang la /
NK101(de)004:3612: de ltar so so'i mtshon tshul ma 'dres na yang
NK101(de)004:3613: ngo bo dbyer med du grol bas mtha' bral yongs
NK101(de)004:3614: rdzogs kyi gnas lugs mthong ste /
NK101(de)004:3615: de las yar gshegs kyang dgung la shul mi mnga'
NK101(de)004:3616: ba'i rtse mor gyur te mthar phyin pa yin pas
NK101(de)004:3618: gzhan yang chos nyid ngo bo ni //
NK101(de)004:3619: rang bzhin nyid las ngo bor grub //
NK101(de)004:3620: snang tshul gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK101(de)004:3621: 'jug pa'i lam yang tha dad do //
NK101(de)004:3622: ngo dang shes dang grol mthong gis //
NK101(de)004:3623: 'jug dang shes dang goms pa las //
NK101(de)004:3624: ngo shes pa las rang ngo ste //
NK101(de)004:3625: yid ches pa yi thug pa'o //
NK101(de)004:3626: thag chad pas ni gdeng du tshud //
NK101(de)004:3627: de ltar gsum gyi nges pa las //
NK101(de)004:3628: ngo bo rdzogs pas rgyu 'gags so //
NK101(de)004:3629: gzhan yang chos nyid rang bzhin bshad //
NK101(de)004:3631: gang ltar btags pa de ltar snang //
NK101(de)004:3632: sna tshogs ming gi gdags gzhi las //
NK101(de)004:3633: sgra tshig du ma'i spros par snang //
NK101(de)004:3634: nges med ming ni sna tshogs las /
NK101(de)004:3635: don yang btags pa tsam gyis stong //
NK101(de)004:3636: stong nyid gang yang ma grub pas //
NK101(de)004:3637: rang bzhin dag pa ltar snang ngo //
NK101(de)004:3638: gzhan yang chos nyid thugs rje bshad //
NK101(de)004:3639: gdul bya'i yul ni sna tshogs pas //
NK101(de)004:3640: 'dul byed sku yang de bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3641: rigs dang dbang po'i rnam 'phrul las //
NK101(de)004:3643: de nyid so so'i yul bzhag na //
NK101(de)004:3644: ma bcos don gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK101(de)004:3647: bya ba bral bar rdzogs pas rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:3648: mtha' dang bral bas dbus mi gnas //
NK101(de)004:3649: yongs su rdzogs pas dngos dang bral //
NK101(de)004:3650: lhag ma med pas cha shas min //
NK101(de)004:3651: gcig tu ma yin gnyis mtha' zad //
NK101(de)004:3652: du mar mi snang gcig las 'das //
NK101(de)004:3653: brjod du med pa'i tshig gi gzhi //
NK101(de)004:3654: dngos bral stong pa snying po'i don //
NK101(de)004:3655: phyogs su ma lhungs lta ba'i don //
NK101(de)004:3658: de ltar 'khrul pa rnams ye nas chos nyid byang
NK101(de)004:3659: chub kyi sems su gnas pa de nyid ji lta
NK101(de)004:3660: ba bzhin du ngo shes shing ma nor bar rtogs
NK101(de)004:3661: pas de las gzhan pa'i sel med pa ni dper
NK101(de)004:3662: na rin chen gyi gling na sa rdo'i sel med
NK101(de)004:3663: pa bzhin no // de ltar yang ye shes gsang sgron las /
NK101(de)004:3664: sems rtogs med cing ye shes gsal //
NK101(de)004:3665: gnas lugs ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NK101(de)004:3666: dper na gser gling phyin pa 'dra //
NK101(de)004:3667: dgongs pa rdo rje 'chang dang mnyam //
NK101(de)004:3669: yin pa gsum gyis thag bcad de //
NK101(de)004:3670: sku gsung thugs la yid ches skye //
NK101(de)004:3671: rin po che yi gser gling du //
NK101(de)004:3672: phyin pas thams cad gser du snang //
NK101(de)004:3674: ce spyang e na'i mig bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:3675: gnyis su med par thag chod do //
NK101(de)004:3677: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las /
NK101(de)004:3678: ji ltar snang ba de bzhin nyid du gcig /'di la su yang 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK101(de)004:3679: ma bcos mnyam pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK101(de)004:3680: mi rtog chos sku'i dgongs pa lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:3683: gzhan yang rab tu bshad bya ba //
NK101(de)004:3684: snang ba 'khrul pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:3685: ye shes yin par sngar ma mthong //
NK101(de)004:3686: rtog bcas 'khrul ba'i gzhi med pas //
NK101(de)004:3687: kun gzhi chos sku chen por rtogs //
NK101(de)004:3688: 'khrul pa'i rang rtog rgyun chad do //
NK101(de)004:3690: yang ni rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK101(de)004:3691: gnad shes pa las ye shes ni //
NK101(de)004:3692: bya bral nam mkha' ji bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:3693: kun tu rtog pas spros dang bral //
NK101(de)004:3694: ngo mtshar rmad byung ye shes ni //
NK101(de)004:3695: sngon med phyis med gdod nas med //
NK101(de)004:3696: da lta rnam rtog yul las 'das //
NK101(de)004:3697: mtha' bral stong ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3698: tshig 'das blo bral ngo bos stong //
NK101(de)004:3699: rang bzhin gang du ma phye bas //
NK101(de)004:3700: thugs rjes mdzad pa mi snang ngo //
NK101(de)004:3701: ye shes snang ba gsum pa las //
NK101(de)004:3703: 'di la rnam par dmigs mtha' med //
NK101(de)004:3704: med pa rmad byung rol pa las //
NK101(de)004:3705: sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'bras bu rnyed //
NK101(de)004:3706: phyi dang nang kun chos kyi dbyings //
NK101(de)004:3707: 'di la gang yang mi snang ngo //
NK101(de)004:3709: gsum pa de ltar rang mtshan mthong bas lta ba'i gdings tshad ngos bzung ba las /
NK101(de)004:3710: lta bas mngon sum rang thog tu pheb pa'i rtags tshad dang /
NK101(de)004:3711: de las rtogs pa gdengs su gyur pa'i rtags tshad gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:3713: rang mtshan mngon sum sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3714: de ltar chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres
NK101(de)004:3715: yongs su rdzogs par mngon suma bzhi rdzogs kyi zang
NK101(de)004:3716: thal du rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rang gsal
NK101(de)004:3717: ma bcos par rtogs na pha bla ma la bka'
NK101(de)004:3718: drin gzo bas dad mos gus pa dang bcas te
NK101(de)004:3720: mched grogs dam ldan kun la rdo rje'i spun du mthong nas gdung sems che la /
NK101(de)004:3721: ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba 'khrul bar zhen pa rnams
NK101(de)004:3722: la snying bartse dang bcas pas phan pa'i sems dang
NK101(de)004:3723: ldan pa dang / bsrung bya dam tshig la brtan
NK101(de)004:3724: par gnas te kun tu rdzogs pas mi 'bral bar
NK101(de)004:3725: rub cing rtogs pa'i don la rten te nyams su
NK101(de)004:3726: len pa la brtson par byed de /
NK101(de)004:3727: des na phyi nang gi dngos po gang la'ang zhen
NK101(de)004:3728: pa mi brtan par dgra gnyen la sogs pa'i phyogs
NK101(de)004:3729: ris kyi gtad 'dzin chung ba dang /
NK101(de)004:3730: nang na rtogs pa'i gdenga dang ldan pas 'bras bu
NK101(de)004:3731: thob tu re ba dang ma thob tu dogas pa
NK101(de)004:3732: med cing / theg pa'i rim pa gang gis kyang
NK101(de)004:3733: don gyi gnas lugs matshana par byed pa'i tshig rnams
NK101(de)004:3734: la yin min gyi yangs dog gi khyad par med
NK101(de)004:3735: med cing / la / gang ltar spyad kyang mi
NK101(de)004:3736: 'ching bas spyod lam yongs la grub mtha' la sogs
NK101(de)004:3737: pa gang gi'ang phyogs 'dzin chung ba sogs kyis rtogs
NK101(de)004:3738: pa'i tshad dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)004:3740: nges par gdengs su sogs rkang pa lngas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3741: de lta bu'i gnas lugs zab mo nges par rtogs te goms pas gdengs su gyur pa na /
NK101(de)004:3742: las kyi skye rkyang chog pas ngan 'gro gsum gyi
NK101(de)004:3743: sdug bsngal las grol nas phyogs med kyi don rtogs
NK101(de)004:3744: pas theg pa dman pa las khyad par du 'phags
NK101(de)004:3745: shing / ci spyod don las mi nyams pas rgyal
NK101(de)004:3746: ba sangs rgyas nyid dang spyod yul gacaga pa thob
NK101(de)004:3747: shing / cing / thun mong tha mal gyi sdig
NK101(de)004:3748: pa'i rnam smin sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu med la
NK101(de)004:3749: shing / cing / / yon tan gyi grangs mtha'
NK101(de)004:3750: yas yang tshad med 'byung bas rgyal bas kyang brjod
NK101(de)004:3753: 'dir ni rang yul bstan pa las //
NK101(de)004:3755: zang ma nyid du thal byung du //
NK101(de)004:3756: yul dang shes pa'i snang cha las //
NK101(de)004:3757: thad ka so so'i gzhi la grol //
NK101(de)004:3758: 'dod yon rnams ni rang rdzogs te //
NK101(de)004:3759: sna tshogs 'gyur ba so so'i gnas //
NK101(de)004:3760: gcig shes pa yis grol bar gnas //
NK101(de)004:3761: des na chos nyid rtogs pa ste //
NK101(de)004:3762: cha shas nyid dang bral ba'o //
NK101(de)004:3764: dam pa'i don ni blo bral nas //
NK101(de)004:3765: dbang po cig char rang grol bas //
NK101(de)004:3766: mngon sum mthong ba'i gnad kyis ni //
NK101(de)004:3767: rang gi grub pa'i mtha' zhig nas //
NK101(de)004:3768: gang la zhen dang 'dzin med par //
NK101(de)004:3769: yang dag chos nyid ro myongs nas //
NK101(de)004:3770: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rten med par //
NK101(de)004:3771: mkha' la mkha' nyid thim pa ltar //
NK101(de)004:3772: rnal 'byor mchog kyang de bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:3774: bzhi pa rtogs pa de nyid gzhan las 'phags pa'i nges gsang gi khyad par bstan pa la /
NK101(de)004:3775: theg pa gzhan gyi rang sa thob kyang mthar phyin mi nus pa'i tshul /
NK101(de)004:3776: don 'di rtogs na snying po'i byang chub la sbyor
NK101(de)004:3777: bas chos nyid rang mtshan mthong ba'i khyad chos ldan
NK101(de)004:3778: tshul / de'i phyir na skal bzang dam pas rang
NK101(de)004:3779: gter long la 'gal rkyen spongs shig par gdams pa
NK101(de)004:3780: tshul / dang gsum las / dang po ni /
NK101(de)004:3781: 'di med don la sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3782: de'i phyir khyad par de lta bu dang ldan pa'i
NK101(de)004:3783: lta ba'i nges gsang 'di nyid ji bzhin du rtogs
NK101(de)004:3784: pa med na theg pa 'og ma pa dag gis
NK101(de)004:3785: rang sa'i don la rtsol ba chen pos ji ltar
NK101(de)004:3786: 'bad cing btsal bar byas kyang mthar thug gi 'bras
NK101(de)004:3787: bu'i sa la gnas pa min te /
NK101(de)004:3788: 'bras bu gong mar skye zhing rang 'bras 'jig pa
NK101(de)004:3789: dang bcas pas na 'khor ba'i phyogs su gyur para
NK101(de)004:3792: gsum la ngos bzung mi mnga' ste //
NK101(de)004:3793: brgyad kyis rang 'dod gnyis kyis log /
NK101(de)004:3794: gcig gis ma rig khas mi len //
NK101(de)004:3795: drug gis lnga yi 'bras bu myong //
NK101(de)004:3796: des na ye shes gsang ba yin //
NK101(de)004:3799: gang dag dag pa'i 'khor lo la //
NK101(de)004:3800: sbyor 'dod rgyur rtsol gang zhig na //
NK101(de)004:3801: mthun pa nyid na mi mthun pa //
NK101(de)004:3802: thug pa med de gang la 'thad //
NK101(de)004:3804: de yi phyir de dag gi rtogs don gang yin pa de nyid dper byas na /
NK101(de)004:3805: nor bu 'ching bu rgyal mtshan gyi rtser zhes rtse
NK101(de)004:3806: mor 'dogs nas bkur sti byas kyang dgos 'dod grub
NK101(de)004:3808: rang sa'i 'dod pa don du gnyer ba tsam las
NK101(de)004:3809: mthar mi phyin par dmar thag las pa ni le'u
NK101(de)004:3810: gnyis par bshad pa'i ma he'i zho'i bcud la snying
NK101(de)004:3811: po rang sa snum par bshad pa de bzhin tsam
NK101(de)004:3812: du nges par gnas pas so //
NK101(de)004:3814: de bas 'di rtogs sogs tshigs bcad phyed dang gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3815: de ltar theg pa gzhan gyis mthar mi phyin pa'i
NK101(de)004:3816: skyon yod pa de bas na rnal ma'i don zab
NK101(de)004:3817: mo 'di nyid ma nor bar rtogs na shes sgrub
NK101(de)004:3818: kyi don ma lus pa kun mthar thug par rdzogs
NK101(de)004:3819: pa yin te / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK101(de)004:3820: ye shes gsang ba'i don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:3821: mi g.yo sems kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK101(de)004:3823: des na kun grol dgongs pa'i thugs //
NK101(de)004:3824: zhes gsungs pas dper na rgya mtsho chen po dang
NK101(de)004:3825: gser gyi 'og gzhi sa yi dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK101(de)004:3826: na kun gyi bkod pa rdzogs pa dang 'dra la
NK101(de)004:3827: / de lta bu'i don gyi ngo bo de yang
NK101(de)004:3828: phyogs kun nasa mthun par mtshon pa'i dpe las 'das
NK101(de)004:3829: pa ni dper na dmus long la mar gyi rang
NK101(de)004:3830: mdoga mtshon du mi btub pa dang 'dra'o //
NK101(de)004:3831: mu matha'i phyogs su 'di lta bu kho na yin
NK101(de)004:3832: zhes tshig tu brjod pa'i tha snyad dang brala ba
NK101(de)004:3833: ni / khams gsum gyi dang po'i zhes dang po
NK101(de)004:3834: 'dod pa'i khams kyi las rnams kyi mtha' nyams su
NK101(de)004:3835: myong tshul sna tshogs pas gcig tu ma nges pa
NK101(de)004:3836: ni / dang 'dra la / chos thams cad ma
NK101(de)004:3837: nor bar chos nyid rang snang gi klong du rdzogs
NK101(de)004:3838: pa ni chu yi rlabs thams cad rgya mtshor ro
NK101(de)004:3839: gcig pa bzhin du yin zhing /
NK101(de)004:3840: rtogs pa'i lta ba gsal na che ba'i yon tan rnams shugs la 'char ba ni /
NK101(de)004:3841: nor bu'i mchog chen dbang gi rgyal po nyid mchod
NK101(de)004:3842: cing bsnyen bkur byas pa dang 'dra ba yin pas
NK101(de)004:3843: rtogs don phul du byung zhing bla na med pa
NK101(de)004:3845: des na skal ldan sogs rkang pa gcig lhag pas tshigs bcad kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3846: bshad ma thag pa de lta bu'i skyon yon gyi
NK101(de)004:3847: khyad par yod pa des na blo mchog skal ba
NK101(de)004:3848: dang ldan pa dag gis rang la yod pa'i dgos
NK101(de)004:3849: 'dod kun 'byung gi gter chen po rmad du byung
NK101(de)004:3850: ba 'di nyid blo gros gsal zhing dad brtson dang
NK101(de)004:3851: gus pas longas la tshul bzhin du spyod cig /
NK101(de)004:3852: ces bskul bar mdzad pa ste /
NK101(de)004:3853: rin po che sprungs pa las /
NK101(de)004:3854: nga ni sgra tshad rang rig la //
NK101(de)004:3855: yon tan rin chen gter chen 'chang //
NK101(de)004:3856: 'di ni bcangs pa tsam gyis kyang //
NK101(de)004:3857: zad pa med pa'i longs spyod thob //
NK101(de)004:3858: zad med 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)004:3859: nub pa med pa'i gter chen rnyed //
NK101(de)004:3860: gter 'di gang gis rnyed pa'i mi //
NK101(de)004:3861: nga yi yon tan 'di la rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:3863: kun tu bzang po klong drug las //
NK101(de)004:3864: bden goms rnal 'byor skal ldan pa //
NK101(de)004:3865: sus ma rnyed pa'i don rnyed de //
NK101(de)004:3866: 'di la rin thang dpag tu med //
NK101(de)004:3867: dpag med nor dang 'phrad pa'i mis //
NK101(de)004:3868: sus ma mthong ba'i snang ba mthong //
NK101(de)004:3869: 'di mthong rang rig ltad re che //
NK101(de)004:3870: de ltar sems la ltad che ba //
NK101(de)004:3871: chos can dum bu phyags mas btab //
NK101(de)004:3872: chos can dum bur sus chod pa //
NK101(de)004:3873: 'dis ni rang rig spar gyi zin //
NK101(de)004:3874: 'di ltar zin pa'i skyes bu ni //
NK101(de)004:3875: sangs rgyas bas kyang sngar sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:3877: rang rig skal mnyam stong nyid grogs //
NK101(de)004:3878: 'di la goms pa'i skal ba can //
NK101(de)004:3879: rtog pa med pa'i sku gzugs te //
NK101(de)004:3880: nga yi thugs rje'i 'od la zhugs //
NK101(de)004:3881: 'di dang nga nyid skal ba mnyam //
NK101(de)004:3882: nga yi dkyil dang 'khor yang yin //
NK101(de)004:3884: de ltar bshad pa las gzhan du ma dad pa
NK101(de)004:3885: dang le lo dang yid gnyis sam the tshom rnams
NK101(de)004:3886: kyis dgos pa'i don grub pa ni 'jig rten gyi
NK101(de)004:3887: khams na 'ga' tsam yang mthong rgyu med par nges
NK101(de)004:3888: te / dper na tsha reg dang grang reg thanga
NK101(de)004:3889: cig 'dres par spyod pas 'bras bu btso bsreg gi
NK101(de)004:3890: las grub pa 'ga' tsam yang mthong ngam ci /
NK101(de)004:3891: zhes mthong du med pa de lta bu yin pa'i phyir na de dag spongs shig par gdams pa'o //
NK101(de)004:3893: rin po che gter gtad pa las /
NK101(de)004:3894: rtogs pa lta ba'i thabs dang ngo bo la sogs
NK101(de)004:3895: pa'i don gsal bar bstan pa'i le'u ste skabs gsum
NK101(de)004:3897: bzhi pa de la 'dris goms byed pa'i thabs kyis rtogs don mthar dbyung tshul bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:3898: thabs mchog lam gyi khyad gzhi 'og ma'i mu matha'i
NK101(de)004:3899: phyogs cha las grol tshul dang bcas te mdor bstan
NK101(de)004:3900: / de yi khyad chos gsal bar ston pa'i thun
NK101(de)004:3901: min lam gyi mtshan nyid rgyas par bshad pa gnyis
NK101(de)004:3903: bshad pa'i bsod nams sogs tshigs gcad dang gcig rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3904: de ltar le'u gsum par bshad pa'i rgyal po gsal
NK101(de)004:3905: rgyal la rang gi bsod nams kyi dbang las pha
NK101(de)004:3906: yis gter chen po gtad pa ltar du /
NK101(de)004:3907: rang gnas gyi gter mchog dam pa mthong nas lta
NK101(de)004:3908: ba rtogs pa'i don la 'dris shing goms pasa 'bras
NK101(de)004:3909: bu mthar dbyung ba'i thabs ni 'di ltar /
NK101(de)004:3910: theg pa 'og ma pa dag gi rtogs pa'i don
NK101(de)004:3911: mu bzhi phyogs lhung gi 'dod pa dang bcas pa
NK101(de)004:3912: ni / yongas gcoda bsgrub bya'i lta ba de nyid
NK101(de)004:3913: de ma yin pa gzhan las ldog pa'i sa yi
NK101(de)004:3915: der dmigs pa gtad nas de las ma yengas par
NK101(de)004:3916: goms pa brtan pa'i rgyu las rang la sngar med
NK101(de)004:3917: kyi 'bras bu phyis dus su 'byung bar 'dod pa
NK101(de)004:3918: las grol ba'i khyad par mchog dang ldan pa yin
NK101(de)004:3919: no // de nyid bstan pa gang zhig yin zhe na /
NK101(de)004:3921: sems nyid sgrub pa'i don lam thug phrad gsum gyis
NK101(de)004:3922: rtogs pa'i ngang la gnas te gdengs chen thob tshul
NK101(de)004:3923: / de yi cha rkyen nges don snying po thabs mchog dam pa gsal bar bshad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:3925: lam mchog nges par mtshon pa'i mthun dpe dang /
NK101(de)004:3926: don lam byang chub sems kyi dngos gzhi bstan gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:3928: rdo rje gling phug sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3929: gnas mchog rdo rje gling phug gi gong na gzhan
NK101(de)004:3930: med pas rtse mo na shing gi rgyal po tsa
NK101(de)004:3931: na'i zhes tsa na ka'i sdong po'i rtsa' zhes rtsa
NK101(de)004:3932: ba'i drung na sa la gnas pa la dbang che
NK101(de)004:3933: bar 'dzin pa'i seng ge mo de nyid /
NK101(de)004:3934: 'dod chags rang grol mtshon pas stobs che zhing /
NK101(de)004:3935: gti mug rang grol mtshon pas ngar skad drag la
NK101(de)004:3936: zhe sdang rang grol mtshon pas khro gnyer dang ldan
NK101(de)004:3937: pa de thabs kyis bsten nas gser gyi zo bar
NK101(de)004:3938: 'o ma'i zhes 'o ma bzhos te thogs med du
NK101(de)004:3939: snum pa'i snying po'i bcud du gyur pa de nyid
NK101(de)004:3940: len pa ltar du zhes pa'o //
NK101(de)004:3942: rtogs pa'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:3943: de ltar lta bas yang dag par rtogs pa'i don
NK101(de)004:3944: chos nyid thig le nyag gcig yin pas tshogs bdun
NK101(de)004:3945: po rnams thig le nyag gcig tu thug phrad gsum
NK101(de)004:3946: gyis dgrol nas don dang mi mthun pa'i rnam rtog
NK101(de)004:3947: thams cad byang chub kyi sems su kar nas dag
NK101(de)004:3948: pa yin la / de ltar rtogs pas ched du
NK101(de)004:3949: ma gtad kyang don gyi ngang der dus nam yang
NK101(de)004:3951: dmigs pa gtad nas bsgom du med kyang rtag tu
NK101(de)004:3952: mi 'bral ba ni sgom pa'i gzer chen po yina
NK101(de)004:3954: ye nas gnas pa rig par shar //
NK101(de)004:3955: de yi so la ma yongs par //
NK101(de)004:3956: snying po rnal ma don gyi rgyud //
NK101(de)004:3957: rtogs pa'i klong du gnas pa tsam //
NK101(de)004:3959: des na rtogs pa'i ngang du dran pa rkyen gya
NK101(de)004:3960: man ngag gis ye nas yina pa'i don de ma
NK101(de)004:3961: nor bar rtogs pa'i so las ma 'das pa tsam
NK101(de)004:3963: slob dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis /
NK101(de)004:3964: de don rtogs so ma 'das par //
NK101(de)004:3965: ma rmongs dran pa'i 'du byed sems //
NK101(de)004:3966: snying po rang grol 'dus ma byas //
NK101(de)004:3967: dus gsum shes bya ma lus pa //
NK101(de)004:3968: skad cig mi gnas rgyun dang bcas //
NK101(de)004:3969: ma chad dum bur ma red pa //
NK101(de)004:3970: ngang du gnas na don mthar son //
NK101(de)004:3971: chu rgyun gnas 'drar ma gtad sdod //
NK101(de)004:3974: yang ti'i don lam chen po ni //
NK101(de)004:3975: khyung chen mkha' la lding ba bzhin //
NK101(de)004:3976: dran pa tsam gyis chos skur rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:3977: de tsam nyid na ye shes thugs //
NK101(de)004:3979: de'i phyir dper na gser nyid la gser 'gyur gyi
NK101(de)004:3980: rtsi mi brten pa ltar du ye nas sangs rgyas
NK101(de)004:3981: par gnas pa la rtsol ba'i thabs kyis mi sgrub
NK101(de)004:3982: par / mngon sum par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:3983: de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:3984: bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:3985: chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba ste snga ma bzhis barda don sprod de /
NK101(de)004:3986: lnga yi tha mas zhes tha ma sangs rgyas med
NK101(de)004:3987: pa'i che bas barda don la nges par 'dzin par
NK101(de)004:3989: brda bral rang grol du rtogs pa'i gdengs chen po
NK101(de)004:3990: dang ldana pa'i skyes bu'i lta ba la zhe 'dod
NK101(de)004:3991: gang yang meda pa ni dper na khyung chena po
NK101(de)004:3992: nam mkha' la ldeng ba la rjes med pa lta
NK101(de)004:3993: bu'o // de ltar yang ye shes gsang sgron las /
NK101(de)004:3994: bstan pa yongs su rdzogs byed pa //
NK101(de)004:3995: las sim khong klod gnyug ma'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:3996: byang sems bde ba che dang 'phrad //
NK101(de)004:3997: mkha' ltar mtha' dbus sems la med //
NK101(de)004:4000: 'di ni theg pa kun gyi rgyal //
NK101(de)004:4001: btang ngo bzhag go rang bzhin te //
NK101(de)004:4002: 'dod pa med cing len pa med //
NK101(de)004:4003: phrod pa rdul tsam mi bskyed do //
NK101(de)004:4004: khyung chen nam mkhar lding ba bzhin //
NK101(de)004:4005: spro ba med cing bsdu ba med //
NK101(de)004:4006: stor bar mi dogs bza' ba med //
NK101(de)004:4007: rgya mtsho bzhin du ye gnas la //
NK101(de)004:4008: chos rnams sna tshogs 'byung bar byed //
NK101(de)004:4009: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK101(de)004:4012: rtogs don la 'dris goms byed pa'i thabs kyi cha rkyen phul du byung ba dang /
NK101(de)004:4013: don lam gyi ngo bo'i cha rkyen rang snang klong
NK101(de)004:4014: dgu'i dgongs pa bla med chen por bstan pa gnyis
NK101(de)004:4016: rang la gyis rtogs goms byed pa'i thabs mchog dngos kyi don dang /
NK101(de)004:4017: de la dngos brgyud nas 'jug pa'i thabs sgo mang ba'i khyad par gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:4019: rim pa dang bcas te 'dris goms byed pa'i lam gyi rnam pa bstan /
NK101(de)004:4020: de ltar lam la goms pa'i rtags tshad 'char tshul gsal bshad /
NK101(de)004:4021: sgom ma sgom gyi skyon yon rnam par dbye ste phrang bsal ba gsum las /
NK101(de)004:4023: nyams rim bzhi po ji ltar skye tshul ngos bzung /
NK101(de)004:4024: de yi gol sa gcod phyir thug phrad gsum gyis gnad la dbab /
NK101(de)004:4025: rtogs nyams don la sbyor ba'i nges pa dngos kyi dmigs bzung /
NK101(de)004:4026: don gyi gdengs chen ldan na rtog grol chig chod yin pa'i khyad chos bstan /
NK101(de)004:4027: de las gzhan pas brtson te goms na mthar phyin pa'i nges pa bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)004:4029: de yang blo gros sogs rkang pa lngas bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4030: de lta bu'i lta ba rtogs pa de la yang /
NK101(de)004:4032: rigs rgyud dbang po chig chod dam //
NK101(de)004:4033: sbyang ba'i 'phro can gang yang rung //
NK101(de)004:4034: zhes gsungs pa ltar blo gros rtsal che chung gi bye brag yod pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:4035: rang bzhin gyi rigs khams shes pa'i rgyud kyi ngo
NK101(de)004:4036: bo dbang po chig chod dang ma ldan pas rtogs
NK101(de)004:4037: pa'i gdengas chen pos grol ba tshad la ma phebs
NK101(de)004:4038: na / teng nge 'dzin gyi ngang la goms dgos pas /
NK101(de)004:4039: nyams kyi rim pa yang dang po gnas par bya ba dang gnyis pa mi g.yo ba dang /
NK101(de)004:4040: gsum pa mnyam pa nyid rnams rim par sbyar nas /
NK101(de)004:4041: tha ma ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i nyams la
NK101(de)004:4042: gnas na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa zag pa med
NK101(de)004:4043: pa'i bde ba che ste chen por 'char bas grol
NK101(de)004:4044: ba tshad la phebs pa 'byung ste /
NK101(de)004:4046: de ltar gnas na dang po gnas pa tsam //
NK101(de)004:4047: skal ldan blo zhan rtags tshad goms byed tshe //
NK101(de)004:4048: mi sdod rtog mang rkyen bral cung zad gnas //
NK101(de)004:4049: sprin bar nyi 'dra yid ches re dogs med //
NK101(de)004:4050: dad pas blo ldog chags chung snying rje che //
NK101(de)004:4051: snang bas g.yang sar mi ltung 'brel bas phrad //
NK101(de)004:4052: zil gnon stobs chung srid pa brgal ma nus //
NK101(de)004:4053: sngar gnas stobs kyis skyon bral phrad par gnas //
NK101(de)004:4054: rgya mtsho'i gting 'dra rtags bzang rab tu 'phel //
NK101(de)004:4055: blo zhan brtag pa mthar zung bag la nyal //
NK101(de)004:4056: ma bral zag bcas goms stobs mthar phyin 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:4057: mtshan nyid dbyer med ngo bor son mdzad pa //
NK101(de)004:4058: ngos bzung mi gnas rtsol 'das don mthar phyin //
NK101(de)004:4059: rtags mtshan yongs rdzogs 'pho 'das bgrod med gnas //
NK101(de)004:4060: rjes thob chung mnga' tshul bzang rtsol ba can //
NK101(de)004:4061: rang sems chos sku zhal 'jal mthar phyin pa //
NK101(de)004:4062: mtshon du med pa nyin mtshan mthar dbus 'das //
NK101(de)004:4063: rtsol med byin rlabs yul gyis cir yang 'char //
NK101(de)004:4064: skyed du byar med phyogs bral rang gsal gdags //
NK101(de)004:4065: rim pa ji bzhin ma lus tshang ba yang //
NK101(de)004:4066: dus la nges med brtson stobs rig pa'i rtsal //
NK101(de)004:4067: 'ga' zhig la lar gnas nas mthar phyin yod //
NK101(de)004:4068: bdag 'dra nges par 'byung na chig chod yin //
NK101(de)004:4071: gnas thabs sprul pa sogs tshigs bcad gsum dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4072: de bzhin du ting nge 'dzin la blo gnas pa'i
NK101(de)004:4073: thabs la yang sprul pa rang gsal rol pa'i sku
NK101(de)004:4074: la rnam pa'i snang tshul bsam yas pa yod pasa
NK101(de)004:4075: / sgo lnga yul mtshan mar 'dzin pa la khyad
NK101(de)004:4076: par bzhi dang ldan pa las dang pos zhes dang
NK101(de)004:4077: po bzhi cha rang gsal gyis rtog dpyod tha snyad
NK101(de)004:4078: 'dogs pa gsum bsgral te yul lngar snang ba tsam
NK101(de)004:4079: mi dgag par de la zhen par mi bya ba'o
NK101(de)004:4080: / // de yang dbugs phyung bas ngal gso ba
NK101(de)004:4081: legs pa'i rtogs pa tsam las spros bral dang rang
NK101(de)004:4082: rig gi dmar thag ma chod par yoda do //
NK101(de)004:4083: rtogs ma rtogs kyi 'khor 'das kyi phyogs rgyal bar
NK101(de)004:4084: byed pas dpa' bo nyon mongs pa rno 'dzug gi
NK101(de)004:4085: mtshon cha thogs pa des 'khor bar 'dzin pa'i lcags
NK101(de)004:4086: kyu dug chen po lnga po de /
NK101(de)004:4087: bdag gi ba ma spang par longs spyod pas mthar
NK101(de)004:4088: thug pa'i dus na rang la rang gnyen por bzlog
NK101(de)004:4089: ste nga bdag dang gzung 'dzin mi spang bar rang
NK101(de)004:4090: rig tu shes pas rang grol du la bazla ba
NK101(de)004:4091: ni dper na bdud kyi dpung gi dgra choms nas
NK101(de)004:4092: dgra nyid gnyen du 'dzugs pa dang 'dra ba yin
NK101(de)004:4093: no // smra ba gtam rgyud mkhan gyi bu mo
NK101(de)004:4094: gnyis thabs kyis mi gnas par byas te spros bral
NK101(de)004:4096: bya ba mang la zin pa nyung bas bya ba zhog cig ces pas zhor la sha gcad de /
NK101(de)004:4097: 'dzangs pa bar pas yul spros bral du bcad pa'i ngaga don /
NK101(de)004:4098: ngas ni gtam rgyud bsam pa med /
NK101(de)004:4099: ces sogs bslab pa ltar mnyan pas snga phyi'i rtog
NK101(de)004:4100: pa sna tshogs kyi gras thag dus der rgyun ba
NK101(de)004:4101: chad la / yid kyi yul du chos khams sna
NK101(de)004:4102: tshogs su snang ba rnams mi gnas par rig pa'i
NK101(de)004:4103: rang sar thabs dam pa des grol bar 'gyur ro
NK101(de)004:4104: chad la / // de lta bu'i rtogs don ma
NK101(de)004:4105: 'dres yongs rdzogs chen po'i ngang la gnas pa'i ngo
NK101(de)004:4106: chad la / // bo ni / ye shes rdzogs pa las /
NK101(de)004:4107: rtsol bral rig pa'i ye shes la //
NK101(de)004:4108: yengs pa med par rang bzhin bzhag /
NK101(de)004:4109: dbang po'i ngo la snang ba la //
NK101(de)004:4110: mi rtog rang bzhin rig par gsal //
NK101(de)004:4112: gang la mi 'dzin rang byung sems //
NK101(de)004:4113: mtshan ma'i spros par 'gyur ba na //
NK101(de)004:4114: brda sgo 'jug pa'i man ngag sbyin //
NK101(de)004:4116: ye shes 'khor lo mtha' dbus med //
NK101(de)004:4118: rnam rtog ye shes nyid du gnas //
NK101(de)004:4120: rang rig stong nyid rnam bcas pas //
NK101(de)004:4121: bde chen lhun grub rang rig gsal //
NK101(de)004:4122: ye shes rig pa'i 'khor lo la //
NK101(de)004:4123: gang yang yin no rnam kun gces //
NK101(de)004:4124: ye shes rang shar ma bsgrubs gsal //
NK101(de)004:4126: rdo rje lta bur dbyer med pa'i //
NK101(de)004:4127: sems kyi rang bzhin kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:4128: sku gsung rdzogs pa'i bde ba che //
NK101(de)004:4129: bsam med bzhag med nyid kyis go //
NK101(de)004:4132: chos nyid yul gyi snang ba la //
NK101(de)004:4133: bsam pa'i dngos po ji snyed pa //
NK101(de)004:4134: 'khrul dang ma rig rgyu yin pas //
NK101(de)004:4135: bsam pa med pa'i rig pa la //
NK101(de)004:4136: don gyi de nyid bzlog par bya //
NK101(de)004:4137: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK101(de)004:4139: 'jug sla btang dka' sogs rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4140: bshad pa de ltar goms par byas pas ting nge
NK101(de)004:4141: 'dzin la 'jug par sla la btang bar dka' zhing
NK101(de)004:4142: rtogs pa rang gi ngo bo bde la gsal te
NK101(de)004:4143: mi rtog par gnas par 'gyur la /
NK101(de)004:4144: nyams skye tshul gyi don gyi rnam grangs ni /
NK101(de)004:4145: pra khrid nyams rim bzhi par re re la'ang ngo
NK101(de)004:4146: bo dpe rtags 'bras bu bzhi bzhir gsal bar bstan
NK101(de)004:4147: pas der shes par bya la /
NK101(de)004:4148: de ltar goms pas 'khrul ba'i rkyen shugs kyi rnam
NK101(de)004:4149: shes tshogs bdun skye lugs gsum du shar ba gang
NK101(de)004:4150: de sems nyid thig le nyag gcig tu grol bar
NK101(de)004:4151: byas te don gyi gnas lugs su 'jug par bya
NK101(de)004:4153: rang gi rang bzhin gshis kyi gnad //
NK101(de)004:4154: brjod pa'i tshig gis ma yin par //
NK101(de)004:4155: dbang po yul la gsal snang bas //
NK101(de)004:4156: cer mthong grol ba'i bdag nyid do //
NK101(de)004:4158: 'di la nyams rim dang po gnyis su bdud dang cha dbye ba shin tu gces par gsungs pas /
NK101(de)004:4159: mdo dang sems phyogs spyi la grags pa rnams bsam
NK101(de)004:4160: gtan nyams sgron dang khrid yig sogs na gsal yang
NK101(de)004:4161: / bka' srol 'di nyid la grags pa rnams kyang
NK101(de)004:4162: brgyud pa'i rang lugs 'dzin pa dag gis shes par
NK101(de)004:4163: / bya ste / ye shes gsal sgron las /
NK101(de)004:4164: bdud dang chos su dbye ba la //
NK101(de)004:4165: rnam pa bco brgyad 'di bshad do //
NK101(de)004:4166: gzugs ni phung po'i bdud yin te //
NK101(de)004:4167: bu sogs lha yi bdud du sprul //
NK101(de)004:4168: de la 'dzin pa nyon mongs bdud //
NK101(de)004:4170: dgos pa'i nor yang bar chod bdud //
NK101(de)004:4171: gnod sbyin lha yang de dang 'dra //
NK101(de)004:4172: stong pa phyang chad lha ba'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4173: had po bogs med sgom pa'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4174: rtogs med rang ga spyod pa'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4176: phra mos chog shes thos pa'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4177: rtsa rlung 'khrug pa rlung gi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4178: grub mtha' log pa chos kyi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4179: mi thub dam bca' sdom pa'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4181: las ngan 'brel ba grogs kyi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4182: the tshom skyes na nyams kyi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4183: thabs kyis ma zin shes rab bdud //
NK101(de)004:4184: bar chad bgegs rnams sems shes pas //
NK101(de)004:4185: bdud kyi gegs sel nyams la phan //
NK101(de)004:4187: rang sems ma rtogs bdud du shar //
NK101(de)004:4188: yod pa ngo shes skyabs yin pas //
NK101(de)004:4189: de mtshon ngo sprod 'di ltar bya //
NK101(de)004:4190: snang ba sems su shes par gyis //
NK101(de)004:4191: sems kyi rang bzhin stong pa yin //
NK101(de)004:4192: stong pa 'dzin med bsam du med //
NK101(de)004:4193: bsam med mtha' bral chos sku yin //
NK101(de)004:4194: zin pa rtsol ba'i nad dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4195: lhun gyis gnas par rtogs pa na //
NK101(de)004:4196: de dang ma bral rnal 'byor rgyan //
NK101(de)004:4197: gzhan btsal 'jigs pa'i skyabs mi rnyed //
NK101(de)004:4198: rang byung ye shes skyel ma 'dra //
NK101(de)004:4199: rang sems chos kyi skur rtogs pas //
NK101(de)004:4200: 'jigs pa yi ni nad dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4202: bye brag tu gzhung 'di nyid las gsungs pa ltar na /
NK101(de)004:4204: rgod pa shes pa skye ba gsum //
NK101(de)004:4205: mtshan mar 'dzin pa yul gyi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4206: snga phyi rjes gcod spros pa'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4207: nga bdag 'dzin pa nang gi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4208: shes kyang mi gnas g.yeng ba'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4209: dngos grub rnal ma'i bar du gcod //
NK101(de)004:4210: ces rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi skye ba gsum dang
NK101(de)004:4211: bag chags kyi rten la gnas pa'i cha nas bzhag
NK101(de)004:4212: pa yin te / rgyas par bstan na /
NK101(de)004:4213: rin po che phreng ba las /
NK101(de)004:4214: de la bar chad rtsa ba sems //
NK101(de)004:4215: ma shes pa dang ma goms las //
NK101(de)004:4216: rnam bzhi'i tshul du shar ba yin //
NK101(de)004:4217: nang ltar shar ba 'dzin pa'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4218: nyon mongs longs spyod ma rdzogs pas //
NK101(de)004:4219: gcod byed rjes su 'brangs nas ni //
NK101(de)004:4220: rang smra rang lan rang gis 'debs //
NK101(de)004:4221: rang grol chen po'i bar du gcod //
NK101(de)004:4222: phyi ltar shar ba yul gyi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4223: brtse lnga sprul par ma shar bas //
NK101(de)004:4224: gcod byed rjes su 'brangs nas ni //
NK101(de)004:4225: dang po snang ba'i 'grang bya byed //
NK101(de)004:4226: rjes 'jug tha ma rkun bur byung //
NK101(de)004:4227: snang ba rang grol bar du gcod //
NK101(de)004:4228: rjes 'jug rang rjes bar gyi bdud //
NK101(de)004:4229: spros pa chos skur ma chod pas //
NK101(de)004:4230: phyi nang bar gsum phyi bzhin 'brang //
NK101(de)004:4231: rang bzhin gnyug ma'i bar du gcod //
NK101(de)004:4232: shes pa mi gnas lding ba'i bdud //
NK101(de)004:4233: brtse gdung bral bas dam mi gnas //
NK101(de)004:4234: kha la khyer te spyi la gnas //
NK101(de)004:4235: bag chag brten la de zhen pas //
NK101(de)004:4237: kun grol chen po'i bar du gcod //
NK101(de)004:4239: nyon mongs pa dug lnga longs spyod rdzogs sku rang
NK101(de)004:4240: rig bde chen du ma rdzogs pas nang gi bdud
NK101(de)004:4241: du shar ba kun gzhi la nga bdag tu 'dzin
NK101(de)004:4242: pa'i nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kyis gzung 'dzin
NK101(de)004:4243: rang grol mtshan nyid rang rig chen po'i bar du
NK101(de)004:4245: yul lnga sprul pa'i sku mchog snang la rang bzhin
NK101(de)004:4246: med par ma shar bas phyi yi bdud du gyur
NK101(de)004:4247: pa yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i sgo lnga'i rnam
NK101(de)004:4248: shes kyis snang ba rang grol rnam pa sgyu ma
NK101(de)004:4249: lhun grub kyi bar du gcod la /
NK101(de)004:4250: yid ches kyi spros pa sna tshogs spros bral chos
NK101(de)004:4251: kyi sku ru ma chad pas bar gyi bdud du
NK101(de)004:4252: shar ba phyi nang gnyis ka'i rjes su'ang 'jug cing
NK101(de)004:4253: rang rigs snga ma'i rjes su 'brang ba'i yid kyi
NK101(de)004:4254: kun tu rtog pas rang bzhin spros bral chen po
NK101(de)004:4255: gnyug ma ma bcos pa'i bar du gcod do //
NK101(de)004:4256: de dag sku gsum du ngo shes kyang rtogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:4257: ngang du ma goms pas kun gzhi bag chags kyi
NK101(de)004:4258: rten la tshogs bdun gyi bag chags de dag zhen
NK101(de)004:4259: pas 'khrul 'khor du 'ching ba ldings ba'i bdud kyis
NK101(de)004:4260: gzhi lam gyi nyes pa kun las grol ba'i yongs
NK101(de)004:4261: rdzogs byang chub snying po'i bar du gcod pa'i phyir
NK101(de)004:4262: ro // de rnams dgrol ba'i thabs ni /
NK101(de)004:4264: de dag grol bar bya ba yang //
NK101(de)004:4265: shes pa skye ba gsum yin la //
NK101(de)004:4266: de yi gnas lugs lhun grub gsum //
NK101(de)004:4267: thug phrad gsum la nges bcad la //
NK101(de)004:4268: so ma lhug pa rang dang gzhag /
NK101(de)004:4269: de yis de nyid der grol 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:4270: chu dang 'khyag pa ji bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:4271: de la nan tan gnas pa gces //
NK101(de)004:4274: gdings chen tshad ldan sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4275: rigs rgyud dbang po chig chod du gyur pas rtogs
NK101(de)004:4276: pa'i gdengs chen po tshad dang ldan te rtogs grol
NK101(de)004:4277: dus mnyam du shar nas dgongs don nar son pa'i
NK101(de)004:4279: che long dus gsum dang zhib par dgu phrug tu
NK101(de)004:4280: dbye ba'i rnam grangs gsum po mnyam pa chen po
NK101(de)004:4281: gcig gi ngang du rdzogs te che long dang zhib
NK101(de)004:4282: mo'i bye brag gis dus nam yanga rtogs pa rang
NK101(de)004:4283: gi so las mi 'da' bar brtan pa thob na
NK101(de)004:4284: / sems gnas pa'i thabs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK101(de)004:4285: skyon bcos pa'i tshul rnams ched du ci la che
NK101(de)004:4286: / ste / sems bsam gtan la gnas pas lhag cing /
NK101(de)004:4287: lus rdo rje'i skyil dkrung dang ngaga rdo rje'i bzlas
NK101(de)004:4288: pa yis lhag pa'i rtags gsum dang ldan pa'i lha'i
NK101(de)004:4289: bu kun dga' snying po de nyid rtogs goms chig
NK101(de)004:4290: chod du grol ba bzhin du skad cig gcig gis
NK101(de)004:4292: sprul sku las yang sprul du byon pa'i gsang bdag
NK101(de)004:4293: gi thugs kyi sras mchog dga' rab rdo rje ngas
NK101(de)004:4294: kyang sku gsum gyi dgongs pa'i thugs kyi gsang bcud
NK101(de)004:4295: mthar thug rjogs par 'thungs pas ma he'i zho'i bcud
NK101(de)004:4296: kyang rdo rjer rdo rje'i bcud du chagas par gyur
NK101(de)004:4297: pa yin te / bshad rgyud nges don mdo bcu las /
NK101(de)004:4298: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don //
NK101(de)004:4299: sprul pa'i gang zag skal ldan gyis //
NK101(de)004:4300: ji ltar rtogs shing rig pa de //
NK101(de)004:4301: lung las ma byung man ngag yin //
NK101(de)004:4304: rin chen gter gyi snying po 'di //
NK101(de)004:4305: kun bzang rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
NK101(de)004:4306: gsang ba'i bdag por bka'i bsgo ba //
NK101(de)004:4307: gsang mdzod rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK101(de)004:4308: sum cu rtsa gsum bum thog steng //
NK101(de)004:4309: srog shing rdo rje rtse dgu par //
NK101(de)004:4311: gsang ba gter 'dzin bdag por grags //
NK101(de)004:4312: dga' rab rdo rje bdag nyid kyang //
NK101(de)004:4313: de wa bzang skyong bu thu bo //
NK101(de)004:4314: kun dga' snying po bya ba yin //
NK101(de)004:4315: lag na rdo rje gsang bdag gis //
NK101(de)004:4317: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud //
NK101(de)004:4318: klong dgu bam po nyi khri gsungs //
NK101(de)004:4319: spyi blugs tshangs pa'i dbang bskur nas //
NK101(de)004:4320: dus mtha' nyid kyis sa la bkod //
NK101(de)004:4322: sems rgyud rig pa'i thor cog can //
NK101(de)004:4323: rgyal gyi rigs can d+r+wa ma'i yul //
NK101(de)004:4324: rgya phug d+ha na ko sha'i gling //
NK101(de)004:4325: phug tu gsal ba'i gnas rab bcas //
NK101(de)004:4326: lung gsum brgyud pa'i rtsa ba'i don //
NK101(de)004:4327: dgu rum sbas pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK101(de)004:4328: sems la blan cing bde la bkod //
NK101(de)004:4329: yid la gnag cing lus la bcangs //
NK101(de)004:4330: bka' yi bde chen ma mthong na //
NK101(de)004:4331: phyi nang brgyud pa'i lung la brten //
NK101(de)004:4332: lus ngag sems kyis bya btsal gyis //
NK101(de)004:4333: brkam chags 'dod pa'i chu bo skyed //
NK101(de)004:4334: bde chen srog dang bral mthong nas //
NK101(de)004:4335: gsal rab gnas su dbugs chen phyung //
NK101(de)004:4336: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin te /
NK101(de)004:4338: btsal ba med cing 'dus ma byas //
NK101(de)004:4339: skye 'jig dang bral mi phyed pa //
NK101(de)004:4340: mtha' kun 'joms par byed pa yi //
NK101(de)004:4341: chos lnga'i phyir na rdo rjer brjod //
NK101(de)004:4344: gzhan du yin don sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4345: de lta bu'i blo che ba de la gzhan du
NK101(de)004:4346: blo chung ba dag gis ji ltar yin pa'i don
NK101(de)004:4347: gyi snying po nyid nges par mthong na yang /
NK101(de)004:4348: 'khrul pa la thog ma med pa nas goms par gyur pa'i bag chags stug pos bsgribs pas na /
NK101(de)004:4349: lta ba mthong ba'i don de blo la yang yang
NK101(de)004:4350: 'dris par byas pas bag chags kyi rnyog gzhi sbyor
NK101(de)004:4351: ba don gyi kun gzhi sangs pas /
NK101(de)004:4352: gzhi gnyug ma don gyi kun gzhi la rnam stun
NK101(de)004:4353: byang ba'i yon tan thams cad ye nas gnas pa
NK101(de)004:4354: nyid mngon gyur du rdzogs te snang zhing gsal bar
NK101(de)004:4355: 'gyur ba'i phyir brtson pa dang ldan pas sgom dgos
NK101(de)004:4357: mngon sum snang ba'i ye shes la //
NK101(de)004:4358: sangs rgyas sems can khyad med kyang //
NK101(de)004:4359: rang dbang sems la mi gnas na //
NK101(de)004:4360: sems nyid bde bar spyod mi nus //
NK101(de)004:4361: 'dzin sems dag gi lcags bkrol kyang //
NK101(de)004:4362: goms pa'i bag chags bcings dang 'dra //
NK101(de)004:4363: ye shes 'khor lo rang dbang na //
NK101(de)004:4364: ji ltar gnas kyang bya btsal med //
NK101(de)004:4365: rig pa mtha' med dkyil 'khor la //
NK101(de)004:4366: lus kyis btsal med chos skur gsal //
NK101(de)004:4367: rang snang rig pa'i 'od gsal la //
NK101(de)004:4368: ngag gis btsal med rig pa'i gsung //
NK101(de)004:4369: mi 'gyur kun bzang ye shes la //
NK101(de)004:4370: thugs kyis btsal med bsam dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4372: bsam dang bral ba'i chos nyid la //
NK101(de)004:4373: ye shes 'khor lo rang bzhag ste //
NK101(de)004:4374: dus gsum 'gyur ba med par gnas //
NK101(de)004:4375: rtog pa'i dngos po gang snang yang //
NK101(de)004:4376: rang byung rig pa'i 'khor los gcod //
NK101(de)004:4377: rig pa rgya mtsho'i klong ltar zab //
NK101(de)004:4379: byang chub snying por bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK101(de)004:4380: ngo bo nyid ni dmigs su med //
NK101(de)004:4381: ye shes kun bzang rnam par dag /'bar ba'i ting 'dzin ngo mtshar che //
NK101(de)004:4384: rang sems dag pa chos nyid la //
NK101(de)004:4385: ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa ste //
NK101(de)004:4386: gang ltar bsgoms kyang thig le'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:4387: dper na til gyi mar me bzhin //
NK101(de)004:4388: phyi nang gsal ba'i rig pa'i mdangs //
NK101(de)004:4389: rang sems rtogs pas sangs rgyas pa //
NK101(de)004:4390: 'og ma'i lam lnga sa mi bgrod //
NK101(de)004:4391: gsang sngags thabs lam skad cig gis //
NK101(de)004:4392: sgrib pa'i phung po gsal bar byed //
NK101(de)004:4393: dga' bde sdug bsngal byung tshe na //
NK101(de)004:4394: btang snyoms chen po'i ngang bzhag pas //
NK101(de)004:4395: nges don bdud rtsi'i sman chen 'dis //
NK101(de)004:4396: nyon mongs nad rnams zhi bar mdzad //
NK101(de)004:4398: gnyis pa de ltar lam la goms pas nyams kyi rtags tshad 'char tshul gsal bar bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:4399: drod dang rtags tshad kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa dngos dang /
NK101(de)004:4400: lam gyi don gnad rig pa rang thog tu dbab pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:4402: de ltar rnyog med sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4403: de ltar bag chags kyi rnyog pa med pa'i ngang du 'dris par byas na /
NK101(de)004:4404: ngar 'dzin pa dang phyogs cha dang zhan pa gsum nub cing /
NK101(de)004:4405: blang dor gyi spyod pa dang /
NK101(de)004:4406: rtsing chos kyi spyod pa dang /
NK101(de)004:4407: khengs dregs kyi spyod pa gsum dang bral la /
NK101(de)004:4408: rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan par snang la rang bzhin
NK101(de)004:4409: med pa sgyu ma lta bur snang ba'i ngang du
NK101(de)004:4411: tha snyad rnams la brjed nges byung nas grol du nye ba dang /
NK101(de)004:4412: phyi nang gi dngos po la chags pa chung zhing /
NK101(de)004:4413: 'khrul pa'i snang ba la ya mtshan skye nas sems
NK101(de)004:4414: can la thugs brtse bas 'khor ba mi spel bar
NK101(de)004:4415: phan sems che zhes chen po dang ldan te /
NK101(de)004:4416: de ltar phyi lus la snang ba dang /
NK101(de)004:4417: nang dbugs la snang nas rang gi myong ba'i drod dang /
NK101(de)004:4418: gzhan la'ang snang ba'i rtags dang bcas pa 'char bas
NK101(de)004:4419: nyams kyi rim pa rnams rdzogs par 'gyur bar gsang
NK101(de)004:4420: sngags rgya mtsho'i yang bcud mchog tu gces pa'i chos
NK101(de)004:4421: mdzoda mi zad par 'dzin pas gter gyi bdag po
NK101(de)004:4422: nyid kyis rgyud du gsungs pa yin te /
NK101(de)004:4424: mkha' mnyam ye shes rang byung la //
NK101(de)004:4425: dus gsum 'da' ba med par gnas //
NK101(de)004:4426: rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor nas //
NK101(de)004:4430: mthong ba sna tshogs rig pa'i nyams //
NK101(de)004:4431: dang po gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:4432: chu drag 'bab pa'i dpe yis bstan //
NK101(de)004:4434: gnyis pa la ni mi g.yo ba //
NK101(de)004:4435: rgya mtsho'i gting bzhin mi gayo'o //
NK101(de)004:4436: gsum pa bzhi pa 'bras bu'i nyams //
NK101(de)004:4437: mnyam nyid ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:4438: snang ba rnam rtog cir mi bstan //
NK101(de)004:4439: dran pa kun spangs ye shes nyid //
NK101(de)004:4440: zin pas rtsol ba'i nad spangs te //
NK101(de)004:4441: lhun gyis gnas par bzhag pa yin //
NK101(de)004:4442: zhes sogs kyis bstan te rgyas par bsam gtan nyams kyi sgron ma las shes pa bya la /
NK101(de)004:4443: ji ltar gom pa'i tshul yang /
NK101(de)004:4445: nyams blangs goms pas mthar 'gyur te //
NK101(de)004:4446: ji ltar bsam pas bzung ba'i blo //
NK101(de)004:4447: ma lus par ni zad gyur nas //
NK101(de)004:4448: mi rtog ye shes gsal mthar phyin //
NK101(de)004:4449: 'gyur med sems kyi g.yung drung la //
NK101(de)004:4450: ye shes rang gsal gyi nar bzhag /
NK101(de)004:4451: dran pa'i rkyen gyis ma shor te //
NK101(de)004:4452: de nyid tshod du lhug par zhog /
NK101(de)004:4455: gnad las byung ba'i mngon sum nyid //
NK101(de)004:4457: rang bzhin dag pas g.yengs pa med //
NK101(de)004:4458: rgyun du gnas pas 'bral ba med //
NK101(de)004:4459: rang snang yin pas rnam rtog zad //
NK101(de)004:4460: rlung zad ye shes nyid la spyod //
NK101(de)004:4462: 'gro drug lam gyi rgyun gcod do //
NK101(de)004:4464: der ma zad dang po'i las can rnams kyis shes
NK101(de)004:4465: rab gsum dang lam lnga la rim pa ltar brten
NK101(de)004:4466: pa'i tshul yang / ye shes gsal sgron la /
NK101(de)004:4467: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK101(de)004:4468: phyi nang chos la sgro 'dogs gcod //
NK101(de)004:4469: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK101(de)004:4470: de don rgyud la goms par bya //
NK101(de)004:4471: tha ma sgom pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK101(de)004:4472: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i nyon mongs gzhom //
NK101(de)004:4473: tshogs lam bla ma mtshon ldan la //
NK101(de)004:4474: mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod pa 'bul //
NK101(de)004:4475: sbyor lam bla ma'i gdams ngag gis //
NK101(de)004:4476: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK101(de)004:4477: mthong lam spyan lnga dag pa yis //
NK101(de)004:4478: rang sems skye med mthong bar bya //
NK101(de)004:4479: sgom lam ting 'dzin rnam gsum gyis //
NK101(de)004:4480: gnyug ma'i yid la goms par bya //
NK101(de)004:4481: mthar phyin nyes pa gnyis zad pas //
NK101(de)004:4482: chos rnams zad par bskyal bar bya //
NK101(de)004:4483: nga ni thabs kyi sa mkhan te //
NK101(de)004:4484: thar lam tshol ba lam 'dir shog /
NK101(de)004:4487: gnas lugs ming la sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyi bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4488: de yang ye shes rdzogs pa las /
NK101(de)004:4489: ye shes rdzogs pa'i sems bskyed bzung //
NK101(de)004:4490: spros pa'i sems ldan don la sbyor //
NK101(de)004:4491: rang bzhag rig pa ma yin pa //
NK101(de)004:4492: brda sgo rtog pa'i rjes ma 'brang //
NK101(de)004:4493: bde chen gsang ba'i 'khor lo la //
NK101(de)004:4494: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin pas //
NK101(de)004:4495: chos can chos nyid gang yang min //
NK101(de)004:4496: 'dod pa'i blo yis gang sbyor ba //
NK101(de)004:4497: dman pa'i sems la bstan par zad //
NK101(de)004:4499: gnas lugs brjod med chen po ming gis mtshon pa la mi gnas pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:4500: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che las /
NK101(de)004:4501: sla zhing dka' la sla phyir dka' //
NK101(de)004:4502: mngon sum mi gnas kun tu khyab //
NK101(de)004:4503: ming tsam 'di zhes mtshon par ni //
NK101(de)004:4504: rdo rje sems dpas yongs ma gsungs //
NK101(de)004:4507: me long dwangs pa'i brnyan mar ltag /
NK101(de)004:4508: rdo rje gsang ba'i gdams pa yis //
NK101(de)004:4509: rig pa'i ye shes kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:4510: yi ge med pa'i don du mthong //
NK101(de)004:4512: gnyis med ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo ma 'dres kun
NK101(de)004:4513: rdzogs su rtogs pa'i don ni de ma yin pa'i
NK101(de)004:4514: ldog pa las grol ba'i phyir /
NK101(de)004:4516: ye shes rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:4517: kun spangs kun gyi dngos gzhi can //
NK101(de)004:4519: byang chub sems su brjod pa yin //
NK101(de)004:4522: phyi rol nang na gnas pa yi //
NK101(de)004:4523: don rnams ma lus ldan par bya //
NK101(de)004:4524: thams cad spang ba'i gzhi med de //
NK101(de)004:4525: de nyid don de yin phyir ro //
NK101(de)004:4526: zhes bka' stsal bar mdzad pasa na //
NK101(de)004:4527: kun grol chen po'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid rang
NK101(de)004:4528: gis rang la dris nas shes rab kyi spyan gyis
NK101(de)004:4531: lhun gyis grub pa'i bde chen de //
NK101(de)004:4532: mtshungs pa med pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK101(de)004:4533: rang gi mthu yis rig pa las //
NK101(de)004:4537: rang sems ston par ma shes na //
NK101(de)004:4538: rang byung mthong bar yang mi 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:4539: des na ye shes rdzogs pa'i don //
NK101(de)004:4540: rang rig bde bas shes par gyis //
NK101(de)004:4543: rang snang thabs kyi rgyal po las //
NK101(de)004:4544: stobs kyi rig pa ma 'gags pas //
NK101(de)004:4545: rang gi shes rab nyid la dris //
NK101(de)004:4546: dmigs pa med pa'i ting 'dzin ni //
NK101(de)004:4547: bya btsal bral ba'i ngang du dris //
NK101(de)004:4548: yul gsal thog ma med pa'i sems //
NK101(de)004:4549: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings la dris //
NK101(de)004:4550: de ni dgongs pa'i don du bstan //
NK101(de)004:4552: des na go rim bzhin du brda don brgyud pa'i
NK101(de)004:4553: bla ma dran pas ji zhig mtshon pa'i tshig tu
NK101(de)004:4554: smra ste brjod du med la /
NK101(de)004:4555: gang yang mnyam pa yin pa la de las gzhan
NK101(de)004:4556: du ji skad brjod pa dang don la mi 'gal
NK101(de)004:4558: rang la rang gis shod cig bu mchog rnams /
NK101(de)004:4560: gsum pa sgom ma sgom gyi skyon yon rnam par dbye ste phrang bsal ba la /
NK101(de)004:4561: rtogs goms la gnas pa'i phan yon bstan te spro ba skyed /
NK101(de)004:4562: de ltar ma gnas pa'i nyes skyon bstan nas sgom dgos par gdams pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:4564: de ltar le lo sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4565: gong du bstan pa de ltar don chen zab mo'i
NK101(de)004:4566: nges gsang la mi brtson pa'i le lo dang 'jig
NK101(de)004:4567: rten gyi g.yeng ba mtha' dag spangsa nas dmigs pa'i
NK101(de)004:4568: yul du ma gtad pa'i ngang nas rtog pa'i don
NK101(de)004:4569: la rtag tu gnas par 'gyur na /
NK101(de)004:4570: bskal pa grangs med mang po nas bsags pa yi /
NK101(de)004:4571: sdiga pa dang sgrib pa'i mun nag tu 'phyan pa'i bag chags kyi rnyogs ma thams cad sangs te /
NK101(de)004:4572: don gyi gnas tshul rnam par byang ba'i rgya mtsho chen po de nyid dwangs pa las /
NK101(de)004:4573: yid la bsam pa bzhin du 'dod rgu tshad med
NK101(de)004:4574: pa sbyin par byed pas yon tan mi zad pa'i
