NK101(de)004:4575: gter mchog rang nyid la mngon gyur du 'achara bar
NK101(de)004:4576: 'gyur bas bdag nyid bde ba chen por grol nas
NK101(de)004:4577: / gdul bya'i 'gro ba skal ldan lam mchog 'di
NK101(de)004:4578: yi don la mos pa rnams kyi bde bas dbul
NK101(de)004:4579: ba sel ba yang zhar la 'char bar 'gyur ba
NK101(de)004:4580: ni dper na 'bras 'khar ma lo 'bras legs na
NK101(de)004:4581: phub sog zhor la 'byung ba lta bur nges te
NK101(de)004:4583: 'khor ba nyid kyi don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4584: mya ngan 'das zhes yod ma yin //
NK101(de)004:4585: nyon mongs lnga yi don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4586: ye shes ming du yod ma yin //
NK101(de)004:4587: sdug bsngal nyid kyi don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4588: bde ba chen po btsal du med //
NK101(de)004:4589: skyon gyi mtha' nyid rab rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4590: yon tan chen po btsal mi dgos //
NK101(de)004:4591: 'khrul pa nyid kyi don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4592: 'khrul med rig pa btsal mi dgos //
NK101(de)004:4593: 'byung lnga nyid kyi don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4594: chen po lnga nyid babs kyis grub //
NK101(de)004:4595: ma rig nyid kyi rtsad chod na //
NK101(de)004:4596: rig pa'i sku nyid ma bsgrub 'grub //
NK101(de)004:4597: sems can nyid kyi don shes na //
NK101(de)004:4598: sangs rgyas nyid kyang ma btsal rnyed //
NK101(de)004:4599: sna tshogs snang ba'i don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4600: rang rig 'od snang ma btsal rnyed //
NK101(de)004:4601: rtog pa nyid kyi rjes chod na //
NK101(de)004:4602: 'khrul pa de nyid rang sar grol //
NK101(de)004:4603: stong pa snang ba'i don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4604: ye shes sku yang lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:4605: dngos por snang ba'i phugs mthong na //
NK101(de)004:4606: stong pa nyid kyang ma bsgrubs rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:4607: chos nyid a yi don rtogs na //
NK101(de)004:4608: skye med chos nyid pha rol phyin //
NK101(de)004:4611: ye shes rgya mtsho mu mtha' med //
NK101(de)004:4612: 'od gsal rig pa gdengs ldan la //
NK101(de)004:4613: mtshon pa'i lam gyis brgyud dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4614: rang byung lung gi don mthong bas //
NK101(de)004:4615: lung chen tshad ma kun gyi bdag /
NK101(de)004:4617: chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK101(de)004:4618: rang byung gsal ba'i nyi ma shar //
NK101(de)004:4619: bsam sbyor blo yi dri ma dag /'dod 'jug rim rtsol kun dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4620: bsam med rang bzhag spyod par gnas //
NK101(de)004:4621: sku gsum rig pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK101(de)004:4622: thugs rje nyi ma'i zer shar nas //
NK101(de)004:4624: thabs kyi rim pa rang shar nas //
NK101(de)004:4625: ye shes gsal bas 'gro don mdzad //
NK101(de)004:4626: ye shes rang byung 'dren skur shar //
NK101(de)004:4627: sna tshogs sprul sku rin chen spros //
NK101(de)004:4628: gang dag dman pa'i 'khor dag la //
NK101(de)004:4629: blo dang mthun pa'i bstan pa bkod //
NK101(de)004:4632: gzhan du skyon kyang sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4633: yon tan las gzhan du ma bsgoms pa'i skyon kyang
NK101(de)004:4634: yon tan de las bzlog pa dang mtshungsa te gong
NK101(de)004:4635: dang sbyar la / de bzhin du zhen pa drug
NK101(de)004:4636: gi sdug bsngal dang theg pa brgyad kyi rtsol ba'i
NK101(de)004:4638: dper bkod na ston thog lo legs pa'i 'bras bu
NK101(de)004:4639: nas sran gro 'bras til nyung ba drug po rtsal
NK101(de)004:4640: rdzogs par smin kyang ma bsdus pa'i dpe ltar /
NK101(de)004:4641: rtogs nas ma goms pa'i don 'dir yang de dang
NK101(de)004:4642: 'dra bar sbyar la gzhan yang rgyal po chen po
NK101(de)004:4643: la sras mtshan nyid dang ldan pa gcig yod pa
NK101(de)004:4644: yin na de nyid rang dang mi mthun pa'i srin
NK101(de)004:4645: pos bzung nas dbang du ma gyur na /
NK101(de)004:4646: rang gi rgyal bu yin ngosa su mthong yang rgyal
NK101(de)004:4647: po'i gdung rgyud mi zina pa'i dpe dang yang 'dra
NK101(de)004:4650: ji ltar rtogs pa'i don la brtson //
NK101(de)004:4651: bka' gzhung rgya mtshor mkhas gsal yang //
NK101(de)004:4652: goms pa'i zil gnon rgyan bral na //
NK101(de)004:4653: mtshan ma'i chu klung sgrol ma yin //
NK101(de)004:4656: goms pa'i lcags sgrog bcings pa 'dra //
NK101(de)004:4657: khyung dang seng ge'i gshog rgyangs rtsal //
NK101(de)004:4658: mngal dang sgong ngas bsgribs dang mtshungs //
NK101(de)004:4659: nges par gdengs su ma gyur na //
NK101(de)004:4660: thos zin go zhing rtogs byas kyang //
NK101(de)004:4662: 'dun pa drag pos mos byas na //
NK101(de)004:4663: 'brel bas mjal ba'i gzungs thag tsam //
NK101(de)004:4664: bskal par sbyangs kyang mthar ma phyin //
NK101(de)004:4665: snying po rnal ma'i snod ldan pa'o //
NK101(de)004:4667: skyon de ltar yod pa des na rtogs pa'i ngang
NK101(de)004:4668: la ma yengs par zhi gnas dang lhag mthong zung
NK101(de)004:4669: du 'brel ba'i sgo goms par byed pa ni shin
NK101(de)004:4672: ma bsgoms pa yi skyon nyid ni //
NK101(de)004:4673: 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid mngon snang bas //
NK101(de)004:4674: bdag dang gzhan te yul shes nas dang //
NK101(de)004:4675: tshig dang bcas pa'i lta ba dang //
NK101(de)004:4676: dmigs dang bcas pa'i yul dag dang //
NK101(de)004:4678: sangs rgyas lam yang stor ba dang //
NK101(de)004:4679: 'bras bu'i rang bzhin ma shes dang //
NK101(de)004:4680: chos kun mnyam pa'i gzhi med dang //
NK101(de)004:4681: rang rig khams gsum 'ching ba dang //
NK101(de)004:4682: rtog dang bcas te ltung bar 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:4684: ma gol gnas pa'i bsgom pa ni //
NK101(de)004:4685: dbang po'i sgo rnams gsal ba la //
NK101(de)004:4686: yid kyi rtog pa ma 'gyus pas //
NK101(de)004:4687: shes pa nyid la dpyod pa'i yid //
NK101(de)004:4688: phyir la shor ba med pa nyid //
NK101(de)004:4689: ris can gsal ba ma yin dang //
NK101(de)004:4690: gud bcad stong bar ma song dang //
NK101(de)004:4691: bde ba rgyun chags ma yin dang //
NK101(de)004:4692: btang snyoms lteng por ma song dang //
NK101(de)004:4693: dran rig gsal ba ngal gso dang //
NK101(de)004:4694: sbyongs pa log cha'i lam song dang //
NK101(de)004:4695: 'dzin cha nang du rgyun bde bar //
NK101(de)004:4696: cha lugs gsal ba'i 'dzin cha dang //
NK101(de)004:4697: kha dog yig 'bru sgyur byed rnams //
NK101(de)004:4698: de rnams phyogs su ma ltung na //
NK101(de)004:4699: ma gol gnas pa'i bsgom pa'o //
NK101(de)004:4700: zhes gsungs te 'di nyid gnad che bas cung zad bkrol na /
NK101(de)004:4701: ma gol bar gnas pa'i bsgom pa ni /
NK101(de)004:4702: tshogs drug gi dbang po'i sgo rnams rang gsal ba la /
NK101(de)004:4703: 'dir bstan pa'i yid gnyis la 'du la /
NK101(de)004:4704: zhib par dbye na gsang ba snying tig gi gzhung
NK101(de)004:4705: las yid drug tu gsungs pa ltar yid kyi byung
NK101(de)004:4706: tshor gyi rtog pa ma 'gyus pas na /
NK101(de)004:4707: stong nyid bsam ngo dang bral ba'i sgom la /
NK101(de)004:4708: phyi rol snang grags kyi chos rnams 'gag med du
NK101(de)004:4709: shes pa nyid la der dpyod pa'i yid rtog rlung
NK101(de)004:4710: la brten nas phyir la shor ba med pa nyid
NK101(de)004:4711: kyi rig dang de mtha' bral yongs rdzogs su skyong
NK101(de)004:4712: ba na / ris can gyi dmigs pa gtad pa phyogs re la gsal ba las /
NK101(de)004:4713: gzhan du de ltar ma yin na /
NK101(de)004:4714: rtag par rang shes la 'jug pa'i sgom pa zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:4715: don gyis khams gsum du 'jug pa'i sgom pa yin
NK101(de)004:4716: pas de ltar ma yin par gsal ba rang ngo
NK101(de)004:4717: la gsal la rtog pa phyogs su ma lhung na
NK101(de)004:4719: yang sems gud du bcad pa'i dus na phyi mi
NK101(de)004:4720: stong la nang stong par song na rnam pa kha
NK101(de)004:4721: 'khyal ba'i sgom pa zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:4722: de ltar ma song bar 'di dus stong nyid ngos
NK101(de)004:4723: bzung dang bral bar shes na sgom gsha' ma yin
NK101(de)004:4724: no // yang bsgom pa'i dus lus ngag gi bde
NK101(de)004:4725: ba khyad par can skyes te de la sems rgyun
NK101(de)004:4726: du chags na zhen pa mtha' yas pa'i sgom pa
NK101(de)004:4727: no // zhes bya ste / de ltar ma yin par /
NK101(de)004:4728: bde ba rang lugs su 'byung la sems nyid rang
NK101(de)004:4729: ngo na gsal yang de la ngos bzung ma rnyed
NK101(de)004:4730: pa ni sgom gsha' ma ma yin no //
NK101(de)004:4731: yang bsgoms pas shes pa btang snyoms su lteng gis
NK101(de)004:4732: song nas de las bogs skyed med pa ni bde
NK101(de)004:4733: chen skye med pa'i sgom pa zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:4735: phyi nang bzhin gyis gsal la /
NK101(de)004:4736: nang rang bzhin ma bcos par mnyam bzhag la lteng gis song na sgom gsha' ma yin no //
NK101(de)004:4737: yang sgom pas phyi nang gi dran rig ma 'gags par gsal ba la /
NK101(de)004:4738: shes pa'i 'phro ma chad par de nyid kyi steng du rang sor bzhag pa ni /
NK101(de)004:4739: sgo lnga'i yul rkyen ma bcos pa'i sgom zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:4740: de nyid du ngal gso mi byed par /
NK101(de)004:4741: dran rig ma 'gags kyang de las 'dzin byed kyi shes pa phyir ma shor bar /
NK101(de)004:4742: nang rig pa rang ngo na gsal ba ni sgom gsha' ma yin no //
NK101(de)004:4744: sems kyi sbyangs pa log cha'i sgom pa sems mtha'
NK101(de)004:4745: yas par khyer nas shes pa nyams thog tu mi
NK101(de)004:4746: phebs pa ni sems rtogs pa sna tshogs pa'i phyir
NK101(de)004:4747: shor ba ste lam gyi snang cha log pa'i sgom
NK101(de)004:4748: pa zhes bya ba yin pas /
NK101(de)004:4750: sems stong pa rang bzhin med par sbyangs pas sems
NK101(de)004:4751: nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal ba nang du stong pa
NK101(de)004:4752: ngos bzung dang bral ba ni sgom gsha' ma yin
NK101(de)004:4753: no // yang sems kyi 'dzin pa'i cha gang de nang du rgyun du bde yang /
NK101(de)004:4754: shes pa gsal tsam las phyi snang ba'i gnod pa
NK101(de)004:4755: ma spong ba ni yul sems nang du log pa'i
NK101(de)004:4757: de nyid du ma song bar nang du bde bar
NK101(de)004:4758: shar la phyir gsal bar nyams su myong na sgom
NK101(de)004:4760: yang stong pa nyid du sgom pa'i dus na yi
NK101(de)004:4761: dam lha yi cha lugs gsal ba'i rnam pa sems
NK101(de)004:4762: kyis 'dzin pa'i char gsal na mtshan ma rang rgyud
NK101(de)004:4763: la blos lta ba'i sgom pa zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:4764: de lta ma song bar nang du sems nyid stong par gsal bas 'gyur ba rang chod /
NK101(de)004:4765: phyir snang ba stong par gsal bas dngos po rang dag pa ni sgom gsha' ma yin no //
NK101(de)004:4766: yang stong nyid ngos bzung dang bral bar ma shes pas /
NK101(de)004:4767: rlung gi kha dog bsgom pa dang /
NK101(de)004:4769: de'i rnam pa sgyur bar byed pa rnams su sgom
NK101(de)004:4770: pa ni stong nyid dngos po la mthar lhung pa'i
NK101(de)004:4772: de ltar ma yin par nang rtog pa'i spros par rang chod nas gsal bar nyams su myong /
NK101(de)004:4773: phyi mtshan ma'i spros pa rang chod nas stong par
NK101(de)004:4774: nyams su myong ba ni sgom gsha' ma yin no
NK101(de)004:4775: // de ltar dgu po rnams kyi mi mthun pa'i
NK101(de)004:4776: phyogs su ma lhung bar rig pa lhun grub rin
NK101(de)004:4777: po che gsang ba'i dbyings rang gsal chen po spros
NK101(de)004:4778: pa ma lus pa kun rnam par dag pa'i ngang
NK101(de)004:4779: la gnas na ma gol bar gnas pa'i bsgom pa
NK101(de)004:4780: // zhes bya'o // de ltar 'grel rin chen sgron ma las gsungs pa'i gnas bsdus pa'o //
NK101(de)004:4781: de bas mtha' bral gting gsal chen po rang rig
NK101(de)004:4782: skye ba med pa'i ngang du mi g.yo bar gnas
NK101(de)004:4783: pa de ni zhi gnas dang lhag mthong zung du
NK101(de)004:4784: 'jug par rtogs nas nor 'khrul dang bral bar yang
NK101(de)004:4785: dag pa'i sgom pa yin te /
NK101(de)004:4788: zang thal rig pa rjen par bzhag /
NK101(de)004:4789: brtan pa bogs dbyung la bzla bas //
NK101(de)004:4790: rang sems dag pa chos sku yin //
NK101(de)004:4791: rang byung ye shes mtha' las 'das //
NK101(de)004:4792: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK101(de)004:4793: rig pa yul gyi mi gnod pa //
NK101(de)004:4797: rnam pa rang bzhin mtshan nyid rnams //
NK101(de)004:4798: bde ba chen por lhun grub pa //
NK101(de)004:4799: lung dang man ngag rig nyams kyis //
NK101(de)004:4800: rtogs pa'i ngang du goms byed pas //
NK101(de)004:4801: de yang ye nas gnas pa las //
NK101(de)004:4802: ma rtogs log brtags nges shes pa'ang //
NK101(de)004:4803: 'khrul pa'i ngan shugs stobs drag pas //
NK101(de)004:4804: gshis kyi ngang du ma goms na //
NK101(de)004:4805: ngo shes tsam gyis mthar ma phyin //
NK101(de)004:4806: rtogs nas ngang du gnas pa de //
NK101(de)004:4807: mkhyen pa'i bsam pa klong du gyur //
NK101(de)004:4808: bsam gtan chen po rtsol bral yin //
NK101(de)004:4809: yengs pa'i dogs med klong chen por //
NK101(de)004:4810: 'bral med don gyi gzungs chen ldan //
NK101(de)004:4811: ye shes ngang gnas ting 'dzin mchog /
NK101(de)004:4812: tshogs brgyad rba rlabs rang zhi ste //
NK101(de)004:4813: bde chen ngang gnas ma spangs lhag /
NK101(de)004:4814: yul med shes rab spyan gyis gzigs //
NK101(de)004:4815: dbyer med rig pa gcig gi ngang //
NK101(de)004:4816: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK101(de)004:4818: de ltar sgro 'dogs gcod pa ni shin tu gces te //
NK101(de)004:4819: kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches //
NK101(de)004:4820: ting 'dzin mngon du ma gyur na //
NK101(de)004:4821: bag la nyal ba'i mdud pa yis //
NK101(de)004:4822: lhun grub mngon du mi 'gyur bas //
NK101(de)004:4823: bsam gtan sgro 'dogs gcod pa gces //
NK101(de)004:4825: gnyis pa de la dngos brgyud nas 'jug pa'i thabs sgo mang ba'i khyad par bstan pa la /
NK101(de)004:4826: blo che ba la rin chen brgyud pa'i thabs kyi dngos su ston tshul /
NK101(de)004:4827: blo chung ba la brgyud nas 'jug pa'i thabs kyi rnam grangs ston tshul /
NK101(de)004:4828: de dag kyang mthar thug don lam la 'dzud pa'i khyad par 'phags tshul bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:4830: thabs rgyal brgyud pa'i sogs rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4831: de yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK101(de)004:4832: bskal pa grangs med sngon rol nas //
NK101(de)004:4833: rdzogs chen don la sbyangs sbyangs pa //
NK101(de)004:4834: ye shes gsang ba'i snod du basngagasa //
NK101(de)004:4835: sgo nga'i nang gi khyung phrug ltar //
NK101(de)004:4836: 'khor ba nyid du ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:4837: sgong chag mkha' la 'phur ba ltar //
NK101(de)004:4838: rtogs pas ma bcos bla ma'i sa //
NK101(de)004:4839: rgya mtsho'i bcud 'dus bdud rtsi bzhin //
NK101(de)004:4841: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK101(de)004:4842: zhes gsungs pa ltar mtshan nyid rdzogs pa'i skal bzang
NK101(de)004:4843: dam pa blo ldan dbang po gsal ba la thabs
NK101(de)004:4844: kun gyi rgyal po snyan khung brgyuda pa'i gdams ngag
NK101(de)004:4845: rin chen 'bar ba gsal bar byed pa'i snying po'i
NK101(de)004:4846: yang bcud chen po'i brda don bkrol ba 'di nyid
NK101(de)004:4847: kyis / dper na rgyal bu mtshan ldan rgyal sar
NK101(de)004:4848: bton pas rgyal po chen por mngon sum du grub
NK101(de)004:4849: para zhes grub pa lta bur sbyar nas bstan pa
NK101(de)004:4850: kyis / yin te / ye shes rdzogs pa las /
NK101(de)004:4851: ye shes rdzogs pa bde ba chen //
NK101(de)004:4852: mtha' yas 'gro ba kun la ldan //
NK101(de)004:4853: rig pa dbyer med kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:4854: gang yang ma yin rig par gsol //
NK101(de)004:4855: rtsol ba'i sems bral mngon sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:4857: rnam byang shes pa rang gnas pa //
NK101(de)004:4858: byed pa nyid kyis mthong bar gyis //
NK101(de)004:4860: ye shes rdzogs pa lung gis ni //
NK101(de)004:4861: thams cad ye shes ngo bor gsal //
NK101(de)004:4862: zhen pa'i sgro skur ma lus pa //
NK101(de)004:4863: ye shes rig pa'i 'khor los gcod //
NK101(de)004:4864: rang gsal rig pa'i snang ba la //
NK101(de)004:4865: gang ldan gsal ba'i rig pas mthong //
NK101(de)004:4868: rdo rje'i bka' ni rtogs pa'i lam //
NK101(de)004:4869: byed pa'i sgra la gnyer ba'i sems //
NK101(de)004:4870: tshul bzang rtsol la gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)004:4871: byed pa'i don dang 'phrad gyur nas //
NK101(de)004:4872: bya ba'i rang bzhin shes par bya //
NK101(de)004:4873: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa nyid rig pa //
NK101(de)004:4874: gsum gyi byed pa'i 'od kyis mthong //
NK101(de)004:4875: gsum gyis 'od gsal gzhi yi lam //
NK101(de)004:4876: byed dang bral ba nyid la gnas //
NK101(de)004:4877: zhes sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK101(de)004:4878: de lta bu gdams ngag gi rgyal po gsal byed rin chen 'bar ba 'di ni /
NK101(de)004:4879: thabs gzhan la rag las pa med de /
NK101(de)004:4881: ma lus 'dus pa'i snying po'i don //
NK101(de)004:4882: rgyu yis ma bskyed rkyen dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4883: bden bzhi rtogs pa'i rgyu dang bral //
NK101(de)004:4885: mtshon med sems kyi ngo bo la //
NK101(de)004:4886: shes rab thabs kyis mtshon du med //
NK101(de)004:4887: rgyu 'bras bral ba'i rig pa la //
NK101(de)004:4888: dbyings dang ye shes rgyu 'bras bral //
NK101(de)004:4889: zhes sogs rgyas par bstan pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)004:4890: rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i theg rim brgyad kyi thabs la mi ltos pa'i tshul /
NK101(de)004:4892: skyon rnams ma spangs yon tan rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:4893: don grub dgra bcom pa las grol //
NK101(de)004:4895: yid bzhin bde ba'i sa las grol //
NK101(de)004:4896: ma sbyangs ma bsags gnas pas grol //
NK101(de)004:4897: lhun rdzogs mdo sde'i sa las grol //
NK101(de)004:4898: bya ba'i las grol yon tan rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:4899: gnyis la ma brten ngang du rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:4900: yan lag dgu yis goms las grol //
NK101(de)004:4901: gnyis lta grol nas yon tan shar //
NK101(de)004:4902: bla dor rnam rtog bde chen gnas //
NK101(de)004:4903: phyi nang mi mnga' spro bsdu med //
NK101(de)004:4904: thams cad de bzhin nyid sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:4905: thub pa'i bsam gtan las grol ba'o //
NK101(de)004:4906: bskyed las rdzogs par btsal ba bral //
NK101(de)004:4907: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis sgrub mi byed //
NK101(de)004:4908: cho ga sngags dang yo byad rnams //
NK101(de)004:4909: btsal bas ma yin ye grol ba'o //
NK101(de)004:4910: rdzogs tshul dkyil 'khor gtsor byed min //
NK101(de)004:4911: dbyings dang ye shes rgyu 'bras bral //
NK101(de)004:4912: brtul zhugs grangs la rag ma las //
NK101(de)004:4913: phyogs med bde chen ye rdzogs mjal //
NK101(de)004:4914: che ba'i che ba zab mo yis //
NK101(de)004:4915: yon tan cir yang basngagasa pa med //
NK101(de)004:4916: don rnams ji bzhin mi bskyod de //
NK101(de)004:4917: bya ba med pas grol ba'ang sgrol //
NK101(de)004:4920: 'khor lo'am rig ma'i bde ba yis //
NK101(de)004:4921: rang gnas rig pa tshol ba nyid //
NK101(de)004:4922: rnam rtog yin te don la min //
NK101(de)004:4923: chags pa'i 'du shes drang ba'i don //
NK101(de)004:4924: nges par spros bral rang byung sems //
NK101(de)004:4925: chags pa'i lam gyis shes mi 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:4926: blang dor med pa'i brtul zhugs kyang //
NK101(de)004:4927: nges par brtags na blang dor nyid //
NK101(de)004:4928: rang rig bsam bral bzhag pa de //
NK101(de)004:4929: don la dngos 'dzin zhen par gnas //
NK101(de)004:4931: rnal 'byor rdzogs pa bcos med la //
NK101(de)004:4932: 'dod spyod thig le spro bsdu med //
NK101(de)004:4933: ye nas rdzogs pa rnam dag la //
NK101(de)004:4934: bsam gtan yan lag kun dang ldan //
NK101(de)004:4935: rlung gis 'jug pa rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:4936: ye shes brtsal med bde ba la //
NK101(de)004:4937: dga' ba bzhi yi yan lag gnas //
NK101(de)004:4938: gsang spyod thabs la ma brtan yang //
NK101(de)004:4939: rin chen snang ba'i thabs kyis shes //
NK101(de)004:4940: brda sprod tshig la gnas gyur kyang //
NK101(de)004:4941: thig le rang byung nyid las 'char //
NK101(de)004:4943: sgyu ma'i ro la ma chags pas //
NK101(de)004:4944: chags med ye shes rdzogs pa'i lam //
NK101(de)004:4945: byang chub sems kyi rang gsal 'di //
NK101(de)004:4946: dngos med shes rab thabs kyis 'grub //
NK101(de)004:4948: ngo bo ma grub me shel 'dra //
NK101(de)004:4949: dngos med ye shes mthong bas grol //
NK101(de)004:4950: gzugs sogs snang ba brtags pa yin //
NK101(de)004:4951: dngos po rang bzhin thams cad ni //
NK101(de)004:4952: chos nyid dbyings kyi thig le yin //
NK101(de)004:4953: de nyid sgrub pa'i thabs su ni //
NK101(de)004:4954: snying po rig pa'i nyi shar bas //
NK101(de)004:4955: mtha' yi mun pa ngang gi dag /
NK101(de)004:4956: sgrub med rang byung bsgrubs pa 'dis //
NK101(de)004:4957: khams gsum 'od gsal thugs su grub //
NK101(de)004:4960: dran rtog rlung gis sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4961: 'on kyang rig pa dran rtog gi rlung gis g.yengas
NK101(de)004:4962: nas rnam par rtog pas 'phyar te blo mi gnas
NK101(de)004:4963: na / g.yo ba 'dzin pa rlung gi man ngag
NK101(de)004:4964: rlung gzung ba la sogs pa'i thabs rnams sbyin te
NK101(de)004:4965: na / / lus dang sems klong la ye shes kyi rlung gi gzer chen po gdab pas /
NK101(de)004:4966: zhor la 'byung ba thun mong gi dngos grub tshe ring ba la sogs pa dang /
NK101(de)004:4967: mthar thug mchog gi dngos grub kyang rdzogs par 'gyur la /
NK101(de)004:4968: yang gdul bya khams gsum gyi dang po'i zhes dang
NK101(de)004:4969: po 'dod pa'i khams kyi mi rnams ni 'dod chags
NK101(de)004:4970: kyi shas draga pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:4971: chags pa la brten te mtshan ma'i spros pa la
NK101(de)004:4972: 'chel nas der zhen gyi dbang gis blo mi gnas
NK101(de)004:4973: pa la / bde ba thig le'i man ngag 'og
NK101(de)004:4974: sgo khams gsum rol pa'i thabs spyod rnams bstan nas
NK101(de)004:4975: mthar 'di la gzud par bya ba sogs gang la
NK101(de)004:4976: gang 'os su bya ba yin no //
NK101(de)004:4977: des na thabs sna tshogs kyis drangs tshul dam tshig gi klong las gsungs nas /
NK101(de)004:4979: de ltar btang snyoms mi gzhag nus tshad drangs //
NK101(de)004:4980: cis kyang rang rgyud dregs pa'i mtshon rno na //
NK101(de)004:4981: re zhig gdul bya ma yin phyis smon la //
NK101(de)004:4982: gcan gzan rgyal po'i tshul du sngar tshul blangs //
NK101(de)004:4985: mdor na gang skyes sogs rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:4986: mdor na thabs kyi rim pa gang la brten nas rtogs pa skyes kyang /
NK101(de)004:4988: sems kyi rnam grangs gang dang gang //
NK101(de)004:4989: de dang de yi rjes mthun par //
NK101(de)004:4990: rdo rje zam pa ma chad pa'i //
NK101(de)004:4991: bla ma rin chen srog gyur des //
NK101(de)004:4992: de de'i sgo nas gter kha dbye //
NK101(de)004:4993: de nyid sgo kun phye ba yin //
NK101(de)004:4994: dbyig gi rdzas dang 'phrad pa yin //
NK101(de)004:4995: dper na lha yi nor bu la //
NK101(de)004:4996: man+dala rtsegs pa'i sgo bzhi yod //
NK101(de)004:4997: gang phye'ang de nyid thob par 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:4998: 'di ni rgyal thabs rin chen te //
NK101(de)004:4999: rtsol dang bral ba'i dngos grub yin //
NK101(de)004:5000: zhes gsungs pa ltar rnal ma don gyi snying po
NK101(de)004:5001: 'di nyid ma nor bar rtogs te rang la gnas
NK101(de)004:5002: pa ni / ting nge 'dzin thams cad kyi mchoga
NK101(de)004:5003: tu gyur pa yin pas dper na brda dang bral
NK101(de)004:5004: ba'i rgyal bu da'u rgyal sar dbang bskur ba dang
NK101(de)004:5007: brda don bral ba'i rgyal bu bzhin //
NK101(de)004:5008: nor bu'i sa nas brda bkrol te //
NK101(de)004:5009: 'khor lo bzhi la dbang byed cing //
NK101(de)004:5010: stobs brgyad mthu yi dag por bskur //
NK101(de)004:5011: de bzhin skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK101(de)004:5012: rang snang brda don grol thob nas //
NK101(de)004:5013: rang bzhin mtshan nyid ma bcos pa //
NK101(de)004:5014: mngon sum bstan pa'i man ngag sbyin //
NK101(de)004:5016: gnyis pa don lam gyi ngo bo'i cha rkyen rang
NK101(de)004:5017: snang klong dgu'i dgongs pa bla med chen por bshad
NK101(de)004:5018: pa la / rang snang klong dgu ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5019: de nyid dpe yis mtshon te tshad ma'i lung dang sbyar ba gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:5021: de yang dang po sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gcig gis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5022: de lta bu'i rtogs pa de yang dang po rgyal
NK101(de)004:5023: thabs spyi blugs tshangs pa chen po'i dbang bskur ba
NK101(de)004:5024: las rig pa rang ngo shes shing rang dbang du
NK101(de)004:5027: dper na rgyal rigs spyi bo nas //
NK101(de)004:5028: dbang bskur brtan pa thob pa bzhin //
NK101(de)004:5029: rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK101(de)004:5030: gzhi snang rgya yi btab ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:5031: de phyir rgyal thabs zhes byar grangs //
NK101(de)004:5034: rgya phug 'khor lo brtsegs pa'i khang //
NK101(de)004:5035: d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu //
NK101(de)004:5036: gser gyi brag phug yu ba can //
NK101(de)004:5037: de'i nang rdo rje'i gdan bting ste //
NK101(de)004:5038: rin chen 'bar ba gsal byed kyis //
NK101(de)004:5039: phyogs mtshams rgyas pa'i gur phub ste //
NK101(de)004:5040: yi ge med pa'i 'bru gsum bstims //
NK101(de)004:5041: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen bkrol //
NK101(de)004:5042: phyogs mtshams rgyas pa'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK101(de)004:5043: rin chen 'phrul gyi me long bstan //
NK101(de)004:5044: rgyu ba med pa'i rig pa bskyed //
NK101(de)004:5045: rang bzhin gsal ba'i 'od la bzhugs //
NK101(de)004:5046: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rgyan dang ldan //
NK101(de)004:5047: spyi blugs tshangs pa'i dbang bskur te //
NK101(de)004:5048: bde chen sa la bkod pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5050: de'i rten gzhi la ni dkyil 'khor dang dam tshig gnyis dang nges par ldan pa dgos te /
NK101(de)004:5053: ji bzhin mngon sum kho na bas //
NK101(de)004:5054: 'di la de bzhin nan tan bya //
NK101(de)004:5055: bkra gsal gzugs dang brjod bral sgra //
NK101(de)004:5056: dngos bral rang bzhin med pa'i dri //
NK101(de)004:5057: mu khe'i thig le dbyings kyi ngang //
NK101(de)004:5058: sna tshogs dbyings nyid bdag ga'i klong //
NK101(de)004:5060: bde ba chen po gcig gi ngang //
NK101(de)004:5061: ye shes mu mtha' med par 'jug /'di ni rang bzhin dkyil 'khor yin //
NK101(de)004:5064: de ni snying po'i don nyid de //
NK101(de)004:5066: ngo bos 'brel phyir nges par longs //
NK101(de)004:5067: kun nas bzlums phyir dkyil 'khor ro //
NK101(de)004:5068: de la gtso bo dbus gnas dang //
NK101(de)004:5069: mtha' na 'khor gnas bzang ngan med //
NK101(de)004:5070: snying po spros bral dbus gnas dang //
NK101(de)004:5071: spros pa'i chos kyi mtha' bskor bral //
NK101(de)004:5073: rang bzhin mtshan nyid rnam par dag /
NK101(de)004:5074: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:5075: bde chen ngang du mnyam pas gdengs //
NK101(de)004:5078: byang sems lhun gnas dam pa'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:5079: rtsol bral gnas la nyams pa yi //
NK101(de)004:5080: 'jigs dogs gdod nas mi gnas te //
NK101(de)004:5081: ka dag yon tan lhun gnas gdengs //
NK101(de)004:5082: des na bsrung bya phyogs ris grangs //
NK101(de)004:5083: rnam par dbye ba bzang ngan dang //
NK101(de)004:5084: mtshams bzung mi gnas bde ba che //
NK101(de)004:5085: rtsol bral nges pa'i srog gis gnas //
NK101(de)004:5087: rtsol bral rig pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK101(de)004:5088: gcig ces 'di zhes grangs btab bar //
NK101(de)004:5089: gnas pa min la gnas skabs su //
NK101(de)004:5090: dgos pas med pa phyal ba dang //
NK101(de)004:5091: gcig bu lhun grub rnam pa bzhi //
NK101(de)004:5092: phyogs dang grangs kyis bsrung bya dang //
NK101(de)004:5093: bral bas med pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK101(de)004:5094: yin min yod med bden rdzun gyi //
NK101(de)004:5095: 'dzin pa bral bas phyal ba yin //
NK101(de)004:5097: dbyer med gcig pu'i dam tshig yin //
NK101(de)004:5098: ngang gnas nyams pa las grol bas //
NK101(de)004:5099: btsal med lhun rdzogs ye grub pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5101: de yi ngang la rtag gnas na //
NK101(de)004:5102: thun mong yon tan cha la rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5103: rin chen zhor la phran bu ltar //
NK101(de)004:5104: khyad par bde chen lhun gyis gnas //
NK101(de)004:5105: sdug bsngal rtsol ba'i nad las grol //
NK101(de)004:5106: don kun ma btsal lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:5107: phyogs ris mi mnga' kun tu khyab //
NK101(de)004:5108: rgyun ma chad par thams cad grol //
NK101(de)004:5109: de bzlog skyon yang rjes mthun te //
NK101(de)004:5111: ji ltar 'bad rtsol brtson byas kyang //
NK101(de)004:5113: rang gshis gnad du ma byin pas //
NK101(de)004:5115: rtsol bas thang chad sdug bsngal la //
NK101(de)004:5116: bde chen snying po srog dang bral //
NK101(de)004:5118: de bzhin du de'i don kun mdzad pa'i rkyen gyi
NK101(de)004:5119: rima pa la'ang phrin las rnams dang ldan par rtogs
NK101(de)004:5120: rig ma 'gags pa'i ngang du rdzogs pa dgos te
NK101(de)004:5122: thugs rjes 'dul dang rang bzhin grub //
NK101(de)004:5123: rnam pa gnyis su bshad pa ni //
NK101(de)004:5124: gdengs la gnas nas mdzad pa bzhis //
NK101(de)004:5125: gang 'dul thugs rjes skyob pa dang //
NK101(de)004:5126: mdzad pa rtsol ba las grol bar //
NK101(de)004:5127: don gyis las bzhir lhun grub pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5130: rang bzhin lhun grub phrin las ni //
NK101(de)004:5131: ye shes rang snang ngang gnas pas //
NK101(de)004:5132: phyi nang rnam rtog ngang gis zhi //
NK101(de)004:5133: ye shes mtha' dbus med par rgyas //
NK101(de)004:5135: phyi nang rnam rtog tshar bcad bsgral //
NK101(de)004:5136: rang bzhin ye nas ma bcos pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5138: de dang mtshungs par rtogs pa don gyi lta ba yang /
NK101(de)004:5140: de dag ldan pas dbang bskur nas //
NK101(de)004:5142: rang grol shar ba'i lta ba ste //
NK101(de)004:5144: rnam rtog rang grol du shar ba ni gsang mchog
NK101(de)004:5145: rgyal po'i lta ba ma nor bar rtogs pa ste
NK101(de)004:5146: / dbang thob pa'i tshad 'khor 'das rang dbang du
NK101(de)004:5147: 'dus pa la sogs pa kun kyang lta ba'i ngang
NK101(de)004:5150: byang sems kun mkhyen ye shes des //
NK101(de)004:5151: kun mkhyen yul med rang gsal ba //
NK101(de)004:5152: dgos pa cir brtags der mi rtog /
NK101(de)004:5153: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rang grol ba'o //
NK101(de)004:5154: de yang rtog pa ye shes su //
NK101(de)004:5155: 'dus pas lta ba'i dbang du rtogs //
NK101(de)004:5156: rtogs pas don gyi snying po longs //
NK101(de)004:5157: lta ba'i dkyil 'khor rtogs pa yin //
NK101(de)004:5158: ngang la gnas pas 'da' med gnas //
NK101(de)004:5159: lta ba'i dam tshig ye bsrungs yin //
NK101(de)004:5160: phyogs 'dzin zhi la ye shes rgyas //
NK101(de)004:5161: don 'dus dngos mtshan tshar gcod las //
NK101(de)004:5162: yul med ye gsal kun mkhyen pa //
NK101(de)004:5163: bltar med lta ba ye bltas mthong //
NK101(de)004:5164: rtogs nas ngang las 'da' ma myong //
NK101(de)004:5165: lta ba'i sgom pa yengs bral ba'o //
NK101(de)004:5166: mkhyen pa'i ye shes 'gag med rol //
NK101(de)004:5167: lta ba'i spyod pa rang rdzogs yin //
NK101(de)004:5168: rtogs pa'i ngang gnas mthar phyin pa //
NK101(de)004:5169: lta ba'i sa lam rang gnas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5170: yin don rtogs las skyes dbyung med //
NK101(de)004:5171: lta ba'i 'bras bu ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:5172: kun la de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK101(de)004:5174: de ltar rtogs pa'i don de bzhag /
NK101(de)004:5175: thabs gsum gyis nyams su blangs shing goms par byas
NK101(de)004:5176: pas 'bras bu mthar phyin par 'gyur ba yin te
NK101(de)004:5178: thun mong min par brda sprad nas //
NK101(de)004:5179: phyogs med rang grol ngang gnas pas //
NK101(de)004:5180: ma gtad ngang du ma yengs gsal //
NK101(de)004:5181: bsgom med sgom pa'i gzer chen yin //
NK101(de)004:5182: gdod nas snying po rnal ma nyid //
NK101(de)004:5183: yengs dang bral ba'i dogs pa med //
NK101(de)004:5185: btsal ba bral ba'i thabs chen yin //
NK101(de)004:5186: thog mar rang rig rnal 'byor pas //
NK101(de)004:5187: rtogs pa phyogs bral nges pa'i sor //
NK101(de)004:5188: ma bcos lhun gyis bder gnas te //
NK101(de)004:5189: ma yengs gnas tsam de nyid sgom //
NK101(de)004:5190: bying rgod 'phro thim cir g.yos kyang //
NK101(de)004:5191: thog ma'i don dang rtogs pa'i gnad //
NK101(de)004:5192: des na spang dag sbyang bsgyur min //
NK101(de)004:5193: de nyid tshod du rang tang gnas //
NK101(de)004:5195: sgyu ma rang rig stong nyid pas //
NK101(de)004:5196: sprul rdzogs chos skur lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:5197: des na ma btsal lhug par zhog /
NK101(de)004:5198: ma shor ma bcos btsal med pa //
NK101(de)004:5199: brjod pa gsum pa dbyer med pas //
NK101(de)004:5200: tha dad rjes su sems mi spro //
NK101(de)004:5201: thig le rang gsal nyag gcig go //
NK101(de)004:5203: de'i bogs 'don lta bur gnang ba dang bkag pa
NK101(de)004:5204: meda pa'i spyod pa spyad de la bzla ba ni
NK101(de)004:5205: lta sgom gyi grogs su med thabs med pa nyid
NK101(de)004:5207: byang sems ngang gnas skyes chen la //
NK101(de)004:5208: thams cad ye shes thugs rjer rol //
NK101(de)004:5209: rnam pa sgyu mar lhun grub pas //
NK101(de)004:5210: blang dor bsam bral gdengs chen ldan //
NK101(de)004:5211: des na gnang bkag spyad pa la //
NK101(de)004:5212: sogs pa'i rjes su sems mi 'brang //
NK101(de)004:5213: gang ltar gnas pas de ltar bde //
NK101(de)004:5214: blang dang dor ba'i yid bral gzungs //
NK101(de)004:5215: 'gro bas gang sgrub der brtson pas //
NK101(de)004:5216: 'dod pa'i don la myur gnas ltar //
NK101(de)004:5217: don grub ngang gnas skyes chen gyis //
NK101(de)004:5218: snying por gnas shing don kun grub //
NK101(de)004:5220: bdag nyid mkhyen goms ngang ma g.yos //
NK101(de)004:5221: gzhan don ma btsal lhun grub pa //
NK101(de)004:5222: byang chub chen po'i don mthar phyin //
NK101(de)004:5223: spyod pa lhun grub de phan yon //
NK101(de)004:5224: de yi don bral rnal 'byor ni //
NK101(de)004:5225: rtogs pa yar bsnyags 'phangs bstod kyang //
NK101(de)004:5226: bus pa'i theg par gnas pa ste //
NK101(de)004:5227: smon lam mos pa de don min //
NK101(de)004:5229: de bzhin du sa la sbyangs dang lam la bgrod
NK101(de)004:5230: du med pa'i sa lam ni yon tan mchog gi
NK101(de)004:5233: ma bcos rang snang bla ma'i sa //
NK101(de)004:5234: sbyangs pas ma yin ye nas grub //
NK101(de)004:5235: rang byung rnam dag kun bzang sa //
NK101(de)004:5236: dbyer med che mchog chos kyi sa //
NK101(de)004:5239: rang byung khyad par lam chen ni //
NK101(de)004:5240: blang dor gnyis med rig pa'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:5241: ye shes dbu ma mtha' bral la //
NK101(de)004:5242: bgrod pa'i lam med ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:5245: ma bcos bla mar gnas rdzogs pa'i //
NK101(de)004:5246: sa lam zhes su gsungs pa yang //
NK101(de)004:5247: gnas shing brten pas byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:5248: 'jug cing phyin pas ye shes lam //
NK101(de)004:5250: de ltar goms pas gzhi lam dang zhor snang gi
NK101(de)004:5251: skyon rnams bral nas sems nyid rang rig pa rang
NK101(de)004:5252: snang ba'i ngang du gsal bar rtogs pa mthar phyin
NK101(de)004:5253: kyang sems las logs nas 'bras bu thob pa dang
NK101(de)004:5254: sgrib pa spangs su med pa ni 'bras bu'i klong
NK101(de)004:5255: chen po sel med pa nyid de /
NK101(de)004:5257: ngo bo sems nyid gsal mthar phyin //
NK101(de)004:5258: gzhi lam zhor snang skyon bral yin //
NK101(de)004:5259: gnas lugs rang snang gdags gzhi can //
NK101(de)004:5260: tha snyad rang grol mngon shar bas //
NK101(de)004:5261: mtshon chos kun grol kun gyi gzhi //
NK101(de)004:5262: rang snang nyid du mthar son yin //
NK101(de)004:5263: rgyu las rkyen gyis bsgyur min la //
NK101(de)004:5264: mthar phyin bskyed du byar med pas //
NK101(de)004:5265: smin pa'i 'bras bur brdar btags pa //
NK101(de)004:5266: mthun pa'i ming du nges pa yin //
NK101(de)004:5269: de kun rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK101(de)004:5270: rang mkhyen pas na stong gsal des //
NK101(de)004:5271: gzhi rten kun gsal spros pa gcod //
NK101(de)004:5272: mtshungs med bde chen mtshan ldan chad //
NK101(de)004:5273: de nyid gdul bya skal ldan la //
NK101(de)004:5274: byin rlabs rang mtshan tshangs pa'i gsung //
NK101(de)004:5275: sgro skur bral bar bstan pa ni //
NK101(de)004:5276: ma rtogs log rtog the tshom bral //
NK101(de)004:5277: sku dang ye shes rdzogs pa che //
NK101(de)004:5278: rnam pas byang chub snying por gnas //
NK101(de)004:5280: de ltar ming gis klong dgu ru btags te bstan
NK101(de)004:5281: pa kun kyang don gyi ngo bo rang snang thig
NK101(de)004:5282: le nag gcig tu yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pa
NK101(de)004:5283: ni rang rig snying po'i rin po che rang 'bar
NK101(de)004:5284: 'od kyi dkyil 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i snang
NK101(de)004:5285: ba dam pa nyid yin te /
NK101(de)004:5287: ma lus 'dus pa'i lus po che //
NK101(de)004:5288: gcig ni kun gyi rang bzhin te //
NK101(de)004:5289: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5292: rang bzhag 'od gsal rig pa la //
NK101(de)004:5293: ma lus dgongs pa thams cad 'dus //
NK101(de)004:5294: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK101(de)004:5295: rang bzhag dgongs pa gcig las med //
NK101(de)004:5297: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che las /
NK101(de)004:5298: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyi med //
NK101(de)004:5299: rnal 'byor nam mkha'i bya lam gnas //
NK101(de)004:5300: ma byung ma skyes snying po la //
NK101(de)004:5301: sgro btags chos kun ga la yod //
NK101(de)004:5304: dgongs pa gcig las g.yos pas med //
NK101(de)004:5305: snang ba snang ba'i thog gsal bas //
NK101(de)004:5306: bzhin dang me long lta bu la //
NK101(de)004:5307: grol ba de dang de nyid grol //
NK101(de)004:5308: shes pa 'gyu ba yul stong pas //
NK101(de)004:5309: mthong shes rig pa tha dad min //
NK101(de)004:5310: de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK101(de)004:5311: gcig shes pas ni kun grol byed //
NK101(de)004:5312: gnyis dang gsum gyi grangs mtha' zad //
NK101(de)004:5313: rtog cing 'dzin pa'i yul mi snang //
NK101(de)004:5315: stong pa'i dgongs pa gsal rdzogs pas //
NK101(de)004:5316: du ma'i grangs mtha' zad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5318: gzhan yang 'dod sems lta ba bshad //
NK101(de)004:5319: kun brgyab gcig kyang ma chod pas //
NK101(de)004:5320: gcig brgyab thams cad gsad par bya //
NK101(de)004:5321: mi brgya lcags sgrog gcig ma thar //
NK101(de)004:5322: gcig gzung bas ni thams cad thar //
NK101(de)004:5323: thar bas gong du grol lam zad //
NK101(de)004:5325: zhes sogs shin tu mang ngo //
NK101(de)004:5326: de ltar ma 'dres mtha' bral rang gsal /
NK101(de)004:5327: yongs rdzogs dbyer med mnyam grol gyi dgongs pa gsang
NK101(de)004:5328: ba chen po 'di ni don lam gyi ngo bo'i
NK101(de)004:5329: cha rkyen med du mi rung ba'i man ngag bla
NK101(de)004:5331: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro tsa nas /
NK101(de)004:5332: tshogs brgyad ye nas gnas ji bzhin //
NK101(de)004:5333: dam pas klong dgu sems la thob //
NK101(de)004:5336: dper na rig gnas sogs rkang pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5337: dper na bzo gso ba sgra gtan tshigs nang rig
NK101(de)004:5338: pa ste rig pa'i gnas chen lnga po yongs su
NK101(de)004:5339: rdzogs pa'i gang zag mkhas pa la /
NK101(de)004:5340: bzo bo dang sman pa la sogs pa'i ming gang
NK101(de)004:5341: du btags kyang yon tan gyi ldog cha so so
NK101(de)004:5342: nas brtsis pas kun kyang bdena par ldan pa bzhin
NK101(de)004:5343: du ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs kyi dgongs pa 'di
NK101(de)004:5344: yang sbyar te rtogs dgos par /
NK101(de)004:5345: gsang sngags rin po che'i mdzod khang gi bdag po
NK101(de)004:5346: gter chen mi zad pa'i snying po 'dzin pa'i ston
NK101(de)004:5347: mchog rdo rje 'chang chen rigs kyi bdag pos ye
NK101(de)004:5348: shes gsang ba'i rgyud sogs las gsungs te /
NK101(de)004:5349: de nyid dgu ldan sems kyi gzhi //
NK101(de)004:5350: rin chen lam gyis nyams su blangs //
NK101(de)004:5351: ma bsgrubs 'bras bu lhun gyis grub //
NK101(de)004:5352: lta ba sems la blang dor med //
NK101(de)004:5353: mtha' dbus med pa'i snying po len //
NK101(de)004:5354: ye shes ma 'gags gsal bar snang //
NK101(de)004:5355: gnang bkag med pa spyod pa'i rgyan //
NK101(de)004:5356: mi bsam ma yengs dgongs pa'i klong //
NK101(de)004:5357: rgyal thabs spyi blugs rdzogs pa'i dbang //
NK101(de)004:5358: bgrod med mthar phyin sems kyi lam //
NK101(de)004:5359: bcos med dam tshig gdod nas dag /
NK101(de)004:5360: rang snang 'bras bu lhun grub klong //
NK101(de)004:5361: zhes pa la sogs pa dang klong dgu bam po
NK101(de)004:5362: nyi khri las shin tu spros te rgyas par gsungs
NK101(de)004:5363: so // de dag gi don gyi gnas ni zab cing rgya che ba yin pas /
NK101(de)004:5364: rgyas par klong dgu so so'i skabs dang /
NK101(de)004:5366: nyung bsdus bdud rtsi chu rgyun las gsungs pa rnams
NK101(de)004:5367: la blo gros kyi 'jug pa gsal bar byas te
NK101(de)004:5368: rnal ma snying po'i nges don la 'jug par bya'o
NK101(de)004:5370: rin pa che gter gtad pa las /
NK101(de)004:5371: rtogs pa'i don 'dris shing goms pa'i thabs kyis 'bras
NK101(de)004:5372: bu mthar phyin par bstan pa'i le'u ste skabs bzhi
NK101(de)004:5373: pa nyid legs par bshad pa'a////lnga pa de ltar mngon
NK101(de)004:5374: du gyur te 'bras bu lhun gyis grub nas ngang
NK101(de)004:5375: la rdzogs tshul bshad pa la /
NK101(de)004:5376: ngo bo sku yi bzhugs tshul /
NK101(de)004:5377: dgongs pa ye shes kyi rang bzhin /
NK101(de)004:5378: khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)004:5380: tsa na'i 'bras ltar sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5381: dper na shing mchog tsa na'i zhes tsa na ka'i
NK101(de)004:5382: 'bras bu la phyi nang dang sgrib byed med pa
NK101(de)004:5383: ltar du rgyu rkyen dang dbyer ba med par rang
NK101(de)004:5384: rig pa skye 'gags gnas gsum dang bral bar rang
NK101(de)004:5385: gsal ba yi 'bras bu nyid rang gi ngo bos
NK101(de)004:5386: ma nor bar 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la khyab
NK101(de)004:5387: gdal du gyur pa cana gyi gnas lugs mngon du
NK101(de)004:5388: gyur pa ni ngo bo nyid kyi sku yin la
NK101(de)004:5389: / de nyid ji ltar gnas pa'i don bzhin du
NK101(de)004:5390: dpal ldan bla ma'i sku drin gyis ma bcos rang
NK101(de)004:5391: grol du ngo shes te rang nyid lam gyis mthar
NK101(de)004:5392: phyin pa'i ye shes rang byung du gsal ba ni
NK101(de)004:5394: ye shes chen po des 'khor 'das kyi bde ba
NK101(de)004:5395: thams cad rang rig bde ba chen por mngon sum
NK101(de)004:5396: du mdzad de chags pa med par longs spyod pas
NK101(de)004:5398: de nyid sa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i ngo
NK101(de)004:5399: la 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po ltar mtshan dang
NK101(de)004:5400: dpe byad kyis brgyan pa'i skur snang ba ni gzhan
NK101(de)004:5401: longs sku te / 'di gnyis yang gsang snying thig
NK101(de)004:5402: gi gazhung las rang snang dang gzhan snang gi longs
NK101(de)004:5403: sku bshad pa dang don du gcig go //
NK101(de)004:5404: de yi rnam 'phrul 'gro ba rigs drug dang srid
NK101(de)004:5405: pa khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi ngo
NK101(de)004:5406: la dag ma dag sna tshogs su snang nas 'khrul
NK101(de)004:5407: pa rim bzhin du sbyong bar mdzad pa ni sprul
NK101(de)004:5408: pa'i sku ste / 'bras bu'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:5409: ngo bo nyid gnas ye shes shar chos sku //
NK101(de)004:5410: de yi 'od shar rigs lnga sprul par bcas //
NK101(de)004:5412: lhun gnas bde chen gdal ba'i sku //
NK101(de)004:5413: chos sku spros pa kun las grol //
NK101(de)004:5414: rang rig bde chen longs spyod rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5416: dbyer med ngang du rdzogs pa las //
NK101(de)004:5417: sa gnas dag pas de bdag byas //
NK101(de)004:5418: mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i skus 'dul mdzad //
NK101(de)004:5419: 'gro drug rgyud dag ma dag la //
NK101(de)004:5420: bdag po de nyid dag pa dang //
NK101(de)004:5421: ma dag sprul pa rgya cher shar //
NK101(de)004:5422: bsam mi khyab pas 'dul bar mdzad //
NK101(de)004:5424: de yang chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas
NK101(de)004:5425: chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i de kho na nyid du
NK101(de)004:5426: gnas pa ni ngo bo yin la /
NK101(de)004:5427: de nyid gnas lugs ji lta bar mngon du mdzad
NK101(de)004:5428: pa'i phyir rang snang rig pa'i mngon sum du sku
NK101(de)004:5429: bzhi po ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin
NK101(de)004:5430: pas ngo bo la dbyer med chen por mnyam pa
NK101(de)004:5431: nyid do // de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK101(de)004:5432: ngo bo mtshan ma'i sku las 'das //
NK101(de)004:5433: kun gyi gzhi rtsa snying po'i sku //
NK101(de)004:5434: bde chen ngos med nyi 'od shar //
NK101(de)004:5435: ye shes mchog sku med las 'das //
NK101(de)004:5436: yod pa'ang yod med las 'das so //
NK101(de)004:5439: rang gsal mi rtog sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5440: sgrib byed med par rang gsal ba'i rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyis chos thams cad /
NK101(de)004:5441: snang ba'i yul du med par chos nyid kyi ngang
NK101(de)004:5442: du mkhyen pa ni me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK101(de)004:5443: te / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK101(de)004:5444: byang chub sems 'di kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:5445: ma lus 'dus pa'i snying po'i mchog /
NK101(de)004:5446: theg pa mkha' 'dra lta ba'i klong //
NK101(de)004:5447: rgya che yangs pa bde ba che //
NK101(de)004:5449: phyogs mtshams kun tu gsal bar 'gro //
NK101(de)004:5450: ye shes me long thams cad gsal //
NK101(de)004:5451: ma bcos gzugs brnyan snang bas na //
NK101(de)004:5452: ye shes me long dag tu bshad //
NK101(de)004:5454: de bzhin du chos thams cad chos nyid de bzhin
NK101(de)004:5455: nyid 'dir bzang ngan dang che chung med par mnyam
NK101(de)004:5456: pa'i stong gsal du mkhyen pa ni mnyam pa nyid
NK101(de)004:5458: rang rig ye shes 'od gsal la //
NK101(de)004:5459: mtho dman rlom sems che chung med //
NK101(de)004:5460: bdag gzhan gnyis med rang rig pas //
NK101(de)004:5462: dbyer med nam mkha' lta bur khyab //
NK101(de)004:5463: snang srid byang chub sems su mnyam //
NK101(de)004:5464: mnyam pa'i rang gsal phyogs bcur brdas //
NK101(de)004:5465: 'od gsal rig pa mnyam par bshad //
NK101(de)004:5467: de bzhin du ji ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad
NK101(de)004:5468: mtshon tshul nas ma 'dres la ye shes kyi ngang
NK101(de)004:5469: du yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pas rgyal ba'i thugs
NK101(de)004:5470: kun gyi badga nyid ni so sor rtog pa'i ye
NK101(de)004:5472: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK101(de)004:5473: gnyis med rig pa kar dag la //
NK101(de)004:5474: ye shes rol pa ma 'dres gsal //
NK101(de)004:5475: kun bzang chos nyid spros med la //
NK101(de)004:5476: rol pa'i 'khor lo bsam mi khyab //
NK101(de)004:5478: 'bar ba'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK101(de)004:5479: rang gsal rig pa kun mkhyen thugs //
NK101(de)004:5480: mnyam la ma 'dres kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:5481: ma 'dres gsal ba'i ye shes so //
NK101(de)004:5483: de bzhin du rtsol bas ma byas par bdag gzhan
NK101(de)004:5484: gyi don du bya ba kun rdzogs par sgrub pas
NK101(de)004:5485: thugs rje'i rnam pa rang shar ba'i mkhyen pa ni
NK101(de)004:5486: / bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te //
NK101(de)004:5487: mi mda' phyag rgya chen po la //
NK101(de)004:5488: rang byung mdzad pa cir yang 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:5489: lhun grub mdzad pa phyogs ris med //
NK101(de)004:5490: kun gyi snying po rang byung la //
NK101(de)004:5491: thugs rje lhun grub shar gyur nas //
NK101(de)004:5492: gdul bya'i bya ba kun mdzad gsal //
NK101(de)004:5493: des na bya ba nan tan no //
NK101(de)004:5495: dgongs pa de dag kun kyang mu matha'i phyogs ris
NK101(de)004:5496: thams cad rang sar grol nas gsal khyab dbyings kyi
NK101(de)004:5497: thig ler lhun gyis rdzogs pas kun 'dus chos nyid
NK101(de)004:5498: dbyings kyi ngo bor ma bcos 'od gsal du mkhyen
NK101(de)004:5499: pa ni stong pa nyid kyi ye shes te /
NK101(de)004:5500: bcos med dbyings kyi rang bzhin la //
NK101(de)004:5501: 'dzin rtog zhen pa'i chos med pas //
NK101(de)004:5502: mi 'gyur ye shes rang byung la //
NK101(de)004:5503: bden par mi 'dzin rdzun pa'ang min //
NK101(de)004:5504: 'dzin med rig pa gnyis bral la //
NK101(de)004:5505: gang yang mi snang kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:5506: chos nyid sems la dngos med gsal //
NK101(de)004:5507: stong pa kun mkhyen ye shes thugs //
NK101(de)004:5508: dngos med kun ldan stong chen po //
NK101(de)004:5510: stong nyid ye shes dag tu bshad //
NK101(de)004:5512: de ltar ye shes lnga po yul med rang gsal
NK101(de)004:5513: rang rig gdod ma'i mgon po byang sems thig le
NK101(de)004:5514: nyag gcig gi ngo bo ni /
NK101(de)004:5515: rang byung gi ye shes zhes ming du gdags pa'i gzhi can nyid yin te /
NK101(de)004:5517: rang gsal ye nas ma bcos pa //
NK101(de)004:5518: don de shes pas ye shes yin //
NK101(de)004:5519: chos nyid ka dag 'od gsal sems //
NK101(de)004:5520: don de shes pas ye shes yin //
NK101(de)004:5521: ma 'gags rang rig rgyu med gsal //
NK101(de)004:5522: rang byung ye shes 'gyur med sems //
NK101(de)004:5523: 'od gsal bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK101(de)004:5524: kun bzang rol pa mtha' dbus med //
NK101(de)004:5525: mi rtsol mtha' bral dbu ma'i sems //
NK101(de)004:5526: mtshon 'das rang rig zhen rtog med //
NK101(de)004:5527: gnyis med rang rig yul dang bral //
NK101(de)004:5529: rang byung ye shes nyag gcig la //
NK101(de)004:5530: yon tan cha res du mar bgrangs //
NK101(de)004:5531: rang rig nyid la yul med pas //
NK101(de)004:5532: yul gyis bskyed pa'i ye shes min //
NK101(de)004:5533: rang byung nyid la rgyu med pas //
NK101(de)004:5534: rgyu yis bskyed pa'i ye shes min //
NK101(de)004:5535: lhun grub nyid la rtsol med pas //
NK101(de)004:5536: rtsol bas bskyed pa'i ye shes min //
NK101(de)004:5539: thams cad rdzogs pas sogs tshigs su bcad pa byed dang gsum gyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5540: de yang tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa thams cad
NK101(de)004:5541: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems su ma 'dres la
NK101(de)004:5542: yongs su rdzogs pas nyan thos ltar spangs pa dang
NK101(de)004:5543: rang rgyal ltar bkag pa dang byang sems ltar sbyangs
NK101(de)004:5544: pa rnams dang bral te mngon sum sangs rgyas par
NK101(de)004:5545: rtogs te / spang 'gegs sbyong ba'i rtsol ba med
NK101(de)004:5546: pas bde ba chen po de nyid shin tu rnal
NK101(de)004:5547: 'byor la rdzogs pas na mtshan nyid sde gsum las
NK101(de)004:5548: 'phags pa'i khyad par gyi che ba bla na med
NK101(de)004:5549: rtogs te / pa ste / snga ma las /
NK101(de)004:5550: mngon par sangs rgyas che ba la //
NK101(de)004:5551: ye shes thig le kun tu gsal //
NK101(de)004:5553: rgyu rkyen 'bras bus bsdus pa'i chos thams cad thig
NK101(de)004:5554: le spros bral gyi ngang du ro gcig pa yin
NK101(de)004:5555: pas rgyu dbyings dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi mtshan
NK101(de)004:5556: nyid dang bral bas chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas
NK101(de)004:5557: par rtogs te rgyu 'bras kyi rtsol ba med pas
NK101(de)004:5558: bde ba chen po nyid de /
NK101(de)004:5559: gang las che na yongs su rnal 'byor a nu
NK101(de)004:5560: yo ga las 'phags pa'i rdzogsa pa chen po'i che
NK101(de)004:5561: ba rmad du byung ba ste /
NK101(de)004:5562: rnam gsum kun bzang thig le nyid //
NK101(de)004:5563: chos nyid dbyings su sangs rgyas che //
NK101(de)004:5565: de bzhin du snang stong gnyis su dbye ba med
NK101(de)004:5566: pas gnyis kyi tha snyad 'dogs pa'i gzhi med la
NK101(de)004:5567: / phyogs ris las grol bas gnyis su med pa'ang min te /
NK101(de)004:5568: gnyis dang gnyis med kyi spros pa de nyid dang
NK101(de)004:5569: brala bas badga nyid chen po sangs rgyas par rtogs
NK101(de)004:5570: te / tshul ngan gyi rtsol ba med pas bde ba chen po nyid de /
NK101(de)004:5571: gang las che na rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa
NK101(de)004:5572: yo ga las 'phags pa'i che ba zla dang bral
NK101(de)004:5573: te / rtsol bral lhun grub thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:5574: bdag nyid che ba'i sangs rgyas yin //
NK101(de)004:5576: blang ba dang dora ba 'di yina dang 'di min
NK101(de)004:5577: gyi phyogs cha thams cad dang brala bas dor ba
NK101(de)004:5578: de nyid blang bya de kho na yin pas sangs
NK101(de)004:5579: rgyas te blang dor gyi rtsol ba med par rtogs
NK101(de)004:5580: pas bde ba chen po nyid de /
NK101(de)004:5581: gang las che na sems dpa' yi rnal 'byor sngags
NK101(de)004:5582: phyi pa las 'phags pa'i che ba phul du byung
NK101(de)004:5583: ba ste / kun bzang thig le byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:5584: thams cad yin pa'i che ba nyid //
NK101(de)004:5586: de dag thams cad kyang dgos pa'i dbang gis ming
NK101(de)004:5587: du btags pa tsam ste dgongs gzhi rmongs pa la
NK101(de)004:5588: don mtshon pa can yin pa'i phyir na /
NK101(de)004:5589: sangs rgyas zhes bla dgas su btags pa'i tha snyad
NK101(de)004:5590: rang grol ba tsam du rtogs pa ni sangs rgyas
NK101(de)004:5591: med pa'i che ba rang byung gi ye shes nyi
NK101(de)004:5592: ma bye ba'i rang 'od sgrib med du brdal yang
NK101(de)004:5593: bya byed ye nas grol bas rtse mo'i yang tog
NK101(de)004:5594: tu phebs te tha snyad kun las 'das pa ste
NK101(de)004:5596: mtha' bral 'od gsal chen po ni //
NK101(de)004:5597: sangs rgyas med pa'i che bar bshad //
NK101(de)004:5599: la shan lta ba'i me long las //
NK101(de)004:5600: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pa'i //
NK101(de)004:5601: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od brdal yang //
NK101(de)004:5602: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du //
NK101(de)004:5603: sangs ma rgyas par bya byed pa'i //
NK101(de)004:5604: chos ni rdul tsam yod min pas //
NK101(de)004:5605: sangs rgyas med pa'i che bar gsungs //
NK101(de)004:5608: rin po che gter gtad pa las /
NK101(de)004:5611: khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba rnams bstan pa'i
NK101(de)004:5612: le'u ste skabs lnga pa nyid rnam par bshad pa'o////rtsa
NK101(de)004:5613: ba'i gsum pa 'byung ba'i dus bstan te gtad rgya
NK101(de)004:5614: mdzad pa la / 'byung dus la bab tshul ngos bzung ba /
NK101(de)004:5615: man ngag gi rgyal po'i bka' gtad mdzad pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)004:5617: rang gnas gter chen sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5618: de ltar rang la ye nas gnas pa'i gter chen
NK101(de)004:5619: po ranga gis ma nor bar rnyed pa'i thabs mchog
NK101(de)004:5621: rang gnas kyi gter de yang gdod ma nas rang
NK101(de)004:5622: dang ma bral bar gnas pa yin kyang rang ngo
NK101(de)004:5623: rang gis ma shes pas dbul bar gyur pa la
NK101(de)004:5624: / rang ngo ji bzhin du shes par byed pa'i
NK101(de)004:5625: thabs kyi rgyal po mtshungs pa med pa'i rtse mo
NK101(de)004:5626: / ste / ye shes rdzogs pa las /
NK101(de)004:5627: rim 'jug blo yi theg pa rnams //
NK101(de)004:5628: 'dren pa'i sku yis drang don bstan //
NK101(de)004:5629: nges pa'i theg gcig snying po la //
NK101(de)004:5630: 'dod pa'i yan lag kun dang bral //
NK101(de)004:5631: ma lus bstan pa'i rnam pa kun //
NK101(de)004:5632: ye shes rig pa'i mkhas la rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5633: zhes gsungs pa bzhin du sh+aakya'i rigs thams cad sgyu
NK101(de)004:5634: rtsal sna tshogs pa'i stobs kyis thub par mdzad pa'i
NK101(de)004:5635: ston pa sh+aakya'i dbang pos dgongs pas zhes drang don
NK101(de)004:5636: dgongs pa can gyis drangs te theg pa sna tshogs
NK101(de)004:5637: kyi don rnams rdzogs pa'i rjes su /
NK101(de)004:5640: nyon mongs rgyud drag mos mthu zhan //
NK101(de)004:5641: las kyi tshe thung bka' don ton //
NK101(de)004:5642: bstan snyigs grub mtha' ngan pas bsgyur //
NK101(de)004:5643: gnyen pos mi non sgrub brtson zhan //
NK101(de)004:5644: de tshe rig pa rnam stong shar //
NK101(de)004:5645: zhes gsungs pa ltar nyon mongs pa'i rgyud drag par byung ba dang /
NK101(de)004:5646: dad pa dang mos pa'i mthu zhen pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5647: las ngan pa'i stobs kyasa tshe thung ba dang /
NK101(de)004:5648: nges pa'i bka' yi don la rton pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5649: bstan pa'i snyigs ma la bab pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5650: grub mtha' ngan pas bsgyur ba dang drug ni 'byung ba'i dus gsungs te /
NK101(de)004:5652: 'byung ba'i dus drug gsungs pa las //
NK101(de)004:5653: bstan pa'i snyigs ma grub mtha' ngan //
NK101(de)004:5654: log rtog mang dus bram ze'o //
NK101(de)004:5655: dad med bka' yi don la rton //
NK101(de)004:5656: nyon mongs rgyud drag rgyal pos bsdus //
NK101(de)004:5657: man ngag spyir gces tshe 'thung bas //
NK101(de)004:5658: dron tshogs chung bar bstan pa yin //
NK101(de)004:5661: de yang nyon mongs pa'i rgyud drag pas byams pa
NK101(de)004:5662: la sogs pa'i gnyen pos zhes gnyen pos phyogs gcig
NK101(de)004:5663: tu gyur pas mi non cing /
NK101(de)004:5664: mos pa'i mthu dman pas sgrub pa la brtson 'grus
NK101(de)004:5665: zhan pa can gyis rigs dang ldan pa de dag
NK101(de)004:5666: yang sprul thugs sras chen po'i rnam pa thams cad
NK101(de)004:5667: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan gyis mthong ba'am gzigs
NK101(de)004:5668: nas / spyir rdzogs pa chen po'i bka' thams cad bsdus shing /
NK101(de)004:5669: de dag gi dgongs 'grel dang gsal byed kyi gdams pa mang pos kun nas rgyas par mdzad la /
NK101(de)004:5670: bye brag tu rtsol ba dang bral bar rang rig
NK101(de)004:5671: bde ba chen po mngon sum du rtogs par byed
NK101(de)004:5672: pa'i thabs kun gyi mthar thug pa /
NK101(de)004:5673: man ngag 'phrul gyi me long gi rtsa ba 'di nyid kyang bka' stsal bar mdzad pa yin no //
NK101(de)004:5675: sku gsum dgongs pa sogs tshigs bcad gsum dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:5676: de ltar thams cad theg pa kun gyi mthar thug
NK101(de)004:5677: pa'i snying po rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston pa
NK101(de)004:5678: rnams kyi mkhyen pa'i dgongs pa dang thugs kyi gsang
NK101(de)004:5679: bcud phyung ba'i bdud rtsi'i nying khu de nyid 'thungs
NK101(de)004:5680: pas byang chub chen po'i chu yis thugs rgyud brlan
NK101(de)004:5681: zhing / gzhan phan gyis smon lam btab pa'i nus
NK101(de)004:5682: mthu drag pos bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi
NK101(de)004:5683: myu gu rgyas te smin par gyur pa na /
NK101(de)004:5684: thugs rjes gzung ba'i yul ngan pa 'gro ba rigs
NK101(de)004:5685: drug la sems gting nas 'phrogs pa'i brtse bas dgongs
NK101(de)004:5686: te / ston pa rang nyid dang rigs rgyud mthun
NK101(de)004:5687: pa 'ga' tsam byung ba la thugs rje'i 'od zer
NK101(de)004:5688: spros nas rnam grol mchog gi lam la 'jug pa'i
NK101(de)004:5689: thabs kyi gdams pa ston pa'i thugs kyi bsam pa
NK101(de)004:5690: mchog tu gyur pa bskyed nas gsungs par mdzad pa
NK101(de)004:5691: te / ste / sgom pa'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:5692: 'gro rnams skye bzhi'i sdug bsngal d+r+wa bar rtag tu 'jug pa chu rgyun de /
NK101(de)004:5693: 'byung ba'i rgyu ni ma rig bdag lta nyon mongs las kyi 'khor lo ste /
NK101(de)004:5694: bde ba 'joms pa'i dgra las rgyal mdzad sku gsum brgyud pa'i bka' la brten /
NK101(de)004:5695: gdams pa 'di yis yid kyi mun pa bsal nas ye shes rgyal mtshan tshugs /
NK101(de)004:5696: 'jam dbyangs byin brlabs bu dang bdag dang rigs mthun skal ldan mos 'jug rnams /
NK101(de)004:5697: 'di la nan tan cher gyi dad brtson dam tshig yod sems la thums /
NK101(de)004:5698: zhes gsungs pa ltar bka' lung thams cad kyi snying
NK101(de)004:5699: po rin chen snang ba'i man ngag dam pa 'di
NK101(de)004:5700: nyid tha snyad kyi rnam grangs spros te rgyas par
NK101(de)004:5701: zer ba'i brjod pa mang po spangs te don gyi
NK101(de)004:5702: gnad rnams 'dus par tshig tshogs nyung dur dril nas
NK101(de)004:5703: / lhag pa'i lha mchog 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi byin
NK101(de)004:5704: gyis brlabs pa nyid kyi thugs sras mchog gi bu
NK101(de)004:5705: la bka' 'di gtad pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:5706: khyed kyis rang dang rigs mthuna pa'i skal ba dang
NK101(de)004:5707: ldan pa 'ga' dang 'ga' tsam byung ba rnam la
NK101(de)004:5708: / rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che yi dgongs
NK101(de)004:5709: pa gsang ba chen po de nyid rang grol ba'i
NK101(de)004:5710: gdams ngag gis skabs phye la brda sprad de /
NK101(de)004:5711: brda don thams cada phyogs ris las grol ba rgyas gdab cing /
NK101(de)004:5712: rnam rtog gi spros pa rnams thig les zhes thig le drug gi gcad pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5713: che ba lngas khyad par du dpags par bstan te dgrol bar mdzad pa la rems shing /
NK101(de)004:5714: de ltar rang la gnas pa'i gter chen po rang
NK101(de)004:5715: nyid la mngon sum du gtad par byed do rigs
NK101(de)004:5716: kyi bu mchog kya zhes bos nas legas par chongsa
NK101(de)004:5718: bram zer snying po grub pa pan chen 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la gtad rgya mdzad pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5719: de ltar gsungs pa rnams kyi don cung zad spros te bshad na /
NK101(de)004:5721: shin tu rnal ma'i ye shes la //
NK101(de)004:5722: sems med gnas pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:5723: spros pa kun bral de mkhyen pa'i //
NK101(de)004:5724: ye shes mtshan nyid rang rig gsal //
NK101(de)004:5725: de 'od rnam pa ci yang shar //
NK101(de)004:5726: dbyer med kun bral ji ma spangs //
NK101(de)004:5727: rang bzhin cis kyang stong pas yod pa'i mtha' las 'das //
NK101(de)004:5728: de mkhyen thams cad rdzogs pas med pa'i mtha' las 'das //
NK101(de)004:5729: mtshan nyid tha dad bral bas gnyis kyi mtha' las 'das //
NK101(de)004:5730: gnyis med ngos bral rol bas der 'dzin ngang las 'das //
NK101(de)004:5731: kun bral ji ma spangs pas kun mkhyen stong nyid rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5732: ye shes yod med mtha' las 'das par bzhugs //
NK101(de)004:5733: kun mkhyen gsal bas ye shes lhag chad med //
NK101(de)004:5734: spros dangbrala bas chos dbyings lhag chad med //
NK101(de)004:5735: ngo bo ma 'dres bden gnyis lhag chad med //
NK101(de)004:5736: rang bzhin dbyer med mnyam nyid lhag chad med //
NK101(de)004:5737: thams cad lhun grub rol pa lhag chad med //
NK101(de)004:5738: rgya ma chad pas ka dag lhag chad med //
NK101(de)004:5739: de ltar mkhyen la nges med rol par shar //
NK101(de)004:5740: ma bcos lhun gnas ye shes bde chen yin //
NK101(de)004:5741: lhag ma med par rdzogs pa chen po yin //
NK101(de)004:5742: rang grol rgyas gdab spros bcad khyad par 'phags //
NK101(de)004:5744: dang po rang grol chen po'i man ngag gis skabs
NK101(de)004:5745: 'byed pa la rgyas par rdo rje sems dpa' nam
NK101(de)004:5746: mkha' che las skabs nyi shu rtsa bdun gyis bstan
NK101(de)004:5748: mdor bsdu na gong du gsal bar bstan pa'i brda don bzhin du /
NK101(de)004:5749: lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro tsa nas /
NK101(de)004:5750: mtshan ma spros pa gzung 'dzin la //
NK101(de)004:5751: gnyen pos mi dgag thug phrad mod //
NK101(de)004:5752: sprul rdzogs chos sku ma 'dres gsal //
NK101(de)004:5753: btsal bas bsnam med lhun gnas nyid //
NK101(de)004:5754: ces gsungs pa ltar sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pas
NK101(de)004:5755: yul lnga la mtshan mar rtog ste rang yul so
NK101(de)004:5757: nyon yid kyis kun gzhi la dmigs te ngar 'dzin pas gzung 'dzin gyi bdag nyid can dang /
NK101(de)004:5758: yid kyi rnam shes ni de gnyis dang rang rigs
NK101(de)004:5759: snga ma'i rjes su ngar 'jug la khyad par du
NK101(de)004:5760: de dag dang snga phyi'i ming la rtog ste spros
NK101(de)004:5761: pa sna tshogs par kun nas 'brang bar byas pas
NK101(de)004:5762: gnyug ma don gyi kun gzhi 'khrul pa'i bag chags
NK101(de)004:5763: kyi bslad de gnas pa la /
NK101(de)004:5764: man ngag 'di yis sgo lnga'i mtshan ma'i yul snang
NK101(de)004:5765: de nyid rnam pa sgyu ma lhun grub tu ngo
NK101(de)004:5766: sprod pas thugs rje sprul pa'i rnam par rol te
NK101(de)004:5767: sprul sku thugs phrad du rang snang bar rtogs nas
NK101(de)004:5768: rang gdangs 'od gsal du grol zhing /
NK101(de)004:5769: de nyid rang gsal du mkhyen pa'i rig cha de
NK101(de)004:5770: nyid mtshan nyid rang rig lhun grub tu ngo sprad
NK101(de)004:5771: pas gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyis 'khor 'das
NK101(de)004:5772: kyi chos kun la chags med bde ba chen por
NK101(de)004:5773: longs spyod cing don gyi ngang la thug phrad du
NK101(de)004:5775: snga phyi kun tu rtog cing rang rigs snga ma
NK101(de)004:5776: dang phyi nang kun gyi rjes su ming la brten
NK101(de)004:5777: nas 'brang ba'i yid kyi spros bral lhun grub tu
NK101(de)004:5778: ngo sprad pas mtha' dbus gang la'ang mi gnas par
NK101(de)004:5779: zhen bsam rnam par dag pa nyid dmigs med chos
NK101(de)004:5780: kyi skur thug phrad du rang grol bas mthong bas
NK101(de)004:5781: / mtshon tshul nas sku gsum du ma 'dres kyang
NK101(de)004:5782: ngo bo yongs rdzogs dbyer med du lhun gyis grub
NK101(de)004:5783: pas gsal stong rig pa'i ye shes kun bzang thig
NK101(de)004:5784: le nyag gcig lhun gnas bde ba chen po yul
NK101(de)004:5785: med rang gsal du mthong ba'i ngang der /
NK101(de)004:5786: so so skye bo ltar rang rtog gis ma bslad /
NK101(de)004:5787: mu stegs ltar nyid rkyen gyis ma bcos /
NK101(de)004:5788: nyan thos ltar gnyen pos ma spangs /
NK101(de)004:5789: rang rgyal ltar rgyu nas ma bgag /
NK101(de)004:5790: byang sems ltar chos nyid du ma sbyangs /
NK101(de)004:5791: sngags phyi pa ltar lha ru ma bsgyur /
NK101(de)004:5792: ma h+aa ltar rtsol bas ma brtsal /
NK101(de)004:5793: a nu ltar rgyu yis ma bskyed par shes pa
NK101(de)004:5794: gsum lhun grub gsum gyi ngo bo nyid du rang
NK101(de)004:5796: rang grol chen po'i gdams ngag gis skabs phye ba'i don mchog rab tu gsang ba yin te /
NK101(de)004:5798: yul la mtshan mar rtog dang ngar 'dzin can //
NK101(de)004:5799: rjes su ming la spros par 'brang bar bslad //
NK101(de)004:5800: de nyid sprul par rol bas de mkhyen pa'i //
NK101(de)004:5801: ye shes kun la bde bar longs spyod rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5802: de nyid rnam dag dmigs med chos skur grol //
NK101(de)004:5803: sku gsum lhun grub kun bzang nyag gcig po //
NK101(de)004:5804: ma bslad ma bcos ma spangs ma bkag cing //
NK101(de)004:5805: ma sbyangs ma bsgyur ma brtsal ma bskyed grol //
NK101(de)004:5807: de ltar 'gag med rang grol gyi thig le chen po'i ngo bo ni /
NK101(de)004:5809: gzhi snang chen po de nyid la //
NK101(de)004:5810: ma rig pa zhes brtag med pas //
NK101(de)004:5811: 'khrul bar grub pa yod ma yin //
NK101(de)004:5812: blo zhes kun tu ma brtags pas //
NK101(de)004:5813: dri ma 'khrul ba'i ming yang med //
NK101(de)004:5814: ming dang yi ge'i tshogs med pas //
NK101(de)004:5815: btags pa'i 'khrul pa yod ma yin //
NK101(de)004:5816: chos zhes ming du ma grags pas //
NK101(de)004:5817: blo btags 'khrul pa mi yang med //
NK101(de)004:5818: sems dang yid du ma grub pas //
NK101(de)004:5820: phra rags dri ma gnyis med pas //
NK101(de)004:5822: bya dang byed pa gnyis med pas //
NK101(de)004:5824: yul dang dbang po gnyis med pas //
NK101(de)004:5827: gsal ba mngon gnas brjid re che //
NK101(de)004:5828: snang ba nyid ni lhun re sdug /
NK101(de)004:5829: chos sku ngo sprod dang re spro //
NK101(de)004:5830: ngo bo zang thal sbubs re yangs //
NK101(de)004:5831: rang bzhin kun khyab gdal re che //
NK101(de)004:5832: thugs rje kun 'byung skyed re che //
NK101(de)004:5833: khyab pa ye gdangs bkrag re gsal //
NK101(de)004:5834: gnas pa thogs med bar re mgyogs //
NK101(de)004:5835: rig pa'i rang gdangs 'od re gsal //
NK101(de)004:5837: ma btsal bzhag pa rgyun re ring //
NK101(de)004:5838: ma bkod rang byung brdal re che //
NK101(de)004:5839: snang srid gzhir bzhengs dpangs re mtho //
NK101(de)004:5840: 'bad med rang grol rgya che che //
NK101(de)004:5841: ye rtogs chen po 'khor re mkhas //
NK101(de)004:5842: kha dog lnga ldan bri re legs //
NK101(de)004:5843: snang srid rnam dag khod re snyoms //
NK101(de)004:5844: rang byung 'od gsal bkod re legs //
NK101(de)004:5845: gzhi snang chen po shangs re che //
NK101(de)004:5847: sku lnga ye shes brtsegs re legs //
NK101(de)004:5848: zhes gsungs pa ltar mtha' bral yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK101(de)004:5849: gzhi snang zang thal chen po'i klong du shes par
NK101(de)004:5850: bya zhing / de yang rin po che spungs pa las /
NK101(de)004:5852: gcig par gnas pa'i ye shes la //
NK101(de)004:5853: ma btsal rang gi rang rnyed pas //
NK101(de)004:5854: sngon nas da yi rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:5857: de phyir gzhi gnas rig pa la //
NK101(de)004:5858: rang shar yin phyir snang ba rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5859: rang byung yin phyir gzhi nyid rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5860: rang snang yin phyir yul yang rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5861: rang grol yin phyir 'khrul gzhi rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5862: rang dag yin phyir lam kun rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5863: rang rig yin phyir shes bya rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5864: rang khyab yin phyir 'bras bu rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5865: rang sa yi na phyir rgyu rkyen rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5866: rang rtogs yin phyir chos nyid rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5868: rang gnas yin phyir rgyud lung rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5869: rang rdzogs yin phyir dus gcig rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5870: rang shes yin phyir gdams ngag rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5871: rang bzhag yin phyir bsam gtan rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5872: rang chas yin phyir dbyings rdzogs pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5873: zhes gsungs pa ltar gzhi grol gdod ma'i chos nyid
NK101(de)004:5874: gnyis med 'od gsal chen po rin po che gsang
NK101(de)004:5875: ba'i dbyings su la zla bar bya'o //
NK101(de)004:5876: de ltar legs par rtogs na skabs kyi man ngag
NK101(de)004:5877: 'di'i dgongs don ji bzhin du lhongs te gnyug ma'i
NK101(de)004:5879: gnyis pa thams cad phyogs grol du rgyas gdab pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK101(de)004:5880: rgyas par nam mkha' che 'chad pa'i skabs su nges don mdo bcu las /
NK101(de)004:5881: mtshan ma'i yul la mi gnas te //
NK101(de)004:5882: ye shes chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK101(de)004:5883: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa //
NK101(de)004:5884: ye shes chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK101(de)004:5885: zhes sogs ye shes rkyen po'i phyag rgya nyi shu
NK101(de)004:5886: rtsa lnga dang rang lugs kyis gcod du 'phrul gyi
NK101(de)004:5887: gzer bu dam pa phyag rgya lngar bstan pa bzhin
NK101(de)004:5888: shes dgos kyang / mdor bsdu na /
NK101(de)004:5889: de ltar gdams ngag gis skabs phye ba yang gzhan
NK101(de)004:5890: sel dang don gnyen gyi dgos ched gnyis yod pa'i
NK101(de)004:5891: phyir brdar brtags nas bstan par zad kyi /
NK101(de)004:5892: gshis kyi ngo bos mtshon brjod las 'das pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK101(de)004:5893: yin min dang yod med kyis mtshon pa las 'das
NK101(de)004:5894: pa'i mtha' grol yongs rdzogs thig le nyag gcig tu
NK101(de)004:5895: bzhugs pa las / yin don gyi chos nyid mu
NK101(de)004:5896: mtha' las 'das pa'i snying por nges pa de la
NK101(de)004:5897: lhun grub gsum gyi tshig gi sgrar byung bas /
NK101(de)004:5898: log pa sde gsum lta bu la la ni phyogs gcig par gol zhing /
NK101(de)004:5899: gzhan zhan drug lta bur ni don la sgrib par 'gyur la /
NK101(de)004:5900: de bzhin du rtsol ba brgyad kyang 'bras bu la
NK101(de)004:5901: zhen pas gnas lugs phyogs med kyi don las rnam
NK101(de)004:5903: de dag thams cad dgos dbang gi tha snyad du
NK101(de)004:5904: brtags pa tsam ste don la zhe 'dod dang bral
NK101(de)004:5905: ba'i ngang du rgyas gdab pa'i phyag rgya nyid la
NK101(de)004:5908: de yang dgos ched gnyis phyir brdar btags kyi //
NK101(de)004:5909: yin min gcig la yin gsum byung bas //
NK101(de)004:5910: la la gol la gzhan bsgribs 'bras bu 'khyams //
NK101(de)004:5911: brtags pa tsam ste 'dod bral dang rgyas gdab //
NK101(de)004:5913: de'ang ming don dpe gsum gyi tshul shes par bya ste /
NK101(de)004:5915: phyag rgya 'di yi rang bzhin ni //
NK101(de)004:5916: rnam pa gsum du shes par bya //
NK101(de)004:5917: ming dang rang bzhin dpe gsum ste //
NK101(de)004:5918: ming ni phyag rgyar bshad pa yin //
NK101(de)004:5919: rang bzhin 'gyur ba med pa ste //
NK101(de)004:5920: rdo rje'i sems la 'gyur ba med //
NK101(de)004:5921: dpe ni nam mkha' lta bu ste //
NK101(de)004:5922: nam mkha'i dpe la mtshon du med //
NK101(de)004:5924: gsum pa rnam rtog gi spros pa thig les gcad pa ni /
NK101(de)004:5925: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i rang rig pa byang chub sems kyi ngo de bstan pa ste /
NK101(de)004:5928: mi g.yo sems nyid ma 'phros pa //
NK101(de)004:5929: thig le spros bral ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:5930: byang chub sems kyi khyad par che //
NK101(de)004:5933: thig le thig le zhes bya ba //
NK101(de)004:5934: spros pa med pa'i don yin te //
NK101(de)004:5935: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:5937: de la spros pa gcod tshul gyis /
NK101(de)004:5938: gshis dang ngo bo dang yon tan gyi ldog cha nas dbye bas rnam grangs drug tu gsungs te /
NK101(de)004:5939: rgyas par nam mkha' che'i skabs don rnams las 'byung
NK101(de)004:5940: ba ltar so so'i khyad gzhi dang khyad par gyi
NK101(de)004:5941: rang gnad la brten te shes dgos kyang /
NK101(de)004:5944: ma bcos pa las yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:5945: shar tshad don dang bcas te ye nas dag /
NK101(de)004:5946: de mkhyen rang gsal de la phyogs ris grol /
NK101(de)004:5947: ma btsal gdod nas rdzogs pa'i bla dwags yin //
NK101(de)004:5948: gsum gyis gshis bstan gcig gis ngo bo bstan //
NK101(de)004:5949: gnyis kyis yon tan khyad par dam pa bstan //
NK101(de)004:5951: yin min dang zhe 'dod kyi spros pa gcod pa chos nyid kyi thig le dang /
NK101(de)004:5952: re ltos dang chad stong gi spros pa gcod pa dbyings kyi thig le dang /
NK101(de)004:5953: dngos mtshan dang rgyu 'bras kyi spros pa gcod pa dbyings rnam par dag pa'i theg le dang /
NK101(de)004:5954: ma rig pa dang grub matha'i phyogs ris kyi spros
NK101(de)004:5955: pa gcod pa ye shes chen po'i thig le dang
NK101(de)004:5956: / bzang ngan dang blang dor gyi spros pa gcod pa kun tu bzang po'i thig le dang /
NK101(de)004:5957: 'bad rtsol dang skyed sgrub kyi spros pa gcod pa lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le rnams so //
NK101(de)004:5959: spyir chos zhes bya ba ni 'dzin pa'i don te /
NK101(de)004:5960: chos rnams kyi rang dang spyi yi mtshan nyid 'dzin pas chos dang /
NK101(de)004:5961: rnam dkar gyi spyod pas ngan 'gror lhung ba las 'dzin pas chos dang /
NK101(de)004:5962: snang grags myang ris rnams ni rigs pas tha snyad bden pa'i don 'dzin pas chos dang /
NK101(de)004:5963: chos can gyi ngo bos ni khyad par gyi rang rnam 'dzin pas chos zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:5964: chos bzhi po de rnams kyi gnas lugs de kho na nyid ni /
NK101(de)004:5966: mtshan nyid 'dzin zhing ngo bos khyad par 'dzin //
NK101(de)004:5967: snang myong rigs pa'i chos las dkar spyod kyis //
NK101(de)004:5968: ltung ba las 'dzin de dag gnas lugs nyid //
NK101(de)004:5969: rang bzhin spros pa kun bral nyid nges te //
NK101(de)004:5970: de mkhyen mtshan nyid rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK101(de)004:5971: de yi rnam pa thugs rje'i sprul par shar //
NK101(de)004:5972: sgyu ma rtsal 'dzin rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK101(de)004:5973: gdod nas 'du 'bral med par rdzogs pa che //
NK101(de)004:5974: de bzhin mu bzhi mtha' brgyad 'khor 'das chos //
NK101(de)004:5975: cir yang 'char bar mi rigs de yi phyir //
NK101(de)004:5976: chos kyi chos nyid gnas lugs der rigs pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5977: zhes gsungs pa ltar mtshan nyid rang gsal /
NK101(de)004:5979: rang bzhin ngos gzung med pa'i don gyi ngang las mi 'da' bas na /
NK101(de)004:5980: des mtshon pa dngos po'i rkyen du chos nyid ces bya ste /
NK101(de)004:5981: des na mtshan mar 'dzin pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5983: gnas skabs kyi rigs pa bden par 'dzin pa dang /
NK101(de)004:5984: ngo bo chos can dang khyad par gyi chos su
NK101(de)004:5985: 'dzin pa rnams kyi mtshan nyid la yin min dang
NK101(de)004:5986: zhe 'dod kyis dmigs pa dang 'dzin pa'i spros pa
NK101(de)004:5987: thams cad gcod pas thig ler bzhag ste /
NK101(de)004:5988: chos bzhir po rang re'i rang bzhin lhun grub gsum
NK101(de)004:5989: las gzhan du mi 'gyur spros pa ye nas med
NK101(de)004:5990: pas na bzhi po de dag dor ba min gyi
NK101(de)004:5991: rang rang gi ngang tshul gdod nas ma bcos par
NK101(de)004:5992: de de lta bu'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK101(de)004:5993: de skad du'ang 'bras bu'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:5994: rang mtshan ltung ba rigs pas ngo bo yis //
NK101(de)004:5995: khyad par 'dzin pas chos rnams de yi gnas lugs ni //
NK101(de)004:5996: rang gsal lhun grub ngos med las mi 'da' //
NK101(de)004:5997: des mtshon dngos po'i rkyen du chos nyid ces //
NK101(de)004:5998: des na mtshan ma rgyu 'bras gnas skabs rigs //
NK101(de)004:5999: chos can chos kyi 'dod pa'i spros pa gcod //
NK101(de)004:6000: rang re'i rang bzhin mi 'gyur spros pa med /
NK101(de)004:6001: de dag dor min ngang tshul de de lta'o //
NK101(de)004:6004: spros med chos nyid thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:6005: ma bcos pa yi byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6006: rang bzhin gnas pa'i thig ler bshad //
NK101(de)004:6007: byang chub sems kyi che ba yin //
NK101(de)004:6010: de ltar chos thams cad kyi ngang tshul rnam par
NK101(de)004:6011: dag pa'i chos nyid kyi klong chen po de ni
NK101(de)004:6012: sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu'i chos rnams kyis yon tan
NK101(de)004:6013: kun dang de nyid rtogs par byed pa'i thabs sam
NK101(de)004:6014: rnam grangs kyi bstan pa rgya mtsho'i 'byung gnas dang
NK101(de)004:6015: chos kun gyi ngo bor gyur pa'i chos nyid kyi
NK101(de)004:6016: dngos gzhir gnas shing ye nas thams cad sdud pa'i
NK101(de)004:6017: dbyings su rdzogs pas chad pa nyi tshe ba'i spros
NK101(de)004:6019: des na chos nyid kyi ngang de 'khor 'das kyi
NK101(de)004:6020: chos kun 'byed pa dang sdud pa'i rgyu'i ngo bo
NK101(de)004:6021: chos kyi dbyings kyi klong du gsal te stong pa
NK101(de)004:6022: nyi tshe ba'i spros pa thams cad gcod pas thig
NK101(de)004:6023: le chen por ye nas mtha' dbus med par rdzogs
NK101(de)004:6024: pa'o // de skad du'ang 'bras bu'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:6025: de ltar ngang tshul rnam par dag pa nyid /
NK101(de)004:6026: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i 'byung gnas gzhir gnas rdzogs //
NK101(de)004:6027: chad pa nyi tshe'i spros pa'ang 'das pa ste //
NK101(de)004:6028: chos nyid dbyings kyi thig le rdzogs pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6031: spros med dbyings kyi thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:6032: thams cad sdud pa'i byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6033: 'byed par byed pa'i thig ler sdud //
NK101(de)004:6034: byang chub sems kyi che ba yin //
NK101(de)004:6037: de ltar chos nyid kyi ngang du kun gyi 'byung
NK101(de)004:6038: gnas su gyur pa'i chos kyi dbyings nyid gzhir gnas
NK101(de)004:6039: su rdzogs pa de yi tshe nyid na'ang yon tan
NK101(de)004:6040: ji ltar shar zhing de'i dgos pa dang bcas pa
NK101(de)004:6041: gang yang don du 'byung sa dang 'byung tshul dang
NK101(de)004:6042: 'byung ba po'i dbyings zhes bya ba'i phyogs ris dang
NK101(de)004:6043: kun btags thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK101(de)004:6044: nas chos kyi dbyings mtha' dbus dang phyi nang med
NK101(de)004:6045: par ngos bzung mtha' dag dang bral bar rang gi
NK101(de)004:6046: ngang du sel med par dag pas dbyings zhes chad
NK101(de)004:6047: stong gi spros pa gcod pa'i dgos dbang gis btags
NK101(de)004:6048: kyi / rang gi ngo bo ye nas phyogs ris
NK101(de)004:6049: thams cad gnyis med kyi klong du dag par gnas
NK101(de)004:6050: kyi / pas / gzung 'dzin phra rags la sogs
NK101(de)004:6051: pa'i spros pa yod do cog kun rnam par bcad
NK101(de)004:6052: pa'i ngang yin pas dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig
NK101(de)004:6055: de tshe nyid na 'byung sa 'byung tshul 'byung //
NK101(de)004:6056: phyogs ris kun brtags rnam par rang dag pas //
NK101(de)004:6057: dbyings zhes dgos pas btags kyi ye dag pas //
NK101(de)004:6058: spros pa'o cog kyang rnam par bcod pa'i ngang //
NK101(de)004:6061: dbyings nyid rnam dag thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:6062: gzung 'dzin dag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6063: spros pa med pa'i thig ler sdud //
NK101(de)004:6064: byang chub sems kyi che ba yin //
NK101(de)004:6066: 'di gsum gyis gshis kyi gnas tshul gyi ngos nas bstan pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6068: de lta bu'i gshis kyi gnas lugs de dag ma 'dres sgrib med du mkhyen pa ni /
NK101(de)004:6069: rang rig pa'i rang 'od rang gsal du shar ba'i
NK101(de)004:6070: rang byung gi ye shes yin nas nyan thos ltar
NK101(de)004:6071: spang ba dang rang rgyal ltar dgag pa dang /
NK101(de)004:6072: byang sems ltar sbyong ba dang gsang sngags ltar rtsol
NK101(de)004:6073: ba la sogs pa'i spros pa thams cad ye nas
NK101(de)004:6074: yul med rang gsal gyi ngang du grol bas /
NK101(de)004:6075: gshis la phyogs ris med par gnas pa'i don de
NK101(de)004:6076: nyid sgrib g.yogs dang bral bar mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK101(de)004:6077: 'gag pa med pa yin pas rtsol brgyad kyi ye
NK101(de)004:6078: shes las khyad par du gyur pa can du rang
NK101(de)004:6079: shar ba ni / kun gsal ye shes chen po'i thig le yin te /
NK101(de)004:6081: de mkhyen rang rig 'od gsal ye shes pas //
NK101(de)004:6082: spang dgag sbyong rtsol spros pa ye gsal grol //
NK101(de)004:6083: phyogs ris med par mkhyen pas khyad par can //
NK101(de)004:6084: rang shar ye shes chen po'i thig le yin //
NK101(de)004:6087: ye shes chen po'i thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:6088: ma bsgribs pa yi byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6089: 'gag pa med pa'i thig ler sdud //
NK101(de)004:6090: byang chub sems kyi che ba yin //
NK101(de)004:6092: 'dis ni rang byung ye shes kyi ngo bo sgrib
NK101(de)004:6093: med zang thal du gsal ba'i cha nas bstan pa'o
NK101(de)004:6095: de ltar ye shes la phyogs ris med pas dgag
NK101(de)004:6096: sgrub blang dor mtha' dag dang bral te chos thams
NK101(de)004:6097: cad ye nas byang chub kyi sems lhun gnas bde
NK101(de)004:6098: ba chen po yin pas yod pa dngos por 'dod
NK101(de)004:6099: la dang med la stong par 'dod pa dang gnyis
NK101(de)004:6100: dang gnyis med du 'dod pa dang kun yin lhun
NK101(de)004:6101: grub tu 'dod pa dang gang yang min pa ka
NK101(de)004:6102: dag tu 'dod pa la sogs pa mu bzhi mtha'
NK101(de)004:6103: drug gi zhe 'dod kyi spros pa thams cad bcad
NK101(de)004:6104: pas / dbyer med bde ba chen por kun 'dus
NK101(de)004:6105: shing shongs bas mnyam nyid yangs pa chen po'i dgongs
NK101(de)004:6106: klong dam pa ni kun tu bzang po'i thig le
