NK101(de)004:6108: de la phyogs ris dgag sgrub blang dor bral //
NK101(de)004:6109: thams cad ye nas byang sems bde chen pas //
NK101(de)004:6110: yod med yin min 'dod pa'i spros pa bcad //
NK101(de)004:6111: bde chen yangs pa chen po'i thig le'o //
NK101(de)004:6114: spros med kun bzang thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:6115: blang dor med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6116: mnyam pa chen po'i thig ler sdud //
NK101(de)004:6117: byang chub sems kyi che ba yin //
NK101(de)004:6119: 'dis ni ngo bo'i yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6121: de ltar kun mnyam ya ngas pa chen po de
NK101(de)004:6122: yi rol pa'i rgyan du chos thams cad rdzogs te
NK101(de)004:6123: sgyu ma dang chu zla la sogs pa ltar du
NK101(de)004:6124: yul gyi rnam pa kun kyang de'i rol par lhun
NK101(de)004:6125: gyis grub nas rigs kyi khyad par du ma rang
NK101(de)004:6126: shar du gsal ba yin pas /
NK101(de)004:6127: nyan rang ltar spong 'gegs dang byang sems ltar sbyong
NK101(de)004:6128: ba dang sngags phyi pa rnam gsum ltar sgyur ba
NK101(de)004:6129: dang nang pa sde gnyis ltar rtsol sgrub las grol
NK101(de)004:6130: bas cir snang cir srid cir 'gyur kyang rgyu las
NK101(de)004:6131: ma byung rkyen gyis ma bskyed par ye nas lhun
NK101(de)004:6132: gyis grub par gnas te gang du'ang ma g.yos par
NK101(de)004:6133: chos kun lhag ma med par byang chub kyi sems
NK101(de)004:6134: bde ba chen por rdzogs pa'i phyir lhun gyis grub
NK101(de)004:6135: pa'i thig le zhes bya ste /
NK101(de)004:6137: de yi rol pa rgyan rdzogs sgyu ma ltar //
NK101(de)004:6138: rnam pa lhun grub rigs kyi khyad par shar //
NK101(de)004:6139: spong 'gegs sbyong sgyur rtsol sgrub las grol bas //
NK101(de)004:6140: lhun gnas bde chen rdzogs pa'i thig le'o //
NK101(de)004:6143: spros med lhun gnas thig le ni //
NK101(de)004:6144: rtsol sgrub 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6145: ma g.yos pa yi thig ler sdud //
NK101(de)004:6146: byang chub sems kyi che ba yin //
NK101(de)004:6148: 'dis ni gshis kyi yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6149: de ltar thig le drug po yang /
NK101(de)004:6152: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le gsum lta ba dang /
NK101(de)004:6153: ye shes chen po'i thig le dgongs pa dang /
NK101(de)004:6154: kun tu bzang po'i thig le spyod pa dang /
NK101(de)004:6155: lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le rang bzhin bstan pa'i sgo nas bzhag pa yin te /
NK101(de)004:6157: rang rig ye shes thig le drug /
NK101(de)004:6158: lta spyod dgongs pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)004:6160: bzhi pa che ba lngas khyad par dpags te bstan pa ni /
NK101(de)004:6162: cha shas nas gsal bar bya ba'i phyir slar yang bshad na /
NK101(de)004:6164: mngon sum snang ba'i rang bzhin ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6165: de yi mtshan nyid chos dbyings mu mtha' grol //
NK101(de)004:6166: de mkhyen ye shes mtha' dbus kun khyab rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6167: de nyid de yin de mtshon nges pa'i tshig /
NK101(de)004:6168: dgos pas sprad kyi sgra la don mi gzhag /
NK101(de)004:6170: rgyas par nam mkha' che'i mtshan don gyi che ba
NK101(de)004:6171: la brten nas thig le drug dang de dag gi
NK101(de)004:6172: brda gsang dgrol ba'i khog don la sbyar te skabs
NK101(de)004:6173: kyi zab gnad bsdu ba'i mngon rtogs kyi tshul du
NK101(de)004:6174: shes dgos kyang / mdor bsdu na /
NK101(de)004:6176: ma spangs mi gnas mi ltos rag ma las //
NK101(de)004:6177: tha snyad kun dang bral ba'i 'bras bu ste //
NK101(de)004:6178: rang byung lhun grub 'dus ma byas pas na //
NK101(de)004:6179: 'bras bu'i rgyal po khyad par 'phags te che //
NK101(de)004:6180: zhes gsungs pa ltar lnga ste /
NK101(de)004:6181: spang gar yang ma spangs par mngon sum du sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:6182: rag gar yang ma las par bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:6183: gnas ci la yang mi gnas par chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:6184: ltos cir yang mi ltos par de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)004:6185: thams cad nas thams cad du sangs rgyas te tha
NK101(de)004:6186: snyad rang grol du shar bas sangs rgyas med pa'i
NK101(de)004:6192: ji ltar che ba dang ldan pas khyad par 'phags snyam na /
NK101(de)004:6194: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i rang gzhung
NK101(de)004:6195: ni mngon sum par sangs rgyas pas che ba rmad
NK101(de)004:6196: du byung ba dang ldan no //
NK101(de)004:6198: zhen pa drug gis gzhi med la bdag dang rang snang la yul du bzung zhing /
NK101(de)004:6199: mu stegs kyis rtag chad du lta la /
NK101(de)004:6200: nyan thos kyis spong ba dang /
NK101(de)004:6202: byang sems kyis sbyong ba rnams las ches 'phags pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6205: don gcod rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK101(de)004:6207: tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa 'di //
NK101(de)004:6208: gsal stong sprul par ma 'dres gsal //
NK101(de)004:6209: zhes gsungs pa ltar spyir shes bya'i dkyil 'khor thams cad dang /
NK101(de)004:6210: khyad par tshogs brgyad skye ba gsum po yul dang bcas pa nyid mtshan nyid rang rig dang /
NK101(de)004:6212: rnam pa sgyu mar mngon sum du ma 'dres yongs
NK101(de)004:6213: rdzogs su lhun gyis grub par rtogs pas che ba'o
NK101(de)004:6215: de ltar rtogs pa'i ngang der gnas bya gnas byed
NK101(de)004:6216: kyi dmigs pa med par ma gtad par gnas na
NK101(de)004:6217: bag chags thams cad kyi gzhi rten kun gzhi cha
NK101(de)004:6218: dang bcas pa rang grol du shar bas /
NK101(de)004:6219: dngos po dang mtshan ma dang ma rig pa'i mun
NK101(de)004:6220: pa thams cad sangs te ye shes phyogs ris med
NK101(de)004:6221: par rgyas pas yul dang yul can gnyis su med
NK101(de)004:6222: cing mthar 'dzin kun dang bral te mngon gyur du
NK101(de)004:6223: sangs rgyas par lhun gyis gnas pa ni mtshan nyid
NK101(de)004:6224: sde gsum man chad kyi dman pa'i theg pa mtha'
NK101(de)004:6225: dag zil gyis gnon pa'i gnyen por gyur pa yin
NK101(de)004:6226: pas che ba de lta bu dang ldan te /
NK101(de)004:6228: rdzogs chen rang gzung mngon par sangs rgyas che //
NK101(de)004:6229: spong 'gegs sbyor las tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas //
NK101(de)004:6230: rang rig spros bral sgyu mar lhun grub pas //
NK101(de)004:6231: der gnas bag chags rten grol dngos mtshan dang //
NK101(de)004:6232: ma rig mun sangs ye shes phyogs med rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6233: dman pa'i theg pa zil gnon gnyen pos che //
NK101(de)004:6236: gang la mi gnas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)004:6237: mngon sum sa ru ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6241: rdzogs pa chen po ni rag gar yang ma las
NK101(de)004:6242: par bdag nyid chen po thog mtha' med par 'bras
NK101(de)004:6243: bu ye rdzogs kyi rig pa ji bzhin du rtogs
NK101(de)004:6244: pas ma h+aa a tir la bzla ba'i che ba
NK101(de)004:6245: dang ldan no // gang las che na /
NK101(de)004:6246: rnal 'byor chen po la sogs pa lha dang cho
NK101(de)004:6247: ga'i yan lag sogs kyis rtsol sgrub kyi gzhan dbang
NK101(de)004:6248: la ltos shing rag las par 'jug pa'i thabs kyis
NK101(de)004:6249: 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa de nyid zil gyis
NK101(de)004:6250: gnon pa'i gnyen por yang che'o //
NK101(de)004:6252: de ltar mngon sum du sangs rgyas par rtogs pa
NK101(de)004:6253: de nyid bdag nyid chen por rang nyid ye nas
NK101(de)004:6254: dbang thob zin te mtha' dbus med par kun la
NK101(de)004:6255: khyab par mthong bas ches 'phags pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6257: ma h+aa man chad kyi 'og ma'i theg pas tshul
NK101(de)004:6258: ngan pa'i rtsol ba thams cad sangs te rang rig
NK101(de)004:6259: pa'i ye shes phyogs med du rgyas pas ngo bo
NK101(de)004:6260: dus gsum du 'du 'bral med par dgongs pa rtsol
NK101(de)004:6261: bral bde ba chen po'i ngang la rnam rol gyi
NK101(de)004:6262: sgyu 'phrul kun kyang lhun rdzogs su shar bas rang
NK101(de)004:6263: rtsal gyi mnga' dbang du sgyur ba'i che ba dang
NK101(de)004:6265: rnal 'byor chen po la sogs rtsol sgrub kyi //
NK101(de)004:6266: gzhan dbang la ltos zil gnon gnyen por yang //
NK101(de)004:6267: bdag nyid chen por rang nyid ye dbang pas //
NK101(de)004:6268: tshul ngan rtsol sangs rang rig phyogs med rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6272: bdag nyid chen por ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6277: rgyu 'bras kyi phyogs ris ci la yang mi gnas
NK101(de)004:6278: par chos dbyings gdal khyab chen por ye nas dbyings
NK101(de)004:6279: rig ro mnyam du gnas par rtogs pas a nu
NK101(de)004:6280: a tir la bzla ba'i che ba dang ldan no
NK101(de)004:6282: rjes su 'jug pa a nu yo ga pas rgyu
NK101(de)004:6283: ni dag pa'i dbyings dang 'bras bu ye shes chen
NK101(de)004:6284: por bzhed pa la sogs pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi mtshan
NK101(de)004:6285: nyid du 'dod pa'i phyogs thams cad yang dag par
NK101(de)004:6286: gnon pa'i gnyen por yang che'o //
NK101(de)004:6288: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu thams cad ye nas chos kyi
NK101(de)004:6289: dbyings su ro gcig par rtogs te klong yangs ye
NK101(de)004:6290: brdal chen po gting mtha' bral ba'i klong chen du
NK101(de)004:6291: gsal bar mthong bas ches 'phags pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6293: rgyu yis ma bskyed rang gi ngo bos cir yang
NK101(de)004:6294: mi gnas gnyan pos 'gag pa min pas de ltar
NK101(de)004:6295: 'dod pa'i phyogs ris thams cad sangs la /
NK101(de)004:6296: mu matha'i chos kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su mkhyen
NK101(de)004:6297: te rgyu 'bras kyi mtshan ma zil gyis gnon pa'i
NK101(de)004:6298: ye shes sgrib med du rgyas pas chos dbyings rang
NK101(de)004:6299: gsal gyis klong la phyi nang med par mtshan nyid
NK101(de)004:6300: kun grol gyi rig pa phyogs bral bde ba chen
NK101(de)004:6301: po lhun gnas kyi dbyings su 'khyil ba'i che ba
NK101(de)004:6302: dang ldan te / 'bras bu'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:6303: rjes 'jug la sogs rgyu 'bras gnyen por yang //
NK101(de)004:6304: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu chos dbyings ro gcig pas //
NK101(de)004:6305: ma bskyed mi gnas 'gag min de 'dod sangs //
NK101(de)004:6306: kun mkhyen mtshan ma zil gnon ye shes rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6309: mtshan nyid med pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)004:6310: chos kyi dbyings su ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6314: gnyis su dbye ba'i phyogs cha la ltos pa'i mtha'
NK101(de)004:6315: snang kun dang bral te cir snang cir srid cir
NK101(de)004:6316: 'gyur yang gnyis med mnyam nyid yangs par kun rdzogs
NK101(de)004:6317: su rtogs pas yo ga a tir la bzla ba'i
NK101(de)004:6320: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor yo ga phyi pa la sogs
NK101(de)004:6321: pa yin min dang blang dor can du 'dod pa
NK101(de)004:6322: de dag thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i gnyen por
NK101(de)004:6323: yang che'o // gang gis che na /
NK101(de)004:6328: kun rdzob dang don dam la sogs pa gnyis chos
NK101(de)004:6329: thams can ye nas chos nyid de kho na nyid
NK101(de)004:6330: de yin par rtogs pas gnyis med mnyam nyid chen
NK101(de)004:6331: po mkha' ltar phyogs ris med pa kun tu mnyam
NK101(de)004:6334: yin pa blang bar bya ba dang min par dor
NK101(de)004:6335: byar 'dzin pa la sogs pa'i phyogs ris thams cad
NK101(de)004:6336: sangs te gnyis med ye shes mnyam nyid rang gsal
NK101(de)004:6337: du rgyas pas mnyam rdzogs gnyis bral lhun mnyam bde
NK101(de)004:6338: ba chen por kun nas zlum pa'i che ba dang
NK101(de)004:6340: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la sogs blang dor can //
NK101(de)004:6341: zil gnon gnyen por thams cad don yin pas //
NK101(de)004:6342: yin min phyogs sangs mnyam nyid rang gsal rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6345: gnyis su med pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)004:6346: de yin pa ru ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6350: rdzogs pa chen po'i rtogs pa don gyi ngo bo ji bzhin pa'i thog tu phebs pa ni /
NK101(de)004:6351: rin po che 'byung bar byed pa sgra thal 'gyur chen po gsang ba sgra yi rgyud las /
NK101(de)004:6352: de yang gnas lugs chen po las //
NK101(de)004:6353: 'khrul zhes ka nas dag pa las //
NK101(de)004:6354: ma 'khrul nyid du bcos su med //
NK101(de)004:6355: med snang mthong ba med pa'i chos //
NK101(de)004:6356: byas byung rtogs pa rang 'gags so //
NK101(de)004:6357: 'khrul nas dmigs par snang ba min //
NK101(de)004:6358: rang bzhin ye gdangs ma g.yos pas //
NK101(de)004:6359: chos kun mnyam par rog cig go //
NK101(de)004:6360: mi mdzad rtog bral ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6361: bcos shing bsgyur du btub pa min //
NK101(de)004:6362: de yi gnad ni yul yin te //
NK101(de)004:6363: yul dang stong pa rig rtsal mnyam //
NK101(de)004:6364: tha dad rtog pas shes pa min //
NK101(de)004:6366: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos nyid ni //
NK101(de)004:6367: ma byas mi 'byed mnyam pa las //
NK101(de)004:6368: sgra tshig ming du ga la srid //
NK101(de)004:6369: ltos gzhi rang dag 'khrul pa dag /'khor 'das ming du ma grags so //
NK101(de)004:6371: mtha' grol 'gag pa med pa las //
NK101(de)004:6372: yongs su rdzogs pa'i gting gsal gnas //
NK101(de)004:6373: chen po yin pas gong na med //
NK101(de)004:6374: rang bzhin g.yos pa med phyir ro //
NK101(de)004:6375: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar sems nyid klong chen yangs
NK101(de)004:6376: par dbyings snang lhun gyis grub pa'i rang byung gi
NK101(de)004:6377: ye shes mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi ngo bor sangs
NK101(de)004:6378: rgyas pa dang ma rgyas pa'i tha snyad thams cad
NK101(de)004:6379: dang bral te chos kun ye nas skye 'gag dang
NK101(de)004:6380: 'byung 'jug las 'das pa'i ngang du sangs rgyas par
NK101(de)004:6381: rtogs te the tshom dang sgro skur gyi phyogs ris
NK101(de)004:6382: gang yang med par sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa lhun
NK101(de)004:6383: gnas bde ba chen po kun rdzogs sgrib med du
NK101(de)004:6384: gsal bar mngon du gyur pa'i che ba bla na
NK101(de)004:6387: a ti yo ga rang gis rgyud lung man ngag
NK101(de)004:6388: gi don gyi khyad par dang brda tshig gis mtshon
NK101(de)004:6389: tshul rnams la zhen pa dang yid dpyod kyi cha
NK101(de)004:6390: can du shor ba'i 'dzin rtog mtha' dag las ches
NK101(de)004:6392: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems lhun gyis gnas
NK101(de)004:6393: pa'i mtha' bral 'od gsal bde ba chen po don
NK101(de)004:6394: dam pa'i chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes rang
NK101(de)004:6395: gsal du rtogs te de'i ngang la sku dang ye
NK101(de)004:6396: shes ma 'dres gnyis med du mnyam par rdzogs shing
NK101(de)004:6397: rnam pas byang chub kyi snying por nges pas ches
NK101(de)004:6400: rtsol ba dang rgyu 'bras dang blang dor gyi phyogs cha gsum po kun dang /
NK101(de)004:6401: der ma zad a ti'i rgyud lung man ngag gi
NK101(de)004:6402: dmigs rnams kyi tshig don du snang ba'i rigs gsum
NK101(de)004:6403: gyi blo yul dang bsam rtog thams cad ma bcos
NK101(de)004:6404: rang grol gyi ngang du kun nas mnyam par la
NK101(de)004:6405: bzlas pas / blta bya lta byed med par rang
NK101(de)004:6406: rig ye gsal chen po kun bral ji ma spangs
NK101(de)004:6407: par ye nas rdzogs pa chen po rgyal ba'i dgongs
NK101(de)004:6408: pa 'dus ma byas pa mtha' grol 'gag med du
NK101(de)004:6409: yongs su rdzogs par khyad chos drug dang ldan pa'i
NK101(de)004:6411: sngar sangs ma rgyas pa zhig phyis sangs rgya bar
NK101(de)004:6412: byed pa'i bya byed dang phyogs ris thasama cad sangs
NK101(de)004:6413: te dgongs pa phyogs bral bde ba chen po ye
NK101(de)004:6414: shes nam mkha'i mtha' ltar rgyas par gyur pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6415: de yang bla dwags thams cad dang bral ba yin
NK101(de)004:6416: kyang gzhan sel dang don gnyer gyi dgos pa gnyis
NK101(de)004:6417: kyi phyir brdar btags pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:6418: gzhan sel ni sangs rgyas dngos po dang mtshan mar
NK101(de)004:6419: 'dod pa dang nyi tshe ba'i stong par 'dod pa'i
NK101(de)004:6420: phyogs ris las grol ba'i ched du bka' stsal zhing
NK101(de)004:6421: / don gnyer ni 'bras bu'i don gyi rang bzhin
NK101(de)004:6422: 'od gsal gnyug ma'i de kho na nyid la rmongs
NK101(de)004:6423: pa'i blo rigs can la de nyid ji bzhin par
NK101(de)004:6424: mtshon pa'i dgos pa yod pa'i phyir bka' stsal nas
NK101(de)004:6425: brda don sprad pa yin gyi /
NK101(de)004:6426: de yang tshig tu btags pa tsam la nges pa'i
NK101(de)004:6427: don du 'dod pa de zil gyis gnon pa'i gnyen
NK101(de)004:6428: por gyur pas / khyad par gyi che ba sangs
NK101(de)004:6429: rgyas med par bla dwags rang grol gyi dgongs pa
NK101(de)004:6430: phul byung bla med chen po dang ldan pa kho
NK101(de)004:6431: por gyur pas / na'o // de skad du'ang 'bras bu'i klong las /
NK101(de)004:6432: lhun gnas bde chen don dam ye shes 'phags //
NK101(de)004:6433: phyogs gsum la bzlas drang gsal ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6434: dngos mtshan nyi tshe'i stong pa las grol zhing //
NK101(de)004:6435: don nyid rmongs la mtshon phyir brda sprad kyi //
NK101(de)004:6436: de yang tshig tsam nges 'dod zil gnon che'o //
NK101(de)004:6439: gang la'ang ltos pa med pa dang //
NK101(de)004:6440: ci la'ang phan dang gnod pa med //
NK101(de)004:6441: thams cad mnyam pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)004:6442: thams cad nas ni thams cad du //
NK101(de)004:6443: sangs rgyas med pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK101(de)004:6444: sems nyid klong chen yangs pa ru //
NK101(de)004:6446: che ba lnga ru mngon sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)004:6448: de yang dang po mngon sum par sangs rgyas pas shes bya'i don gyi rang bzhin bstan zhing /
NK101(de)004:6449: de nas bdag nyid chen po dang chos kyi dbyings
NK101(de)004:6450: su sangs rgyas pa gnyis kyis gnyis med mtshon bral
NK101(de)004:6452: thams cad de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pa gcig
NK101(de)004:6453: gis dbyer med phyogs grol gyi nges tshig bstan te
NK101(de)004:6454: tha mas sangs rgyas med pa'i che bas de dag
NK101(de)004:6455: gi brda don gyi nges par 'dzin pa mtha' dag
NK101(de)004:6456: dgrol te rgyas gdab pa yin pas /
NK101(de)004:6457: de lta bu'i che ba lngas khyad par du 'phags
NK101(de)004:6458: pa des na mtshan med 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen
NK101(de)004:6459: po ni theg pa kun gyi rtse mor gyur pa'i
NK101(de)004:6460: che ba phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK101(de)004:6461: ldan par shes par bya ste /
NK101(de)004:6463: dang pos shes bya'i rang bzhin gnyis mtshan nyid //
NK101(de)004:6464: gcig gis nges tshig tha mas rgyas btab pa //
NK101(de)004:6465: che lngas khyad 'phags des na rdzogs pa che //
NK101(de)004:6467: de ltar man ngag gi rgyal po rdzogs pa chen
NK101(de)004:6468: po'i rgyud lung man ngag thams cad kyi yang snying
NK101(de)004:6469: bka' lung dri ma med pa 'di ni gnad chen
NK101(de)004:6470: po'i nges gsang gi bcud mchog de lta bu dang
NK101(de)004:6473: bdag ni ma rig gnas nas dbyung ba la //
NK101(de)004:6474: rtogs pa rin chen gdengs med thabs 'ga' yang //
NK101(de)004:6475: rnyed par ma gyur dus bab dbang pos bskul //
NK101(de)004:6476: sku gsum chu rgyun babs pas ma rig pa'i //
NK101(de)004:6477: dri ma dag nas ye shes kun mkhyen gsal //
NK101(de)004:6478: 'khrul pa gzhan mthong snying rjes rtogs thabs bkod //
NK101(de)004:6479: 'di la brten nas thams cad mig rnyed shog /
NK101(de)004:6482: de bzhin rang la gnas pas tshul ngan rtsol min bslad 'khyams las grol phyir /
NK101(de)004:6483: gdengs chen gnas te zhen mtha' kun grol nges par dmar thag kun gsal ba'i /
NK101(de)004:6484: snying po'i don ston sgron ma 'di la skal ldan 'ga' gnas srid na gter du long /
NK101(de)004:6485: de lta min na brgyud pa'i stegs bu tshul gzhan spang min shugs kyis 'jug /
NK101(de)004:6488: 'di ni dngos grub dam pa'i bcud //
NK101(de)004:6490: gdod nas ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK101(de)004:6491: bde gshegs dus gsum rgyal ba yi //
NK101(de)004:6492: thugs dgongs mkhyen pa'i ye shes te //
NK101(de)004:6493: ma nor don la rig pas 'byor //
NK101(de)004:6494: yang rab skyes bu'i spyod yul nyid //
NK101(de)004:6496: mtshungs pa med pa'i gsal mkhyen yin //
NK101(de)004:6497: gdod nas gnas pas bskyed pa med //
NK101(de)004:6498: sgro skur bral ba'i nges don nyid //
NK101(de)004:6499: skal ldan rnams la bzhag pa yin //
NK101(de)004:6503: rgyal ba'i bka' lung zab mo la //
NK101(de)004:6504: brgyud pa'i brda sprod gnyer ldan pas //
NK101(de)004:6505: gzhi don bden par gnas pa yi //
NK101(de)004:6506: yon tan zer mthong nga rgyal la //
NK101(de)004:6507: mthong ba'i dgos pa 'ga' yis rkyen //
NK101(de)004:6508: bya med chos la blo gtad nas //
NK101(de)004:6509: dad ldan skal ldan blo brlabs pas //
NK101(de)004:6510: dngos grub chu rgyun ma bcad par //
NK101(de)004:6511: rin chen brgyud pa mtshon pa'i tshig /'di la brten la tshad la phob //
NK101(de)004:6512: 'di dang bral na skye bo nyid //
NK101(de)004:6514: des na skal ldan rin chen rten //
NK101(de)004:6515: dgos pa phra mor ma spyad par //
NK101(de)004:6516: 'di yis grub pa'i grogs mchog mdzod //
NK101(de)004:6518: de ltar bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i snyan brgyud kyi
NK101(de)004:6519: gdams ngag 'di dang 'phrad pa'i skal ldan blo gros
NK101(de)004:6520: gsal ba rnams kyis shan 'byed kyi gnam thig ma
NK101(de)004:6521: nor ba dang ldan pa'i tshad ma'i lung rigs la
NK101(de)004:6522: brten nas khe nyan ma 'chol bar don gyi gsang
NK101(de)004:6523: bcud len pa la gnas pas ngang pa'i rgyal po'i
NK101(de)004:6524: sgyu rtsal gyi tshul la mkhas par bya ba ni
NK101(de)004:6527: rtsol bral gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK101(de)004:6528: lha gnas gsum du grags gyur nas //
NK101(de)004:6529: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras kyis //
NK101(de)004:6530: 'dzam gling dbus su rgyas par byed //
NK101(de)004:6531: rgyal sras gsang ba'i snod ldan la //
NK101(de)004:6532: rna brgyud rig pa sngags kyi don /
NK101(de)004:6533: 'phrul tshig rig pa'i sgo nas bstan //
NK101(de)004:6534: gsang 'dzin rig pa'i snod ldan rnams //
NK101(de)004:6535: ma bcos gsang ba'i don go nas //
NK101(de)004:6537: de nas gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK101(de)004:6539: de yang gsang ba dam pa 'dis //
NK101(de)004:6540: skal ldan gdul bya'i ngo dag tu //
NK101(de)004:6541: rig pa'i sgron ma byed par 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:6542: de nas thugs rje'i skal med pas //
NK101(de)004:6543: gsang ba dam pa nub par 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:6544: gsang ba'i theg pa dam pa 'di //
NK101(de)004:6545: gzhan gyis nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK101(de)004:6546: dri med bdud rtsi rtogs dka' la //
NK101(de)004:6547: rna brgyud 'phrul tshig mi ldan par //
NK101(de)004:6548: sgra bzhin dpyad nas smra ba dag /
NK101(de)004:6549: lta spyod log pa'i nga rgyal can //
NK101(de)004:6550: ma bcos rang snang rol pa dang //
NK101(de)004:6551: rnam rtog zhen pa'i brtags pa dag /
NK101(de)004:6552: bye brag ma phyed rmongs pa'i blo //
NK101(de)004:6553: rdo la gser du 'dzin pa bzhin //
NK101(de)004:6554: 'od gsal lhun grub rang snang dang //
NK101(de)004:6555: brtags pa'i zhen pa bsres nas smra //
NK101(de)004:6556: ma bcos rig pa'i gdengs med par //
NK101(de)004:6557: rang lta ya rabs mtho 'dod pa //
NK101(de)004:6558: bab col 'dod lnga spyad pas log /
NK101(de)004:6559: de yi dus kyi gang zag dag /
NK101(de)004:6560: sbrel ma g.yang du lhung ba bzhin //
NK101(de)004:6561: rdo rje'i khab tu lhung gyur nas //
NK101(de)004:6562: byang chub sems kyi rigs dang bral //
NK101(de)004:6564: zhes pa la sogs pa bka' lung gi tshig las mthong bas so //
NK101(de)004:6565: des na bdag legs su 'dod pa rnams kyis /
NK101(de)004:6566: byang chub kyi sems nyid ma'i snying po las /
NK101(de)004:6567: kye ho dpal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK101(de)004:6568: mkhas pas don las mi 'khyar bya'i //
NK101(de)004:6569: tha snyad tshig rjes ma 'brang zhig /
NK101(de)004:6570: don med tshig snyan 'brang min gyi //
NK101(de)004:6571: don mtshon tshig la ma dgag cig /
NK101(de)004:6572: rtogs don gnas sam gnas rtogs bya'i /
NK101(de)004:6573: zhi gnas nyams la ma zhen cig /
NK101(de)004:6574: ma rtogs nyams zhen gtad spang gi //
NK101(de)004:6575: dngos grub chu rgyun ma gcad cig /
NK101(de)004:6576: don 'gyur lhag spyod btsun bar bya'i //
NK101(de)004:6577: btsun dregs gzhan brnyad ma byed cig /
NK101(de)004:6578: rang don 'jur bus basngama spang gi //
NK101(de)004:6579: dkar nag rgyu 'bras ma zlog cig /
NK101(de)004:6580: mtha' bzhir phyogs lhung grol bar bya //
NK101(de)004:6581: rtogs thabs mu bzhi ma dag gcig /
NK101(de)004:6582: mu bzhi lde'u mig rang grol bya'i //
NK101(de)004:6584: nges par gdengs su thebs par bya //
NK101(de)004:6585: shes tshul rang bslu ma byed cig /
NK101(de)004:6586: ces gsungs pa ltar dal rten la snying po len
NK101(de)004:6587: pa ni rang gzhan kun la don chen po'i dpal
NK101(de)004:6588: dang ldan pa nor 'khrul med pa'i gdams ngag gi
NK101(de)004:6589: gnad kyis rtogs don la 'jug pa'i bcud 'dus kyi
NK101(de)004:6590: snying po nyid du shes nas zab mo'i don la
NK101(de)004:6591: rton par bya'o // gsum pa zhugs pa rdzogs pa mjug gi don la mdzad byang dang /
NK101(de)004:6594: rin po che gter sogs kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:6595: man ngag 'phrul gyi me long gi rtsa ba rin
NK101(de)004:6596: po che gtad pa mdor bsdus te bstan pa rgyal
NK101(de)004:6597: ba sku gsum gyi byin rlabs las shar ba'i sprul
NK101(de)004:6598: pa'i sku mchog las slar yang thugs rje'i yang sprul
NK101(de)004:6599: du byon pa'i gsang chen bdag po'i thugs sras mtshan
NK101(de)004:6600: dpe rdzogs pa'i slob dpon chen po gsang bdag dga'
NK101(de)004:6601: rab dpa' bo dgyes mdzad bzhad pa rdo rje'i zhal
NK101(de)004:6602: snga nasa bka' stsal bar mdzad pa'i sde gsum klong
NK101(de)004:6603: dgu mtha' dag gi yang bcud thugs kyi dgongs pa'i
NK101(de)004:6604: yang snying du gnas pa'i bstan pa rin po che'i
NK101(de)004:6605: btsas dam pa gdams ngag thams cad kyi rgyal po
NK101(de)004:6607: zhes lhag ma med par mthar phyin pa'i don to //
NK101(de)004:6609: rgya gar gyi sogs kyis bstan te /
NK101(de)004:6610: rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul gyi mkhan po chen po
NK101(de)004:6611: pan+di ta'i rgyal po sh+r+ai seng+ha pra b+ha ta zhes
NK101(de)004:6612: grags pa bod skad du dpal seng ge'i 'od can
NK101(de)004:6613: dang / bod kyi lo ts+aa ba chen po nam
NK101(de)004:6614: mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dge slong bee ro tsa
NK101(de)004:6615: na zhes bya ba sku chung ngu'i dus kyi mtshan
NK101(de)004:6616: ga 'ajaga sdang dam skad gsar bcad du gan jag
NK101(de)004:6617: thang ta zhes grags pa dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK101(de)004:6618: kyi zhal gzigs pas sprul pa'i skyes bu des yul
NK101(de)004:6619: d+ha he na'i 'du khang du bsgyur zhing zhus te
NK101(de)004:6620: gtan la phab nas rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po
NK101(de)004:6621: la bka' 'di gtad pa'i sku drin las /
NK101(de)004:6622: gangs dkar gyi phreng bas yongs su bskor ba'i bde
NK101(de)004:6623: khams dam pa'i chos kyi yul ljongs 'dir yang rgyal
NK101(de)004:6624: bstan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sgron me'i zhing gi bsod
NK101(de)004:6625: nams kyi dpal dang ldan te dge zhing bkra shis
NK101(de)004:6626: pa'i snang bas kun tu khyab par gyur pa'o //
NK101(de)004:6627: de dag gi sgo nas man ngag gi rgyal po
NK101(de)004:6628: gter gtad pa nyid spyi don lnga'i tshul gyis legs
NK101(de)004:6630: de'ang gcig shes kun rtogs kyi skabs la /
NK101(de)004:6631: dam pa snga mas dpe gnyis dang don rdzogs chen spyi la sbyar ba las /
NK101(de)004:6632: g.yu ljang ri khrod kyi rnal 'byor pa grags pa dpal bzang gis /
NK101(de)004:6635: chos rnams rang bzhin mthong 'dod na /
NK101(de)004:6636: sogs kun byed rgyal po la sbyar te bstan kyang /
NK101(de)004:6638: spyir thams cad gal che zhing khyad par du'ang man
NK101(de)004:6639: ngag 'di nyid kun gyi srog bcud du gyur te
NK101(de)004:6640: chos sku'i rang ngo shes shing ye shes kyi rang
NK101(de)004:6641: sa zin nas dgongs pa 'gyur med la gnas pas
NK101(de)004:6642: dwangs ma'i 'byung ba la rten te rang snang sku
NK101(de)004:6643: gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs pa mthar phyin par
NK101(de)004:6644: byed pa'i gdams ngag mtha' dag gi snying po 'dus
NK101(de)004:6645: pa'i man ngag gi rtsa ba bla na med pa
NK101(de)004:6646: yin pas na thams cad sbyar nas 'di skad du
NK101(de)004:6648: rgya mtsho chen po'i chu la 'thungs //
NK101(de)004:6649: ltad mo sna tshogs lta 'dod na //
NK101(de)004:6650: ri bo chen po'i rtse nas ltos //
NK101(de)004:6651: chos rnams thams cad thos 'dod na //
NK101(de)004:6652: rdzogs chen theg pa'i yang rtse nyon //
NK101(de)004:6653: kun gyi rang bzhin mthong 'dod na //
NK101(de)004:6654: byang sems kun byed rgyal po ltos //
NK101(de)004:6655: yongs rdzogs rang gter rnyed 'dod na //
NK101(de)004:6656: gter gtad man ngag bcud mchog long //
NK101(de)004:6659: rmad byung theg mchog rgyal po'i dgongs pa'i mthil //
NK101(de)004:6660: sku gsung thugs bcud tshad ma'i bka' yi lung //
NK101(de)004:6661: snyan rgyud 'phrul tshig man ngag snying po'i don //
NK101(de)004:6662: brgyud pa'i gsung sgros la brten gsal bar bkrol //
NK101(de)004:6663: sngon chad ma byung ba yang 'dir brjod med //
NK101(de)004:6664: sdeb sbyor mkhas pa'ang bdag la yod min te //
NK101(de)004:6665: de phyir gzhan don sems pa'ang bdag la med //
NK101(de)004:6666: rang gi yid la bsgom phyir ngas 'di brtsams //
NK101(de)004:6667: dge ba goms phyir bdag gi dad pa'i shugs //
NK101(de)004:6668: 'di dag gis kyang re zhig 'phel 'gyur la //
NK101(de)004:6669: bdag dang skal ba mnyam pa'i thos bsam pa //
NK101(de)004:6670: gzur gnas gzhan gyis mthong na'ang don yod 'gyur //
NK101(de)004:6671: de slad mchog gzigs dam pa'i skyes bu bzhin //
NK101(de)004:6672: zab don rtogs te rang dbang 'byor min kyang //
NK101(de)004:6673: skyabs mchog pan grub bla ma'i bka' drin gyis /
NK101(de)004:6674: mun pa'i blo la snang ba'i zer tsam shar //
NK101(de)004:6675: khyad par yang sprul thugs sras dpa' bo yis //
NK101(de)004:6676: tshig sdebs legs pas phyi rabs rigs can la //
NK101(de)004:6677: 'phrul gyi yi ge btsas su bzhag pa'i don //
NK101(de)004:6678: cung zad des phyir brgyud pa'i brda yang 'phros //
NK101(de)004:6679: de phyir 'di la legs par bshad pa'i cha //
NK101(de)004:6680: gang mchis dam pa gong ma'i byin rlabs dang //
NK101(de)004:6681: bla ma'i drin phyir rang bzo tshig gcig med //
NK101(de)004:6682: rab dkar legs byas 'byung la the tshom bral //
NK101(de)004:6683: kye lags skal ldan blo gros gsal ba rnams //
NK101(de)004:6684: man ngag gsang bcud 'di 'drar 'phrad dka' bas //
NK101(de)004:6685: mgo la me 'bar gsad las rings tshul du //
NK101(de)004:6686: snying po'i zab don len la 'jug par 'tshal //
NK101(de)004:6687: dus kyi snyigs ma mun gnag bzhin du bdo //
NK101(de)004:6688: tshe la 'gal rkyen rlung gseb mar me 'gran //
NK101(de)004:6689: chos min 'tshe ba char sprin 'khrigs 'dra ba'i //
NK101(de)004:6690: tshul 'dir dgongs la snying po'i don mchog long //
NK101(de)004:6691: bdag kyang deng nas byang chub mchog gi bar //
NK101(de)004:6692: man ngag 'di dang nam yang mi 'bral zhing //
NK101(de)004:6693: chung nas bshes gnyen dam pas rjes bzung sde //
NK101(de)004:6694: rang gter ji bzhin mngon du 'gyur bar shog /
NK101(de)004:6695: a ti yo ga sems klong man ngag sde //
NK101(de)004:6696: spyi ti yang ti'i bka' dang dgongs 'grel gnad //
NK101(de)004:6697: kun bzang rdor sems dga' rab dpa' bo yi //
NK101(de)004:6698: thugs dgongs zab mo ma nor rnyed par shog /
NK101(de)004:6699: theg mchog rgyal po'i bstan don ji lta bar //
NK101(de)004:6700: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i ring lugs tshad ma ltar //
NK101(de)004:6701: dam pa yab sras kun mkhyen snga phyi dang //
NK101(de)004:6702: mi pham chos rje'i dgongs mdzod rtogs par shog /
NK101(de)004:6703: sku gsum rgyal ba'i ye shes sgyu ma'i 'phrul //
NK101(de)004:6704: pan chen bla ma chos kyi rgya mtsho dang //
NK101(de)004:6705: grub brgya'i spyi dpal byams pa chos 'dzin rje'i //
NK101(de)004:6706: dgongs don 'khrul med rgyud la skye bar shog /
NK101(de)004:6707: mdor na snyan rgyud ston pa'i bla ma rnams //
NK101(de)004:6708: 'bral med 'khor lo'i mgon du rang bzhugs nas //
NK101(de)004:6709: mtshan med 'od gsal mtha' bral yongs rdzogs kyi //
NK101(de)004:6710: rang rig gnyug ma'i rang gzhan mthong bar shog /
NK101(de)004:6711: legs gsung bka' la rtogs goms skyed pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:6712: man ngag tshad ma'i lam bzang gsal byas pas /
NK101(de)004:6713: tshe 'dir khyad chos drug ldan gdod ma'i sar //
NK101(de)004:6714: mngon byang chub ste don gnyis lhun grub shog /
NK101(de)004:6715: dge ba de yis 'brel thob yid can kun //
NK101(de)004:6716: rgyal ba dgyes pa'i thabs la nges brten nas //
NK101(de)004:6717: rnam grol rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mgon byas te //
NK101(de)004:6718: khams gsum 'khor ba dong sprugs dpa' thob shog /
NK101(de)004:6719: gzhan yang dkar dmar zab dang sru gos gyon //
NK101(de)004:6720: khal rta zhon pa'i 'gro ba gtsor gyur pa'i //
NK101(de)004:6721: ma lus sems can kun gyi rmongs pa'i yid //
NK101(de)004:6722: bsal nas kun mkhyen ye shes rgyas par shog /
NK101(de)004:6723: rang snang 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i mkhar /
NK101(de)004:6724: lung rtogs bstan pa'i 'od stong gsal bkra bas //
NK101(de)004:6725: bla med 'bras bu'i dpal 'byor rab 'phel te //
NK101(de)004:6726: phyogs dus kun tu dge ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK101(de)004:6727: ces rin po che gter gtad kyi 'grel ba 'di
NK101(de)004:6728: yang skyabs rje bka' drin mtshungs med gdod ma'i mgon
NK101(de)004:6729: po gsang ba'i mnga' bdag grub dbang thams cad mkhyen
NK101(de)004:6730: pa'i bka' yi gnang ba thob cing /
NK101(de)004:6731: chos rje mkhan chen rin po che thub bstan legs
NK101(de)004:6732: bshad dul ba'i sde'i zhal nas sems phyogs la'ang gsal
NK101(de)004:6733: byed kyi yi ge re cis kyang gyis shig ces
NK101(de)004:6734: gsung bskul mdzad pa bzhin rang yang man ngag zab
NK101(de)004:6735: mo la blo gros rgyas pa'i 'brel 'jog tu bri
NK101(de)004:6736: 'dun skyes nas gser khang ri khrod bdud 'dul phrin
NK101(de)004:6737: las kun khyab gling du 'chad thabs lnga'i spyi khog
NK101(de)004:6738: tsam bris shing / de rjes lta bde ba'i phyir
NK101(de)004:6739: rmugs sangs chos dgon mi 'gyur bkra shis 'od 'bar
NK101(de)004:6740: gyi yang dben dgon stod lhun grub dga' tshal gyi
NK101(de)004:6741: mchod sdong byin rlabs 'od snang gi nye 'khor du
NK101(de)004:6742: se ston 'byung ldan gyi phyag mchan la brten nas
NK101(de)004:6743: gzhung dngos tsam nyung ngu zhig bris pa las /
NK101(de)004:6744: slar yang rigs bdag ma h+aa pan+di ta kun mkhyen
NK101(de)004:6745: si tu rin po che'i yang sprul byams chen chos
NK101(de)004:6746: kyi nyi ma'i mdun nas nam mkha' che dang 'di
NK101(de)004:6747: nyid la byin rlabs kyi bka' khrid zhus tshe 'grel
NK101(de)004:6748: pa dgos pa'i zhal lung gser gyi cod pan spyi
NK101(de)004:6749: bor son pa dang snga phyir dam pa 'ga' yis
NK101(de)004:6751: sprang 'khyams thub bstan mkhyen brtse blo gros kyis bro brdung gsang sngags chos gling gi yang bden /
NK101(de)004:6752: g.yu phud brag dkar rtse mtho'i ri dogs /
NK101(de)004:6753: sa 'dzin sman shing 'khrigs pa'i spang mthongs /
NK101(de)004:6754: bkra shis dge legs rgyas pa'i bsti gnas /
NK101(de)004:6755: lha bya skad snyan sgrogs pa'i dga' tshal /
NK101(de)004:6756: gtsugs lag nor bu'i brgyan pa'i khang bzang /
NK101(de)004:6757: theg mchog 'od gsal mdzod kyi bshags chung du bar
NK101(de)004:6758: mtshams su ji ltar rigs pa bsnan cing mjug gi
NK101(de)004:6759: skabs don man chad rdzogs par byas te mthar phyin
NK101(de)004:6760: par bgyis pa 'dis kyang rgyal bstan spyi dang snga
NK101(de)004:6761: 'gyur mdo sgyu sems gsum 'od gsal rdo rje snying
NK101(de)004:6762: po dang bcas pa'i bstan pa rin po che rnams
NK101(de)004:6763: phyogs dus gnas skabs kun tu dar zhing rgyas la
NK101(de)004:6764: yun ring du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur cig //
NK101(de)004:6765: sarba d+aa k+aa l+y+aa n+aam b+ha ba tu /
NK101(de)004:6767: ye grol ka dag zang thal kun tu bzang //
NK101(de)004:6768: yongs grol gnyug ma rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK101(de)004:6769: lhun grub rol rtsal ma 'gags dga' rab rje //
NK101(de)004:6770: dbyer med rig stong don gyi bla mar 'dud //
NK101(de)004:6771: dgos 'dod nor bu rgya mtsho'i klong bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:6772: sems kyi rin chen rdo rje'i gter chen po //
NK101(de)004:6773: kun bzang rdor sems dga' rab thugs kyi btud //
NK101(de)004:6774: sh+r+ai seng+hasa chings lnga'i brda yis bkrol //
NK101(de)004:6775: dpe don rtags kyi spras pa'i man ngag rnams //
NK101(de)004:6776: dgongs brgyud phar zog thob pa'i skal ldan pa //
NK101(de)004:6777: shar grol ris med rang byung brdas bstan pa //
NK101(de)004:6778: kun la yod kyang kun gyi spyod yul min //
NK101(de)004:6779: rang sbas gab pa gsang ba'i don 'chol na //
NK101(de)004:6780: ma grol grol ba'i gnad gsang rtogs daka'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:6781: 'phrul gyi me long gsal ba'i lde mig 'di //
NK101(de)004:6782: pan grub brgyud pa'i lung rigs man ngag bzhin //
NK101(de)004:6783: dga' rab zhal mthong gnyug ma'i de nyid mkhyen //
NK101(de)004:6784: rtsol med brtse ba'i kho lag ras rgyas shing //
NK101(de)004:6785: gzi ldan blo gros nyi ma'i rang rtsal gyis //
NK101(de)004:6786: rang bzhag klong nas rang grol tshig gis bkrol //
NK101(de)004:6787: rgyud kyi don bkrol lung gi mdo bzung nas //
NK101(de)004:6788: man ngag snying byung dgongs pa'i la bzla ba //
NK101(de)004:6789: gnas lugs don bstan rig pa gnad pa phab //
NK101(de)004:6790: tshig gi brda bkrol byang sems mngon du bstan //
NK101(de)004:6791: skyes bu'i lus la gces pa'i srog bzhin du //
NK101(de)004:6792: sde gsum klong dgu'i gnad ston gzhung lugs 'di //
NK101(de)004:6793: mi nyams phyogs dus kun tu spel ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)004:6794: s+aur+ya'i mtshan can bla mas spar du bzhengs //
NK101(de)004:6795: dbul po'i gter dang sems nyid sangs rgyas rnams //
NK101(de)004:6796: ye nas gnas kyang ma shes log par 'khyams //
NK101(de)004:6797: deng 'dir 'di'i mthus rang gnas gnyug ma'i khams //
NK101(de)004:6798: ye grol chos zad kun khyab thig le che //
NK101(de)004:6799: gzi byin nyi ma 'bum las ches lhag pa //
NK101(de)004:6800: 'gro ba'i yid mkhar rab tu brtan gyur nas //
NK101(de)004:6801: sa 'dzin spo la dge legs gru char gyis //
NK101(de)004:6802: pad dkar chun 'phyangs kun gnas bltar gyur cig /
NK101(de)004:6803: ces spar 'di rmugs sangs gsang sngags gling du bzhugs
NK101(de)004:6804: pa yul phyogs thams cad du dge zhing bkra shis
